Comment: Began smartly, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly, scored by 3 lengths.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Reared at start and lost ground, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, bumped near 900M, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, stayed on for 4th.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.

Jumped well from gate 9, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, sent forward after passing 1200M, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, bumped near 900M, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, pace good, made steady ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 2-4 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 150M weakened.
At back, pace good, held up 4-2, made ground when clear.
Eased to sit just off the front runners, 2 wide, pace good, hampered 300m, weakened afterwards.
Eased to sit in midfield, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Never improved at rear.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, emptied 300M.
Ridden along to take lead near 800M, ran on strongly in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Raced outside the lead, continued to make ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Travelled midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, gradually gained ground in the straight, finished well.
Urged along after start, raced in handy position on rail, fought hard in the straight, worked home OK.
Fractious in barrier, taken back at start, raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, made some ground in the straight, stalls test.
Jumped well, raced in front of midfield, tried hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Slow to begin, settled midfield on rail, kept on rail to save ground rounding the Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Began only fairly then was crowded for room, raced at tail, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Settled midfield, raced wide and without cover passing 1000M, gave ground passing 300M.
Raced behind the leaders, weakened badly passing 300M, lame left hind next day.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight, failed to run on.

Wasn't the fastest away but gathered early speed & positioned one pair behind leaders on the outside. Raced keenly near the 650m. Moved three horses wide just prior to straightening before sprinting well in final section.

Was one of the slowest into stride and was ridden up in first section to be second from last between runners. Was 5 lengths from lead on cornering before moving out second widest at the 350m and finishing strongly last 300m.

No early pace and settled in midfield early before drifting back to third from last at 800m. Inconvenienced at the 650m. 5 lengths from lead on cornering & stayed close to the rail before making some ground in final section.
Jumped well and showed good early speed to get lead before shifting across to the rail at the 950m. Headed at the 350m but tried hard in final 300m.
Was only fairly away before gathering speed to position on leaders back in first section. Moved away from the fence shortly after straightening but was one paced in final section.

Was ridden forward into midfield but raced three wide with cover in middle section. Was 3.5 lengths from lead on cornering & moved wider in the straight before racing greenly & not finishing off as strongly as expected.
Was ridden hard from wide barrier before shifting across to be outside the leader at the 900m. Was hard ridden from 400m to challenge but offered little response and weakened last section.
Began well but didn't have early speed of others & settled in midfield on the fence. Was 3 lengths from the lead on cornering & improved between runners shortly after before weakening last 200m.

Began well, eased across into midfield one horse from rail. Raced keenly near 650m & steadied away from heels. 3 lengths from lead on corner. Inconvenienced at 150m but didn't respond thereafter. Blood in trachea post-race.

One of the slowest into stride & settled back in the field. Raced three horses wide with cover in middle section. Moved out wider at the 550m. 5 lengths from lead when cornering as the widest runner but didn't threaten.
Had no early speed and was hard ridden but was 6 lengths behind second last horse at the 800m. Conceded substantial margin on cornering and managed to pass one in the final section.
Began very well and was allowed to stride across but was posted three horses wide without cover in middle section. Continued to race wide until cornering and weakened out in final section.
Began well from gate 12, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield, closer on turn, took the lead near 300M, kept on well thereafter to score by a neck.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground throughout, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Stumbled shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/4L, travelled well to turn, challenged by rivals from 550M, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Restrained at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on rail, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in the box-seat, gradually pulled away to score from 200M without pressured, very impressive.
Taken back and raced at the rear, along the rail, ran home strongly from 150M but was still no match.
Hard ridden and settled in front of midfield, stayed 2 wide, kept on well to the line.
Settled in about midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on fairly.
Raced in just behind midfield, 2 wide throughout, continued on fairly to the line.
In midfield along the rail, in touch with the challengers until 150M, no extra thereafter.
Settled to race close to the tail, 3 wide but with cover, made ground steadily on the outside track.
Crowded at start and raced at the rear, 2 wide, continued to make ground until late.
Taken back to be at rear, wide and without cover, only past tired runners.
Settled to be in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, run ended when crowded at 350M.
Hard ridden forward and settled outside the lead, no more fuel at 300M.
Urged to forward to lead, emptied at 300M.

Slightly slow out, soon recovered to forward of midfield in 6th, continued progress to 2L back in 5th rounding home bend, gained upper hand under pressure inside the final 50 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Recovered quickly from a moderate start to soon lead, obtained rails run passing the 1000 metres, led the field most of the way until collared close to home.
Prominent early, settled worse than midfield, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend, steadied entering straight, responded well under pressure inside the final 250 metres.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, virtually last into the straight, made significant progress down the inside between runners, nearest at finish.
Soon dropped towards the rear on the rail, commenced move approaching the home turn, inconvenienced early in straight, finished off race nicely.
Jumped well settling in rear of midfield in 8th on the rail, saved ground on inside turning in, did not find much room early in straight, fought on nicely to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace, joined the lead after straightening, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden early, settled just off the pace on the rail, baulked for a run most of the way in straight and not tested.
Began well from the widest gate, settled wide in midfield, shifted slightly backward nearer the rail rounding home bend, kept on same pace without threatening.
Awkward start, ridden along 3-wide in first few, inconvenienced and dropped slightly backward to 6th coming onto home bend, weakened into home straight.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, travelled 3-wide without cover within 1L of pace around home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, tailed-off throughout. (Questioned for disappointing performance, jockey stated stiff fores.)
Travelled smoothly in midfield, about 4Ls to make up on leader leaving the turn, quickened up impressively and hit the line nearing 50M, won going away. (Blood in trachea.)
Went forward, established clear lead before the turn, harassed by rival 600M, kept on well and kicked away mid-straight but no chance with impressive winner final 100M.
From draw 1 scrubbed along after the start, chased leaders along the rail, stayed on moderately passing 400M, no match with first 2.
Jumped on terms and settled midfield in 6th, 4Ls to make up 400M, kept on steadily but not pace to challenge leaders.
Settled 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, just battled away in the straight, out of contention passing 200M.
Pressed forward to be chasing the pace in 2nd, moved up to be alongside leader 600M, tried to stay on early straight, no extra and weakened final 150M.
Restrained after the jump, ended up in last, raced keenly early stages and again from 600M, stayed on fairly in the straight passing tired runners only.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls off the pace, couldn't make any headway in the straight, never involved.
Held up behind midfield, taken keen hold middle stages, couldn't quicken passing 400M, no impression. (Jockey : uncomfortable action, lay out badly making the turn.)
Crowded for room on jumping, went back to the rear, 10th on turn, never got going leaving the bend.

Restrained to race near the rear, bumped 600M and forced wide, couldn't go on and eased down in straight. Unacceptable performance. (Jockey : unbalanced when bumped 600M, didn't respond to riding after.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, hampered near 1000M, improved from 550M, finished off well to score with some in hand.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield early, found a 2- wide spot near 1000M, 2 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, hampered near 1000M, 2 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, unable to obtain clear running after straightening, made some progress when clear final 100M.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a tricky draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, led by 3/4L at 400M, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Hampered at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, sat 1-1/2L behind thereafter, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Steadied off heels shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, improved from 650M, taken wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, hampered near 1000M, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, improved from 500M, hit the front early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, headed near 300M, kept on evenly thereafter to take 3rd. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with field, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, travelled keenly after passing 1200M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, in traffic early in straight, finished off one-pace when clear thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, passed a few tired rivals in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, weakened gradually from 300M.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, Inconvenienced early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to may any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.

Began well & showed speed positioning third off the fence. Obtained cover at 900m. 2 lengths from lead on corner. Moved out & bumped another runner on straightening. Joined lead at 250m after sprinting hard & went on for easy win.

Had soft run in midfield on the fence. Over raced slightly in middle section due to slow pace. Moved away from the fence on cornering before improving between runners and finishing well in final section.

Began well from out wide and worked across the front of the field before crossing outside the leader at the 900m. Cornered well and looked prominent in lead before being headed by winner at 300m. Fought on well last 250m.

Came across from wide barrier to be one off the fence before moving three wide near the 800m & improving around outside. Was 3 lengths from lead on cornering. Was hampered shortly after straightening and ran home evenly.
Began very fast and assumed lead before crossing to the fence after 250m. Was the first horse to corner before being joined at the 250m and tiring over the last 100m.

Began well to be just behind leading group. Travelled keenly & raced close to heels in middle section before becoming unbalanced and checking away from heels at the 600m. Bumped at the 350m before getting home evenly.
Began fairly before ridden into midfield. Improved into tight running at the 600m before being checked back. Conceded 5 lengths on cornering and only battled in final section.
Began well from inside barrier before settling on leaders back after 250m. Travelled strongly in middle stages and despite racing in restricted room near the 350m, failed to run on in final 300m.

Was the last into stride before making up some ground to position just worse than midfield between runners. Moved out 3 horses wide approaching the 600m. Was around 5l from lead on cornering and didn't catch eye last 300m.

Hampered on jumping before easing back behind runners. Was in last position in middle stages between runners. Was steadied near the 600m. Had clear running in the straight but couldn't make up ground in slow run race.

Jumped well but was eased back from wide barrier. Continued to ease until settling near the tail of the field, three horses away from rail. Was a clear last on cornering and was never likely from that position.

Was away fairly but ridden for speed, coming across from out wide. Left three wide without cover from the 1000m. Moved up to be 1.5L from the lead before being bumped heavily & unbalanced at the 425m & tiring out from 350m.

Began moderately before moving across to be worse than midfield three wide with cover in middle stages. Continued to race wide before shifting 4 wide at the 600m. Was the widest runner on turning and weakened out late.

Had no early speed & settled at the rear of the field close to the fence. Was still well back at the 600m before being checked & ease. Was again eased on cornering & was never competitive from rearward position.

Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 3 wide, 1-1/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, missed 2nd on line.
Crowded out start, taken back to race at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 300M, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 to 4 wide with cover in midfield, raced tight near 700M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Shifted in at start and made contact, unable to slot in, raced very wide at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Settled in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, blocked 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to the line, just missed by a narrow margin.
Slow away, at back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
At rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
In front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Box seat, harmed by the fast pace, led 300M, out of fuel 100M.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, suited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 200M, checked 100M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, suited by the fast pace, no progress, on heels 150M.
At rear, held up whole straight, not tested.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, emptied 200M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Settled at tail, always niggled, near 200M shifted in away from heels and became unbalanced, quickened when obtained clear run, worked home strongly to score.
Raced behind leaders in middle of track, asked for effort passing 600M, made up nice ground passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, settled behind leaders on outside rail, near 300M was steadied then was badly held up for running until near 100M, gained ground passing 100M.
Jumped nicely, settled outside the lead on rail, limited response when under pressure, failed to make impression.
Travelled behind leaders, commenced to improve passing 500M, fought hard but gave ground in final 50M, bled.
Urged along to take lead on one-off to outside rail, gave ground passing 100M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover from 700M, same margin back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter.
Stumbled at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Got head up on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar positon on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, lay out on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, closer on turn, bumped near 400M, finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin.

Stumbled at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to take 3rd.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 200M to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, closed off well when clear thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead from near 900M, hard ridden after turning in, headed near 150M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped early in straight, finished off evenly.
Began fairly from a middle draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward on the first turn, took the lead 1200M, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, a length or so back, similar positon on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 2 wide, made steady ground and ran on nicely for the win.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 2 wide, battled on but was bumped at 150M and close to the line again. (See Incident Report)
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, fought on gamely only to be headed by the first two inside final 50M.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield along the rail, ran on well to the finishing line.
Awkward start and failed to muster, in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, improved steadily until bumping a runner prior going to the line.
Jumped well, took box-seat with ease, battled on until couldn't find extra to keep up over final 150M.
Asked to go forward, shared lead on rail, continued on until weakened and headed at 150M.
Hard ridden, settled towards the rear along the rail, never had daylight in the straight, not properly tested.
In just behind midfield, along the rail, badly held up at 350M, kept on to the line thereafter.
Failed to muster before settling just behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, bumped at 450M, did not improve.
Bumped start, in worse than midfield, 2 wide, caught heels when shifted out at 450M, run ended thereafter.
Asked and settled in one-off one-back position, kept on till approaching 300M.
Sent forward, travelled keenly in lead, weakened at 350M. (See Incident Report)
Prominent but wide, gave ground from 600M. Finished tailed out, must trial.
Moderate start from the widest gate, soon ridden to lead obtaining rails runs shortly after, kicked about 2L clear after straightening, held on well to the line.
Settled just worse than midfield, switched out for a run inside final 300 metres, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, trailed the field to home straight, switched out for a run 300 metres out, finished off the race well.
Broke well, gradually drifted backward to midfield while travelling wide on the far side, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Moderate start, travelled not far off the pace but wide without cover to home straight, gained 2L 2nd shortly after straightening but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled wide in last few, produced good late impression inside the final 300 metres.
Settled within 3L of pace most of the way to home straight, kept on steadily without quickening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began well, settled just off the pace on the rail, came under pressure upon straightening, faded gradually. (Tactic questioned)
Never better than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Ridden early, prominent to 300 metres, folded up quickly. (Lame)
Taken back from draw 14, settled towards the rear 3-wide 7Ls off the pace, wide into straight, quickened up strongly and rounded them up 150M from home. Comfortably.

Restrained in midfield early stages, wide no cover from 1100M strode closer to be 4th chasing the leaders, ran on well in the straight, no match with winner final 150M but kept battling to hold 2nd in a bob.
Held up in mid-division along the 2-path, stayed on well over final 400M but not pace of winner final 150M, just missed 2nd in a bob.
Reserved in mid-pack, 5-6Ls off the pace middle stages, peeled out 4-wide from 550M, chased steadily final 400M but always held by leaders.
Eased back to race in last, bustled along 700M, widest into straight, stayed on well without threatening leaders.
Rolled forward from wide draw, unable to obtain cover and ended up leading the field, set good pace to straight, fought on until headed 150M, no extra late. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Settled ahead of midfield and always in touch behind leaders, went 2nd 300M, outpaced by pursuing rivals final 200M.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, settled midfield in 8th spot, saved ground along the inside, fought on same pace in straight and failed to make appreciable ground.
Began awkwardly, held up behind midfield 7Ls off the good pace, awkwardly placed for some distance passing 500M but gave limited response only when asked.
Settled 3-wide behind midfield, 6-7Ls off the good pace middle stages, switched wider 550M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Jumped evenly, moved up to chase leader in a race run at consistent good tempo, held ground early straight, run ended 200M and weakened towards the line.
Scrubbed along to be chasing the leader, came under pressure 600M from home, out of contention early straight, eased final 150M when no chance.
Taken back from wide draw, held up near last 8Ls off the good pace, failed to respond to the riding entering straight. Never factored.
Steadied after the jump and taken across to the fence, settled 7Ls back near the rear, didn't finish it off passing 400M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 550M, finished off well to score comfortably.

Jumped well from a wide draw, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1200M, raced 2 wide in 2nd on turn, took the lead early in straight, headed after passing 200M, kept on evenly thereafter to take 2nd.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd despite some inconvenience near 100m.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, improved from 550M, made good progress in straight to make frame. (Minor laceration to the left front coronet.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, checked off heels near 450M, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1200M, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, improved from 600M, bumped near 550M, kept on well early in straight, weakened from 200M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased after passing 150M. (Lost right front plate near 750M.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a tricky draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, got cover on turn, unbalanced near 550M, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 650M, angled out near 600M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced in midfield, difficult to settle early, 3 lengths back on turn, angled out near 550M, raced tight early in straight, failed to quicken under pressure thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 700M, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 550M, made some headway in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, difficult to settle early, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, angled out near 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, closer to lead when pace slackened rounding home bend, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back, 2 wide from 600M, no clear running in straight, not able to be fully tested.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the challengers late.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, hard ridden from 450M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still 7 to 8 lengths behind, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, steadied off heels near 150M, one-paced thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide on turn, one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, allowed rival to cross near 1300M, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader thereafter, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly in the middle stages, shared lead turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1250M, led by 1/2L to turn, shared lead with rival on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Hard ridden to share the lead on the fence at good pace, hung on well to score.
Very slow away, took rail at back, pace good, progressed steadily 200M for 2nd.
Bumped start, pushed to obtain a midfield spot, pace good, made steady ground 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead at good pace, ran on well until 100M run ended.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, pace good, moved around the field 3-6 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up at back, 3 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
At rear along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Bumped start, at back, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden but failed to cross, trapped 4 wide in front of midfield, weakened quickly 400M.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped very wide, then moved forward, 3 wide in the lead, faded 300M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, emptied 400M.
Raced at rear on rail, kept on rail rounding Home Turn, quickened passing 200 after obtaining clear run, scored unchallenged.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 400M, continued to make ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled midfield, fought hard in the straight, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along to take lead near 600M, responded nicely in the straight, worked home well.
Urged to race behind the lead on rail, placed pressure passing 400M, gave ground passing 100M.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 450M, one-paced.
Travelled midfield, near 700M was left racing wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, passing 300M shifted in when disappointed for running, then near 250M shifted out away from heels, worked home OK.
Raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Urged along to race in front of midfield on rail, came under pressure near 150M, failed to run on.
Travelled wide and without cover in 4 wide position, widest on straightening, gave ground in the straight.
Ridden along then settled in handy position, weakened badly near 200M.
Began well and showed good early speed to assume lead after 100m. Travelled well in front before setting up a 2L margin before cornering. Sprinted hard after balancing to score well.
Began fairly before improving quickly to position just behind leading pair at the 800m. Followed leader and was not far away on cornering before making late closing ground over the final 150m.

Eased back & across behind runners and was ridden up in middle sections to maintain position around 6 lengths from lead at the 400m mark. Moved out wider on straightening and made some late ground without threatening winner.

Was away well but didn't have the early speed of others and settled in midfield around 3 lengths from lead on the rail. Stayed close to the rail on cornering and tried hard in the final section and wasn't beaten far.

Shifted and bumped at the start and subsequently ridden up to hold midfield position in early stages. Was 4L from lead in cornering and was only even in the run to the line. Sustained over reach wound to front right leg.

Was away well but could not cross speed inside & subsequently eased after 150m. Raced wide for first 300m before getting behind leading pair at the 650m. Moved 3W on cornering but never sprinted quick enough to threaten.

Began fast but was not bustled, eased across from wide barrier to be in midfield around 4.5L from lead at the 600m. Moved out wider approaching the corner and turned as the widest runner before getting home evenly late.

Began fast but was eased across into midfield from wide barrier before racing wide and without cover for the majority. Was 4L from lead approaching the bend before cornering wide and weakening out late.

Away only fairly but was hard ridden for first 100m before positioning outside the leader after 200m. Was under pressure on cornering after leader kicked away before weakening noticeably in the final section.

Began awkwardly with rider losing his iron and consequently being some 8 lengths from the lead at the 800m. Continued to concede a considerable margin in middle stages and was never likely after bombing start.
Stood flat-footed as the start and lost a considerable amount of ground. Was in excess of 10+ lengths last throughout the race and maintained that margin in the run to the line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by a narrow margin.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide after passing 800M, improved from 450M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after passing 800M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Jumped with field, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 800M, 3 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off one-pace in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, difficult to settle early, moved closer after passing 700M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried wider near 700M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Niggled along and took up the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L behind, battled on nicely to score by 3/4L.
Taken back and trailed at the rear, always on rail, shifted widest in the straight, made nice ground and closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 3L behind along the rail, ran on well but just caught by 2nd on the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led by about 1L, one paced and headed approaching 100M.
Raced close to the tail, 5-1/4L behind and shifted 3 wide after 800M, made ground all the way to the line.
Lost ground when crowded shortly after the start, in behind midfield, 4L off and shifted 3 wide prior to 600M turn, made ground steadily in the straight.
Asked and raced in one-off one-back position, about 2-1/2L off, stayed one paced.
Bumped start, settled in about midfield along the rail, no daylight until 200M, ran on thereafter.
Crowded shortly after the start, improved gradually to sit outside the lead, emptied near 150M.
Crowded shortly after the start, settled midfield but wide all the way, never ran on and eased down at 150M. (See Incident Report)
Travelled 3-wide in midfield around first bend, settled 2-wide in back straight, saved ground on inside turning for home, ran on well to assert authority near the finish.
Settled in rear, gained slightly closer coming onto home bend, widest runner entering home straight, ran on to hit the front briefly inside the final 100 metres.
Soon took up running from a wide draw, obtained rails run passing winning post the first time, led the field until swamped inside the final 50 metres.

Travelled prominently and wide without cover around first bend, improved steadily from 2L 4th to join the leaders 3-wide 600 metres out, fought on steadily to hold some chance 200 metres out, soon swamped.
Travelled wide towards the rear on first bend, took closer order to wide in midfield down back straight, shaken up entering home straight, ran on under pressure to narrowly miss a placing.
Settled just behind the leader on the rail, tight for a run over 200 metres out, kept on same pace without quickening in closing stages.
Broke well, settled within 3L of pace in 5th, came under pressure entering home straight, found nothing.
Crowded at start, always in last few, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Broke well, soon taken back to last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, made no impression.
Broke well, close up to home straight, folded up quickly.
Soon taken well back, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran past one beaten horse closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in midfield on the rail, given reminders to maintain position leaving the Rock, soon weakened. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Chased leaders in 3rd, travelled keenly early and middle stages, quickened up smoothly to lead inside 200M, kept on well to notch his 4th win, always in control final stages.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off leaders in 6th, peeled out 350M to challenge, chased solidly and made it to 2nd near the line, couldn't get to the winner.
Held up midfield along the fence, made steady headway passing 400M, tried hard but couldn't reel in the winner.
Settled in 4th, within striking distance always, battled on evenly in the straight, not finishing pace of first 3 final stages.
Dropped back to the rear from draw 11, 9Ls off leaders home turn, closed fastest in straight, made up good ground to go 5th near the line.
Always in touch 3Ls off the leaders in a race run in good tempo, kept on steadily in the straight, held ground final 200M.
Bustled along after the jump, vied lead on outside, flat from 200M, soon swamped by rivals.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, 5Ls to make up top of straight, ran on mildly before encountering traffic problems final 50M, not ridden out to the line.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear 7Ls back, made limited progress turning home, never a threat.
From wide draw soon taken across behind runners, settled near last, crept closer making the home turn but couldn't sustain run passing 200M. (Bled.)
Eased back to race in the rear 8Ls off the pace, found nothing when asked in the straight. Never involved.
Began well to be vying for the lead on inside, emptied nearing 200M, weakened rapidly to last.

Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly despite bumped near 250M, scored by 3/4L.
Began fairly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed and weakened after passing 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame.
Commenced well, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide from near 850M, 1-1/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, bumped near 250M, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, travelled keenly near 850M, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide in midfield early, couldn't maintain position on turn, dropped to last turning in, showed nothing in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final furlong.
Pushed to keep up in midfield early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 1400M to sit outside the lead to take advantages of the slow tempo, ran on well to score.
Pushed to take a midfield sport early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 1400M to track the leaders, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M weakened.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Very slow away, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, emptied 300M.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
Trapped wide, never better than midfield.
Never a factor.
Fast out, urged to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Settled in handy position, continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home solidly, just missed by a neck.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield on rail, niggled passing 600M, quickened passing 200M, made up nice late ground.
Ridden along to race behind leader, fought hard entire straight, worked home one-paced.
Took lead with nice early speed, tried to improve passing 400M, gave ground passing 150M.
Ridden along after start, travelled in front of midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Slow out and then was crowded for room, raced at tail, wide on straightening, one-paced.
At the start bumped a runner and became badly unbalanced, raced at back, still green, failed to respond and finished disappointing.
Shortly after the start stumbled, raced at back, near 600M was taken wider, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced greenly, settled midfield, no response.
Travelled midfield, near 900M was left racing wide and without cover, failed to run on.
Raced midfield on rail, weakened badly near 200M.
Began well and settled in midfield on rail. Was 3.5L from lead and staying close to fence on cornering. Raced tight when improving along rail at 200m, before snatching lead in final 25m to score.

Was hard ridden for first 200m before eventually getting across to the fence & the lead at the 900m. Was challenged for lead from 800m. Kicked strongly & shook off challengers at 300m before being caught late on the line.

Was the last horse into stride before making ground quickly to settle worse than midfield one horse away from rail. 5 lengths from the lead & made the turn the widest runner before getting home strongly from rearward position.
Began fairly and ridden up for 150m before settling in midfield on the outside. Moved three wide at the 600m. Was 4L from lead on cornering before battling on well in the final section.

Began well and showed good speed to come across from wide barrier before racing three horses wide without cover 1L from lead. Was still prominent until the 200m before getting tired late after covering ground on good speed.
Hard ridden early before coming across to position outside the leader after 250m. Challenged for lead approaching the 800m. Continued to challenge for lead until tiring out over the final 250m.
Wasn't fast to begin and settled around midfield on the rail. Was around 5L from lead on cornering before coming around heels at the 150m but only slightly reducing that margin in final section.

Jumped fairly but gathered speed to go forward before settling in good position behind leaders. Moved three wide at the 500m when only 2.5L from lead but never threatened to join lead in final section and got tired last 150m.

Showed good natural speed before being crossed after 300m and travelling on leaders back from that point. Moved away from fence on cornering and had clear running but was under pressure before weakening out in final section.
Bumped at the start before being eased back behind runners settling at the tail. Was around 9 lengths from the lead on cornering and passed a few in the straight but was never likely.
Was eased across after the start before settling with only one pair behind after 300m. Was around 7 lengths from lead approaching the corner and never threatened in the straight.
Had no early speed and settled in second last pair on the rail. Was always well back in middle sections and was under pressure a fair way.

Shifted in and became unbalanced at the start before easing back behind runners to settle at the tail on the fence. Conceded a huge margin approaching the corner and never made any ground in final section.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1000M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, easy run on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.

Bumped on jumping, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, showed good progress early in straight, blocked near 250M then awkwardly placed near 150M, made some progress thereafter to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, made some headway in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight despite inconvenienced near 200M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the early lead, 2 wide, headed near 950M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from near 1000M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Commenced well from the widest draw, race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, bumped near 1200M, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, brushed after passing 400M, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, severely checked after passing 200M. eased thereafter.
Inconvenienced start, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, difficult to settle and bumped early, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
In midfield initially then became prominent, 3 wide, held onto 3/4L margin from on straightening to the line.
Raced at the rear, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on very well to be closest at the finish.
Settled to race in midfield, 2-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, continued on gamely and held on for 3rd.
Travelled in about midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, worked home well inside final 200M.
Bumped start, settled midfield but wide and without cover, ran on fairly.
Taken back to be at the rear, 3 wide but with cover, made ground steadily to the line.
Urged forward and took up the box-seat, sat 2L off, found no extra for final 150M.
Eased and travelled in worse than midfield, 3-3/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, one paced.
Bumped start, eventually took lead and rail at 1200M, headed passing 300M, emptied soon after.
Settled towards the tail, on rail, showed slight dash in top of the straight only.
In behind midfield, 2 wide throughout, run ended when checked at 350M.
Hard ridden from the start, raced in one-off one-back, faded from on straightening.
Hard ridden forward and settled outside the lead, gave ground from rounding home turn and finished tailed out. Disappointing and must trial.
Settled wide behind midfield, widest runner turning for home, sustained effort to assert authority 250 metres out.
Slowly away, trailed the field to the 300 metres, finished off the race well to grab 2nd place inside the final 50 metres.
Settled in last few, circled the field rounding home bend, just over 2L off and wide in midfield entering the straight, ran on early but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.

Jumped fairly from a wide gate, raced prominently and wide in early stages, travelled alongside the leader around home bend and hit the front on straightening, unable to sustain effort and swamped over 250 metres out.

Soon picked up to forward of midfield, travelled keenly in slackened pace around the bend, switched off the rail for a run on straightening, failed to quicken to threaten inside the final 200 metres. (Lame after 2 days)
Settled just over 2L off the pace in 6th early stages, drifted back to midfield coming onto home bend, steadied at the 400 metres and checked passing the 200 metres hence never threatening.
Sluggish at start, travelled just worse than midfield early stages, saved ground on the rail turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
In front briefly, ceded advantage for 1L 3rd on the rail passing the 1300 metres, steadied for a run over 350 metres out and soon faded under pressure.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, remained well behind to home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled not far off the pace 3-wide early stages, some 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, tight in running 300 metres out and soon dropped out.
Began well from a wide gate, gradually taken back to midfield but remained wide without cover, took closer order 3-wide rounding home bend, hampered 200 metres out and soon weakened.
Amongst the leaders, obtained lead on the passing the 1300 metres, steadied pace in front around home bend, soon headed on straightening and dropped out under pressure.
Settled behind leaders, in 5th 3Ls off the slow pace, briefly waited for a gap early straight, stayed on strongly final 300M to take lead close home.
Always prominent, settled 3rd on fence in a slowly run race, moved up alongside leader 200M, kicked on well to gain lead near 100M, nailed late by winner.
Crossed to the lead passing 1200M, led unchallenged, tackled by rival 200M, gave way grudgingly final 100M.
Held up midfield in a slowly run race, 4Ls to make up 400M, stayed on well to go 4th near line, lay in final 200M.
Driven forward to be tracking leader on settling, scrubbed along 450M to hold position, battled on final 400M under pressure but always held by first few.
Checked when crowded for room on jumping, recovered to race behind midfield, difficult obtain clear running until 250M, stayed on mildly towards the finish.
In 4th never far off the pace, had his chance turning in, fought on same pace, out of contention 150M.
From draw 1 settled midfield along the fence, battled away passing 400M, not reached leaders.
Positioned just ahead of midfield, kept on same pace in straight, no threat.
Towards the rear in 11th spot, 8Ls off the slow pace, switched out 300M, boxed on fairly to the line, not reached leaders.
Reserved behind midfield 6-7Ls off the pace, couldn't muster the pace to challenge leaving the bend. No impression.
Taken across behind runners, settled 10Ls back in the rear, failed to pick up on straightening, well beaten.
Began awkwardly, dropped back to rear 10Ls off the pace on settling, struggled to get going on straightening. Never involved.
Steadied from wide draw, held up near the rear, soon outpaced turning in, eased when well beaten.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1000M, improved on turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Began smartly from gate 12, raced prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 700M, travelled well on turn, headed early in straight, stayed on well thereafter to take a place.
Moderately away from the widest draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 550M, finished off well to make frame.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, checked near 500M, angled out thereafter, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, 3 wide, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, moved closer on turn, angled out near 550M, finished off evenly in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly near 1000M, angled out near 800M, 3 to 4 wide on turn, one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, inconvenienced near 900M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, carried wider after passing 750M, 5-1/2L back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Hampered start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, found rail after entering the back straight, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 700M, weakened turning in, emptied early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take a place.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening. (Mucus in trachea.)
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear early, 2 wide from near 800M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from 550M, 4-1/2L back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 at rear in the early stages, found rail near 800M, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off strongly, scored by a head.
Slightly inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, took the lead near 400M, kept on strongly in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and made contact, took the early lead, headed near 1600M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail thereafter, moved closer on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, similar position to turn, angled out near 450M, finished off evenly.

Slowly away and bumped the outside of its stall, difficult to settle early, pulled way forward after passing 1800M, took the lead near 1600M, led by 1 to 2 lengths, headed 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, closer on turn, showed no response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased back, took rail, pace good, dashed strongly 200M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, led 300M, overhauled 50M.
Pushed forward, one out one back, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail and led at good pace, soon emptied 200M.
Checked early, took rail in midfield, pace good, on heels 200M, no progress.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, no turn of foot.
At rear, took rail, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never better than midfield.
Never a factor.
Settled midfield, after the 1000M travelled keenly, in the straight responded strongly to score.
Taken back at start, improved passing 400M, made nice ground passing 150M, finished solidly.
Ridden along to take lead, rounding the home turn lay out, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home nicely.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve near 700M, made ground passing 150M, finished well.
Raced outside the lead, niggled passing 600M, came home OK.
At start was crowded for room, settled behind midfield, placed pressure passing 700M, in the straight fought hard but only limited response.
Raced behind midfield, always back, limited response, mucus in trachea.
Taken back at start, passing 400M tried to improve but no response, failed to run on.
Very fractious and reared on number of occasions in the barrier, rider's saddle shifted back in the early stages, travelled behind midfield on rail, failed to run on, must trial.
Raced midfield, placed heavy pressure near 700M, very wide on straightening, weakened in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover, gave ground noticeably after 800M, must trial.

Strode forward before settling in midfield away from rail. Travelled well in middle stages before awkwardly placed behind runners approaching the turn. Eased wider on cornering before sprinting well & obtaining lead last 25m.

Was eased at the start before being cramped for room and positioning second from last on the rail. Was checked when getting close to heels approaching the bend before staying close to rail and striking lead at 150m.

Raced 3 wide in first section before easing back to be second from last at the 1200m. Improved three wide at the 450m before cornering four horses wide and 3L from lead. Made up some late ground but 3L from winner.

Was bumped at the start before easing back into midfield away from the rail. Moved three wide and improved quickly at the 450m before entering the straight the widest runner and only 2L from lead. Battled on in straight.

Had no early speed and subsequently settled a clear last after 250m. Improved between runners near the 400m before easing at the 350m. Was around 4L from lead on cornering and passed a few in the run to the line.

Began fairly but was ridden up in first 200m before settling in lovely position behind leading pair away from the rail. Moved around heels approaching the 400m and struck lead at the 250m before tiring out over final 200m.
Eased across after the start to position away from the fence and in the second last pair. Was the last horse to turn for home and managed to pass a few late but didn't threaten.
Showed good speed early to position on leaders back after 300m. Shifted away from the fence and raced tight on cornering but failed to run on over the final 300m.

Settled in midfield on the rail. Raced keenly approaching the 600m before racing close to heels at the 400m. Was checked & stumbled rounding the turn. Held up for room approaching the 200m and no clear running last 100m.
Began well and was ridden forward before getting outside the leader after 400m. Was ridden up from the 500m mark to hold position before folding up in the last section.

Began only fairly but was hard ridden in first 250m to assume lead before crossing to the rail at the 1200m. Travelled well but was headed at the 250m and stopped quickly from that point. Vet reported no abnormalities.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar positon on turn, finished off strongly to score narrowly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly for a short distance after passing 1000M, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off very well, just beaten by a nose.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, improved from 500M, carried very wide turning in, finished off very strongly, just missed by a nose.
Average to begin, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame, just couldn't hold off the first few late.
Jumped with them, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, led narrowly 100M, headed and missed frame near the finish.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly from gate 10, raced 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly after entering the back straight, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to final 50M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, shared lead turning in, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter, eased final 50M. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well from a middle draw, raced prominently, 3 wide, 1-1/2 length back on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
In midfield, 4L off along the rail, battled on all the way and held off a late challenge to score by a short-head.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, ran home strongly to take 2nd.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 5-1/2L off 2 wide, showed good kick at 200M, worked home well.
Bumped start, settled one-off one-back, 2-3/4L off, ran on fairly to the line.
Sent forward, took rail and led from about 700M, couldn't find extra and headed approaching 100M.
Awkward start and raced at the tail, along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily on the outside track.
Asked to race in the box-seat, kept on until out of steam passing 150M.
In midfield, 3-1/2L behind but wide and without cover, found nothing to challenge.
Urged and settled to race 1-1/4L off and outside the lead, faded out from 200M.
Bumped start, in worse than midfield along the rail, showed nothing. (Lame right front)
Bumped start, settled just in front of midfield along the rail, emptied at 200M.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, commence move 4-wide rounding home bend, hung in early in straight, ran on well to gain upper hand close to home.
Began well, settled one-out-one back mainly in 3rd, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, hit the front 100 metres out only to be pipped at post.
Drawn wide, raced wide in early stages before improving to join the leader 600 metres out, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.

Taken back from a wide gate to trail the field, switched wide turning for home, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish. (Jockey reprimanded for his riding in early and middle stages)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-1/2L lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, went wide in second last turning for home, ran on down the centre of the track without threatening.
Very slowly away, soon recovered along the rail to about 4L back in 7th, did not find much room early in straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear, ran on down the inside of the track to be nearest at finish.
With leaders early, snatched 2L back to 4th 900 metres out and became 5th approaching the Rock, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly settling better than midfield, switched wide into the straight and found nothing.
Drawn wide, ridden positively to obtain lead on the rail at the Rock, led until headed over 200 metres out and soon weakened.
Moderate start, soon picked up to lead briefly at the 1000 metres, lost advantage at the Rock, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Lame)
Not hurried after the start, settled in midfield along the fence in a fast run race, 3Ls to make up top of straight, made good progress to be leading inside 50M, kept on well to the line.
Chased leader early, eased back to 4th 850M, pressed on home turn, responded well to be vying for the lead mid-straight, held by winner final stages.
Emerged as leader passing 1400M, set fast pace in the lead, kept on well in the straight, caught by first 2 near 50M.
Taken back from wide draw, 8Ls back at the rear in a fast run race, plenty to do turning in, closed off fastest to go 4th near line.
Chased leaders early before settling down in midfield, hampered by weakening rival 450M, stayed on mildly over final 300M, couldn't reel in leaders.
Eased and taken across behind runners, held up towards the rear, headway form 500M along inner, boxed on fairly in the straight and always held by leaders.
Began well from gate 2, chased leader along the fence, pressed along 500M, kept battling to hold his position early straight, faded final 150M.
From draw 10 shifted across behind runners, towards the rear always, made some progress in the straight but never reached contention.
Travelled 3-wide in mid-division, lost cover entering back-straight, took closer order passing 700M, peaked on its run 200M, no extra final stages.
Towards the rear, ended up as the back-marker from 800M, struggled to get going in the straight, never involved. (wound to the left hind fetlock.)
Settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, pushed wide home turn, couldn't quicken when asked, eased final 100M when no chance.
Caught wide no cover from 1400M, strode forward to be closer to the rail after 1000M, under pressure 600M, gave way rapidly to finish last, tailed out. (RH fetlock and stifle being struck into.)
