Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1100M, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight and scored by a nose.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, challenged the leader after turning in, kept on very well to the line, just missed by a nose.

Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd without threatening the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, improved from 600M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider turning in, raced tight near 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out fro near 550M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, found rail after passing 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 900M, 3 wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the inside, checked near 800M, 6 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from near 1000M, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pressed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield along the fence, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
At rear, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide, bumped 450M whilst weakening.
Eased to sit in midfield, dropped off 400M.
Never competitive at rear.
Slow away, never a factor.
Settled at back, widest on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Shortly after the start lost its right front plate, urged along to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded nicely in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield on rail, gained ground passing 150M, finished nicely.
Settled behind midfield, after 900M raced wide and without cover, commenced to improve passing 800M, battled hard in the straight, made some ground passing 100M.
Settled behind leaders, tried to improve near 500M, responded nicely in the early part of straight, came under pressure passing 300M and gave ground passing 150M.
Ridden along to race midfield om rail, improved to handy position after 800M, one-paced in the straight.
Travelled midfield, asked for effort but only limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, then was bumped and lost ground, settled at tail, always back, never in it.
Raced at back on rail, lay out throughout the race, no response in the straight.
Niggled along to take lead, no response when placed pressure, weakened badly near 200M, failed to run on.
Ridden hard for first 150m before assuming lead and coming across to the rail. Steadied the pace second section before sprinting strongly passing the 400m and going on to record easy win.
Began well and was prominent before being crossed and settling on leaders back at 900m. Sprinted well inside 400m but couldn't real in winner. Margin back to third.

Was steadied back behind runners after the start. Moved out three wide approaching the 600m when pace slowed. Was at least 5 lengths from lead on cornering before making good headway in final section.

Began fast but wasn't bustled before settling in midfield on the rail, 3 lengths from lead at the 800m. Held up in early stages of straight. Got clear running at the 350m and closed off satisfactorily.

Slow away but mustered speed to position worse than midfield on the rail. Was making ground near the 300m before being bumped and then blocked near the 200m. Got clear after the 150m and finished nicely.

Obtained lovely trailing position in midfield away from the rail. Was 3L from lead at 800m before being forced three wide near the 700m as the pace slowed. Had clear running after straightening but worked to the line only evenly.
Began fast but drifted back in first furlong to be in midfield away from the rail. Was 3.5L from lead at the 400m. Was held up slightly near the 200m but was only even after that point.

Slow into stride and subsequently settled last on the outside. Continued to race at the tail, conceded 5 lengths on cornering. Made some ground and passed a few in final section. Vet reported mucus in trachea post-race.

Began well before coming across from wide barrier, racing three horses wide in midfield. Made the turn awkwardly after the 900m, before being bumped & forced 4 wide at 700m. Packed up in final section following tough trip.

Began well and ridden forward but raced three wide without cover from the 900m. Improved around outside in middle section to make a line of three approaching bend before fading out from the 350m. Lame after race.
Ridden hard after the start to move forward before to position outside the leader near the 900m. Came under pressure on cornering and before giving ground from the 400m.

Fast away before easing and being crossed at the 900m, getting nice position behind speed. Held up for clear running early in straight before being bumped & crowded for room near the 300m and couldn't pick up from that point.
Was eased after the start to come across closer to the rail worse than midfield. Conceded over 5 lengths approaching the corner and didn't really run on in the final section.

Began awkwardly and bumped, consequently settling at the tail of the field after 250m. Raced keenly and was checked away from heels near the 700m. Was a clear last on cornering and didn't make any headway in final section.
Jumped with them, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out and made contact near 300M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, 3/4L back on turn, made contact and unbalanced near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Raced close to the tail, 2 wide throughout, worked home very well to score by 1-1/4L and with something in hand.
Jumped only fairly, in midfield along the rail, ran home solidly to pinch 2nd prior going to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide throughout, ran on well to take 3rd.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2 wide, bumped after 300M, ran on well thereafter.
Moved into the box-seat steadily, led briefly in the straight before battling on to the line.
Eased and settled in behind midfield, along the rail, made ground and ran on fairly.
Rolled forward, raced in front of midfield along the rail, continued on to the line.
Ridden forward to take rail and led, kept on until 200M then found no extra.
Pushed early and settled in one-off one-back, awkward to heels at 400M then held up at 350M, did not run on.
Taken back and raced at the rear, wide but with cover, was one paced.
Bumped start then eased to settle in behind midfield, wide but with cover, did not improve.
In midfield, wide and without cover, did not feature.
Jumped slowly, remained at the rear throughout, saved no ground.
Prominent but wide early, improved to sit outside lead at 800M, emptied from 250M.
Soon took up running setting a sound pace, spread-eagled the field effortlessly upon straightening, won unchallenged.
Settled within 2L of pace in 3rd on the rail, failed to respond to winner's turn of foot in straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in close-up 2nd, lost position on straightening, kept on same pace.
Broke well from the wide-ish draw in the small field, gradually taken back to 4th 2-wide just over 2L off the speed, in similar position turning for home, failed to quicken under pressure.
Settled in 5th on the rail just over 3L off the speed, saved ground turning in before angling off the rail to challenge, kept on same pace without quickening.
Moderate start, trailed in last of 6-horse field about 4L off the pace, ran home one-paced.
Positively ridden to take the lead along stand's rail, fended off challenge of rival inside 200M, drew clear final stages to win by dominant margin.
Tracked the pace along stand's rail, stayed on steadily to go 2nd near 50M, no impression on winner.
Shared lead, fought head to head with winner until outpaced 200M, lost 2nd 50M out.
Close up to the pace, battled on passing 500M but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Always within striking distance, kept on steadily over final 400M, held by leaders.
Up with leaders, hard driven passing 450M, kept on same speed, faded final 150M.
Not far off the pace first half, unable to quicken when asked, never threatened.
Towards the rear, switched out to challenge halfway, plodded on fairly, not reached leaders.
Reared at the start and lost ground, raced in mid-division on the outside of field, couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaders, kept on same pace to line.
Held up behind midfield, ran on same pace from 400M, never in contention.
Raced keenly behind leaders, kept on same pace and no impression over final 400M.
Settled down behind midfield, found very little when placed under pressure inside 400M, never near to challenge.
Began awkwardly, held up towards the rear along stand's rail, driven along 400M but couldn't pick up under pressure. (Lame next day.)
Crowded for room on jumping, ended up in last, couldn't keep up and detached from field halfway, soon beaten.
Clean jump, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score with something in hand.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths or so back turning in, No clear running early in straight, checked off heels near 300M, finished off strongly thereafter to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to take a place.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out near 650M, raced tight and steadied off heels near 500M, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1000M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 1000M, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, angled out after passing 650M, 7 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never competitive. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length behind on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score by 2-1/2L.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled comfortably on turn, showed very good response early in straight, crowded near 200M, kept on well thereafter to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight.

Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently early, allowed rival to cross 950M, sat 1 out 1 back thereafter, angled out after passing 550M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from near 900M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 950M, led by half length turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, similar positon on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently but very wide in the early stages, 2 wide from near 900M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail after entering the back straight, improved on turn, finished off strongly in straight and scored.

Taken back from a wide draw, 9 lengths back, sent forward short after entering the back straight, took the lead near 700M, led by half length turning in, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner, finished 2nd.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place.

Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 11 lengths back in the early stages, moved closer after entering the back straight, 6 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden from near 750M, 3-1/2L turning in, kept on evenly to the line.

Began well, took the early lead, allowed rival to cross near 1600M, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader thereafter, hard ridden from 700M, half length back turning in, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began awkwardly, raced prominently but wide early, found rail after passing 1600M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, 2 wide from near 800M, hard ridden from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced prominently but wide early, sent forward to take the lead after passing 1600M, peaked near 700M, weakened thereafter, emptied in straight, finished tailed out.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, carried wider after 1600M, 3 wide with no cover thereafter, showed limited response and gradually lost position after entering the back straight, last on turn, eased final 400M.

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, slightly taken back to race 3 wide in midfield near 1700M, moved a bit forward after passing 1200M, weakened from 700M, eased thereafter.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on ok.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, took cover, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 2 wide, lack turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at rear on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Slow away, at back 2 wide, on heels 600M, held up badly 200M, not fully tested.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 400M.
Eased back, took rail, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Crowded on jumping, settled midfield on rail, quickened nicely passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, widest on straightening, made some ground passing 100M, worked home nicely.
Fast out, ridden to take lead, fought hard in the straight, worked home OK.
Settled in box seat, kept on rail to save ground rounding Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
In the early stages failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, settled in front of midfield, one-paced.
Urged along to settle behind the lead, fought hard but only limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start form the widest gate, raced at tail, made up some ground passing 100M.
Settled at back on rail, kept on rail rounding Home Turn to save ground, had difficulty to obtain clear running near 150M.
Began only fairly, settled in handy position, gave ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, made some ground when asked for effort in the straight.
Ridden along to take forward position, travelled wide and without cover, weakened in the straight, must trial.

Didn't have early speed & positioned in second half of field. Improved three wide nearing the 500m. Was 4L from lead approaching the turn before balancing up the widest runner & closing strongly striking lead at 150m mark.

Began well but was eased back into midfield position on rail, 4L from lead at 800m. Moved around heels at 550m before being shifted wider & bumped on cornering. Clear running after straightening & closed strongly in straight.

Eased back and across behind runners from wide gate after the start. Raced at the tail before being ridden up from the 500m to improve. Was still at rear, 5L from lead on cornering before making late ground in final 300m.

Began well from wide barrier, striding across to be one off the rail, 2.5L from lead at the 900m. Moved around heels three wide at the 500m. Tried hard in final 300m but couldn't go with closing trio in the last 200m.

Steadied after the start coming across from wide barrier but raced three horses wide near the tail. Continued to improve position around the field from the 750m before pushed 4 wide at the 450m when only 2.5L from lead.
Began well and ridden forward before crossed at the 850m and settling in third off the rail without cover. Was a length from lead on cornering but just peaked last 150m.

Was ridden forward to be prominent at the start before being crossed bear the 850m and positioning on leaders back. Stayed close to the rail on cornering. Raced tight near the 200m but looked to be all out by that stage.

Showed good early speed to come across from middle barrier to obtain lead after 200m and then cross to the rail at the 850m. Raced unchallenged in middle stages and turned over 1L clear before tiring last 150m.

Wasn't fast away before racing into midfield away from the rail. Raced tight near the 550m and was then bumped & unbalanced on cornering. Wasn't too far off on the turn but tired out last 300m. Mucus in trachea post-race.

Went forward after the start before positioning in midfield on the rail, 2.5L from lead at 800m. Shifted off the rail on cornering and had clear running but didn't impress in final section. Muchus in trachea post-race.

Didn't have the early pace of rivals & drifted back to be worse than midfield, 6L from lead at 800m. Continued to drift back before being last under heavy riding near the 500m. Couldn't pick up in run home.
Was the slowest into stride and settled near the tail on the rail. Stayed close to the rail on cornering and weakened out in final section to be well beaten.
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, slightly improved after passing 500M, closed off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, raced tight early in straight, inconvenienced shortly thereafter, finished off evenly when clear final 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a tricky draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, improved on turn, took the lead near 500M, bumped early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still 8 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back, there to turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same position on turn, showed some response early in straight, raced tight near 100M, not ridden out thereafter.
Average to begin, hard ridden early to take the lead, led by a length to turn, headed near 500M, bumped early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Urged and settled outside the lead, kicked away strongly from 200M, scored with plenty in hand.
Settled in one-off one-back position, closed off well to the line but was no match.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 2 wide, worked home okay to take 3rd.
Slotted in to race in midfield, along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Hard ridden to take rail and led, headed at 200M and weakened out.
Sat just in front of midfield, along the rail, kept on till about 100M, found no extra thereafter.
Eased, travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide until shifted to rail rounding home turn, was one paced.
Sat just behind midfield, 2 wide, raced keenly, lay in in straight, ran home late.
Pushed and raced in the box-seat, found no extra approaching 150M.
Failed to muster, sat towards the tail, 2 wide, detached and urged to keep up, couldn't make up ground.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, never in it.
At the rear throughout, never a factor.
Inconvenienced at start, waited with in last few, obtained a run passing the 200 metres, finished off race well to snatch victory near the line.
Close up, commenced move rounding home bend, hit the front from tiring pacemaker over 200 metres out only to be caught close to home.
Settled in rear of midfield, baulked for a run early in home straight, produced good late finish once into the clear inside the final 200 metres.
Slightly slow out settling well behind, commenced move rounding the final bend swinging widest into home straight, ran on well down the centre of the track.
Settled towards the rear, circled the field rounding the final bend and the widest turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear of midfield from a wide gate, produced short-lived effort early in home straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning for home, produced good late impression in the final stretch doing best work late.
Settled in forward of midfield mainly within 3L of the pace in 5th, came under pressure rounding the final bend, one-paced in home straight.
Travelled wide in 4th around the first bend, remained 3-wide without cover in 3rd mainly within 3L of the pace in back straight, in similar position rounding the final bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield in 6th on the rail, saved ground on the rail turning in, ran home one-paced.
Began well, settled about 2L off the pace in 3rd on the rail, came under pressure rounding the final bend, kept on before weakening inside the final 200 metres.
Improved gradually to take up running passing the winning post the first time, obtained rails run over 1200 metres out, led until finding no extra over 200 metres out.
Jumped well from draw 1, tracked leaders from 1400M, moved up to the lead 250M, pressed by rivals 150M, held on gamely. (Objection from 2nd overruled.)
Failed to muster speed, held up keenly in mid-division, peeled out 400M, loomed up to challenge winner mid-straight but unable to reel in rival. (Objection on winner overruled.)
Settled down behind midfield, made his move on outer 650M, vied for lead mid-straight, tried hard but held by first 2.
Crowded for room on jumping, ended up behind midfield on settling, kept chasing in the straight but no match for first 3.
Shifted across behind runners after the start, held up near the rear hugging the rail, stayed on mildly on straightening, not reached leaders.
Chased leader early, 5th at 1000M, shuffled back to midfield home turn, kept battling away over final 300M without threatening.
Slow away, held up 3rd last 8Ls off the pace, peeled wide nearing 400M, kept grinding on down outside but never a real danger.
Eased after the start and dropped back to last 9Ls off the pace, bustled along 500M, made some ground passing weakening rivals but never likely.
Caught wide early stages, strode forward to be chasing leaders entering back-straight, couldn't go on passing 300M, soon out of contention.
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, shuffled back 600M, didn't respond to urgings on straightening, soon behind.
Rushed forward from draw 11, crossed to the lead 1200M, led a good gallop, caught 250M, soon no extra and weakened badly.
Took early lead until 1200M, stayed prominent behind leader, pushed along 450M, failed to run on weakened out to be last.

Commenced well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled well to turn, improved from 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths or so back, improved from 700M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 600M, hard ridden from 300M, made some headway in straight to take 3rd.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 2W behind midfield, 4Ls back, sent forward after passing 700M, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on evenly thereafter but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, sent forward after passing 800M, took the lead near 650M, peaked after turning in, headed 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position to turn, peaked on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead and set a very slow tempo, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed after passing 650M, kept on evenly to the line.
Pushed to lead at fast sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly 200M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, held ground for 3rd.
At back, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
At back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 200M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Very slow away, at back, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Eased back, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden at back, suited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Never competitive.
Began awkwardly, ridden to settle midfield, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 450M, responded solidly, just missed by Neck.
Ridden along to take lead, responded nicely in the straight, near 50M became badly unbalanced when raced in restricted room, lost ground and rider had to stop riding.
Near 1000M steadied to obtain a position close to rail, raced behind midfield on rail, gained nice ground passing 100M.
Travelled at back, commenced to improve passing 500M, made some ground passing 50M.
Raced in box seat, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Taken back at start, kept on rail ground the Home Turn, made some late ground.
Raced midfield, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.

Eased across into midfield away from the rail. Was bumped at the 1000m before drifting back to be 6 lengths from lead at 800m. Travelled well on corner before shifting out nearing the 300m & finishing strongly to win.

Crowded for room after the start before gathering speed along the rail to be on leaders back approaching the 1000m. Moved away from rail at the 550m before sprinting fast, captured lead passing 150m before being caught late.

Began awkwardly before being ridden to be prominent, settling between runners behind leading trio after 300m. Was around 4L from lead at the 400m before getting clear running after turning and closing well in final section.

Shifted back and across behind runners after the start, settling a clear last at the 1000m. Moved out wider at the 600m and again on the corner, conceded 8L at 400m but made significant ground in last section after.

Showed early speed & strode across before easing after 200m, racing three wide. Shifted closer to rail approaching the 900m. Was 5L from lead at the 400m and finished off fairly in last section. Blood in trachea post-race.

Bumped at start and had no speed thereafter, positioning in midfield on rail. Improved position along the rail nearing the 1000m. Was 6L from the lead at the 400m before turning in and making some ground in final 300m.

Wasn't the fastest into stride but gathered early speed to hold the lead along the rail. Travelled strongly when leading in middle stages & was 2L clear at the 400m. Joined in the lead at 150m at tired out from that point.

Was ridden across from wide barrier but was trapped wide before easing back further near the 1200m. Raced 4 wide without cover throughout. Was 7L from lead at 400m and finished off ok in final section considering tough trip.

Showed good early speed to settled outside the leader after 400m. Raced in the clear in second section and was over 2L from the lead at the 400m. Was ridden up on cornering but didn't finish off in final section.

Was eased back behind runners shortly after start. Raced three horses wide, between runners at the 800m, 8L from lead. Continued to race at the tail on cornering and couldn't threaten in the final section.

Eased across after the start into midfield but then drifting further back, between runners in a group at the tail. Was one of the last to corner in conceding nearly 8L at the 400m. Hung in at 300m but was never likely.
Restrained back behind runners from wide barrier after the start. Stayed close to rain in middle section. Was crowded near the 300m but was never likely to figure from rearward position.

Showed early speed before throwing head and racing ungenerously when being restrained at the 1200m. Continued to be restrained until 1000m. Came under heavy pressure at the 500m and yielded ground in final section.

Was worse than midfield early. Proved difficult to settle and was checked away from heels at the 1000m. Continued to race wide and was then left without cover after the 900m. Dropped out under no riding in final section.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, easily scored.
Slowly away, recovered quickly to race 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, angled out near 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths back, severely checked near 1000M, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, headed near 450M, weakened early in straight. (Bled.)
Bumped start, raced better than midfield early, went wrong after passing 1000M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
In front of midfield, 3 wide and without cover, worked home nicely and held on to score by a neck.
At rear as usual, 2-3 wide, switched widest in straight and battled on strongly, missed by a neck.
In behind midfield, 2 wide, worked home well to take 3rd.
Niggled along then eased to be in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, saved ground.
Hard ridden but had to settle in one-off one-back, no daylight until 250M, closed off only fairly.
Travelled in midfield, however wide and without cover, ran on one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced in the straight.
Jumped fairly only, in worse than midfield along the rail, did not improve.
Eased then settled near the tail, navigated the turns on rail, made no impression.
Only able to share lead in a 2 wide position, emptied and headed near 250M.
In box-seat initially, 4-1/4L off, lost ground when rounding home turn.
Shared lead on the rail, weakened badly near 250M.
Checked shortly after the start dropping to last, remained in last or near last to the straight, swung widest turning in, ran on well to assert authority inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, settled in rear to the straight, obtained a clear passage over 250 metres out, quickened well to reach 2nd over 100 metres out, never threatening.
Niggled at early stages before settling behind the midfield on the rail, produced good late impression between runners inside the final 200 metres.

Moderate start, soon picked up to 4th within 3L of pace on the rail, soon came to challenge after straightening reaching 2nd passing the 300 metres, unable to sustain effort and swamped over 100 metres out.

Began from the widest gate, gradually taken in for cover in 5th in midfield within 3L of pace, came to challenge under pressure and looked a place chance 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort and soon swamped.

Soon led 2-wide, obtained rails run approaching the home bend, maintained fast pace kicking over 1.5L clear rounding the bend, unable to sustain effort and dropped out under pressure inside the final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled behind the midfield, found no response under pressure in the straight.

Ridden early, settled just behind the leader in 3rd 2-wide, awkwardly placed close to the leader when steadied 1000 metres out, in similar position entering home straight but soon dropped out. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Niggled at early, travelled just off the pace in 2nd on the rail, slightly further off the speed on home bend, kept on early in straight before fading inside the final 300 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Not hurried early stages, settled behind midfield on inner, behind traffic top of straight, barged his way out 350M causing interference to rivals, stormed to the front inside 150M and raced away.
Chased leaders, held up for clear running until a gap on inside opened up nearing 200M, fought on steadily to clinch 2nd before line but no match with impressive winner.
From draw 14 crossed to the lead without making too much use, driven along near 400M, kept going well, couldn't hold off winner inside 150M, edged out to 3rd in photo finish
Jumped on terms from draw 12, caught wide no cover from 1400M, steadied back to near last for cover, 6Ls to make up 400M, bumped near 300M, re-grouped and stayed on well to take 4th.
Dropped back from wide draw to be racing in last 8Ls behind leader, brought widest to challenge leaving the bend, checked near 300M then made moderate progress to the line.
Taken back from wide draw, held up on inner towards the rear, stayed on mildly over final 400M. Good run against higher rated rivals.
Jumped evenly, moved up to race outside leader, driven passing 350M but held ground only, no extra late stages. (Lame RF and restriction action both fore next day.)
Restrained after the jump, behind mid-pack in 10th position, proved very difficult to settle after 1400M, no clear running early straight, ran on without threat final 250M.
Settled in 4th 2-3Ls behind the pace, kept on same pace turning home, outsprinted by pursuing rivals from 200M.
Restrained behind midfield, checked near 1400M and pushed to a 3-wide spot, 4Ls to make up top of straight, tried hard but fought on same pace only.
Dropped back to race near the rear, 6Ls behind leader home turn, ran on one-paced in the straight, failed to reach contention.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in midfield along the fence, couldn't make much headway in the straight, no threat to the front runners.
Raced keenly in midfield, 3-wide no cover from 1000M, couldn't lift in the straight off a tough run, never threatened.
Settled down in midfield, difficult to settle 1300M, checked 350M, persevered for a short distance before giving ground badly to finish tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance / Lame next day.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score. (Lost right front plate near 1050M.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar positon on turn, awkwardly placed near 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in midfield on rail, steadied off heels near 1000M, 2-1/2L back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to make frame.

Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide in midfield, found cover after passing 900M, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-1/2L back turning in, made good progress in straight despite being unbalanced near 250M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at rear on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, raced tight near 200M, inconvenienced 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with field, raced 2 wide at rear, checked near 1000M, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened after passing 300M, eased final 150M.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 1-1/2L back on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 50M, scored by a neck.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, but just couldn't hold off the winner.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made good response in straight without threatening.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 1000M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 13, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Began well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently,3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, angled out near 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Jumped well from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead after passing 200M, kept on well thereafter and scored.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail after entering the back straight, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Crowded start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 wide after passing 800M, there to turn, angled out near 350M, finished off evenly.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 950M, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M. (Lame right front and right hind legs.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.

Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after entering the back straight, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began awkwardly and bumped, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from near 800M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed to secure box seat, pace good, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, overhauled 200M, ran on for 2nd.
Eased at start, took rail, pace good, held up 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, held ground in straight.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 300M, made minor ground when clear.
Midfield 2 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Slow away, pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, no dash.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up at rear, pace good, lack room 300M, ran on ok.
Pushed early, 2 wide behind midfield, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, hard ridden early but not muster, 2-3 wide, pace good, no dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide at back, pace good, no progress.
Trapped very wide in midfield, emptied 400M.
Raced in box seat, near 400M help up, made up good late ground, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start from wide barrier, asked for effort passing 550M, widest on straightening, quickened passing 100M, finished solidly.
Taken back at start from widest barrier, commenced to improve passing 600M, wide on straightening, responded solidly and continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, placed pressure passing 500M, gained ground passing 100M, finished nicely.
Raced at back, improved to lead rounding the Home Turn, gave some ground passing 100M.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, gave ground near 100M.
Crowded on jumping, settled midfield, improved to outside the lead passing 1000M, limited response in the straight.
Ridden to race outside the lead, came under pressure near 650M, failed to run on.
Took lead with nice early speed, weakened badly in the straight.

Began fairly but gathered speed to settle behind leading pair. Ridden up near the 600m to hold position before running a little wide on bend. Raced greenly when sprinting fast in final section & won with something in reserve.
Was very fast away and gathered speed to cross to the rail after 150m when leading. Was over 1 length clear when cornering and was still in the lead until caught in last 30m by promising winner.

Began well before positioning on leaders back after 150m. Travelled strongly behind leader approaching the turn. Had clear running after balancing and challenged fleetingly near the 200m before peaking last 50m.
Had no speed early before coming across to the rail and settling near the tail. Improved along rail in middle section, conceding 5L at the 400m. Finished off better than most in final section.

Strode forward after the start to come across and position outside the leader after 250m. Went up to be 1 length behind leader approaching the bend before hanging in badly and having difficulty finishing off.
Allowed to find feet after the start, settling in midfield on the rail. Was 4 lengths from the on cornering and finished off only fairly in the final section.

Crowded for room on jumping & subsequently raced worse than midfield between runners. Stayed close to the rail, conceding 6 lengths at the 400m. Crowded at the 50m when making some ground but was always well away from lead.

Steadied and shifted back behind runners after start. Travelled keenly & checked away from heels at the 900m. Continued to over-race in middle sections. Made late ground in final section to reduce significant margin.
Began well and ridden forward from wide barrier but raced wide throughout without cover. Was 4.5L from lead at the 400m but couldn't go on in final section after wide run.

Came across after the start but raced three wide with cover near the tail. Inconvenienced and pushed wider near the 900m before being relegated to last and 9L from lead on cornering. Maintained that margin in final section.
Began fairly and came across before obtaining cover three horses wide. Continued to race wide and couldn't improve before peaking in final section.
Was ridden forward after the start to position in midfield between runners. Was under heavy pressure passing the 500m and hung out near heals and restrained near 400m. Looked beaten long way out.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, improved from 450M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out near 350M, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide from near 700M, carried wider on turn, made some headway in straight. (Lost left hind plate.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, found a 2 wide spot near 700M, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, wider on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, wider from near 400M, made no progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Jumped with field, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back, couldn't maintain position after passing 700M, weakened gradually on turn, emptied early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, worked home nicely to score by a neck.
Urged to lead along the rail, battled on but caught by winner approaching final 50M.
Rolled forward into the box-seat, stayed on well for 3rd.
Raced towards the rear, 2 wide, improved steadily to the line.
Sat just behind midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground.
In midfield, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight.
At the tail, along the rail, ran home one paced.
Went forward, sat outside the lead, emptied at 200M.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, did not run on.
Broke well from the middle gate to lead, travelled off the rails in back straight before coming across onto home bend, driven clear after straightening.
Soon taken back to the rear, commenced move on the inside after straightening, obtained a run about 180 metres out and quickened well to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start, took closer order going up the Rock, ran on to reach 2nd briefly over 200 metres out.
With leaders and wide early, gradually drifted back to midfield approaching the home bend, remained wide in midfield entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Prominent without cover after beginning from the widest gate, taken back to rear of midfield for cover after the first 200 metres, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres in straight.
Moderate start, soon recovered to within 3L of pace in 7th, became 6th rounding home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Crowded at start, niggled along and wide in first few early stages, just over 2L back and 3-wide in 5th coming onto home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in the straight.
Soon dropped to midfield despite ridden along after a moderate start, dropped further back coming onto home bend, widest runner turning in, kept on steadily under pressure.
Failed to muster dropping to the last, trailed the field most of the way, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Moderate start, ridden forward to be just off the pace, unable to sustain effort and weakened inside the final 200 metres. (Irregular hear beat)
Ridden forward from a wide gate to be close-up 2nd when wide, still close up turning in, found no extra and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Improved steadily along the rail early stages to be just off the pace, soon faded after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Chased leader, quickened up smartly to take lead inside 250M, kept on well to the line holding off pursuing rivals.
From draw 1 tracked leaders in 3rd, lacked winner's acceleration early straight, chased solidly final 200M, nearest finish.
Eased back to be 2nd last on settling, 7Ls to make up home turn, closed off strongly final 300M, nearest finish.
Never far off leaders, caught wide no cover, kept on evenly final 300M, held ground only.
Positively ridden, crossed to the lead 1000M, led uncontested, caught by winner passing 250M, no extra and weakened towards the line.
Drifted back to race towards the rear, ran on fairly passing 400M, never got into a contending position. (Jockey dropped whip 250M.)
Began only fairly, behind mid-division, shuffled back 500M, only made limited response when placed under pressure, never threatened.
Held up midfield, over-raced middle stages, 4Ls off leader 400M, only battled in the straight.
From wide draw taken back to last, 9Ls off the pace home turn, passed a couple without making ground on the front runners in the straight.
Jumped on terms, raced 3-wide in midfield, didn't run on when driven from 450M (Jockey reported uncomfortable action)
Jumped well, restrained to race in midfield, checked 500M, niggled along on turn and dropped out in the straight.

Bumped shortly after start, raced a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 400M, finished off strongly to score.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at rear, 4 lengths back, made very good progress in the final 400M to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently on the stand side, hard ridden after passing 350M, peaked and headed near 150M, stayed on evenly to the line.

Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands rail, crowded near 500M, angled out after passing 400M and made contact, kept on evenly until crowded close home.
Began smartly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, made some headway final 400M, inconvenienced close home.
Moderately away from gate 10, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, one-paced in the final 400M.
Crowded on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, 2 to 3 away from the stands rail, ridden 400M out, weakened final furlong, checked close home.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the stands rail, weakened after passing 400M, eased final 150M.
At rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 500M around the field and scored.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 5-3, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed to hold the rail and lead, under pressure throughout and clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground in straight
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
At back along the rails, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward along the fence, harmed by the fast pace, on heel 450M, weakened 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Slow away, on heels first bend, took rail at rear, never improved.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 400M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 400M.
Bumped start, trapped 3 wide, never competitive.
Raced at back on rail, always niggled, improved near 450M, quickened passing 150M, finished unchallenged.
Fast out, ridden to race behind leader on outside rail, responded solidly passing 200M.
Raced at tail, passing 300M had difficulty obtaining clear running, continued to make ground, came line nicely.
Began awkwardly, hard ridden to race behind leaders, near 750M steadied away from heels, responded nicely when asked for effort near 400M, finished well.
Jumped nicely, settled behind the lead, worked home OK, blood trachea.
Settled behind midfield, near 750M checked away from heels, passing 700m was crowded for room and lost ground, one-paced when asked for effort.
Ridden along to take lead, tried to improve near 400M, gave ground passing 100M.
Slow out, settled behind midfield, raced in middle of track, limited response when asked for effort passing 500M, gave ground passing 150M.
Moderate start, raced in handy position, weakened passing 250M.
Ridden to share lead in middle of the track, passing 300M came under pressure and finished only fairly, lame right front next day.
Very fractious in the barrier, raced at tail, shifted in to improve passing 500M, weakened passing 200M, must trial.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, weakened passing 400m.
Settled midfield, gave ground near 400M, lame right front next day.
Urged along to race in handy position, gave ground passing 500M, failed to run on.
Began well and had leaders back in early stages before inheriting the lead on the rail at the 900m when leader hung off. Kicked strongly on cornering and was always well clear in the straight.
Was eased across after the start to settle in midfield on the rail. Stayed close to rail on cornering. Shifted ground in final 200m but closed off well.
Was eased back and across behind runners after the start. Was 6 lengths from the lead approaching the bend before moving out wider on the track and closing well between runners in final section.
Was not fast to begin but gathered speed to rail up into midfield. Improved onto leaders back and only 2L from lead on cornering and finished of soundly in final section for debut run.
Eased across from middle barrier to be worse than midfield away from rail. Was 4 lengths from lead at the 400m and worked home evenly in final section.

Began well and was prominent early settling behind leading pair. Raced without cover from the 900m when leader hung off track. Was one length behind winner on cornering but couldn't challenge in final section.
Eased back from wide barrier settling at the tail, conceding 6.5L at the 800m. moved three wide approaching the corner before balancing up the widest runner and making some ground in final section.
Began awkwardly and subsequently slow to begin before ridden hard to position midfield away from rail. Was 3 lengths from lead on cornering before peaking at 200m.

Began awkwardly and lost ground at the start before settling a clear last after 200m. Was hard ridden from the 650m and conceded 6.5L at the 400m. Shifted out wider after cornering but could only maintain margin to the line.

Began well and positioned outside the leader after 200m. Was bumped and badly hampered when the leader hung off the track after the 900m, and raced three wide from that point. Weakened out over the final 400m.
Began fast to assume lead after 75m. Raced with head on the side before hanging out off the track passing the 900m. Took no competitive part in the race after the 900m.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well, positioned on rail behind midfield, improved from 600M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out near 550M, 4 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, angled out near 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, unbalanced near 700M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and stumbled, raced at rear on rail, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, sent forward after passing 1050M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out shortly after start and bumped, raced at tail, moved a bit closer on turn, still 7 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
At rear, wide but with cover, worked home very strongly to catch leader late, scored by 1/2L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed good kick from 250M, ran on but couldn't hold off the winner.
Settled in the box-seat, battled on well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, sat in front of midfield, on rail, ran on well despite being checked at 250M.
In behind midfield, along the rail, no daylight early, closed off fairly thereafter.
Sent forward to take rail and led, kept on until weakened approaching 200M.
Bumped start, raced close to the tail, 2 wide, failed to improve.
Slow to jump, sat in worse than midfield, 2 wide at turns, found nothing.
Settled in behind midfield, 3 wide and without cover, never improved.
Taken back to be at rear, along the rail, not competitive.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back, emptied approaching 300M. (Lame right front)
Urged forward, sat outside lead, gave ground from on straightening. (Lame right front)

Crowded at start, settled towards the rear in 9th on the rail, inconvenienced at the 800 metres, switched out and obtained a run inside the 300 metres, quickened well to assert authority 100 metres out, won cosily.
Crowded at start, travelled in last few, finished off strongly to grab 2nd placing closing to home.
Taken back to last from the widest gate, trailed the field to the 300 metres, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.

Broke well, gradually drifted back on the rail to midfield despite ridden along, inconvenienced coming onto home bend and switched 2-wide, ran on steadily under pressure to hold some chance briefly 100 metres out.
Ridden along in midfield gaining to 4th and within 3L of speed on the bend, ran on after straightening to hold some chance but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.

Awkward start, travelled wide without cover in midfield, took closer order rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to hold some chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled within 2L of pace in back straight, took closer order rounding home bend and gained slender advantage over 350 metres out, unable to sustain effort and swamped close to home.
Soon led crossing to the rail shortly after, fought on well to resist challenges early in straight, headed 200 metres out and swamped closing stages.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, travelled keenly 3-wide around the bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Began fairly from a wide gate, settled towards the rear and wide behind midfield, ran home one-paced.
Prominent on the rail, inconvenienced and dropped some 3L back to 4th early on home bend, found nothing in the straight.
Began well from a wide gate, chased the leader most of the way, came under press after straightening, soon weakened.
Taken back, raced at the rear over 10Ls away in early and middle stages, peeled out into clear 250M then closed off strongly to prevail in a 4-way photo.
Restrained to race behind mid-pack 7Ls off leader, held up early straight, kept finding the line well over final 300M, held by winner late stages.
Stumbled at the start, held up in midfield along the rail, shifted away from fence 550M, ran on well to be vying for lead 150M, edged out to 3rd close home.
Held up towards the rear, well off the pace early and middle stages, made steady progress leaving home turn, vied for lead from 150M, fought on to just miss 3rd in a 4-way photo.
Positively ridden to be chasing leader, strode up to lead inside 250M, headed soon after and weakened last 150M.
Away well, settled down ahead of midfield, moved up to a striking position from 550M, quickened up to challenge for the lead early straight, one paced final 150M.
Restrained after the jump, sat behind midfield 7-8Ls off leader, saved ground on inner but couldn't quicken to challenge leaders in straight, laboured over the final 300M.
Held up in 11th spot 8-9Ls back, pressed along 500M, had traffic issues early straight, made ground over final 300M but not close enough to challenge.
Behind midfield, caught wide no cover from 1300M, strode closer to pace home turn, ran on only fairly, shifted out under pressure 200M.
Slightly slow away, settled in mid-division 5Ls off the pace, brought wide into straight, plodded home, no threat to leaders.
Reserved near last 10Ls off the pace, widest on straightening, didn't close off.
Never far off leaders, ahead of midfield throughout, ranged up 4-wide from 550m, peaked on its run mid-straight, soon out of contention.
Stumbled on jumping, pressed forward from widest draw to be tracking leader along the 2-path, came under pressure 500M, soon weakened on straightening.
Strode forward from wide draw, crossed to the lead near 1400M, led uncontested, caught by rivals 250M, weakened rapidly to finish last.
Clean jump, taken back to race wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.

Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently but very wide, 2W from near 1000M, half length back turning in, took the lead after passing 300M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late, finished 2nd.

Began smartly from a tricky draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, pushed on until settled 2 wide, half length back near 1300M, a length or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield early, improved after passing 1100M, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 1-1/2L back on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame. (Lost right hind plate.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, closer turn, unable to obtain clear running until near 150M, made some progress thereafter.

Began well, severely checked early, raced 3-4Ls behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out near 450M, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear final 200M. (Lost left hind plate.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, a length or so back in the early stages, 3 wide with cover from near 800M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running until near 200M, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside early, checked near 1500M, 2 wide thereafter, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length to turn, peaked early in straight, headed after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, slightly improved after passing 600M, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, made some headway thereafter to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out from 550M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced prominently on rail, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, led by a length on turn, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, recovered quickly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 550M, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, closer on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from near 1100M, slightly improved on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
