Bumped start, raced 2W, 3Ls back early, sent forward after passing 1500M, settled outside the leader near 1200M, shared lead turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter and scored. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped with them, raced at tail early, 5 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, last turning in, no clear running early in straight, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.

Began smartly, raced prominently early, carried wide near 1300M, positioned 3 wide and without cover in midfield thereafter, 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail early, 2 wide from near 1300M, angled out turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened from 300M.
Very slow away, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M, dominated until 50M overhauled.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail, suited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight and checked, made ground when clear.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, however held up most straight, not fully tested.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked fast sectionals under pressure, ran on well until 200M weakened.
Eased back, on heels early, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward to take box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Pushed forward to sit outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 350M.
Hard ridden early, never competitive.
At the start was crowded for room, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, worked home strongly to score.
No early speed, raced at tail, commenced to improve near 450M, made up some nice late ground, worked home solidly.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield, gradually gained ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield, in the straight until 200M was held up for running, came line nicely.
Passing 1200M travelled keenly when being steadied, raced in handy position, responded nicely in the straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Urged to race in handy position on rail, made ground in the early straight, gave ground passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield, fought hard but only one-paced, mucus trachea.
Settled midfield on rail, responded OK in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 150M.
Very slow out, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight, stalls test.
Wide in early stages and hard ridden to take lead passing 900M, faded out passing 200M.
Slow out, always back, never in it.
Pushed hard in the early stages to race behind the lead, weakened badly passing 300M, failed to run on.
Began fast, assumed lead after 50m. Travelled strong & 2 lengths clear at the 800m. Kicked clear inside 250m and strong to the line.
Began fairly before making quick ground in first 150m to settle midfield on rail. Steadied & shifted away from rail at 600m. Held up near 200m before finishing hard late.
Ridden forward early before easing back into midfield away from rail. Moved three wide approaching the corner, 2 lengths from lead at 400m. Finished off well in final section.
Bumped at start before striding forward to position midfield away from rail. Moved wider on cornering and ran on steadily in last section.

Strode forward under hard riding but unable to cross and travelled three wide without cover throughout. Continued to stride forward, half a length from lead at 400m. Peaked 250m but didn't give it away.
Began fairly before mustering speed and settling on the leaders back. Was less than 2 lengths from lead at 400m but couldn't finish off in final section.
Was steadied back behind runners after the start. Raced third from last and 4.5 lengths from lead at 400m. Shifted around heels at the 300m but only maintained margin in run to the line.
Was bumped and crowded at the start before striding across behind runners early. Stayed close to rail on cornering, changed direction inside final 200m.

Began awkwardly veering out & losing ground. Gathered stride & settled second from last, 10 lengths from lead at 800m. Ridden forward & shifted wider at 600m. Six lengths from lead at 400m, maintained margin in final section.

Had no early speed and subsequently trailed the field, over 12 lengths from lead at the 800m. Made some ground in middle section, and was 8 lengths from lead at 400m before passing a few in last section.
Wasn't fast away but hard ridden early to stride up into second position away from rail. Was joined in second position at the 700m before coming under pressure and yielding ground from the 500m.

Bumped at start before coming across to midfield but racing three wide with cover. Continued to race wide with head on the side before weakening out badly in final section. Mucus in trachea post-race.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, checked and stumbled near 900M, saved ground on turn, finished off nicely despite crowded 100M out, scored narrowly. (Lost left front plate and lame left front leg.)
Began well, raced 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, checked near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept on very well in straight, led narrowly 50M out, just headed on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to take a place.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the middle stages, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 1000M, carried wider near 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back turning in, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, 3 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield 2 wide, fought on solidly from 200M to catch leader late, scored by a head.
In box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off, hit front at 50M but ran down in final strides.
Sent forward to take rail and led, caught at 50M but ran on.
Awkward start and lost ground, recovered in worse than midfield 2 wide, closed off fairly.
In about midfield, 2 wide, failed to settle, ran on and made minor ground late.
In midfield initially, moved forward at 800M but was still left wide, failed to improve in the run home.
Raced in front of midfield, wide but with cover, ran on until emptied late.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, found no extra approaching 200M.
Wide early then eased to be at the tail, 2 wide, pretty one paced but ran on.
Taken back, at the rear along the rail, never improved.
Urged and settled in one-off one-back, ran on till 150M.
In worse than midfield, wide but with cover, raced ungenerously and was one paced only.
Slow jump, in about midfield along the rail, run ended at 200M.
Eased then settled in midfield, trapped very wide, steadied at 350M, did not run on thereafter.
Jumped best from a wide gate, travelled very wide without cover mainly in 6th or 5th in better than midfield, quickened well to hit the front over 100 metres out, won cosily.
Midfield early, took closer order coming onto home bend, inconvenienced shortly after straightenin but ran on well.
Ridden along after a moderate start, chased the leader on the rail, switched out to challenge entering home straight and led shortly after, headed by the winner 100 metres out.
Jumped well, travelled prominently 3-wide without cover in 4th, in similar position entering home straight, kept on same pace without threatening.
Moderate start, gradually picked up to just worse than midfield rounding home bend, wide turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without threantening.
Soon took up running, led the field to the 400 metres, gradually faded under pressure.
Soon dropped to last few, inconvenienced and switched in for a run upon straightening, made up some late ground. (Jockey reported horse intractable most of the way.) (Lame next day)

Moderate start, travelled keenly in early stages, gradually shifted back for rails run just worse than midfield, snuck up on inside turning in, baulked and switched for a run 200 metres out, made no show closing stages.
Began fairly from a wide gate, ridden but soon dropped to last few, widest runner turning into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Bumped on jumping, soon recovered to travel prominently, folded up quickly from the 250 metres. (Bled)
Moderate start, travelled just worse than midfield, took closer order along the rail rounding home bend, short-lived effort to reach 3rd shortly after straightening, soon weakened.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, never seen with a chance finishing tailed off.
Held up towards the rear in 6 runner race, quickened up top of straight making smooth headway to lead 200M, raced away for a dominant win.
Steadied to obtain cover, raced in last of 6, peeled out to challenge top of straight, stayed on well to go 2nd 80M out, couldn't get close to winner
Emerged as clear leader passing 1000M, led at good pace, headed by winner near 200M, no extra final stages.
Began only fairly, settled 4th of 6, moved within striking distance 500M, tried hard but couldn't muster the speed to challenge, out of contention 150M.
Shared lead early stages, eased back to sit in 2nd from 1000M, couldn't keep up with leaders 250M, faded towards the line.
Settled in 3rd, battled on same pace early straight, weakened final 150M. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation for the disappointing performance.)
Moderately away, raced 4 lengths back on rail, angled out after passing 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score. (Dead-heat)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 800M, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly to gain a dead heat victory.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, slightly headed from near 900M, travelled well on turn, retook the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter, just could not hold off the first few late, pleasing debut.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail after passing 900M, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider near 600M, 3-1/2L back turning in, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 to 3 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well, raced 3 to 4 wide, 6 lengths back, no cover throughout, same margin back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently but wide, took the lead after passing 900M, led narrowly on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield early, 2 wide from near 1100M, 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 10 lengths back at 800M, a bit closer on turn, taken wide after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, moved forward after passing 1000M, took the lead near 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, crowded near 1100M, awkwardly placed near 850M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear early, slightly improved after passing 1200M, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Crowded on jumping, recovered to race on rail in midfield, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly. (Lost right front plate.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at rear, closer on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made little progress.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a middle draw, showed good speed to take the early lead, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, weakened early in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths back, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began well and shared lead for first 500m before continuing on and crossing to rail at the 900m. Steadied speed in penultimate section before kicking strongly after cornering for strong win.

Eased after the start & shifted back behind runners. Raced third from last, 7 lengths from lead passing the 800m. Moved 3 wide and made ground passing the 600m before finishing off very strongly over final 300m.
Hard ridden in first 200m before striding up into midfield on rail. Was 3.5L from lead at 400m and after getting clear running after the 300m finished off well closer to rail.

Came across into midfield from wide barrier but was left racing three wide without cover from the 1200m. Improved out wide approaching the turn and conceded only two lengths at 400m. Maintained margin in last section.

Shifted across behind runners after start before racing keenly and shifting out near the 1300m. Raced tight and shifted when making ground at the 300m before shifting wider and making further late ground in final 100m.

Began well and strode forward from wide barrier before settling in midfield three wide but with cover. Balanced up and made ground conceding 2.5L at the 400m before maintaining that margin to the line.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail conceding 7.5 lengths at the 800m. Moved away from the rail on cornering before balancing up as second widest runner and finishing off strongly last 300m.

Ridden forward early before striding across to share lead early. Eased back into third position without cover after 450m. Strode up to be less than 1L from lead approaching the corner but weakened out from the 300m.
One of the last into stride, settling at the tail away from the rail. Moved wider on cornering before conceding 6 lengths at the 400m, before passing a few in last 300m.
Allowed to find feet after start, settling at the tail on the fence. Was a clear last entering the straight before making some headway in the final 400m.

Eased across into midfield after 200m, racing between runners in early and middle sections. Looked to shift out but disappointed for clear running at the 400m before easing back and then finishing one paced final 300m.
Strode forward in first 300m to settle behind leading group on the rail. Moved away from the rail at the 450m and only 2.5 lengths from lead at 400m. Peaked at 350m and tired out from 300m.

Not fast away but gathered early speed to go forward before racing keenly passing the 1400m. Settled better in middle section, less than 3L from lead at 800m. Hard ridden passing 500m before weakening out in final section.

Hard ridden in first 250m to share the lead before being headed near the 1000m and then crossed at the 900m. Held leaders back momentarily but came under pressure passing the 500m and tired out in straight.

Began smartly from the widest draw, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well thereafter and scored.
Commenced well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight and made contact, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, 4 lengths or so back, found rail near 800M, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began fairly, raced 6 lengths back at rear, 2 wide on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Out in line, raced wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, hampered early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, bumped early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Jumped well from gate 10, hampered early, raced very wide with no cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, still no cover on turn, checked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, dominated 300M.
Slow away, pushed forward, sat 2 wide, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Very slow away, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up most straight, dashed strongly to the line.
Pushed to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 250M overhauled.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by slow pace, lack room in straight, little dash when clear.
At back, along the fence, harmed by slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by slow pace, no dash.
Very slow away, raced 2-4 wide at back, harmed by slow pace, no progress.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 2-3 wide, never competitive.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, niggled passing 600M, gained ground passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Began awkwardly, raced midfield on rail, made up some nicely late ground.
Raced behind the lead on rail, response nicely in the straight, finished well.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, gained ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, asked for effort near 550M, widest on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Slow out, raced at rear on rail, limited response in the straight, stalls test.
Crowded at start, passing 1600M difficult to settle in the lead with quick tempo, under heavy pressure in the early straight, failed to run on.
Ridden forward from start and arrested lead before coming across to rail at the 900m. Travelled strongly in middle section, kicked clear on cornering before going away from 350m for easy win.
Began well and raced in midfield before improving on leaders back passing the 800m. Had clear running after cornering and tried gallantly but couldn't go with winner in final section.
Was slow away before hard ridden into midfield away from the rail. Was 3 lengths from lead at 400m and moved wider on cornering before finishing off soundly to snare third.
Strode across from wide barrier before racing worse than midfield and wider on the track. Continued to race wide and conceded over 4L at the 400m before making good late headway in final section.
Didn't show abundant pace and settled close to the tail between runners. Bumped at the 300m before rebalancing and then making some ground in final 250m.

Strode forward but was held out & raced three wide, before being left without cover nearing the 700m. Pushed 4 wide approaching the 600m. One length from lead at 400m but peaked at 250m and tired last furlong.

Had no early speed & was shifted back behind runners after start. Shuffled to the tail of the field in middle section. Moved out wider on cornering before hanging in passing the 300m. Rider reported uncomfortable in action.

Hard ridden and strode forward early before being crossed at 900m and settling behind leading pair. Shifted three wide at the 600m. Was still prominent in chasing pack before being over-run in last 150m.
Showed pace early before easing back and settling in midfield between runners. Was less than 3 lengths from lead at 400m but peaked last 150m and was soundly held.

Steadied after the start and eased back behind runners near the tail. Moved away from the rail approaching the 600m, before cornering 4 lengths from lead. Stayed close to rail in straight but didn't give anything last 250m.
Showed customary early speed to come across from outside barrier to be outside leader passing the 900m. Laid out on cornering before weakening out over final 300m.

Slow to begin & subsequently settled near the rear of the field on the rail. Improved gradually into midfield before coming under pressure and beginning to yield ground passing the 600m. Blood in trachea post-race.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 5 to 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out near 650M, checked early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter and scored.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, took the lead near 250M, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the first two.
Lifted its front feet off the ground at the start and began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, headed near 250M, kept on well to the line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear running until passing 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from near 1200M, moved a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and made contact, recovered to race outside the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from 300M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made nice ground and ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Urged and settled to race outside the lead, worked home solidly for 2nd.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, kept on only to be headed by the others approaching final 50M.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, continued on well to the line despite laying out in the straight.
In box-seat, sat 3L off, ran on but never saved ground on the leaders.
Raced just in front of midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on till 150M.
Taken back to be at the rear, 3 wide but with cover, saved ground and closed off fairly.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved slightly only.
Asked along, raced prominently but trapped wide, found no extra at 250M.
Sat behind midfield, along the rail, was one paced.
In one-off one-back, 3-3/4L off, run ended at 300M. (Mucus in trachea)
Eased to be in behind midfield, 3 wide, saved no ground and was eased down at 200M.(Lame left front)
Awkward start, remained at the tail, never a factor.
At rear, never improved.
Moderate start, ridden early to recover to midfield, travelled keenly in the slow pace around the bend, responded well under pressure in the final 200 metres to snatch victory near the line.
Jumped fairly, gradually improved to 4th just over 2L off the pace, nearer the lead entering home straight, soon came to challenge after straightening, fought on dourly to snatch second late.

Ridden positively from a wide gate, restrained outside the slow pace-setter rounding home bend, amongst the leaders on straightening, hampered before hitting the front 100 metres out, but only to be caught close to finish.
Towards rear before taking closer order out wide rounding home bend, carried wider by the winner passing the 700 metres, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Close up from a wide gate settling one out one back, had to shift off heels 600 metres out due to the slow pace, hit the front passing the 300 metres but shifted in and had to be straightened 200 metres out, swamped 100 metres out.
Failed to muster, remained in last few to the straight, fought on to be nearest at finish.
Began well but soon dropped to midfield, dropped further back rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back after a tight run at the start, reached last 1000 metres out, awkwardly placed behind runners on the rail entering home straight, only ran on past well-beaten horses late.
Moderate start, towards the rear in back straight, made short-lived effort along the rail rounding home bend, found no extra in home straight.
Held slender lead in a dawdling pace, raced awkwardly under constraint around the bend, soon headed upon straightening, looked beaten when badly checked over 200 metres out
Dropped in behind leaders, travelled strongly, came through down center of track and took over nearing 100M, eased off close home when well in control.
Bumped on jumping, settled in midfield, stayed on well final 400M but couldn't reel in the winner.
Outpaced early, settled last 5-6Ls off the pace, made good progress final 300M when switched across to center of track, got up for 3rd late stages.
Fast into stride, up with early pace, took up lead from halfway, responded well under pressure, headed near 100M but kept fighting, edged out to 4th close home.
Bumped on jumping, towards the rear and not hurried early stages, 11th at 400M, ran on steadily for 5th.
Began awkwardly, 3Ls back in mid-division, ran on final 400M without threatening leaders.
Up with early pace, 2nd at 400M, battled at same pace under pressure, no extra close home.
Away well to be tracking leaders on settling, couldn't quicken when asked passing 400M, beaten at 150M. (Jockey unable to explain for its poor run.)
Settled near rear along the stands' rail, 12th at 400M, stayed on past weakened rivals only, never reached contention.
Began awkwardly, settled towards the rear 4-5Ls behind leader, didn't quite finish off when driven out inside 400M.
Up with early leaders, outpaced passing 400M, soon out of contention.
From draw 14 rolled along the stand's rail to be just off the pace, found little when pace quickened halfway, soon weakened away.
Close up early stages, dropped away 500M, weakened rapidly.
Sped forward, stayed prominent on the outside of group until halfway mark, didn't run on and weakened rapidly latter stages.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, hung in and unbalanced near 800M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, 2 wide from near 800M, a length or so back turning in, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden from 550M, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Stumbled at start, positioned on rail in midfield, hampered near 800M, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced wide at rear early, found a 2 wide spot near 700M, very wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, got cover from near 700M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, detached from the main group after 1000M, still well back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.

Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, bumped near 700M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear running until passing 200M, finished off very strongly thereafter to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail after passing 1000M, angled out near 650M, no clear running early in straight, closed off well to make frame.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, angled out from near 700M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, bumped near 700M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, took the early lead, 2 wide, headed near 1000M, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked after passing 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out near 550M, finished off evenly. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 4-1/2L back turning in, brushed early in straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1000M, travelled well on turn, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled well to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, unable to slot in early, trapped 4 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight.

Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but could not hold off the winner.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind on turn, kept on well to the line, missed 3rd on line.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped start, raced at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at tail, 12 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (Bled.)
Average to begin, raced wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 350M, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, raced keenly, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, took cover, trapped 2-3 wide, no dash.
Very slow away, took rail at back, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
At back, checked early, sat 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, never improved.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 400M.
Urged to race inside the lead on rail, responded solidly when asked for effort, scored unchallenged.
Settled in handy position, gained ground passing 150M, finished strongly.
Settled in front of midfield, very wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Raced midfield, wide on straightening, gained nice ground passing 150M, finished well.
Travelled midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, worked home OK.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to lead in one-off position, gave ground passing 100M.
Hard ridden but failed to muster speed, traveled only fairly behind midfield, rider concern its action, must trial.
Settled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Ridden along to race behind leaders, tried hard but gave ground near 150M.
Taken back at start, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, always back, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, raced greenly, brushed running rail and became badly unbalanced passing the 600M, never in it.

Began well and strode forward, crossed to rail when leading approaching the 1200m. Challenged for the lead past the 650m before breaking clear on cornering. Fought bravely last 100m after fast middle sections.

Crowded at the start before shifting behind runners settling near the tail. Moved three wide passing the 750m, pushed wider still passing the 400m. Cornered 4.5 lengths from lead before making significant ground in straight.

Slow to begin before ridden up to maintain midfield position. Improved close to heels at the 450m. Conceded 5 lengths at the 400m, before cornering close to the rail and making good ground in final section.
Tightened and checked in early stages before settling midfield between runners. Moved three wide approaching the 600m before cornering the second widest. Made good headway in last 300m.

Settled in midfield on the rail. Was only 3.5L from lead at the 800m before drifting back approaching the turn. Shifted out & raced tight at the 300m. Made good late ground between runners over final 75m under little riding.

Showed early pace to stride forward before shifting across to be outside the leader passing the 1200m. Headed and passed on the outside at the 700m. Raced behind leading pair on the corner before peaking at the 100m.
Crowded at the start before shifting across into midfield away from the rail. Raced tight passing the 300m before shifting out shortly after and finishing off fairly final 200m.

Crowded at the start before easing across to race at the tail. Continued to rail at the rear, 8L from the lead passing the 800m. Moved wider approaching the corner and made steady ground from rearward position in final 300m.
Had no early speed & shifted across towards the rail after 150m. Shuffled back to last passing the 700m. Conceded 9 lengths at the 400m when a clear last before halving that margin in final section.

Strode forward three wide around midfield in first section. Ridden forward approaching the 750m and worked very hard outside leader before challenging for lead at 600m. Hard ridden passing 400m and tired out last section.
Ridden forward after the start before positioning behind leading pair away from the rail. Three lengths from lead at the 400m but didn't finish off in last 300m.
Crowded shortly after start but recovered to hold position on the leaders back after 400m. Ridden hard passing the 450m and weakened out from the 250m.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1400M, sat 3L behind the leader on rail thereafter, angled out near 800M, improved from 450M, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly and scored.
Commenced well, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd on line.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, taken very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.

Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 1400M, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader thereafter, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, no cover from near 1300M, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, peaked turning in, bumped and unbalanced near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Shift out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1300M, travelled well to turn, challenged by rivals turning in, bumped and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden from 500M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider near 750M, hard ridden on turn, bumped early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, taken back to race behind midfield, 7 lengths back, improved on turn, weakened early in straight.
At the rear along the rail, closed off nicely inside final 150M to score by a neck.
Sent forward and shared lead along the rail, emptied late but hung onto 2nd.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, showed good dashes early and ran on well for 3rd.
At the tail along the rail, closed off well despite unable to be properly tested late.
Slotted in to race in midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and continued on well to the line.
Sat just behind midfield, along the rail, made minor inroad in straight.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, made ground and ran on.
Sat one-off one-back, kept on until flattened at 150M.
In box-seat, 2-1/2L off along the rail, pushed from 700M, emptied after 150M.
Sent forward, shared lead 2 wide, gave ground on straightening.
Broke well, led on the rails setting quick middle sectionals, just over 1L clear entering home straight, kept on before tiring inside the final 100 metres but just held on.

Began well settling in midfield or slightly worse, about 4L back in 7th most of the wayvin back straight, went wide turning for home, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres but just failed to get up on line.
Slightly slowly away, settled in midfield in 6th on the rail within 4L of the pace, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily down the inside without threatening.

Taken back to the rear for rails run, one from last rounding stables bend before gaining one closer in back straight, commenced move turning in but did not find much room until after the 100 metres, finished off the race well.

Ridden positively from the widest gate of 10, travelled wide without cover in midfield rounding first bend, remained wide despite improving to 4th just over 2L back, kept on steadily without quickening.

Moderate start, shared early pace, taken back to 4th nearly 3L back rounding first bend, became 5th in a similar position at the 800 metres, bumped shortly after straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Pressed forward from a wide gate racing wide around the first bend, settled 1L back 2-wide travelling down back straight, found no extra inside the final 250 metres.
Taken back for cover early stages, remained at rear most of the way before dropping to last on final bend, made no impression in the run home.
Moderate start, settled not far off the pace in 3rd on the rail, remained similar to home turn, soon weakened under pressure.
Ridden but failed to muster and soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Settled ahead of midfield in a fast run race, quickened up well passing 300M, strongly challenged leader final 100M to share the spoils.
Quickly into stride, led at fast pace, held 1L lead on straightening, joined by rival final 100M, dug deep to force a dead heat at the line.
Taken back from wide draw, settled 2nd last in a fast run race, 6Ls off the pace 400M, closed off well for 3rd but couldn't get to first 2.
Restrained to race near the rear, in 10th spot 5-6Ls off the fast pace, awkwardly placed top of straight, checked 250M, switched lane and closed off strongly, just missed 3rd.
Held up behind midfield along the fence, 8th at 400M, kept on steadily on straightening but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Began awkwardly, took up a midfield spot on the inside, 6th on settling, driven along 400M, only battled away at same speed.
Dropped back to the rear as expected, 7Ls off the fast pace middle stages, made some ground on straightening but never reached contention.
From draw 11 unable to get closer than 3-wide, behind midfield 8th on settling, ran on moderately over final 300M, never threatened.
Caught wide no cover early stages, strode closer to leaders passing 1100M but remained wide throughout the trip, kept in touch until faded 250M.
Held up in mid-division, 4Ls off leader in a fast run race, wide into straight, couldn't muster speed to be closer.
Driven forward from widest draw, chased leader in a fast run race, battled on same pace early straight, no extra final 200M.
Bustled along after the start, stayed prominent behind leaders in a fast run race, gave ground passing 500M, quickly dropped out of contention.

Gathered early pace before easing into second away from the rail. Joined on the outside passing the 700m before striding forward to challenge lead at the 450m. Assumed lead in final 200m before drawing away impressively.
Began fast from wide barrier before striding across to assume lead after 200m. Crossed to rail approaching the 850m. First to corner and held the lead until last 200m before fighting on bravely late.

Shifted across behind runners after the start and the tail after 200m. Stayed close to the rail in middle stages. Conceded 5 lengths at the 400m and made good ground along the rail in the final section.

Slow to begin and subsequently settled near the tail. Improved position in middle section before making further ground approaching corner. Four lengths from lead entering final section and made ground but perhaps not suited.
Bumped and race tight at the start before gathering speed to race on leaders back in middle section. Moved away from the rail on cornering before peaking at the 100m.

Ridden forward but couldn't go early speed and settled three wide near the rear. Continued to cover additional ground and cornered very wide before making late ground in final section after conceding considerable start.

Bumped & unbalanced at the start before settling worse than midfield away from the rail. Shuffled back to last, 6L from lead at 800m. Presented with clear running after cornering & made some ground between runners final 300m.
Bumped heavily and veered in at the start consequently settling worse than midfield on the rail. Stayed close to rail on cornering before peaking 250m and giving some ground in last 200m.

Bumped heavily after the start before gathering speed to stride forward three wide. Continued to race wide and improve position, joining leaders near the 550m. Came under pressure at the 400m and weakened out final section.
Began fairly before showing early speed to be prominent behind leading pair. Eased passing the 850m and shifted closer to rail. Ridden-up from the 450m before tiring out in final 300m.

Hard ridden after the start but raced four horses wide outside the leaders for the first 600m. Eased back passing midway but continued to race extremely wide. Lost position approaching the 400m and tired out in the run home.

Began well but couldn't hold position in first 200m and raced in midfield. Ridden-up to hold position in middle section. Drifted back and conceded over 5 lengths at the 400m before continuing to give ground in final section.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well in straight and scored.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, still 6 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, positioned in midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, raced in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take 4th. (Lost left front plate.)

Clean jump from gate 1, raced at rear on rail, 8 to 9 lengths back, 2 wide from near 1100M, bumped 1000M, still well back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, bumped near 1000M, 9 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9 to 10 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, hard ridden turning in, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M.
Moderately away, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
At back, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, closed off strongly when clear and score.
Slow away, at back, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Shared the lead at fast sectionals, ran on well until 50M overhauled.
Midfield, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Just off the leaders, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in final stages
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, made some ground 300M.
At rear, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
At back, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Slow away, at rear, suited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Shared the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Pressed forward, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Began only fairly, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, settled midfield, quickened passing 300M, came line strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 550M, quickened passing 200M, worked home solidly.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield, niggled passing 700M, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, responded nicely in the straight, finished well.
Raced at rear on rail, gained some ground in the straight, worked home OK.
Began awkwardly and raced at back, battled hard in the straight, made some ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made up some late ground.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced detached in the early stages, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Hard ridden from wide barrier then took lead passing 1000M, gave ground passing 200M.
Raced wide and without cover then passing 900M improved to outside the lead, faded out near 250M, failed to run on.
Slow out then was crowded, raced midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Ridden to race in box seat, weakened badly passing 300M.
Raced in front of midfield, came under pressure passing 600M, in the straight weakened noticeably, must trial.

Showed speed to share lead early before being crossed near the 900m. Raced close to heels near the 650m before shifting around heels at the 375m. Joined lead before the 200m and strong to line late stages.

Hard ridden early to gain prominent position before racing forward of midfield but three wide until the 600m. Was 2.5L from lead on cornering before shifting out last 100m but finishing well. Blood in trachea post-race.

Had no early speed, shifted across behind runners worse than midfield. Raced three-wide with cover near the rear before moving 4 wide on cornering. Conceded 4 lengths at the 400m but finished off hard down center of track.

One of the last into stride but held rail position and made ground into midfield after 200m. Shifted away from the rail on cornering, conceded 3.5 lengths at 400m before finishing off well in last 250m.
Began well before being passed early and settling in midfield away from rail. Shifted out wider after straightening before making very good closing ground in final 250m.
Stayed away from the rail in early stages before striding forward between runners, 2.75L from lead at 800m. Was making ground inside the final 100m before being hampered and losing clear running.

Bumped on jumping and consequently shifted back and across behind runners after 200m. Raced worse than midfield around 5 lengths from lead at 800m. Raced tight near the 150m before finishing of pretty well in late stages.

Eased after the start before shifting across and racing one pair from the tail. Was near enough to last, 6 lengths from lead on cornering. Shifted out wider on the track on cornering before making steady ground in final section.

Began awkwardly before gathering speed to stride forward into second place without cover. Travelled strongly approaching turn, shared lead at 300m, before peaking at 250m and tiring out. Overreach wound left heel post-race.
Was very slow to begin and shifted across behind runners, settling last on the rail. Shifted away from the rail on cornering and passed a few in late stages but never a threat from back in field.

Began well before being restrained after 150m and coming across and racing three wide in midfield. Continued to race wide with cover in middle section. Shifted out wider on cornering but tired out shortly after.

Showed speed before being crossed after 300m and racing better than midfield, two lengths from lead at 800m. Was ridden-up approaching the corner and stayed close to rail but peaked inside final 250m and tired thereafter.

Steadied after start and shifted behind runners, settling second from last away from the rail. Moved out 3 wide passing the 700m before cornering the widest runner 6 lengths from lead. Could only maintain margin final 400m.
Bumped on jumping before gathering speed to challenge for lead. Came across to the rail at the 900m when leading. One length clear on cornering but packed up in last section, well beaten.
Made contact on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from near 1000M, improved after passing 550M, finished off strongly to score by a head.

Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on well thereafter, but could not hold off the winner late. (Lost right front plate.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear final 150M.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed near 300M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer on turn, finished off evenly. (Mucus in trachea.)
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Sent forward to take rail and led, ran on comfortably to score by 1-3/4L.
Settled to race in the box-seat, battled on nicely to take 2nd.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off gamely to take 3rd.
Jumped smartly, raced in front of midfield along the rail, continued on well to the line.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Sat just behind midfield, 2 wide, ran on to the line.
Eased and raced at the rear, along the rail, was one paced. (Lame right hind)
Jumped slowly, recovered in behind midfield along the rail, made no ground.
Missed start, remained at the tail, never threatened.
Eased and raced at the rear, 2 wide, did not feature.
Settled behind the midfield from a wide draw, travelling keenly before commenced run halfway out to take up running on top of home bend kicking nearly 3L clear 150 metres out, won readily.
Settled in midfield some 7L off the speed, became last few when pace quickened coming onto home bend, ran on well inside the final 300 metres but never threatening.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, became last coming onto home bend, did not find much room early in straight, finished off the race well inside the final 150 metres for distant 3rd.

Broke well, soon taken back to 3rd just over 2L off the pace, became 5th in a similar position coming onto home bend, came under pressure entering home straight but did not find much room early on, fought on nicely.
Amongst the leaders on the rail early, ceded lead to track the leader approaching back straight, 1L back in joint 2nd turning for home, unable to sustain effort shortly after straightening.

Settled at the back, commenced move half out making swift progress around the field to reach 2L 4th 3-wide on top of home bend, shared 2nd on straightening but unable to sustain effort 150 metres out.
Began well, settled in distant 4th some 5L off the pace in back straight, became 7th in a similar position on the rail coming onto home bend, failed to quicken under pressure in the run to the line.

Began well from the one gate settling in rear of midfield some 7L off the pace in back straight, drifted further back to last on the rail coming onto home bend, ran on past beaten horses inside the final 100 metres.
Settled in last few, carried wide rounding home bend, made no impression in home straight.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate, gradually shifted towards the rear 3-wide, steady headway to reach midfield halfway out, just over 2L back in 5th upon straightening, soon faded.
Worked his way from a wide gate to take up running on top of the first bend, led until headed by eventual winner 700 metres out, kept on before fading from 1L 3rd into home straight.
Rolled forward from draw 1 to lead from 1300M, pressed by rival 600M, skipped clear top of the straight, still 2Ls clear 150M, eased off late just lasted home over the fast finishing 2nd.
Steadied early stages for cover, settled 2nd last 8Ls off the pace, held up for clear running early straight, motored home from 300M, just held.
From wide draw urged forward, caught 3-wide no cover outside leaders, kept chasing the eventual winner from top of straight but was always held, lost 2nd 60M.
Sat just behind the leading trio, battled on same pace over final 400M, couldn't get closer.
Eased back and held up in detached last 10Ls off the pace, progressed steadily against inside rail on straightening but no threat to first 3.
Restrained in midfield 5Ls behind leaders, bustled along 600M, stayed on fairly over final 400M, never able to challenge.
Held up 3-wide towards the rear of midfield, widest into straight, passed a few but never likely.
Jumped on terms, held up towards the rear, 6Ls off leader home turn, wide into straight, kept on same pace not making much progress.
Began well, restrained to race ahead of midfield, driven out 450M, plugged away without improving.
Chased leader, came under pressure 550M, out of contention early straight, weakened final 300M.
Slightly slow out, settled towards the rear along the fence, peeled out 500M, couldn't finish off.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, couldn't go on from 350M, struggled from there.
Began awkwardly, took up midfield spot along the inside, hampered by weakening rival 500M, no extra turning home, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Placing: PU
Comment: Began only fairly, improved to be 5th on settling, gave ground passing 600M, eased top of straight. (Collapsed after 200M.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight and scored by a length.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, moved closer after passing 1200M, a length or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner. (Lost left hind plate.)
Clean jump, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on rail, 2 wide from near 1000M, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide at rear, improved after passing 1100M, 3 wide in midfield on turn, finished off evenly.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, hampered near 1400M, positioned 6 to 7 lengths behind on rail thereafter, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle after passing 1400M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.

Stood flat-footed as the start and lost a considerable amount of ground, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle after passing 1400M, still last turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide turning, taken wide early in straight, failed to make any progress.
Shifted in abruptly on jumping, taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, 3 wide, 6 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1000M, found rail at 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Began well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1000M and allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 7 lengths back at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 2 wide from near 700M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening. (Lost right front plate.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.

Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3W, 2W from near 850M, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, inconvenienced near 1200M, difficult to settle thereafter, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 250M, made no progress thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 8 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, hampered early, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out from near 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.

Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide in midfield, slightly improved after passing 1000M, no cover throughout, 2 lengths or so back turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out near 500M, closed off well to take a place.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 900M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail near 700M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, difficult to settle early, raced 3 wide at rear, awkwardly placed off heels near 750M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to may any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Steadied shortly after start, difficult to settle, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Slightly slow out and made contact, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, benefited by the slow pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, took rail behind midfield, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back took rail, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Eased at start, 2 wide, made early move 800M but trapped 4 wide, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, made early move 600M but trapped 4 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, checked 450M whilst weakening.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied 500M.
Jumped well, settled in front of midfield, continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home solidly to score.
Raced outside the lead, commenced to improve passing 400M, made up nice late ground, just missed by Neck.
Ridden to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, worked home nicely.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield, made some ground passing 100M.
Urged to settle in box seat, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, tried to improve near 400M, finished one-paced.
Raced at rear, near 1000M was left racing wide and without cover then steadied to obtain cover, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Slow out then bumped heavily with a runner and became unbalanced, after that taken back, limited response, lame right front after racing.
Taken back at start, always back, no response in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, lay out in the middle stages, still green, never in it.
Travelled midfield, fought hard but failed to run on.
At start bumped heavily with a runner and became unbalanced, then failed to muster speed despite ridden along and raced back, near 900M was left racing wide and without cover, weakened near 150M.

Positioned on rail behind leader after 200m. Improved quickly away from the rail nearing 400m before sprinting hard once balanced. Joined lead at 250m and cleared away in final 200m despite hanging in.
Began well before getting great position away from rail one pair behind leaders. Moved up three wide on cornering before finishing off well last section despite being no match for winner.
Bumped at the start before getting midfield position on rail. Had clear running after straightening and made steady ground before shifting in at 150m when improving.

Began well before striding across into midfield away from the rail. Pushed three and then four wide on the corner when making ground. Conceded 3 lengths at the 400m and maintained that margin in final section.

Not bustled after the start and raced in second last pair away from rail. Moved three wide passing the 350m but conceded nearly 6 lengths at that point. Shifted out wider on straightening and closed very well in last 250m.

Ridden forward after the start to improve position into midfield away from the rail. Hard ridden from the 400m when conceding over 4 lengths, before finishing off evenly despite laying in over final 200m.

Wasn't fast away and settled worse than midfield. Moved away from the rail on cornering before shifting out near the 200m when disappointed for clear run. Not tested last 100m when racing close to heels.
Crowded for room on jumping before shifting back behind runners shortly after. Moved out wider near the 400m when 7 lengths from lead before cornering very wide. Only maintained margin last 300m.

Wasn't fast away but was hard ridden from the start to improve from rearward position around field before getting outside the leader near the 700m. Shared lead on corner before tiring out last 250m after torrid run.

Showed speed to hold the early lead before headed after 200m. Held the rail position before being crossed neat the 600m. Stayed close to the rail on after cornering before peaking on effort at the 200m and tiring late.

Showed speed before getting the lead after 200m but racing away from the rail. Eventually crossed to the rail at the 600m after working hard early. Joined on the lead at the 250m and tired out final 200m.
Shifted ground after start before easing across behind runners and settling at the tail. Was a clear last when cornering in and didn't make up any of the margin in final section.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 7 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail after passing 700M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Asked to be in the box-seat, 2-1/4L off at 800M, fought on gamely and hung on to score by 1/2L.
In midfield, 2 wide, held up at home turn, then showed good kick from 200M, battled on to finish 1/2L behind.
In front of midfield, but trapped wide throughout, stayed on well to take 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, continued on strongly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced in midfield along the rail, closed off fairly inside final 100M.
Sent forward to take rail and led, flattened and headed by winner at 150M.
Failed to muster, tapped wide in behind midfield, made ground steadily.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground.
In front of midfield, about 4L off the lead, emptied passing 200M.
Eased back, at rear along the rail, did not improve.
In midfield along the rail, showed nothing.
At rear, 2 wide, did not close off in the straight. Was disappointing, must trial.
Ridden along from a middle gate to soon take up running, held slender advantage just outside the 2nd, drew clear inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden along in first few, settled one-out-one-back in 3rd to home straight, kept on steadily to reach 2nd inside the 200 metres.
Settled 3-wide in midfield, drifted further back leaving the Rock, finished off the race from last few into the straight, did best work late.
Settled behind midfield, ran on under pressure without threatening.
Moderate start, recovered along the rail before settling inside the leader, weakened over 200 metres out.
Settled in midfield, swung wide into the straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Travelled wide in midfield early stages before ridden forward to 3L 4th nearer the rail approaching home bend, slightly worse in 5th entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Prominent, drifted back to just over 3L back in 4th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on without quickening.
Settled in rear, never seen with a chance.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to the straight, never nearer.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, made no impression.
Chased leader in a fast run race, bustled along 500M, wrestled the lead near 200M, held on well closing stages.
Eased back to be last 7Ls off the fast pace, ran on strongly into 2nd passing 100M, just couldn't peg back the winner.
Given a patient ride near the rear, 6Ls off the fast pace on settling, angled out into clear 200M, came with a strong late run to take 3rd.
From draw 1 stayed close to the pace throughout, 3rd at 400M, kept battling to the line but always held by leaders.
Settled behind midfield 5Ls off the fast pace, into clear 250M, kept working to the line, not reached leaders.
Guided to a midfield spot along the inside, 4Ls off the fast pace, finished off steadily without threatening leaders, even effort.
Positively ridden, crossed to the lead 1200M, led fast, headed 250M, faded towards the line.
From widest draw taken across behind runners, settled towards the rear 5-6Ls back, failed to respond when asked, battled on at same pace over final 300M.
Jumped on terms, restrained to race in midfield along the 3-path, bought wide into straight, couldn't quicken, just plugged away.
From draw 11 unable to cross, caught 4-wide no cover throughout, found no extra final 300M.
Held up midfield, scrubbed along home turn, failed to run on.
Chased leaders along the 3-path, wide no cover throughout, gave ground passing 500 to finish last. (Lame next day.)
