Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, awkwardly placed turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, checked shortly thereafter, raced 7 lengths back at rear, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, slightly improved from 600M, 3/4L back turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Average to begin, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 300M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on rail, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and made some headway without threatening.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, one-paced thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, in traffic early in straight, finished off one-pace when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, showed good speed to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, angled out near 650M, peaked turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from 1100M, carried wider and made contact near 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, sat outside the leader from 1100M, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, commenced to buck shortly after start, dropped out of contention thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped on jumping, checked shortly thereafter, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths back, difficult to settle after passing 1000M, same margin back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong. (Bled.)
Eased back, 2 wide, made early move 600M to take advantages of the slow pace, kicked away 400M to score with ease.
Settled just off the leader in 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, held ground for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up with the field, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Pushed early, took rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, held up 500M, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Took rail easily and led at advantageous slow sectionals, however soon emptied 400M.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled nicely, responded solidly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Jumped well, urged to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, finished strongly.
Hard ridden after start, near 800M was hampered when crowded for room, then raced in front of midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Shortly after the start was hampered, settled midfield on rail, passing 200M shifted in on a number of horses to obtain clear running, gained ground passing 100M.
Jumped sharply, settled in handy position, near 850M was inconvenienced, fought hard, gave ground near 50M.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, passing 600M lay out, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, one-paced when being tested.
Urged along to race behind leaders, took rail near 700M, weakened passing 150M.
Moderate start, raced midfield on rail, near 700M gave ground despite being ridden along, limited response in the straight.
Shortly after the start was hampered, raced at back, near 250M shifted out abruptly away from heels, no response in the straight.
Settled at back on rail, always back, never in it.
Ridden to race in front of midfield, faded out near 250M, failed to run on.
Became fractious and reared in barriers, then began awkwardly and lost ground, never in it, must trial.
Mustered early speed to assume lead after 50m. Was half a length clear on cornering before responding strongly when challenged passing the 250m. Broke clear last 100m.
Began fast, settled outside the leader. Was close enough on cornering and tried valiantly entire length of straight but couldn't get to leader.
Had nice position on leaders back throughout early and middle sections. Travelled strongly on cornering before moving around heels at the 300m. Looked prominent before peaking at the 200m.

Strode across after the start before drifting back into midfield and three wide passing the 1100m. Shifted out wider on cornering and conceded 6 lengths at this point before making up some ground in final 400m.
Strode across from widest barrier before settling in midfield but three wide with cover. Continued to cover ground in middle sections before running home evenly in the final section.
Settled midfield between runners, eased away slightly passing the 900m when racing close to heels. Was 5 lengths from lead after cornering and maintained that margin to the line.
One of the last into stride before gathering speed and railing along into midfield after 200m. Stayed close to the rail in the final section but failed to make any ground up in last 300m.
Slow to begin before making some ground to settle in midfield on the rail passing the 900m. Stayed close to rail but drifted over 6 lengths from lead at 400m before maintaining that margin late.

Began well before drifting back after the start, settling near the rear. Hung outwards passing the 700m and covered additional ground in middle section. Cornered as the widest runner before working home evenly in last 300m.
Ridden forward after the start but tramped three wide without cover in middle sections. Was around 3.5 lengths from lead on the corner before peaking shortly after and tiring last 300m.

Was very slow to begin and subsequently settled at the tail of the field. Was making ground passing the 300m when steadied away from heels. Hung in passing the 200m and continued to be restricted for room in late stages.
Began only moderately before gathering speed and positioning forward of midfield between runners. Hard ridden approaching the turn before weakening out in final 200m.
Shifted back behind runners from and settled second from last away from the rail. Moved out wider on the track approaching the turn but never really featured in final section.

Shifted back behind runners after the start and settled at the tail. Raced close to the rail in middle section. Looked to improve from rearward position but was unlucky in last 300m (see racing incidents).
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.

Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, awkwardly placed near 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, improved after passing 550M, took the lead near 300M but shortly headed thereafter, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, bumped shortly after start, raced 9 lengths back at rear, moved closer on turn but still 6 lengths back, passed a few tired runners in straight but still beaten a long way.

Average to begin, positioned 5 to 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear final 200M.
Began smartly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, improved from 500M, very wide turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, restrained after entering the back straight to sit 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, raced tight and carried wider after passing 600M, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 1000M, wider turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Shifted out on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Began well, took the early lead, headed near 1300M, retook the lead after entering the back straight, led by 2 lengths on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)

Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1300M, restrained after entering the back straight to allow the rival to take the lead, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, held up early but ran on nicely to score by 1/2L.
In midfield, wide but with cover, kept going and held off challenge for 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield, 2 wide, battled on gamely to finish 1/2L behind in 3rd place.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly late.
In worse than midfield, 2-3 wide when rounding turn, continued on well to the line.
Raced at the rear, 2 wide, didn't settle, made ground despite bumped at 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, along the rail, bumped at 200M, saved ground.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, showed dashes early and ran on fairly to the line.
About midfield initially but wide, improved at 700M, showed nothing in the straight.
In front of midfield, along the rail, was one paced.
Sent forward to take rail and led, weakened out gradually from 300M.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, never improved.
Raced in the box-seat, emptied passing 200M.
At the rear and wide throughout, never a factor.
Began well from a middle gate, settled just off the pace in 5th, switched in for a clear run inside the 300 metres, ran on under pressure to hit the front 50 metres out.
Jumped well, settled in midfield, came under pressure inside the 300 metres holding every chance until outsprinted nearing finish.
Hampered at the start and soon dropped to last few, ran on under pressure inside the final 200 metres to narrowly miss 2nd.
Jumped fairly, led or disputed lead to the 100 metres, found no extra.
Broke well, settled in rear of midfield, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind, commenced move at the centre of the track after the halfway mark, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Soon dropped the rear, made short-lived effort inside the 300 metres, faded 100 metres out.

Very slowly away, soon recovered to rear of midfield about 3L off the pace, came under pressure coming onto course proper improving to within 2L of pace 100 metres out, unable to sustain effort nearing finish.
Showed early speed to cross from a low draw to dispute the lead near stands rails, lost touch inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon came to stalk the leaders, gained even closer passing the 400 metres but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Close up, faded steadily from 200 metres out.
Moderate start, soon dropped to the rear of midfield on stands rails, dropped further back despite reminders over halfway out.
Began well from draw 1, restrained to race in mid-division, travelled strongly, quickened to lead 300M, kept finding to the line holding pursuers at bay.
Held up in midfield 4Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inner, chased hard over final 400M to claim 2nd near the line.
Close up behind leaders, ideally placed to strike leaving the bend, lacked winner's acceleration but refused to give in when headed, raced tight closing stages and lost 2nd near line.
Taken back from draw 13, caught 3-wide towards the rear, crept closer from 650M, ran well final 200M to just miss 3rd.
Began only fairly, restrained to race behind midfield, travelled well into straight, chased solidly behind leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, settled towards the rear, 13th spot making the turn, swung wide 600M, stayed on moderately.
Switched off after the start, raced in last on settling and 10Ls off the pace at 800M, chased on steadily between runners, made some ground but not threatening first few.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, plugged away in the straight, never reach contention.
Taken back from wide draw, settled towards the rear along the inside, stayed on fairly final 400M, made no impression on leaders.
Went forward to be tracking leader, took over 500M, held position to 300M, effort levelled off there.
Caught 3-wide behind midfield, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, pushed along 500M, past a few beaten ones, no threat to leaders.
Keen early and restrained, caught wide no cover throughout the race, 7th at 400M, soon gave ground in the straight.
Quickly into stride, led to near 1100M, 4th at 400M, ran out of gas mid-straight, dropped away.
Pushed forward to be tracking leaders 2-wide, over-raced and took outright lead 1100M, under pressure 500M, soon no extra weakened to last.
Began smartly, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer on turn, took the lead near 500M, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Out in line, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, closed off well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line, just missed 3rd on line.
Away with them, taken back to race at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway early in straight, blocked near 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 850M, headed turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear running from 250M, not able to test properly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced very wide with no cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-1/2L behind on turn, awkwardly placed near 300M, weakened thereafter. (Lost right hind plate.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, finished last.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled well to turn, checked and carried wider near 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away with them, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide at rear, still well back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail shortly after entering the back straight, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, checked near 1200M, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 9 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out near 500M, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, still 10 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly, trapped very wide early, settled 3 wide with cover in midfield after entering the back straight, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1-3/4L back, lost position on turn and dropped out in straight.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.

Away with them, checked off heels shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1100M, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, hard ridden from 500M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Moderately away, bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length behind on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 1 off the fence from near 700M, 3 lengths back on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off one-pace.
Steadied on jumping, bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield in the early stages, found a 2 wide spot near 1100M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off one-pace.

Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, awkwardly placed after passing the winning post on the first occasion, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped 300M, failed to make progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, weakened from 750M, eased final 400M. (Finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.)
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear and scored only by a narrow margin.
Pushed to take the rail and led at good pace, pressured from 800M, hung on well until last stride.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M whilst hanging in.
Settled in front, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield along the fence, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, made early move 1000M to sit outside the leader, ran on until 150M emptied.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, out of fuel 250M.
Never competitive
Pushed hard to take lead, continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home strongly to score.
Ridden along to take box seat, asked for effort near 400M, finished strongly, missed by 1/2L.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield on rail, continued to make ground rounding the home turn, responded nicely in the straight, finished solidly, missed by 1/2L.
Hard ridden to race outside the lead, fought hard in the straight, shifted in when raced tight after 150M, finished nicely.
Raced behind midfield, improved passing 350M, worked home one-paced.
Hard ridden after start then steadied near 700M, settled midfield, shifted out to improve in the straight, finished OK.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Crowded after start, near 900M steadied away from heels, settled at back, always niggled, made some ground passing 200M.
Ridden to race one off one back, placed pressure passing 500M, limited response in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, always back, made up some ground in the straight.
Began only fairly, at 850M lost its left hind plate hind plate, settled at rear on rail, limited response in the straight.
Ridden forward after the start, crossed to rail in the lead near 850m. One length clear on turn, rallied hard final 200m to hold off challengers.
Began fast before easing behind leading pair after 200m. Raced close to rail in middle section & 3 lengths from lead at 400m. Switched around heals at the 250m before closing hard late to just miss.

Crowded on jumping before gathering speed to challenge for lead. Easing at 900m before positioning behind leader. Raced in restricted room passing the 250m when close to lead before shifting out & finishing evenly last 200m.
Position midfield on the rail, 4.5 lengths from lead at the 800m. Stayed close to inside on cornering before shifting out passing the 250m and making good late headway in final 150m.

Began well before being eased after 100m and shifting across into midfield away from rail. Five lengths from lead passing the 400m before shifting wider on cornering and making up a length or so in the straight.
Steadied after the start and settled second from last away from the rail. Conceded hefty margin on cornering before shifting out and making some ground in final 250m from rearward position.
Showed early speed to come across from outside barrier to position outside the leader passing the 800m. Moved up to challenge approaching the corner before peaking on effort at 150m and tiring late.
Didn't have much early speed and settled near the tail. Stayed close to the rail after cornering and passed a few but conceded too much ground to be a winning chance.
Began awkwardly losing ground and subsequently settled worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail on cornering but only maintained margin in straight.
Steadied after the start and shifted back to the tail of the field. Was ridden up passing the 450m when conceding 8 lengths and could make up the ground in final 400m to play a part.
Began well, raced in midfield away from rail. Was hard ridden passing the 400m and weakened out in the last section.

Steadied after the start before shifting across from outside barrier, racing three wide near the tail. Continued to cover additional ground without cover in middle stages before yielding ground from the 400m.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved closer after passing 700M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Drifted back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 1300M, angled out after passing 700M, 3 wide turning, closed off well to take a place.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn but still 6 lengths behind, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, 3 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, weakened early in straight. (Mucus in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, ran home gamely to score by 1-1/4L.
Forward to take the rail and led, battled on spiritedly to hold onto 2nd.
Eased to be at rear, 2 wide, closed off very strongly inside final 100M.
Bumped start, then eased and found cover in about midfield, on rail at turns, ran on.
In midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Raced in one-off one-back position, emptied at 150M. (See Racing Incident Report)
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, run ended when steadied at 200M.
Raced in the box-seat, kept on till 100M. (Bled)
At the tail, along the rail, saved ground.
Jumped fairly only, in worse than midfield on rail, one paced, but was checked away from heels in final 50M.
Bumped start, just behind midfield, 2 wide, one paced and weakened late. (Mucus in trachea)
In front of midfield, wide and without cover, gave ground from home turn.
Travelled just worse than midfield in 9th, commenced move rounding home bend swinging widest into the straight, ran on well near the centre of the track to prevail in closing stages.

Amongst the leaders early, settled two back in 4th coming onto first bend, commenced move rounding final bend, hit the front under pressure inside the 200 metres only to be worn down shortly afterward.
Settled in last few, switched wide into home straight, ran on well under pressure without threatening.

Broke well and 4-wide with the leaders early stages, settled 1L back in 2nd in back straight, hit the front from weakening leader over 450 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed inside final 200 metres.
Travelled keenly at times in midfield, not far off turning into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.

Settled in midfield on the rail after beginning from a wide gate, in similar position turning into home straight, shaken up upon straightening but was held up early on, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled well back from the widest gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, hampered over 200 metres out, sustained progress final stages without threatening.
Settled at the back from a wide draw, trailed the field to straight, saved ground turning in, ran past well-beaten horses.
Broke well from the one draw sharing early pace, taken back to track the leader coming onto back straight, weakened noticeably inside the final 400 metres.
Niggled at early before settling in 5th some 4L off the pace, travelled 3-wide without cover down back straight and around final bend, dropped out tamely after straightening.

Broke well, settled in forward of midfield in 6th on the rail, became 5th when pace slackened going up the Rock, inconvenienced early in home straight and soon faded. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Vied for lead early eventually assuming the leader's role on the rail on top of stables bend, held position until weakening over 450 metres out.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, settled midfield, on straightening stuck to the inside and stayed on strongly, led near 150M, kept on to win well.
Jumped well, restrained in midfield about 4Ls off the good pace, worked home well from 300M and pushed winner all the way to the line.
Slow to begin, recovered to race behind midfield, responded well turning home, had to shift out for clear running mid-straight, made up good late ground to snatch 3rd near line.
Began only fairly, held up in midfield, bought wide from 400m and ran on well, shifted in under pressure 200M, lost 3rd close home. (Jockey questioned re his riding over concluding stages.)
From wide draw eased back to the rear, 7Ls behind leader 400M, closed off fastest but had too much to make up. (Jockey fined for weighing in 2 lbs heavy.)
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settled in 9th 5Ls off the good pace, shifted widest to challenge in straight, chased on well final 200M but never seriously threatened.
Caught wide early stages, pressed on to track leader 2-wide, loomed up 250 and looked a real chance, peaked on run 150M and faded towards the line.
Taken back to race along the fence in the rear, over 6Ls to make up 400M, held up 300-150M and again close home. Inconclusive run.
Began well from draw 2, tracked leader in a strongly run race, kept on evenly early straight, crowded for room 150M, no extra late stages. (Lame LF leg.)
Quickly away, eased back to sit behind leaders in 4th, held ground early straight then weakened over final 150M.
Jumped well and pressed on to lead setting fast sectionals, caught by pursuing rivals inside 200M, weakened away.
Ridden along on jumping from gate 11 but failed to muster speed, caught wide towards the rear and no cover from 800M, never got going. (Mucus in trachea / Lame next day.)

Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, improved from 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, showed good speed to take the lead near to the stands rail, led by half length, hard ridden from near 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner.
Commenced well, raced 1-1/2L behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 400M, closed off well to take a place, just missed 2nd.
Average to begin, raced behind lead nearer to the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, kept on well to make frame. (Lost left front plate after the race.)
Bumped start, raced prominently on the stands rail, hard ridden from near 400M, kept on well to 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 4 to 5 lengths back in the middle of the track, peaked on run near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from near 400M, raced greenly under whip 200M out, ran on evenly thereafter. (Lost right front plate.)

Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 450M, showed some response before inconvenienced near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, checked 50M.
Jumped with them, raced at rear nearer to the stands rail, made little progress in the final 400M.
Moderately away, raced 4 to 5 lengths back in the middle track, made no impression final 400M.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the stands rail, failed to make any progress final 400M. (Lost left front plate.)
Slowly away, raced at rear in the middle track, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced at rear near to the stands rail, showed no response to vigorous riding after passing 400M, weakened thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.)
Moderately away, raced prominently in the middle of the track, weakened from 500M, eased final 200M. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Settled outside the leader, drifted away 300M to score.
Bumped start, eased back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, soon out of fuel 300M.
At back along the fence, lack turn of foot.
Bumped start, eased back, no progress.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Dipped start, hard ridden forward, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 400M.
Ridden along to take lead with nice early speed, travelled comfortably, responded solidly in the straight to score.
Settled in front of midfield, passing 300M was held up for running the near 150M shifted out, finished strongly, missed by Neck, rider questioned.
Settled in handy position, responded well in the straight, made up some nice late ground.
At the start was inconvenienced, raced behind midfield, made nice ground in the straight, finished well.
Ridden to race in box seat, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home one-paced.
Raced at back, widest on straightening, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished OK.
After 1000M was left racing wide and without cover, travelled midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced.
Jumped sharply then taken back at start, raced at tail, wide on straightening, made some ground passing 100M.
Settled 3 wide behind midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Settled at rear on fence, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Urged along to race outside the lead, limited response when asked for effort, gave ground in the straight.
Difficult to settle in the early stages, travelled midfield, limited response in the straight, rider concerned its action, OVE.
Taken back at start, near 1100M was crowded then passing 1000M lost its rightful running, no response in the straight.
Near 1100M lost its left hind plate, settled midfield on rail, weakened near 200M.

Began well, strode forward to position one pair from lead on the outside. Shifted three wide on cornering before hitting top gear passing the 150m, snaring lead at 100m. Held off late challenger in closing stages.

Eased back behind runners after the start and raced near the rear on the rail. Conceded 7.5 lengths at the 800m, shifted away from rail on corner. Wound up passing the 200m before finishing fast in last 100m to just miss.
Strode to midfield before racing keenly and checking near the 1100m. Raced between runners in middle section and conceded over 3 lengths past the 400m. Ran on strongly in final 200m.

Steading and shifting back behind runners settling 8 lengths from lead. Moved three wide past 500m and made ground approaching the turn. Cornered the widest before making late headway in final section.
Showed early speed to come across to lead after 100m. Was clear on cornering and held the lead gallantly until being joined and headed at the 150m.
Held the rail to settle on leaders back after 200m. Had clear running after staying close to rail in the straight, before peaking on run at 150m.
Was the slowest into stride before gathering speed along the rail and settling midfield. Looked to make ground passing the 200m before peaking shortly after to be well held.
Began fast and was ridden across to position outside lead. Was half a length from lead from the corner until peaking at the 150m before giving some ground last 100m.

Bumped and unbalanced after the start before gathering some speed to position midfield. Shifted three wide passing the 750m before shifting wider on turn. Four lengths from lead on balancing & made up a length final section.
Bumped heavily and then check after the start before shifting towards rail and improving to midfield near the 1000m. Shifted ground past the 300m but couldn't pick up to threaten in last 250m.
Bumped and crowded after start before racing three wide with cover in midfield. Strode closer approaching the corner before peaking on run inside 300m.

Bumped at the start and couldn't muster before settling worse than midfield away from rail. Shifted out on point of corner but conceded 5.5 lengths at the 400m and couldn't make any headway into that margin in last section.
Steadied and shifted back to the tail of the field after the start. Was a clear last entering the straight and failed to run on, maintaining margin in final section.
Worked hard in early stages, racing three wide and improving to be 1.5 lengths from lead passing the 800m. Continued to race wide before shifting out on the corner and giving ground from the 300m.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, steadied off heels near 500M, no daylight early in straight then bumped near 300M, made very good progress thereafter to take a place.

Jumped well, unable to slot in early, raced 3W in front of midfield, sent forward after passing 1000M to sit outside the leader, 3/4L behind turning in, took the lead near 300M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight.
Clean jump, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly near 800M, saved ground on turn, no clear running and checked early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, kept on evenly early in straight, brushed and unbalanced near 100M, not ridden out thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, bumped 300M, dropped away thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Prominent, wide and without cover, ran on nicely to score by 1L. (Lame right front)
Eased and slotted in behind midfield, 2 wide, battled on gamely to the line for 2nd.
Settled in one-off one-back, ran on well to take 3rd.
Sent forward to lead, sat 2 wide, headed near 100M and emptied late.
Sat just in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on.
In worse than midfield, on rail, closed off fairly on centre track.
Prominent and on rail, kept on going to the line.
Failed to muster, settled in worse than midfield and wide, made minor ground late.
Sat in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
In front of midfield, wide but with cover, weakened half way in the straight.
At the tail, on rail, never improved.
At rear, 2 wide, never a factor.
Jumped well to lead, held narrow advantage on the rail setting a steady pace, kicked over 2L clear inside the 200 metres, hung on well to finish.
Crowded at start, settled just worse than midfield near the rail, baulked and switched for a run just inside the 300 metres, finished off the race strongly.
Moderate start, settled just better than midfield in 5th just over 3L off the pace, quickened well inside the final 300 metres but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Taken back to last, trailed the field to home bend, commenced move on the outside 500 metres out, ran on near the centre of the straight, nearest at finish.
Broke well, disputed lead most of the way to straight, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away, travelled in last few, did not find much room early in straight, kept on steadily without quickening inside the final 250 metres.
Jumped well but soon dropped to midfield, remained in similar position to straight, found nothing under pressure.
Crowded at start, well back and awkwardly placed rounding home bend, trailed the field into the straight, ran past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, improved gradually to within 2L of pace in 3rd on the rail, chased the leader into home straight, faded under pressure.
Always in last few, hampered and lost position rounding home bend, no further impression.
Travelled wide in last few, made no impression in straight.
Began well, prominent in 4th to the straight, dropped away quickly inside the final 300 metres. (Bled)
Up with early pace, eased back to track leaders on settling, quickened up well to lead 200M, kept kicking to hold off challenger for narrow win.
Guided to a rail position behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, had difficulty obtaining clear run early straight, stayed on strongly over final 250M to just miss.
Tracked leaders along 2-path, raced keenly, checked early straight, battled on between horses, got up for 3rd 50M but always held by winner.
Dropped back to race near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, finished off honestly down outside to claim 4th.
From draw 14 unable to get closer than 3-wide, raced without cover outside the lead, fought on well to lead briefly mid-straight, run ended 100M lost several places near line.
Taken back from wide draw, raced near last 7Ls off the pace, closed off reasonably well down outside, raced tight between rivals late.
Restrained to race behind midfield, difficult to settle 1000M, peeled out to challenge in straight, made late headway without threatening.
Held up 3Ls off leader in midfield, saved ground on inside, not clear run 200M, switched but couldn't finish well enough.
Began only fairly, settled down 3-wide in midfield, kept chasing early straight and had his chance, weakened 100M.
Pressed forward, led along fence from 1050M, headed passing 300M, no extra final 200M.
Settled down in midfield, 7th at 400M, unable to obtain clear running mid-straight and not tested over final 200M.
From draw 12 crossed to race 3-wide ahead of mid-division, battled on same speed turning home, faded 150M.
Began awkwardly, sat in last 8Ls off the lead, couldn't quicken in straight, never involved.
Vied for lead on outside, commenced to weaken inside 350M, dropped out tamely. (Jockey : gave ground rapidly early straight, eased down as the horse may have gone amiss.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths or so back, improved on turn, very wide into straight, showed very good response in straight and won comfortably.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover on turn, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until final 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, bumped near 200M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 1100M, half length back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on rail in the early stages, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled well to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Slowly away, recovered quickly to sit on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, travelled keenly early, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place,
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 550M, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 1100M, 5 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, showed nothing in straight, eased final furlong.

Began only fairly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 700M, steadied off heels near 650M, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to score.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead near 600M, led by 2 to 3 lengths turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M, stayed on for 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned on rail behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take a place. (Dead-heat for 3rd.)
Commenced well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out near 700M, 5 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a place. (Dead-heat for 3rd.)
Began smartly from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide throughout, 2 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, inconvenienced near 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 11 lengths back in the early stages, moved closer after entering the back straight but still 8 lengths behind, taken very wide after turning in, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied off heels near 650M then bumped 550M, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 600M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 800M, hard ridden from near 700M but showed limited response, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, made all.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, held ground for 3rd.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, midfield 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 300M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never improved.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, checked 600M, out of fuel 300M
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 4 wide, bumped and became badly unbalanced, eased out of race.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, checked and blundered badly 500M, emptied.
Began awkwardly, settled in front of midfield on rail, near 500M checked away from heels, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Took lead with nice early speed, responded well in the straight, finished solidly.
Taken back at start, lay in passing 600M, commenced to improve passing 500M, continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home nicely.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, wide on straightening, made up good late ground.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort near 350M, gained ground near final 50M.
Moderate start then ridden to race in handy position, one-paced when asked for effort.
Settled midfield on rail, passing 200M was awkwardly placed for some distance, taken in close to finishing line and not fully tested.
Ridden to settle in box seat, lay out passing 1000M, near 500M again lay out then struck heel and blundered badly, one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield, tried to improve near 450M, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then hard ridden to race outside the lead, near 500M was galloped on, commenced to give ground passing 100M, close to finishing line was checked.
Settled at rear, very wide on straightening, limited response in the straight, bled.
Slow out, raced at rear on fence, crowded passing 600M, no response in the straight.

Worse than midfield away from rail in early stages. Moved three wide and improved with cover passing the 800m. Continued to improve wide before cornering 1 length from lead. Sprinted well final 150m, snaring lead last 50m.

Raced three wide with cover in early section before making sweeping move passing the 850m, striking lead near the 700m. Continued on to be a length clear near cornering. Dashed clear in straight before being caught last 50m.
Raced in midfield away from rail before shifting three wide and forced 4 wide in middle stages. Cornered around 3 lengths from lead before finishing well in last 250m.
Settled behind leading pair away from rail early, before shifting three wide near the 650m. Raced tight on straightening before finishing off fairly in last 300m.
Raced wide early before striding forward to be outside leader past the 1100m. Hard ridden to move up to leader on cornering but couldn't challenge a gave a length or two in final 100m.

Shifted across to the rail after the start and raced near the rear throughout. Moved away from the rail approaching the 450m when racing over 5 lengths from lead. Shifted out passing the 200m and finished off fairly late.
Had early speed and crossed to lead after 250m. Headed in the lead passing the 700m before getting leaders back. Was close to rail and 2 lengths from the lead on corner but gave ground in last 300m.

Fractious in barriers and began slowly before making up ground to race in midfield on rail. Shuffled back to near last on the corner before being held up near the 200m and effectively untested in late stages.
Strode across behind runners early settling a clear last after the first section. Moved three wide past the 400m and cornered the widest runner before maintaining margin in final 300m.
Strode forward after the start and settled outside leader early before obtaining cover near the 1000m. Lost position and raced tight when passing the 400m and weakened out in final 300m.

Began well and had leaders back in first two sections. Shuffled back to midfield past the 500m, but only conceded 3 lengths nearing the corner. Stayed close to rail on turning but couldn't make any headway in straight.
Restrained and shifted across behind runners after the start and raced at the tail. Moved three wide approaching the turn but couldn't make up ground in final section.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths, travelled well to turn, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly thereafter to take a place.
Shifted in abruptly at start and made contact, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 450M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Out in line, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, taken back to race at rear, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Reared start and lost ground, raced at rear on the inside, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, kicked away nicely at 100M to score by 2-1/2L.
Sent forward to take rail and led, headed by winner at 100M but fought on to the line.
Raced at the tail, 2 wide at turns, made good ground inside final 200M.
Eased then raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, made ground and closed off fairly.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground. (See Incident Report)
Travelled in the box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, bumped 250M, ran on fairly until flattened late.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, was one paced in the straight.
Went forward, sat outside lead until 800M, found no extra for final 150M.
In midfield 2 wide initially, moved forward after 1100M and sat outside the lead, emptied near 200M. (See Incident Report)
Awkward start, settled at rear, 3 wide at turns but with cover, checked at 350M, did not run on thereafter.
Crowded start, in midfield but trapped wide all the way, run ended when bumped at 350M.

Pressed forward between runners before settling just outside the leader passing the 800 metres, came to join the leader entering straight and hit the front under pressure 200 metres out, just held off late challenges.
Settled in midfield after a moderate start, came under pressure entering straight, ran on well under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Niggled along from the two draw before settling in forward of midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, switched twice for a run early in straight, finished off the race strongly.
Close up early before settling just over 2L back in 4th or 5th, came under pressure in similar position turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.

Broke well but soon taken back to just worse than midfield travelling 3-wide without cover, came under pressure entering home straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, soon recovered to last few racing keenly approaching the Rock, gained towards midfield entering home straight, did not find much room most of the way.
Began well settling just off the pace on the rail, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Pressed forward to soon take up running, obtained rails run 800 metre out, led until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped well behind, produced good late impression final stages, never nearer.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, fought on well without threatening.
Ridden after a moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, remained similar into the straight, kept on same pace without quickening.

Ridden along from the widest gate, wide in midfield entering back straight, gained closer while remaining wide up the Rock reaching close-up 3rd 3-wide on home bend, dropped out tamely upon straightening.
Bumped by rival and lost ground at start, improved to be racing behind midfield, did not obtain clear running until inside 200M, let down strongly and wrestled the lead 100M, held sway.
Settled down midfield in 6th spot 3Ls off the pace, responded well to be hitting the front nearing 150M, soon joined by eventual winner, fought hard but no match final 100M.
Switched off to last on jumping from wide gate, detached from the field in first half, moved closer to be 6Ls off at 400M, finished off well to go 3rd near line, not reached first 2.
From draw 12 slotted into a midfield spot along the 2-path, closed off hard early straight but peaked on its run 150M, lost 3rd late.
Held up behind midfield, pushed to 3-wide 700M, 5Ls off the pace home turn, ran on mildly towards the line but never dangerous.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled near last 6Ls off the pace, peeled wide to challenge leaving the bend, stayed on past beaten rivals but no threat to leaders.
Led from draw 1 as expected, soon pressed by rival, held slender lead on straightening until headed 150M, no extra late stages.
Tracked leaders along the fence, kept on fairly turning in, out of contention from 100M. (Jockey expressed concern regarding the action of his horse.)
Travelled outside the leader, failed to quicken as expected early straight, weakened noticeably. (Unacceptable Performance / Lame next day.)
Up with early pace, lost ground 1000M and shuffled back to midfield, didn't run on in the straight. (Bled 2nd time.)
Chased leaders, didn't respond when placed under pressure early straight, weakened rapidly. (Jockey unable to explain for the disappointing run / Unacceptable Performance.)

Ridden along but unable to get across, was steadied in an attempt to obtain cover but remained wide without cover throughout the trip, gave ground noticeably over the home turn, eased. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Moderately away, raced in 2nd, half length back on turn, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead after passing 150M, won with some in hand.

Began smartly, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, led by half length on turning, kept on strongly in straight, lost out final 150M but still a solid effort. (Lost left hind plate passing 1000M.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight, no threat to the first two.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Very slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden early, 2 wide in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
At back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2-3 wide, ran on well until 200M weakened.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden throughout, trapped 3-4 wide, never traveled better than midfield.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by fast pace, dropped off quickly 500M.
Moderate start then ridden hard to take lead, travelled well, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, fought well in the straight, just missed by SH.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, made up good late ground, finished nicely.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, gained nice ground passing 200M, worked home OK.
Urged along to race in box seat, tried to improve passing 500M, gave some ground passing 100M.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but gave ground passing 150M.
Raced midfield, rider dropped his right rein near 150M, gave ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, commenced to improve passing 500M, limited response in the straight.
Raced at tail, always back, never in it, lame left front next day
Travelled midfield, tried hard but failed to run on.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on fence, placed pressure but no response.

Raced worse than midfield away from rail. Awkwardly placed near the 350m before shifting out and bumping when looking to get clear. Picked up last 300m before running away with easy victory in final 100m.
Began well, raced in midfield on the rail. Steadied near the 800m when 4 lengths from lead. Held up on cornering and again near the 350m before getting clear and finishing well in final 300m.

Eased across behind runners after the start, before settling midfield away from rail. Moved three wide past the 700m and obtained nice trail into bend. Bumped by winner at 350m before making gradual ground in final furlong.
Raced in midfield away from rail between horses. Sprinted quickly between runners after straightening and shared lead past the 200m before peaking last 100m.

Strode across to midfield, three wide without cover passing the 1000m. Continued to cover additional ground in middle section before cornering four wide. Made steady ground, joining lead at 200m before peaking late.

Had no early speed and settled near the tail of the field. Moved wider passing the 550m and cornered the widest of all. Balanced up four lengths from the lead at 400m before making good ground in final section.

Hard ridden first 150m to get clear in the lead before crossing to the rail after 300m. Raced a length clear in the lead in middle section before being joined past the 300m mark. Peaked on run inside final 200m.

Began fast and strode forward before getting leaders back after 300m. Moved around leader's heels on straightening before racing tight past the 300m. Peaked on run shortly after and gave ground in final 250m.

Hard ridden from start before being crossed after 400m and getting trailing position behind leading pair. Moved three wide past the 600m when within three lengths from lead. Peaked at 300m and gave ground late stages.

Crowded after the start and subsequently raced near the rear of the field. Stayed close to the rail on turning but conceded over six lengths entering final section. Made no headway in final 400m and was well beaten.

Didn't jump fast but was hard ridden shortly after the start to come across and position outside leader approaching the 1000m. Hard ridden past the 550m to keep with leader before weakening out in the straight.
Taken back after the start and raced at the tail of the field. Was a clear last and under heavy pressure at the 400m and gave further ground in last section.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by 3 lengths at 400M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well, positioned slightly better than midfield on the middle track, 3 lengths behind at 400M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began fairly, positioned behind midfield on the middle track, 4 lengths or so back at 400M, finished off strongly to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear near to the stands rail, still 7 lengths back at 400M, made very good progress thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began well, raced in midfield nearer to the middle track, 4 lengths behind at 400M, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, raced in midfield on the middle track, 4 lengths or so back at 400M, inconvenienced near 250M, finished off evenly. (A small cut to the inside of the right front fetlock.)
Slightly slow out and made contact, raced at rear on the stands rail, 7 lengths back at 400M, made little progress thereafter. (Jockey dropped his right rein near 900M.)
Began well, raced prominently on the stands side, 3 lengths back at 400M, showed limited response to hard riding, weakened from 250M, eased final 100M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the middle track, peaked after passing 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the stands rail early, peaked near 500M, weakened gradually after passing 400M, eased final 150M.
Away with them, raced behind midfield in the middle track, 6 lengths or so back at 400M, weakened thereafter, finished last.
Sent forward and led by about 5L, maintained margin to score impressively.
In box-seat, 6L behind however, stayed on but was no match.
Sat in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on to the line.
Bumped start, raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Crowded start, at rear along the rail, saved ground.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, one paced.
Sent forward, sat about 5L off the lead, 2 wide, lost ground in the straight.
At the rear, 2 wide, only past tired runners.
Sat just behind midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide at turns, emptied passing 200M.
At the tail, 3 wide with cover, did not improve.
Crowded start, settled in worse than midfield, 3 wide without cover, never ran on.
Soon took up running after a moderate start, drew clear upon straightening, unchallenged.
Inconvenienced at start and settled well behind, commenced move rounding home bend, finished off the race well down the centre of the sloppy track.
Amongst the leaders 3-wide, shifted 2.5L back to 4th coming out of back straight, became 5th rounding home bend, fought on steadily to reach 2nd 200 metres out only to lose it close to home.
Began fairly, improved steadily to reach 1L 2nd coming out of back straight, unable to sustain effort and lost placing over 200 metres out.
Inconvenienced at start settling in midfield, hugged rails turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Broke well, prominent and wide early before taken back to midfield shortly after, renewed effort 4-wide rounding home bend, kept on steadily before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Settled wide in last few from a wide gate, made headway rounding home bend, baulked briefly early in straight, kept on well.
Never better than midfield, inconvenienced rounding home bend, made no impression in the straight.

Began well from a wide gate, prominent without cover early, shifted back towards midfield before moving forward coming onto home bend, reached 4th some 2L back and 3-wide turning in, weakened noticeably in straight.
Gradually dropped back towards the rear despite ridden along, one from last turning for home, made no impression in straight.
Ridden forward to recover from a moderate start, settled some 2L back in 3rd approaching home bend, dropped away quickly inside the final 300 metres.
Began awkwardly losing ground, remained well behind throughout, awkwardly placed behind runner twice early on home bend, went wide into home straight.
Dropped back from wide barrier, in last 9Ls off the pace on settling, closed off strongly on outside, got there in last stride.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, travelled well behind leaders early straight, driven out 300M, led from mid-straight just couldn't withstand winner's run late stages, headed in last stride.
Reserved near last 7-8Ls off the good pace on settling, finished off nicely final 300M to go 3rd near line, couldn't reel in first two.
Never far off, 3rd chasing leaders home turn, moved up 3-wide vying for lead 500M, held narrow lead early straight, outsprinted final 200M.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled down behind midfield 6Ls off the good pace, ran on without menacing.
Tracked leader in a fast run race, moved up to joint leader 500M, battled on to 150M, faded towards the line.
Didn't show sufficient early speed, raced in midfield further back than hoped, flat footed from 600M, took time to muster speed, ran past a couple late but was never in the reckoning.
Always within 4Ls from leader, in 4th spot making home turn, kept on fairly in the straight, no extra late. (Blood in trachea / RF heel overreach injury).
Sped to the lead, set good pace early and middle stages, taken on by rival 500M, headed early straight, faded final 200M to finish last.
Away with them, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out after passing 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on strongly after turning in, just unable to hold off the winner late.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, wide into straight, made some headway in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 600M, 4 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, severely checked near 1400M, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide at rear, bumped near 1200M, no cover thereafter, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped shortly after at start, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, crowded near 1300M, awkwardly placed shortly thereafter, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Commenced well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 1-1/2L back on turn, finished off very strongly, scored by 2-1/4L.
Began smartly from gate 11, raced prominently but wide, half length back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame. (Lame right hind leg with a laceration over the stifle next day morning.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, sat 2Ls behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly after passing 900M, clipped heels & stumbled shortly thereafter, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, raced tight near 900M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide behind midfield, raced tight near 900M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Raced wide before being ridden forward to midfield around 3.5 lengths from lead at the 1000m. Had clear running after straightening and made good headway to join a line of five at the 100m before continuing on for narrow win.

Began fairly and strode to midfield, three wide with cover. Bumped and unbalanced at 1300m before settling 4.5 lengths from lead at 800m. Sprinted well to join leaders inside last 150m before narrowly beaten on the line.

Made ground after start to settle midfield 3.5 lengths from lead after 400m. Stayed close to rail before being held up on the turn. Was making ground along rail when checked near the 200m before finishing hard in final 175m.

Strode forward to race behind the leader who crossed to rail after 500m. Stayed close to the rail on turn before shifting around heels at the 325m. Moved up near the lead inside the last 100m before being over-run in last 50m.

Showed early speed and strode forward from wide barrier to eventually cross outside the leader after 500m. Moved up to share lead on cornering before being joined in a line of five at the 100m and over-run last 50m.
Began well and strode across to lead before crossing to rail after 500m. Was challenged on cornering before fighting hard until being joined at the 100m and steadying shortly after.

Shifted behind runners after the start and raced worse than midfield away from rail. Six lengths from the lead passing the 800m before moving four wide near the 550m. Cornered wide before finishing strongly in last section.
Strode forward after the start but didn't cross and was then forced three wide without cover past the 1100m. Continued to cover ground approaching the turn before battling on in last 400m.

Crossed behind runners to race in rearward position after the first section. Moved away from rail past the 600m before shifting wider on turn. Conceded nearly 5 lengths at the 400m & made up a length or two in final section.

Had no early speed and drifted back to the tail shortly after start. Hard ridden past the 550m to improve position. Conceded big margin entering the final section before making some headway in the straight.
Allowed to settle in midfield and raced on the rail 4.5 lengths from lead at halfway. Had no dahs after straightening and yielded a length or so over the final 400m.

Raced in midfield between runners before bumping heavily near the 1300m. 4.5 lengths from lead at halfway and cornered conceding similar margin. One-paced over final 300m and didn't threaten placed horses.
Showed some speed after the start to stride forward and race behind leading pair away from the rail. Came under pressure approaching the bend and gave ground in the final section.
Steadied and shifted back to last shortly after the start. Was a clear last approaching the turn before yielding ground in the last 400m to be well beaten.
