Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 750M, retook the lead on turn, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, hard ridden after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually from 150M.
Away with them, bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with no cover, better than midfield, peaked on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress early in straight, steadied off heels near 100M, raced tight thereafter, not able to be ridden out late.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
Pushed early, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 100M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, lack room 200M, just held ground.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 200M.
Slow away, behind midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased at start, benefited by the fast tempo, 2 wide at rear, no progress.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Ridden along to race in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, quickened passing 150M, scored unchallenged.
Jumped well then ridden along to take lead, fought nicely in the straight.
Jumped OK, settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, made up some late ground.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, improved on straightening, worked home well.
Settled midfield, in the early part of straight lay in and passing 200M shifted out abruptly away from heels, fought hard but one-paced after that.
At start was hampered and lost ground, raced at back, always niggled, passing 200M steadied and shifted in for clear run, finished OK.
Began only fairly then taken back, wide on straightening, made some ground passing 100M.
At start was hampered and lost ground, travelled behind midfield on rail, near 400M lay in, finished one-paced.
Urged along after start, settled outside the lead, weakened passing 100M.
Fractious in barrier, hard ridden after start, travelled wide and without cover in midfield, rider dropped whip near 150M, limited response in the straight, stalls test.
Jumped well then taken back, raced at tail, never in it.
Raced in front of midfield, near 550M lay out, faded out passing 150M.

Assumed good position one pair behind lead after 300m. Moved three wide passing the 400m and conceded 3.5 lengths at this point. Made quick ground once balanced, struck lead inside final 150m and drew away in closing stages.

Slow to begin before ridden hard to get to midfield on the rail. Travelled strongly passing the 400m when 4 lengths from lead. Cornered on the rail before making good ground along the inside in the final 150m.

Bumped at the start before shifting back behind runners early. Shifted wider around the final turn before balancing up over 5 lengths from the lead. Made steady headway as the widest runner over the final 250m.

Checked after the start before striding forward to midfield. Shifted out near the 850m before improving around field to strike lead at 550m. Continued on to lead by over 1 length on corner. Peaked on run & joined at 150m.

Began awkwardly and checked before clipping heals near winning post & settling worse than midfield. Moved out 3 wide at the 650m before improving position 2.5L from lead at the 400m. Lay in in straight before peaking late.

Bumped at start before restraining shortly after to race at the tail of the field. Five lengths form lead between runners passing the 400m. Shifted in after straightening but only maintained margin in straight.
Bumped at start before restraining back behind runners & settling near the rear. Raced on the rail when conceding 5 lengths past the 400m.

Began fast and assumed lead after a few strides. Was headed in the lead at the 550m, before cornering over a length from the lead. Peaked on effort shortly after straightening and weakened out over final 250m.

Strode forward to get leaders back shortly after start. Shifted around heels past the 400m before being tightened on the corner. Around 2.5L from lead on straightening but never ran on and gave ground in final 200m.

Showed some speed to stride forward outside leader early. Raced over one length from lead in middle stages. Bumped and eased near the 400m before being tightened & checked on the corner. Gave ground in the straight.
Bumped at the start and raced wide before settling at the rear on the outside. Was hard ridden passing the 500m when a clear last and made no headway in the final section.
Strode forward after the start but raced three wide without cover just forward of midfield. Was under heavy pressure passing the 550m and began yielding ground shortly after.
Made contact at start, raced wide with cover at rear, moved closer after passing 700M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, sent forward after passing 700M, a length or so back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, inconvenienced near 550M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well to make frame without threatening the first two.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide in the early stages, settled 2 wide, a length behind the leader after 1100M, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, sent forward after entering the back straight, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide on turn, finished off evenly.

Away with them, raced 3 wide, slightly better than midfield, improved from 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded out start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, sent forward to take the early lead, led by a length, headed near 650M, weakened gradually on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final furlong.
Sent forward to take rail and led, ran on nicely to score by 1-1/2L.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 2 wide, made nice ground and closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in the box-seat, challenged until emptied passing 100M.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 2 wide, closed off well to the line.
In about midfield, along the rail, kept on fairly until late.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 2 wide, ran home one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, showed dashes early and ran on.
Awkward start, in worse than midfield along the rail, saved ground early but flattened approaching 100M.
Bumped start then taken back, raced along the rail, saved no ground.
In worse than midfield, wide and without cover, did not threaten.
Raced in one-off one-back position, found nothing to sustain run in the straight.
Settled outside the lead, gave ground from rounding home turn.
Settled in midfield on the rail, snuck up to hit the front passing the 200 metres, hung on well to the line.
Close up early, settled worse than midfield coming onto back straight, swung widest turning for home, ran on well down the centre of the track. (Tactic questioned)
Moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, finished off the race nicely between runners, did best work late.
Began well from a low draw, gradually shifted back to race mainly in midfield, switched out for a run on straightening, ran on to hold some chance but unable to peg back the place-getters throughout.
Amongst leaders early, settled just better than midfield in 4th and then 5th, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.

Amongst the leaders early stages, taken back to rear of midfield rounding stables bend, gained slightly closer out wide in back straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening in the run to the line.

Broke well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on the rail, drifted some 2L back in 4th early in back straight, became closer when pace slackened on home bend, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Very slowly away travelling well back, fought on past beaten horses in home straight.

Ridden positively for narrow lead early, gradually ceded advantage for one back position coming onto back straight, renewed effort to join the leader making home turn, unable to sustain effort and weakened inside the final 200 metres.
Driven forward from a wide gate eventually taking up running on top of stables bend, led until faded under pressure 200 metres out.

Vied for early lead from a wide gate, taken 4L back to 5th and remained without cover in back straight, moved back up closer to pace in 3rd passing the 800 metres, soon dropped out of contention after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Settled well back from a wide gate, never seen with a chance. (Lame next day)
Pushed along to be vying for lead on outside, took over 300M, kicked on well under pressure, stayed tough final stages to hold off pursuing rivals.
Began well, eased back to race in midfield 3Ls behind leader, ran home strongly from 300M, just missed.
Tracked leaders, ideally placed turning home, tried hard to run down leader, made steady headway towards the finish, just held.
Taken back to last from draw 12, 6Ls off the pace on settling, came widest into straight, closed off fastest for 4th. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Began fairly, held up in midfield along the fence, 3Ls off leader turning for home, kept battling to the line but always behind by leaders.
Shifted across behind runners after the start, saved ground racing at the rear, finished off moderately, awkwardly placed 100M.
Chased leaders along the fence, kept on one paced from 300M, couldn't get closer.
Began awkwardly, failed to muster speed, settled down in midfield 3-wide, 3Ls off top of straight, effort petered out at 200M.
Began well from draw 1, ended up leading the field from 800M, headed early straight, faded final 150M. (Jockey : didn't finish off its race after being required to lead.)
Shifted across behind runners, raced towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, pressed along 400M couldn't go on with it.
Vied for lead 3-wide early stages, eased back to race in chasing group from 800M but unable to find cover, weakened in the straight. (Jockey told not to cover unnecessary ground.)
Driven along early from draw 10 but unable to cross, caught 4-wide no cover throughout, gave ground rapidly on straightening.

Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, finished off strongly to score.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a little bit closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few late, missed 3rd on line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar positon on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sat 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide throughout, a length behind at 400M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar positon on turn, no clear running early in straight, blocked near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, raced tight early in straight, weakened gradually from 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 to 6 lengths back, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, clipped heels and stumbled near 500M, 10 lengths behind at 400M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield early, difficult to settle near 900M, weakened on turn, eased early in straight. (Bled.) (Lost left hind plate.)
Settled in front, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, dominated from 300M.
Settled in box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, held ground for 2nd.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Bumped start, midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 100M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, held up most straight, not properly tested.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, trapped 3 wide in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 400M, emptied 150M.
Bumped start, at rear, trapped 3 wide, never improved.
Never a factor.
Taken back at start from wide gate, raced at tail, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Raced midfield, unable to maintain its position passing 900M, always niggled, made up good ground passing 100M, missed by SH.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, responded nicely in the straight.
Checked on jumping, travelled at back on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, gained ground passing 150M.
Pushed to settle in box seat, commenced to improve on straightening, made some ground in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, one-paced.
Ridden to race outside the lead with nice early speed, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, unable to obtain clear running in the straight, not fully tested.
Ridden hard but failed to muster speed, travelled wide and without cover in handy position, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, battled hard but only limited response.
Settled in one off one back, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start from widest gate, widest on straightening, no response when placed under pressure.
On jumping was badly crowded for room, settled behind midfield, held up in early part of straight, failed to make impression, lame left fore.
Raced midfield, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.

Eased across after start to race worse than midfield with cover. Made ground passing the 600m before being pushed very wide on cornering. 5.5L from lead at 400m before sprinting fast in straight to win by big margin.

Raced in midfield a little wide before shifting closer to rail past the 800m when over 5L form lead. Shifted out past the 500m & cornered second widest. Couldn't go with winner once balanced but made good headway last 300m.

Strode across from outside gate to race outside leader after 200m. Challenged for lead passing 900m with fast mid-race sections. Obtained lead past 500m and still well clear inside 200m before being joined in the last 100m.
Began well and strode forward before getting on leaders back after 250m. Hard ridden passing the 550m before cornering 2 lengths from the lead. Maintained margin in straight without threatening.

Slow to begin & raced near tail. Lost a length at the 900m when avoiding fallen rider. Hard ridden from the 700m to improve when 9L from lead. Shifted wider on balancing & made considerable late ground from rearward position.

Very slow to begin before hard ridden to muster and settled at the rear. Raced on the fence in middle section, 7L from lead at halfway. Raced along rail in straight and made up a few lengths in final 300m.
Strode forward from outside barrier before racing three wide without cover behind leading pair. Hard ridden into the corner before peaking on run in straight and giving a length or two in final 400m.

Raced wide on the track for first 600m before shifting into 3 wide line with cover near the 850m. Pushed four wide passing the 600m when 4 lengths from lead. Battled on after straightening before peaking inside last 250m.

Showed early speed before restraining into trailing position. Drifted to midfield in second section, conceding 4L at halfway. Four lengths from lead on balancing & made no impression late. Lame right front leg.

Maintained rail position and raced in midfield. Hard ridden passing the 500m before cornering along the rail. Four lengths from lead on balancing before peaking on effort inside the final 250m and tiring late.

Began fast & showed early speed to lead. Challenged for the lead at the 1300m before drawing clear. Again challenged passing the 850m resulting in fast sectionals. Headed in the lead at the 500m and weakened out in straight.

Began only fairly and raced near the tail. Checked near the 900m after being unable to avoid fallen rider. Tailed out after incident and took little part in race. Vet exam revealed slight abrasions post-race.
Began awkwardly before mustering speed to stride up behind leading pair away from rail. Came under heavy pressure passing the 700m before yielding ground a long way out.

Placing: UR
Comment: Slightly slow away before striding into midfield after 250m. Stumbled badly near the 900m and unseated rider
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled well throughout, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, finished 4th. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out thereafter, made some progress when clear final 100M.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still 9 lengths behind the leader turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to final 50M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 900M, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 3 wide form 800M, 8 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, 10 lengths back, still 7 to 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths or so back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, failed to make any progress.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, settled 2 wide from near 950M, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M.
Rolled forward into the box-seat, got going at 250M and ran on to score by 1L with relative ease.
Asked and raced prominently, battled on nicely but couldn't hold off the winner, finished 1L behind.
Awkward start, raced just behind midfield 2 wide, ran on well inside final 100M and got 3rd.
Settled in midfield, along the rail, closed off to take 4th.
Raced in about midfield, 2 wide, continued on fairly to the line.
Took position in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on okay until flattened late.
Crowded start, shifted across to be in behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground in the straight.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, locked in battle until 150M when weakened.
Took back, in worse than midfield, on rail until shifted out at 700M, made ground steadily.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, was one paced and emptied late.
Eased and took cover, in worse than midfield 2 wide, didn't save ground.
At rear and 2 wide throughout, never improved.
Midfield initially but wide, improved at 1200M but continued to race wide, lost ground in the straight.
Eased and remained at the rear, never a factor.
With leaders early before taken back to 4th just over 2L off the pace, quickened well to lead 200 metres out, won cozily.
Vied for lead 4-wide after beginning from a wide gate, pressed forward to take up running on the rail about 900 metres out, led until headed under pressure 200 metres out.
Settled wide in midfield after a moderate start from the widest gate, without cover rounding home bend and into the straight, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled wide in last few, remained same into the straight, quickened well inside the final 300 metres, did best work late.
Broke well to lead, snatched back to 2nd 2-wide approaching home bend and travelled alongside leader turning for home, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away and slow to muster travelling well behind, badly hampered making home bend, produced strong late finish inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well but settled towards the rear, hampered 600 metres out, ran on past beaten horses in home straight.
Ridden after a moderate start, settling in midfield when hampered on top of home bend, lost position when tight between runners turning into home straight, kept on steadily while hanging in.

Began fairly from the one draw, raced keenly in 5th about 3L off the pace, checked off heels on top of home bend and did not find much room shortly after straightening, found nothing under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Soon taken back to trail the field, improved to join other back-markers rounding home bend but forced very wide making final turn, went past well-beaten horses closing stages.

Niggled at early sharing pace on the rail, dropped 2L back to 3rd rounding home bend and checked off front-runner's heels when pace slackened, folded up quickly inside the final 300 metres. (Blood in trachea)

Began awkwardly losing ground, recovered quickly to rear of midfield on the rail, forced to check and lost a few lengths on top of home bend, saved ground making home turn, soon weakened in straight. (Tactic questioned)
From draw 12 rolled forward to settle ahead of midfield, raced keenly when pace slackened middle stages, made home turn 3-wide, quickened to lead 300M and stayed strong to the line.

Taken back from draw 14, in 2nd last over 10Ls off the pace, flat footed when pace quickened 1000M, got back into contention 600M, stayed on strongly to claim 2nd near line but couldn't reel in winner. (Jockey questioned.)
Began fairly, recovered to race ahead of midfield, in 7th place 400M, chased well over final 200M but always held by winner, edged out to 3rd late stages.

Settled 3-wide in midfield but racing without cover, forward move from 1200M to be tracking leaders entering home turn, battled for lead mid-straight, one paced final 150M after tough trip, lost 2 places final stages.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, crept closer from halfway, made steady ground final 200M and kept coming to the line.
Guided to a midfield position, stayed in touch with leaders home turn, tried hard in straight and had every chance, couldn't get there.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back to race in 3rd last, saved ground along fence but got held up on inside 300M-150M, switched lane and ran on well towards the line.
From draw 1 went forward chasing leaders, box-seated early straight, gave brief response from 300M, couldn't sustain run final 150M.

Dropped back to last from wide draw, over 10Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, swung wide for home, stayed on past weakening horses but never a threat to leaders. (Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Sent forward, led steadily early stages, prompted by rival from 1000M resulting in quicker sectionals, lost lead entering straight, couldn't go on.
Tracked leader 2-wide, pressed on for the lead passing 1000M, held narrow lead on straightening, headed inside 300M then faded away.
Held up in mid-division, raced 3-wide from 1200M, came under pressure 600M, couldn't quicken on straightening, made no impression.
Restrained behind midfield 7Ls behind leader, in similar position making the turn for home, failed to finish off.
Prominent behind leaders, found little upon straightening, weakened to last.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score by a head.

Moderately away, raced 3W with no cover in midfield, found cover near 700M, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Out In line, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, travelled keenly after passing 800M, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to take a place.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, struck on heels and unbalanced near 400M, made good progress thereafter, steadied off heels close home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, challenged the rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.

Began well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival on turn, kept on well until headed near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, wider from 500M, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly, sat 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress in straight.
Fast to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, 2 lengths behind at 400M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 1100M, 1-1/2L behind on turn, unbalanced early in straight, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made no progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide from near 700M, 2 lengths back turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1150M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored by 2-1/2L.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off well when clear final 150M.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 3rd without threatening.
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened close home.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, awkwardly placed near 1100M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running until passing 200M, finished off evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.

Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, wider on turn, 6 lengths back at 400M, made no progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still last turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 450M, finished off very well to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 3/4L at 400M, kept on well in straight, just could not hold off the first two late.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, recovered to race at rear on the inside, 7 to 8 lengths back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, closer on turn but still 6 lengths behind, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 200M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off one-paced. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside early, 2 wide after entering the first turn, ridden from near 600M, 4 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L behind on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, weakened early in straight.
Settled in midfield along the fence, dashed well 250M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, lack room 300M, just held ground for 3rd.
Very slow away, took rail at back, pace good, lack room until 300M, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide at back, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Slow away, at back 2-3 wide, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, soon emptied 200M.
Slow away, eased back, raced 3-4 wide, pace good, made ground 150M.
Very slow away, pace good, no dash.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, never improved.
Eased at start, pace good, never competitive.
Settled at back, widest on straightening, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Raced at tail, niggled passing 800M, quickened passing 100M, worked hone solidly, distressed.
Raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, fought hard, worked home one-paced.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield on rail, came under pressure passing 700M, failed to made impression.
Urged to take lead, commenced to improve near 300M, gave ground near 50M.
Settled behind leaders, tried to improve passing 400M, weakened passing 200M.
Ridden to settle outside the lead, no response in the straight, failed to run on.

Settled in midfield away from rail after 400m. Travelled strongly in middle section before improving three wide approaching the corner. Sprinted fast past the 250m, striking lead at 100m & going on for comfortable victory.

Strode forward to race in fourth position, 5L from fast leader at the 1000m. Travelled strongly & strode up 2L from the lead on the corner. Hit lead inside final 175m before being joined and passed inside final 100m.

Began fairly before settling in midfield position on the rail. Raced six lengths from lead at half way. Moved away from rail approaching the 400m & shifted wider again in the straight, before making steady headway final 250m.

Raced tight after start before easing across to race in rearward position away from rail. Ridden forward to improve near the 400m when still 6.5L from lead. Balanced up one of the widest before making up 3L in final 300m.
Began well and settled in midfield on rail, 5 lengths from lead after the first section. Travelled strongly & close to heals on cornering before maintaining four length margin in the straight.

Crowded at start before mustering early speed to stride forward. Trailed the pacesetter, 1.5L from lead in middle stages. Moved up to join lead at the 300m before being overtaken inside the last furlong.

Strode forward after start to get good position midfield after 200m. Strode closer near nearing the 400m when around 4L from the lead. Three wide on the point of the corner and yielded a length or so in the last furlong.

Slightly slow away before shifting back behind runners and racing at the tail after the first section. Continued to race at the tail, nearly 9L from lead at half way. Shifted out wider on cornering but was always rearward.
Began fast before being crossed in the lead near the 1200m. Hard ridden passing the 500m and maintained three length margin until cornering before weakening out in the straight.
Raced worse than midfield away from the rail early before shifting back to rail near the 1000m. Stayed close to the rail on cornering but made no headway in the straight.

Crowded and checked on jumping and consequently raced in a rearward position. Drifted back to last on the rail past the 800m. Hard ridden when conceding over 9 lengths entering the final section and made no impression late.

Mustered early speed to lead before striding across to the rail near the 1200m. Raced over 1L clear in second section when setting good speed. Joined in lead shortly after straightening before weakening out in last 300m.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, hard ridden from 400M, bumped early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from near 700M, half length back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away from a tricky draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after entering the back straight, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, same position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, raced tight near 200M, made little progress thereafter until crowded near the finish.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 1000M, 2 lengths back on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, sat 1 to 2 length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 50M.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly until crowded near 100M, not fully ridden out thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to made any progress in straight.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, ran home gamely and took lead just before going to the line, scored by a head.
Sent forward to take rail and led, battled on spiritly but couldn't hold off the winner in final strides.
Raced at the tail, 2 wide, swung widest and closed off strongly for 3rd.
In midfield, 2 wide, saved ground in the straight. (Lost left hind plate and rider expressed concern over action)
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat about 1-1/2L off, ran on the finish.
Bumped start, settled towards the rear, along the rail, made ground steadily.
Raced just behind midfield, wide however, steadied at 150M, closed off well late.
Raced prominently, 1L off and outside the lead, did not run on. (Blood in trachea and see Incident Report)
In midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Bumped start, settled at the rear 2 wide, ran home but did not challenge.
Taken back, at tail and on rail, never featured in the straight.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on the rail mainly in 4th, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily to hit the front inside the 100 metres.
Settled towards the rear in 9th, raced wide into straight, finished off the race well to just fail to get up on line. (Lame next day)
Ridden along wide in forward of midfield early stages, improved to join the leader at the Rock, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily without threatening.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, headed 100 metres out.
Broke well, settled in rear of midfield on the rail in 7th, remained similar to home straight saving ground making home turn, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing considerable ground, raced keenly in rear early in back straight, remained well behind and swung wide into home straight, made good progress inside the final 200 metres.

Jumped fairly but soon picked up to first few, drifted back to 6th within 3L of pace coming off the Rock, in similar position turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening in the run to the line.
Prominent out wide early stages, sharing pace before taken one back to 3rd at the Rock, swung wide entering home straight, one-paced under pressure.

Amongst the leaders when steadied and lost position early stages, shuffled further back to midfield coming onto back straight, remained similar to home turn, did not find much room early in straight and kept on same pace.
Inconvenienced at start, towards the rear on the rail, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled well back from the widest gate, tailed-off into home straight and never a danger.
Prominent and wide to home straight, folded up quickly. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Quickly away from draw 1, settled just behind leaders, let down well to find the lead 100M , held sway final stages.
Slotted into a midfield spot along the 2-path, pressed along 600M out, 5th turning in, worked home well to go 2nd near line, nearest finish.
Went forward to be tracking leader 2-wide, kept on solidly entering straight and vied for lead until late stages, lost 2nd close home.
Restrained to race towards the rear, 8Ls off the pace on settling, caught up in traffic entering straight, blocked 300M until final stages, had plenty to offer late. (not properly tested.)
Never far off the pace, settled in 5th early and middle stages, battled well in the straight but always held by leaders.
Emerged as leader passing 1500M, led them at good pace from 1000M, fought on well and remained in contention until weakening final stages.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up near the rear 7Ls back in 8th, finished off well down outside final 300M.
Close up 4th on settling, well placed to strike turning home, kept battling in straight until fading over final 150M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up last 10Ls behind leader, saved ground on inside but ran on only fairly in the straight, no impact.
Restrained to race behind mid-division, in 7th place 4.5Ls off the pace 400M, disappointed for running early straight but never got close when clear.
Shifted out on jumping and was checked, raced in 2nd last 9Ls behind leader, failed to improve turning home, never threatened.
In mid-division 5-6Ls off the pace, came under pressure 550M, found little in the home run.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently but trapped wide, checked off heels near 1100M, positioned 3 to 4 wide in midfield thereafter, peaked on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Commenced well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield in the early stages, slightly taken back near 1000M, found cover 900M, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, travelled keenly for some distance after passing 1150M, raced 3 wide better than midfield thereafter, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Led easily at good pace, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, pace good, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to track the leader, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up with the front runners, pace good, ran on ok.
Settled in front, pace good, ran on ok but without threats.
Bumped start, at back, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
At back, pace good, never improved.
Pressed forward, pace good, out of fuel 250M.
Midfield, pace good, emptied 350M.
Never better than midfield, on heels 100M.
Checked start, never competitive.
Awkward away, never a factor.
Settled in box seat, travelled nicely, badly held up in the early part of straight, quickened passing 150M, worked home strongly to score.
Began awkwardly and stumbled, settled midfield, commenced to improve near 600M, gradually made ground in the straight, made up nice late ground.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 200M, came line solidly.
Raced midfield on rail, tried to improve at 450M, finished well.
Raced behind midfield on rail, in the early part of straight had difficulty obtaining clear running, near 150M was steadied when crowded for room, worked home OK.
Took lead with nice early speed, fought hard but gave ground passing 100M.
Travelled at back, one-paced when asked for effort in the straight.
Raced behind the lead, tried to improve near 500M, weakened near 200M.
Failed to muster speed after start, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, no response.
Jumped nicely, travelled wide and without cover outside the lead, made the turn awkwardly then gave ground, failed to run on.
Clipped heels and stumbled when taken back, weakened in the straight, lame left front next day.

Hard ridden at start before racing in midfield, three lengths from lead. Shifted three wide on cornering and made ground quickly after straightening to join lead approaching 200m. Dashed away in final furlong for easy win.

Mustered early speed to dispute lead before being crossed approaching the 700m. Tracked leader into the straight before improving into a gap near the 250m. Finished well but couldn't repel winner. 1.5 lengths to third.

Slow to begin and subsequently raced a clear last in first section. Shifted wider on cornering but still conceded nearly six lengths passing the 400m. Made good headway from rearward position in final section.

Showed some pace to race prominent, two lengths from lead and away from the rail near the 800m. Eased away from heals near the 700m and lost a length. Boxed on in straight but was fair way from winner.
Hard ridden after start before making some ground to midfield. Moved away from the rail at the 550m and only conceded 2.5L past the 400m. Boxed on in straight but was fair way from winner.

Didn't have early speed and ridden up entering second section to hold position. Conceded 4.5 lengths entering the final section and shifted wider on the corner. Couldn't make up the ground required to challenge the frame.
Couldn't go the early pace and subsequently raced near the rear. Five lengths from lead passing the 400m and couldn't make sufficient ground to be a threat.

Showed speed to challenge for lead before eventually being crossed near the 750m. Raced one pair behind lead in middle section. Joined lead fleetingly near the 250m before peaked in final stages. Bled both nostrils.

Showed fast early speed to stride across in the lead from outside barrier. World hard before crossing to the rail past the 750m. Joined in the lead approaching the final 250m before tiring out in the final furlong.
Strode forward to be prominent after start before ridden hard passing the 800m to come across to race outside leader. Moved up to challenge after straightening before tiring out in the final 300m.
Couldn't go with the early speed and raced in midfield in the rail. Hard ridden entering the final section when 4 lengths from the lead before tiring out badly in the straight.
Began awkwardly and subsequently raced at the rear. Became unbalanced at the 900m and continued to yield ground in middle section before tailing out for remainder of race. Unsatisfactory performance.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score with still something in hand.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but not able to hold off the winner late.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, awkwardly placed near 950M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M to take a place.

Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 500M, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 11, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, a bit closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, checked near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, race prominently but trapped very wide, slightly taken back near 900M, 1 out 1 back on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 900M, led by 1/2L on turn, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 550M, 3 to 4 wide turning in, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.

Out in line, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 900M, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, kept to inside after straightening, but unable to get clear run, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently but wide early, slightly taken back after passing 1150M, 3 wide with no cover in midfield on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, found rail near 1000M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, failed to make any progress when clear thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Sent forward to share lead, on stand-side, kept on nicely to the finish. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield, on stand-side, battled on nicely to the line.
In midfield, sat one-off until took running on outside rail at 500M, checked at 150M when closing off nicely, ran on thereafter.
Sat in front of midfield, on stand-side, ran on nicely to the line. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, raced at the rear on stand-side, made ground and closed off okay.
Settled in just behind midfield, on centre-track, ran on fairly to the line.
Raced at the tail, on centre-track, saved ground.
Raced prominently, on stand-side, flattened passing 200M.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield along the outside rail until 400M, did not improve.
Hard ridden to be prominent, on centre track, did not run on. (See Incident Report)
Raced at the rear, on centre track, found nothing.
Sat towards the rear, on centre track, made no impression.
Led along the outside rail, gave ground from 200M. (Blood in trachea and see Incident Report)
Prominent, stand-side, weakened from 400M.
Soon took up running, headed under pressure on straightening, renewed effort to assert authority inside the 300 metres, just held on to the line.

Travelled 3-wide with the leader down back straight, came to challenge entering home straight and hit the front briefly on straightening, headed inside the 300 metres but fought on dourly to just fail to peg back the winner.
Moderate start, settled mainly within 4L of pace in 6th, switched out for a run from 3-wide into home straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled within 2L of the pace on the rail, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few from the widest gate, remained very wide turning into home straight, finished off the race well down the centre of the track. (Lame)
Sluggish at start and given reminders, picked up along the rail to about 4L off the speed in 7th 1200 metres out, ran on well to reach 3rd 50 metres but ran out of room and steadied close to home.
Well back, tailed-off in middle stages, commenced move and swung widest turning for home, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Prominent early, gradually taken backward to 5th just over 2L back coming onto home bend, jockey reported the horse hung out a difficult ride, kept on same pace until forced to check late.

Jumped awkwardly, travelled wide without cover in prominent position down back straight, remained 3-wide rounding home bend and into the straight, folded up quickly under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Began well, restrained to race near the rear, 3-wide home turn, let down strongly in the straight to lead near 100M, fought off the renewed challenge from runner up late stages.
Settled down in midfield, chased on well on straightening, fought hard alongside eventual winner final 200M but always held.
Chased the pace, moved up to join leaders 500M, quickened up to lead 350M, kept on well, headed by first 2 100M, held on to 3rd just.
Dropped back to the rear, 4Ls off the pace top of straight, ran on moderately between horses to just miss 3rd at the line.
Eased back to race in the rear, 4Ls off the pace at 400M, into clear 300M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
Bustled along from draw 10 and moved up to race outside leader, one paced from 250M, weakened out of contention.
Led briefly early stages, settled behind leaders going into the turn, battled on fairly from top of straight, couldn't go on final 200M.
Unable to slot in from draw 9, caught wide no cover for most part of the race, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Held up in midfield, didn't respond to riding in the straight, never threatened.
Sent forward, crossed to the lead 900M, weakened steadily turning home and dropped back to finish last.

Moderately away, raced 2Ls behind the leader, steadied off heels 1300M, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, 1-1/4L back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 300M but headed shortly thereafter, kept on well thereafter to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle near 1300M, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide at rear early, 3 wide from 1300M, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, difficult to settle early, hampered near 1300M, 7-1/2L back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover in the middle stages, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Commenced well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off well to score by a nose.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 1100M, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began smartly from gate 13, raced prominently but wide, 3/4L back on turn, bumped early in straight, kept on well to 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, finished 3rd.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.

Taken back from gate 11, raced 8 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, taken very wide early in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Clean jump, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1000M, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, bumped and unbalanced near 1150M, 8 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight. (Lame right front leg.)

Began awkwardly and stumbled, raced 3 wide with cover at rear early, difficult to settle and bumped near 1150M, 2 wide thereafter, 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off one-paced.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.

Placing: PU
Comment: Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, pulled up early in straight. (Bled.)

Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, 3 wide into straight, brushed early in straight, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began only fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly near 1050M, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside early, checked off heels near 1050M, 2 wide thereafter, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably throughout, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at tail early, a little bit closer after entering the back straight, still 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield in the early stages, 3 wide after entering the back straight, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, carried very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, brushed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight. (Lame right front leg post-race.) (Lame both front leg next day.)
Eased for cover, 1 out 1 back, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at back, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Took rail easily and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2 and checked, dashed well when clear.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace little dash 200M.
Pushed to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 400M.
Urged along to race outside the lead, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Jumped well then pushed to lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded solidly in the straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Began only fairly and lost ground, raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, made up some nice late ground.
Lay in making the turn passing 1100M, settled 3 wide midfield, made ground passing 100M.
Ridden after start, settled midfield, gained ground passing 200M, finished well.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 550M, very wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, awkwardly placed in the early part of straight, finished one-paced.
Ridden along to race outside the leaders, travelled wide and without cover, wide on straightening, weakened passing 150M.
Taken back at start, always back, limited response.
Travelled at rear, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Urged to race in box seat, no response in the straight, faded out near 150M.
Settled in one off one back, nothing when asked for effort.

Began fast to assume lead before being joined and headed after 200m. Crossed after the 550m and trailed leader. Sprinted fast after straightening to assume lead near the 200m and continued on for easy big margin win.

Began well but couldn't go early speed, positioning midfield on rail. Five lengths from lead entering the final 400m. Stayed close to the rail after straightening & made late ground inside last 150m, never a threat to winner.
Steadied after start and shifted across from wide barrier behind runners. Nearly 6 lengths from lead passing the 400m before making up a few lengths in final section.

Steadied after the start and shifted across to midfield but raced a little wide with cover in first section. Shifted wider passing the 500m and cornered very wide. Ran on fairly in last 250m but not a threat.

Showed early speed to stride across and share lead after 200m before continuing on to cross to rail near the 550m. Held around 2 length lead approaching the corner before being joined at the 200m and peaking on run last 75m.

Lost ground after start and couldn't go the early speed to tack on, racing nearly 9L from lead after first section. Continued to race rearward and conceded big margin on straightening before making late headway to midfield

Jumped fast and hard ridden before shifting across behind leading pair after 250m. Raced in third but over 3L from lead entering the straight before peaking on effort at 200m and giving a few lengths late.

Lost ground after the start and raced rearward. Bumped at 850m before making 600m turn awkwardly and losing further ground. Cornered well back and couldn't make ground late but never looked comfortable.
Obtained good position in midfield away from rail. Shifted wider on cornering when 5 lengths from lead but peaked on effort at 250m and gave a few lengths late.
Very slow to begin and didn't have early speed, racing 5 lengths from second last horse. Eleven lengths from lead at 800m and over 8 lengths from lead entering final section. Not in race.

Showed speed to race on leaders back early before shuffling back to midfield after laying out near the 600m. Only 3.5L from lead passing the 400m before cornering close to rail. Weakened out last section.

Didn't jump fast but strode forward after start and raced not far from lead but three wide. Continued to race wide without cover in middle stages. Gave some ground approaching the corner and weakened out in last section.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 750M, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly to score with still plenty gas in tank.
Commenced well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off well to take 2nd.

Began well, difficult to settle early, positioned on rail in midfield, 3-1/2L behind, saved ground on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 200M, headed shortly thereafter, ran on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside early, angled out after passing 950M and began forward move, 2nd on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1800M, settled 2 wide in 2nd in the middle stages, peaked near 650M, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1400M, 3 lengths back in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, weakened early in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 800M, peaked on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
Sat just in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on nicely to score by 1-1/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made nice ground and closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled to race in the box-seat, stayed on until emptied late.
Sat in just behind midfield, along the rail, improved and kept on well to the line.
Taken back, at the rear and on rail, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Eased and raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, emptied and headed at 150M.
Settled in one-off one-back position, weakened out at 100M.
Urged then settled outside the lead at 800M, emptied approaching 200M.
Ridden before taken back, stayed 2 wide, did not improve.
Bumped start, raced in midfield and 2 wide, run ended passing 200M.
In front of midfield, however wide and without cover, lost ground in the straight.
Made all from a low draw, held on well to the line.
Chased the leader throughout, unable to quicken to threaten throughout home straight.
Ridden early before travelling keenly when held up between runners in midfield in back straight, 3-wide rounding home bend before swinging wider into home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Slightly slow out, soon picked up to 4th about 2L off the speed on the rail, held a similar positon into home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, recovered steadily to within 3L of pace in 5th 2-wide over 600 metres out, in similar position turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.

Improved steadily to join the leaders briefly 3-wide approaching the Rock, drifted back to 3rd some 1.5L off the speed around home bend, lost position on straightening after racing wide throughout, fought on steadily.
Gradually dropped to last few, came under pressure early on home bend, tight between runners after straightening, ran on well to do best work late.
Settled well back for cover, saved ground on the rail turning for home, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres. (Questioned for riding in the straight)
Settled well back from the widest barrier, came under pressure from last few into home straight, made good progress early on but ran out of room nearing finish.

Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate losing ground, gradually taken back towards the rear in back straight and carried further back approaching the Rock, widest runner when last turning for home, finished off the race well.
Ridden early, improved to just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in but soon weakened under pressure.

Broke well from a wide gate, gradually shifted back to behind midfield but remained 4-wide without cover throughout back straight, still 3-wide rounding home bend, made no impression in the run to the line.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, reserved towards the rear 7-8Ls off the good pace, ran on strongly down outside on straightening, got up close home.
Settled down midfield, chased hard to be fighting for lead inside 200M, briefly lead inside 100M, headed by winner late.
Chased leader in a strongly run race, quickened to lead 250M, battled on when challenged by rivals both sides, peaked late had to settle for minor placing.
Never far off from leaders, swung wide into straight, ran on well and looked winning chance 200M, outstayed by top 3 final stages.
Reserved behind mid-division, 5Ls off the pace in 8th spot, saved ground throughout, worked home well but always held by leaders final 150M.
Guided to the fence after the jump, held up near rear 7Ls off the fast pace, ran on moderately on straightening, held by leaders.
Strode forward, raced keenly after 1200M setting fast tempo, headed 250M, dropped away. (Jockey : would not relax in the lead and not able to finish off the race.)
Settled just ahead of midfield, wide no cover from 1300M, swung wide home turn, failed to quicken, never a threat at any stage.
From draw 12 eased back to last after the start, over 8Ls off the good pace on settling, still the back marker turning for home, ran past weakening rivals only, Never threatened.
Slow to begin from draw 1, held up in midfield along the fence 4Ls back, came off the bridle 500M, couldn't muster the pace to get closer. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Dropped back to race behind midfield 5-6Ls off the good pace, pressed along 500M, shifted widest on straightening, didn't finish off.
Went forward from draw 9, tracked leader in a fast run race, no extra turning in, weakened rapidly to finish last.
