Hampered at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L behind the leader on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, took the lead near 200M, kept on very well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, brushed early in straight, closed off well to take a place. (Jockey dropped his right rein near 150M.)
Made heavy contact shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, headed near 200M, ran on well to final 50M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out abruptly at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly and checked, raced at rear on rail, moved closer on turn, angled out from 600M, finished off evenly.
Commenced well from a tricky gate, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, brushed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Hampered at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, slightly taken back to race 3 wide in midfield, lay out around turn, weakened early in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed forward to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, blocked 4-2 and checked severely, just ran on.
Pushed early, in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, took rail, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast tempo, sat 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Dipped badly at start, at rear, never progressed.
Eased back, never improved.
Never competitive.
Ridden along to race in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Fast out then urged along, took lead near 700M, asked for effort passing 350M, finished solidly, missed by 1/2L.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail in the straight, battled well, worked home nicely.
Travelled midfield, tried to improve passing 600M, continued to gain ground in the straight, came home well.
Ridden forward with nice early speed, settled in box seat, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M, finished OK.
Slow out, settled at back, fought hard in the straight, made up some late ground.
Settled behind midfield, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Urged to race in front of midfield, gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, no response in the straight, failed to run on.
Crowded at start then failed to muster speed despite being ridden along for some distance, limited response in the straight.
Pushed forward to race in handy position, emptied near 200M.
Always niggled but no response, raced at rear, never in it.

Began awkwardly before mustering speed to race in midfield away from the rail. Travelled 4 lengths form the lead at the 800m. Sprinted fast once balanced, striking lead at the 150m then pulling away for effortless victory.
Began fast and hard ridden to come across to race outside leader. Obtained lead at the 300m before being joined by winner at the 150m.

Strode forward after start before settling third in the clear, 2.5 lengths from lead after first section. Around 2 lengths from lead once balancing and battled on hard but couldn't match winner in last 300m.

Raced in midfield but left racing wide without cover after the 900m marker. Improved position approaching the turn and cornered 4 lengths from lead. Made some headway late but never a threat to winner.
Ridden across to race in midfield, away from rail, 5.5 lengths from lead at the 800m. Ridden hard to improve position after the 550m, before conceding 6 lengths on turn. Made up a length or two late.
Taken back after the start and raced near the rear, three wide with cover. Shifted wider on the turn before balancing up 6 lengths from lead. Battled on but never likely.
Began fast and strode to lead. Joined in the lead at the 350m before peaking on effort at the 250m and giving ground late.
Had no speed and raced rearward. Badly checked by yielding runner at the 850m and again at the 650m effectively putting pay to any chances.

Shifted across behind runners after the start and raced at the tail. Awkwardly placed behind checked horse near the 700m. Over 8 lengths from lead entering the final section and made little headway in run to line.

Began awkwardly & crowded and consequently raced rearward. Checked at the 750m before veering away from heels shortly after. Conceded 6.5 lengths after straightening and made no headway in last section.

Mustered speed to rail up to midfield in first 250m. Made the turn at the 900m awkwardly before yielding ground abruptly, throwing away any competitive chance. Reluctant to hold position  rider. No veterinary abnormalities.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, improved from 600M, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race wide behind midfield, found cover after passing 800M, wider from 600M, made some headway in straight without threatening.

Began only fairly, raced wide in midfield, no cover from near 1200M, sent forward to sit outside the leader thereafter, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began well, travelled keenly early, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off one-paced.

Jumped well, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, sat 1-2Ls behind the leader in the middle stages, easy run on turn, angled out 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out near 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently but wide, found cover near 900M, a length or so back on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1300M, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked on run near 500M, weakened thereafter, finished last.
Raced in the box-seat, battled on spiritly to the line to score by a short-head.
Sent forward to take rail and led, looked likely but was caught by winner late.
Awkward start, settled in just behind midfield, along the rail, worked home strongly from 150M to take 3rd.
Raced in one-off one-back position, travelled keenly, ran on well to the line.
Rolled forward and sat outside the lead, stayed on well until 100M despite hanging out throughout.
Settled just in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly until awkward to heels late.
Feet off at start and lost ground, recovered to be just in front of midfield, 2 wide, one paced in the straight.
Raced in just behind midfield, 2 wide, continued on one paced.
Eased then raced at the rear, along the rail, one paced and weakened late.
Bumped start, raced just in front of midfield, wide and without cover, weakened out at 200M.
Awkward start and lost ground, raced at the rear 2 wide, did not improve.
Jumped well, settled to race at the tail, asked to keep up all the way, found nothing in the straight.
In midfield, trapped wide however, not competitive.
At rear, 3 wide throughout, eased from 300M. (Hear irregularity)
Ridden along from a wide gate before settling two back in 4th coming onto home bend, cantered to lead 200 metres out, won comfortably.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, obtained lead on the rail 800 metres out, fought hard to defy challenge early in straight, but unable to fend off winner's late surge inside the final 200 metres.
Settled slightly worse than midfield, in similar position entering home straight, finished off the race nicely to snatch 3rd closing stages.
Prominent early settling in midfield and 3-wide most of the way, ran on steadily but lost 3rd inside the 100 metres.
Stumbled at the start, soon dropped to last few, remained well behind into home straight, made up good ground inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Broke well settling towards the rear, produced good late impression inside the final 250 metres despite an interrupted passage.

Pressed forward from the widest gate travelling very wide in first few, crossed to race alongside the leader coming onto home bend, unable to sustain effort and faded out of contention inside the final 300 metres.
Broke well from a low draw, settled not far off the pace in 5th on the rail, found nothing under pressure in the run to the line.
Moderate start, travelled wide behind midfield, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Jumped well, soon dropped to rear of midfield on the rail, kept on under pressure until running out of room in final 200 metres.
Close up early, gradually settled over 3L back in 6th approaching home bend, dropped further behind after straightening.
Hit the front briefly after the first 200 metres, ceded lead for 3rd rounding home bend, switched out for a run upon straightening but soon dropped out of contention.
Very awkward start losing considerable ground, remained well back racing awkwardly and went widest into home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Soon dropped to the tail end, never seen with a chance.
Driven forward leading at good pace along fence, kicked clear early straight, stuck to task when challenged by runner up late stages, held on bravely.
Began well, tracked leader in a fast run race, took a while to respond on straightening, chased well final 200M, nearest finish.
Jumped well, restrained and settled down behind midfield 7Ls off the fast pace, closed off solidly from 400M, went 3rd near 50M, nearest finish.
Began awkwardly from draw 1, settled near the rear 8Ls from leader, switched to outside 550M, stayed on moderately for 4th, safely held by first 2.
Began fairly, dropped back to 2nd last about 10Ls off leader in a fast run race, made good progress on straightening and stayed on into 5th close home.
Jumped on terms from wide draw, bustled along to be chasing leaders, caught wide until 700M, battled on and held 2nd until 200M, faded towards the line.
Close up behind leaders in a fast run race, tried hard in straight but couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaders, out of contention 150M.
Up with early pace, sat behind leaders on settling, kept on same pace final 400M, never likely.
Shifted across from wide barrier, held up behind midfield 6-7Ls off the pace, battled on fairly in the straight, no threat to leaders.
Away on terms, raced in mid-division along the 2-path, 6Ls back in 7th turning for home, kept on same pace in straight, no impression on leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, settled last over 10Ls off the fast pace in middle stages, plodded past a few weakening horses in straight. Never a factor.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, didn't go on passing 400M, weakened away.
Shifted across from wide barrier, always towards the rear, failed to respond to urgings early straight, eased final 200M. (Jockey : horse action deteriorated in straight.)
Jumped fairly, recovered to race in midfield, gave ground rapidly turning in, eased when no chance. (BLED.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly after turning in, headed close home.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still last turning in, finished off very strongly to make frame without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1000M, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide with cover in midfield, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 2nd, a length or so back, same position on turn, peaked on run near 300M, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Quickly into stride, raced 3 wide, 1-1/2L back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually from 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, checked near 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened after passing 250M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out near 600M, 4 wide turning in, took the lead near 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out from near 500M, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, improved from 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Jumped well from a middle draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, got cover from near 1000M, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line, finished 4th.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear running until passing 200M, made reasonable headway thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on evenly to final 50M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out near 550M, no daylight early in straight, bumped near 300M, inconvenienced shortly thereafter, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)

Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 1000M, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to final 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, no early speed, detached from field in the early stages, gradually recovered, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, awkwardly placed near 400M, made some progress thereafter until blocked near 150M, ran on one-paced.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from 1000M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 300M, then hampered shortly thereafter, ran on one-paced to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, weakened after passing 200M.

Chased leaders along the inside, travelled well, quickened to lead nearing 200M, kept on to hold off late challenge of 2nd.
Eased back and held up in the rear 3-wide, widest home turn, ran on strongly final 300M but couldn't reel in winner.
Settled behind midfield 5Ls off the steady pace, hard driven from 350M, boxed on evenly for 3rd, no impression on first two.
Dropped back to rear 8Ls behind leader, had some work to do turning in, made steady progress to be 4th without threatening first 2.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, gave brief response turning in, effort levelled off final 200M.
Went forward chasing leaders, improved to 2nd halfway, took over before straightening, headed near 200M, faded towards finish.
Reigned back to race in the rear 8Ls off the pace, in similar position turning in, stayed on to pass tired rivals.
Driven forward to be chasing leader, sat in 3rd from 800M, kept on same pace early straight, faded final 200M.
Settled behind midfield, caught wide no cover from 1200M, didn't respond to riding, never looked to threaten.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, couldn't finish off in the straight, never in contention.
Began awkwardly, drifted back to near the rear, in 11th spot on settling, had ground saving trip but didn't run on in straight.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot behind midfield, under serious pressure home turn, eased when no chance in straight. Tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Strode forward, crossed to lead on fence near 1200M, headed by rival 450M, gave ground rapidly to finish tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Pushed to take rail and lead, drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, settled outside the leader, ran on well for 2nd.
Slow away, hard ridden to hold the fence at back, lack room 5-3, dashed strongly when clear.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, trapped 4 wide, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, trapped 5 wide, dashed well 300M.
At back, 3 wide, blocked most straight, dashed well.
At back, trapped 4 wide throughout, little dash 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 5 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, checked badly 600M, no progress.
In front of midfield along the fence, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 400M.
Jumped sharply, ridden to take lead, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Settled in box seat, commenced to improve near 500M, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Travelled at rear, always niggled, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M, blood trachea.
Settled midfield, one-paced when asked for effort in the straight.
At start stumbled and lost ground, raced at tail, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, near 550M was checked when crowded for room, one-paced in the straight.
Urged to race outside the lead, responded OK in the early part of straight, weakened passing 100M.

Began well before shifting across one horse from rail near the 700m. Raced in fourth, 5 lengths behind tear-away leaders at the 600m. Moved up to assume lead at the 200m before drawing away late for easy victory.

Couldn't gather speed & drifted back worse than midfield. Lay outward making the turn in middle section before balancing up 7L from lead in straight. Made significant headway last section but winner was too far clear.
Began awkwardly before mustering speed to race third on rail some 3 lengths behind fast leaders at the 800m. Moved up to share lead at the 200m mark but couldn't go with winner in last furlong.

Had no speed in the early stages and consequently raced at the tail. Three lengths behind second last horse and 9 lengths from lead at 800m. Conceded huge margin at top of straight before making good headway in last 250m.

Had nice midfield position, four lengths from lead after first section. Hampered near the 700m and lost position, consequently conceding nearly 8 lengths on corner. Made some headway in straight but wasn't a threat.
Raced in midfield hard on the rail. Stayed close to the inside and conceded 5.5 lengths on cornering and effectively maintained that margin in the run to the line.
The slowest into stride and consequently raced rearward, some 7 lengths from the lead at the 800m. Continued to race rearward approaching the corner before passing a few late but not threatening.

Had speed to lead out wide before shifting across at 800m, sharing lead. Raced head-to-head with co-leader setting up 3L margin nearing corner. Joined at 200m before weakening. Rider questioned- considerable mid-race margins.

Began awkwardly before mustering early speed to challenge for lead. Shared lead approaching the 800m before challenged in middle section setting up 3L margin to third horse. Joined at 200m and weakened out late.
Hard ridden at start but had no early speed and raced at the rear of the main bunch. Lost further ground in second section, cornering last, and 10 lengths from lead. Didn't run on in straight.

Strode forward to good position early, away from rail in first four. Cornered awkwardly at the 700m and lost ground. Hard ridden from the 600m when continuing to lose position. Well back on corner & gave further ground late.

Raced worse than midfield away from rail. Was conceding substantial margin throughout, including over 8 lengths on straightening. Gave further ground in straight. Vet exam revealed blood in trachea & lame (right fore-leg).
Always close up behind leaders, moved up to 2nd on straightening chasing leader, hit lead 50M after a prolonged tussle with that rival. (Jockey fined for improper use of whip.)
Pushed forward, crossed to the lead 1400M, set steady pace, taken on by winner mid-straight, rallied to the line and only gave way grudgingly close home.
Began well from draw 1, eased back to midfield, 3Ls off leader at 400M, stayed on well to be nearest at the finish. (Lame next day.)
Settled down in midfield 2-wide, just over 3Ls off the pace entering home turn, brought wide to challenge, chased steadily to finish a non-threatening 4th.
Soon pushed along after the start, improved to race outside leader 1200M, under pressure to keep up 500M, battled on same pace in straight, no threat to leaders passing 200M.
Settled 5Ls back in a position behind midfield, shifted out 800M to improve on outside, just battled in the straight and never close enough. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Not hurried early stages, held up near last, driven along 450M but just plugged away to the line, made no impression.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, reserved in the rear, last turning in, ran past tired rivals only.
Began only fairly, proved difficult to settle from 1300M, in 8th place turning for home , didn't do much in the straight, never in the hunt.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, always towards the rear, failed to respond to riding 500M, never a threat. (Lame next day.)
Crowded on jumping, chased leaders 2-wide, under whip to hold position 550M, dropped away in the run home. Tailed out (Unacceptable Performance.)
Sent forward to take rail and shared lead, kept on going to score rather comfortably by 1-1/4L.
Urged and settled in front of midfield, wide when rounding turn, worked home well to take 2nd.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, continued on fairly for 3rd.
Raced in one-out one-back position, kept on until found no extra late.
Lost ground at start, and subsequently on rail at the tail, saved minor ground in the straight.
Sat just behind midfield, 2-3 wide at turn, pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, checked at 350M, did not run on thereafter.
In about midfield, wide until 700M however, did not quicken at any stages. (See Incident Report)
Awkward start, settled in box-seat, dropped back in the straight.
At rear, 2 wide, not competitive.
Urged, shared lead at 2 deep, gave ground on straightening.
Didn't muster, at rear and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Began well to lead, quickened to hold a clear advantage rounding home bend, still held 1L break after straightening, just held on under pressure.
Ridden early and soon came to chase the leader, travelled just over 2L back in 3rd in fast split rounding home bend, fought on well inside the final 300 metres to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in last few, finished off the race strongly from a long way back into the straight but the post came too soon.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield some 6L off the speed, made steady headway in straight but never going to feature.

Recovered swiftly from a moderate start settling within 3L of pace in 3rd on the rail, gained closer for 1L 2nd into the straight despite the fast pace around the bend, folded up quickly inside the final 150 metres.
Taken well back from a wide gate, commenced move and went 4-wide into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate settling wide in midfield, in similar spot in remote 4th turning into home straight, one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield on the rail, faded gradually after straightening.
Jumped very awkwardly losing ground, remained well behind most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Moderate start, niggled along in first few, unable to keep up when the quick pace on the bend, dropped further away after straightening.
Began well, soon led, quickened up pace from 1000M, shook off nearest pursuer early straight and kept galloping strongly to the line, never in any danger.
Handily placed behind leaders, tried hard in straight but couldn't get closer to the leader (eventual winner), held 2nd comfortably.
Unable to slot in, raced 3-wide in mid-division, 3Ls behind eventual winner at 400M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 3rd.
Away with them , ended up in a 3-wide spot behind midfield, driven out 500M, made some progress but never close enough to challenge leaders, stayed on into 4th late.
Went forward and prompted the pace on outside, held ground early straight, faded final 150M.
From draw 12 taken across to race at the back, swung wide for home and ran past tired rivals only, no impression on leaders
Settled down in midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, battled at same pace only, never reached contention.
Dropped back from draw 13, raced in last early stages, moved a bit closer entering back straight, wide on final bend and couldn't finish off. (Blood in trachea / Lame next day).
Reserved behind midfield 6-7Ls back, in 10th place on settling, driven out 500M but run ended quickly on straightening.
Towards the rear, never travelled and had to be niggled along from halfway, never involved.
Shifted across from draw 11, held up 2nd last , over 8Ls off leader home turn, ran past well beaten rivals only. Never in the picture.
In midfield 4-5Ls away, checked 600M losing ground, kept to inside on straightening but couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Pressed forward from draw 14 to be chasing the pace, caught wide no cover throughout, no extra passing 450M, weakened away finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Close up in 5th on settling, came under heavy pressure after 800M to maintain its position, gave ground 600M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance / Lame next day).

Strode forward, always in the firing line, emerged to lead 400M, fought on well to the line holding off rivals on both sides.
Tracked leaders along the stand's rail, chased on well final 400M, but always held by winner.
Rolled forward to be right up with leaders, kept on steadily when driven out 350M, held by winner final 150M.
Shared lead towards the stands' rail, couldn't go on with leaders near 200M, one paced late stages.
Began fairly, chased leaders in mid-pack, driven out 400M, ran on fairly to the line, never dangerous.
In mid-division, just over 2Ls off leaders halfway, plodded on without threat final 400M.
Awkwardly away, outpaced early stages and raced in detached last, made some progress up the fence final 400M but not reaching leaders.
Never far off from leaders, ran past well beaten horses only. No impression on leaders.
Awkwardly away, close up behind leaders, raced towards the center of track, came under pressure 500M, outpaced and weakened final 200M.
Towards the rear of the main group, couldn't quicken when asked, never involved.
Pressed forward to be up with the pace, commenced to hang in from 800M, proved difficult to ride, eased final 200M. (Unacceptable racing manner.)
At back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M to score with ease.
Midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, led 400M, overhauled 200M, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, at rear, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, weakened 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, eased back, suited by the fast pace, lack turn of foot.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, favoured by the fast pace, never improved.
Eased at start. 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, faded 350M.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off quickly 400M.
Raced in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, quickened near 100M, finished strongly to score.
Settled outside the lead, fought hard in the straight, worked home solidly, missed by Neck.
Niggled to take lead passing 800M, responded nicely in the straight, finished solidly.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at tail on fence, tried to improve passing 600M, limited response in the straight.
Very slow out, settled behind midfield on rail, passing 1000M commenced to prove very difficult to settle, no response in the straight, stalls test.

Raced in midfield on the rail, 3.5 lengths form lead at the 800m. Improved along the rail to be on the leaders back on corner. Eased around heels at the 400m, struck lead at the 350m & ran away in final furlong for easy win.
Showed early speed to stride to the lead, crossing to rail after 200m. Joined and headed at the 250m before fighting back gamely in the last 100m to reclaim second, winner was too good however.

Hard ridden to be prominent in early stages. Hampered at the 950m when crossed before settling behind leading pair 2 lengths from lead. Eased three wide at the 500m, shared lead at the 250m before boxing on late.

Had no early speed and raced at the tail on the fence. Six lengths from lead after the first section. Improved position, 2.5L from lead on cornering before shifting out at the 350m and passing a few in the run home.
Steadied behind runners towards to tail shortly after start. Shifted out and was the widest runner on cornering, some 4 lengths from lead. Made up some ground relative to all except the winner.
Began fast from wide barrier and strode across to race outside the leader after 200m. Raced at the leaders flanks entering the last section before weakening out in final 300m.
Hard ridden after start before settling in midfield between runners. Conceded 4 lengths passing the 800m. Had clear running after straightening but peaked on effort at 300m.
Bumped & hampered after start and subsequently raced worse than midfield. Drifted back in middle section before cornering next to last, over 4L from lead. Gave further ground in the run to the line.
Had no early speed and raced at the tail. Next to last when taking the turn but failed to run on in the straight.

Gathered speed after start & strode forward to midfield. Hampered near the 950m before being left racing wide without cover. Cornered 3 lengths from the lead before peaking at the 400m and tiring out in the last section.

Strode to midfield but raced four wide without cover in first section. Continued to cover extra ground in middle section before cornering wide, 3L from lead. Yielded considerable ground in the straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Shifted in at start, raced at rear on rail, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Began well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover better than midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1100M to race outside the leader, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently, got cover after passing 1100M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, steadied off heels near 750M, angled out after passing 500M, failed to make any progress in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, sent forward after passing 1100M to sit outside the leader, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden from 550M, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final furlong.
Prominent, wide and without cover, kept on going and hung on to score by a nose.
In front of midfield, 3 wide with cover, fought on gamely and pushed winner to the wire, missed by a nose.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, found no daylight from 300-200M, continued nicely once cleared.
Asked to be in one-off one-back position, ran on well to the line.
Urged and settled to race outside the lead, in touch until emptied late.
Awkward start and lost ground, settled at rear along the rail, was improving until held up at 150M, ran on.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 2 wide, saved ground in the straight.
Settled to race in the box-seat, ran on until emptied inside final 150M.
Raced at the tail, 2 wide, made ground in the straight and ran on.
Bumped start, then taken back to be at the rear, 2-3 wide, saved minor ground.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, improved slightly.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, weakened and headed passing 200M. (See Incident Report)
In midfield, along the rail, one paced and emptied 150M out.
Slow to jump, recovered in behind midfield, never competitive.
Made all, won unextended.
Moderate start, settled one from last, remained same into the straight, finished off the race strongly to snatch 2nd final strides.

Moderate start, settled some 3L back 2-wide in midfield in 6th or 5th, shifted wider for a run entering straight, ran on to reach 2nd over 200 metres out, lost 2nd to fast-finishing EAGLE WAY final strides.
Broke well, settled just over 2L back in 4th, in similar position into the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well, settled one back in 3rd shifting one off the rail for cover behind the leader when passing the 900 metres, chased the leader into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in rear from the widest gate, trailed the field into straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Improved steadily along the rail to midfield 1200 metres out, remained similar turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in last few in 7th, in similar position turning in, made no impression in the run to the line.
Began from a wide gate, travelled alongside the leader most of way until the 400 metres, folded up quickly.
Pushed forward under 10lb claimer, crossed to lead just before the turn, kept responding in straight, dug deep closing stages to fend off a strong challenge from the runner up.
Tracked leaders 2-wide, into top gear chasing winner from 250M, held by short head. Well clear from remainders.
Jumped well from draw 1, chased leaders, checked 850M and drifted back to midfield, ran on well in the straight to get 3rd but couldn't reach first 2.
Checked at the start, raced in 2nd last, badly held up 300M-150M, chased strongly when clear to just miss 3rd. Entitled to finish closer.
Jumped evenly, drifted back to race towards the rear, wide home turn, closed off well down outside, nearest finish. (Lame next day.)
Dropped back from wide barrier, improved position to be racing behind midfield home turn, brought wide to challenge making some late headway without threatening.
Brushed with rivals after the start, raced in mid-division, 3-wide no cover from 900M, kept on evenly on straightening, held ground final 200M.

Hampered at the start, restrained in midfield, pushed along from 600M, kept grinding on early straight but unable to quicken final 250M. (Jockey : first time race round a turn may contribute to disappointing performance.)
Pressed forward to be outside leader entering the turn, ran on early straight and had every possible chance, peaked on its run 200M, weakened towards the line.
Eased back to rear from wide barrier, moved closer to be just behind midfield 700M, 5Ls to make up 400M, not much into finishing effort.
Raced in mid-division, 3-wide making home turn, came off bridle 600M, didn't finish off the race.
Up with early pace, severely checked 900M, in 3rd place home turn, found no extra passing 300M, weakened away.
Reared at the start losing ground, detached in rear, eased down turning home, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, improved from 700M, 3 wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 150M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden from 550M, finished off evenly.

Commenced well from gate 12, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, hard ridden turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Out in line, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, one-paced when clear thereafter.

Began well, sent forward to take the lead, headed after passing 1300M, retook the lead near 1000M, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed to cross near 1200M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from gate 14, race 3W with no cover, 1 to 2Ls back, moved forward after entering the back straight, took the lead near 1300M, headed near 1000M, peaked turning in, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Out in line, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near after passing 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, improved from 550M, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take a place.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, cover, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, 2nd on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 13, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly from 1200M, closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.

Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover at rear early, moved a bit closer in the middle stages but still very wide, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, blocked near 150M, eased thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Began well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, improved from 450M, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made no progress when clear final 200M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, 2 wide on turn, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide at back, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the lead, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 300M, weakened 150M.
Hard ridden to keep up at back on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M weakened.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
At back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 200M, little dash.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, suited by the slow pace, weakened 250M.
Failed to muster speed to lead, trapped 3 wide in midfield, emptied 300M.
Settled in front of midfield, asked for effort passing 650M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, battled strongly to score.
Travelled midfield, improved passing 400M, responded solidly in the straight, finished strongly, missed by Nose.
Settled in box seat, passing 1000M travelled keenly, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, improved near 600M, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 600M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, fought well in the straight.
On jumping was bumped and became unbalanced then taken back, midrace move to outside the leaders, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
On jumping was bumped and became badly unbalanced, raced behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Urged to race outside the lead, near 650M hard ridden to prevent a runner to cross, gave ground near 100M.
Ridden along to lead, niggled passing 650M to keep leading, weakened passing 100M.
Raced midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 450M, limited response in the straight.
On jumping was checked when crowded for room, then taken back, asked for effort near 600M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
On jumping was hampered then taken back, moved to midfield near 600M, failed to run on in the straight.
Showed early speed to stride to the lead after 150m. Raced a length clear on cornering before racing 2 lengths clear inside final 250m. Got a little tired near line but had enough in hand.
Obtained trailing position just worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail at the 450m before cornering 4.5L from lead. Made good headway in final 250m but winner was too far clear.
Began fairly before mustering early speed to race behind leading pair. Under 2 lengths behind the winner on cornering and finished off soundly in the straight.

Crowded after the start and subsequently raced at the rear of the field, conceding 6 lengths after the first section. Stayed close to the rail on cornering before shifting in at the 225m when making good late ground.
Began well before sliding across to midfield away from the rail. Strode closer passing the 450m, before cornering 2.5L from lead. Peaked on run inside final 100m.

Ridden forward after the start to gain midfield position on the rail. Hard ridden past 400m before shifting wider on cornering, 3L form lead. Peaked on run after straightening, and yielded a length or two late.

Hampered after the start & subsequently raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Five lengths form the lead at half-way, before being forced wider near the 450m. Cornered very wide and made no ground in straight.

Began fast & strode forward to dispute lead in early stages before settling 0.5L from lead at half-way. Ridden up on cornering to keep in touch with leader before peaking in straight & giving ground in last furlong.
Crowded and lost ground at the start and consequently raced at the rail. Continued to race rearward and conceded 7 lengths entering the final section, failed to make up any ground in the straight
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length on turn, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide from near 800M, half length back on turn, finished off well but couldn't catch the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off one-pace. (Lost right front plate.)
Clean jump, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, inconvenienced near 400M, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight. (Roarer.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, showed a good turn of foot passing 200M to run on and scored by a neck.
Awkward start, sat just in front of midfield along the rail, worked home nicely to take 2nd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, weakened late but hung onto 3rd.
Rolled forward into the box-seat, ran on fairly to the line.
Inconvenienced after the start, slotted into midfield 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Taken back, raced at the rear 2 wide, made ground steadily in the straight.
Raced in one-off one-back position, bumped at times between 300-200M, pretty one paced thereafter.
Eased and sat in worse than midfield, along the rail, made ground steadily in the straight.
Failed to muster, sat just behind midfield along the rail, not fully tested at times when reluctant to shift out.
Eased and raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, saved no ground.
Crowded after the start, at tail along the rail, did not improve.
Prominent but wide initially, moved to race outside lead at 1400M when asked, weakened upon straightening.
Made all, held on under pressure.
Always thereabouts, dropped 2L back to 3rd rounding home bend, renewed effort after straightening but unable to peg back the winner.
Moderated start, soon recovered to 5th within 3L of pace despite inconvenienced 1000 metres out, in similar position turning into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon dropped to last few, saved ground on the rail turning in, baulked before obtaining a clear passage over 200 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start, soon recovered to rear of midfield in 8th about 6L off the pace, ran on in straight without threatening.

Recovered quickly under pressure from a moderate start, caused interference 1000 metres out when 2.5L 4th and wide before continuing to improve to join the leader, weakened out of contention inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to last, trailed the field to the 200 metres, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, one-paced.
Niggled at early, travelled 3-wide without cover in midfield in back straight, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate settling well behind, inconvenienced upon straightening, made some late impression.
Began well from the widest gate, soon taken back towards the rear but remained wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace in the straight. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped well, settled just over 2L back in 4th on the rail, came under pressure to hold place 600 metres out, faded under pressure after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began well from draw 1, settled just behind leaders, quickened to lead 150M, kept on well to line holding off 2nd.
Taken across behind runners, towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, ran on well final 300M, held by winner.
Caught wide early stages, improved to race outside the lead 1000M, battled on well in the straight but not pace of first 2 final 150M.
Settled down 2-wide in mid-division, switched out from 700M going forward to join leaders, kept on steadily on straightening, outstayed by first 2 late stages.
Crossed to the lead passing 1400M, led steadily, found less than expected when tackled by rivals the straight, headed 200M out, faded.
Shifted across from wide draw, held up near last 7Ls back, stayed on into 6th but no threat to leaders.
Held up in midfield along the fence, kept on same pace final 300M, never a serious threat. (Lame next day.)
Taken across to race behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace in 9th on settling, bid his time on inside but closed off only fairly in the straight.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, raced in last 8Ls from leader, bustled along 600M out, stayed on past beaten rivals, never near to challenge.
Restrained in midfield along the 2-path, swung wide home turn, couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Always close up but caught wide without cover, couldn't go with leaders early straight, faded away 200M. (Lame next day.)
Tracked leaders in a steadily run race, weakened steadily turning home and dropped back to finish last.

Jumped well, showed very good speed to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on very strongly to the line and scored, impressive debut.
Commenced well, raced prominently, a length behind the leader at 400M, finished off well to take 2nd but had no chance with the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 lengths or so behind the leader in the early stages, peaked near 400M, kept on evenly to the line, no threat to the first two.
Began well but got no early speed, crossed by the rivals easily, 5 lengths behind at 400M, finished off evenly to make frame, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, sent forward to race prominently, crossed by the rival near 600M, peaked shortly thereafter, weakened gradually after passing 400M.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Began fairly, positioned a length behind the leader early, peaked in the middle stages, weakened quickly thereafter, finished tailed off. (See Racing Incidents.)
Pushed to keep up just off the leaders on the fence, ran on well 300M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily.
Slow away, at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground without threats.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made minor ground.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide, ran on fairly.
At back, trapped 2-4 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Never a factor.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, soon emptied 250M.
Ridden to race behind leaders, responded solidly when asked for effort near 400M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Took lead on outside rail with nice early speed, responded nicely when placed pressure, worked home solidly.
Raced behind the lead on outside rail, battled well passing 200M, finished well.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield, niggled near 600M, shifted in to improve passing 300M, made up some nice late ground.
Niggled along to race inside the leader, gave some ground passing 200M.
Urged to settled midfield on outside rail, tried to improve near 400M, one-paced.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled behind midfield, shifted in to improve passing 400M, one-paced when asked for effort.
Urged along to race in front of midfield, limited response when placed pressure passing 400M.
Jumped OK, settled inside the lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Began only fairly and lost ground when crowded for room, then taken back, gained limited ground near 150M.
Crowded at start then taken back, settled at tail on outside rail, no response when asked for effort.
Raced behind leaders, hard ridden but weakened passing 200M.
Settled behind midfield, always back, failed to run on.
Raced midfield in middle of track, faded out passing 300M.

Crowded after the start, consequently racing worse than midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail when improving approaching turn. Sprinted hard past the 350m before taking lead inside 200m & continuing on for easy win.

Began well striding to midfield 2.5 lengths from the lead passing the 800m. Strode closer, one length from lead entering final section before striking front at 300m. Yielded lead at furlong marker before fighting on late.

Showed early speed to share lead before steadying behind leading pair after 400m. Raced on leaders back taking the corner before improving between runners to share lead at 300m. Peaked on run at 150m.

Steadied after the start & shifting across to race second from last. Moved away from the rail at 500m before shifting out further & bumping on turn. 5 lengths from lead on balancing & maintained that margin in the straight.

Settled worse than midfield away from the rail. Moved three wide passing the 800m when 7 lengths from lead. Forced very wide passing the 550m & cornered very wide before passing a few in the run to the line.
Held rail position in midfield racing 4.5 lengths form the lead after the first 600m. Shifted out approaching the turn when racing adjacent with the winner but couldn't go in in the final section.

Shifted out on jumping & lost ground before gathering speed to improve to midfield. Drifted back in middle section before being checked near 550m. Next to last, 6L from lead entering final section before passing a few late.

Ridden forward before shifting across & racing three wide with cover throughout early & middle sections. Shifted wider on cornering before being bumped on straightening. Peaked in the final section & gave a few lengths late.

Ridden forward in first 250m before drifting back to midfield away from the rail. Continued to drift back passing the 750m before shifting wider passing the 550m. Raced tight at the 300m but was always well back.

Strode forward to contest lead when racing wide on the track in first 400m. Shifted across one off rail to share lead at the 850m turn. Forfeited lead passing the 400m and gave significant ground in the last 300m.

Strode forward to assume narrow lead after 250m. Joined in the lead on the outside at the 850m turn. Had sole lead momentarily entering the final section before being joined at the 300m and peaking on run in the final 250m.
Had no early speed and was 3L behind second last horse after 200m. Continued to race a clear last 8L form lead at the 800m. Hard ridden on cornering and never featured.
Began only fairly before holding the rail and improving to midfield. Cornered close to the rail but was hard ridden prior to straightening. Folded up in the last section and was well beaten.
Showed early speed to be prominent but was left without cover and a little wide for most of the middle stages. Ridden up from the 500m to hold position before yielding ground from the corner.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began well, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out after passing 600M, finished off evenly to take a place.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter, nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, 4 wide turning, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Crowded out start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, weakened gradually after turning in, eased after crowded near 200M.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, carried wider near 550M, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out.
Crowded start, settled in midfield 2 wide, showed good kick at 150M, ran on nicely to score.
Niggled along, took rail and led, continued until caught by winner at 50M, held on for 2nd.
Eased back, raced in behind midfield 2 wide, made nice progress to the line to take 3rd.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off strongly.
Awkward start, then raced in the box-seat, ran on fairly.
At rear, along the rail, made minor ground in the straight.
Awkward start, settled in one-off one-back position, kept on going to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, was one paced.
Failed to muster, prominent but wide and without cover, faded from passing 250M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover, did not threaten.
In midfield, wide but with cover, lost ground in the straight.
Hard ridden to race outside the lead, dropped off at 300M.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, commenced move making final turn, responded well under pressure in straight to just get up on line.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, commenced move rounding home bend, sustained progress from 6th into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Moderate start, led the main group before ceding front-running rail position approaching home bend, came to challenge under pressure from 1L 2nd into straight, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out only to be caught late.
Travelled wide in first few early stages settling some 2L back in 3rd approaching home bend, unable to quicken under pressure to challenge inside final 400 metres.
Settled just off the pace on rail, some 2L back in 4th into straight, improving steadily when hampered 150 metres out, kept on under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on the rail, shaken up rounding home bend and saved ground into straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield 2-wide, slightly worse coming onto home bend and switched wide into straight, produced good early impression down the centre of the track.
Crowded at start, settled in last few, widest runner turning for home, one-paced.

Led from the widest gate, stuck to the far rail before crossing for inside rail approaching the first bend, maintained over 1L advantage on the bend and early in straight, swamped over 250 metres out.
Jumped very awkwardly losing considerable ground, soon recovered to last few on the rail, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on at the one pace.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Settled mainly in midfield, wide into home straight, made no impression. (Blood in trachea)
Niggled along in midfield early stages gaining closer to 5th 3-wide coming onto home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.

Placing: PU
Comment: Jumped fairly, prominent in back straight, drifted back to 6th some 4L off the pace coming onto home bend, pulled up on top of home straight. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well, just couldn't hold off the winner.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, moved a bit forward after passing 1000M, 3 wide, a length or so back on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked on run near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, 3 lengths or so back, raced tight near 950M, 3 wide with cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Commenced well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 550M, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, crowded near 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, bumped near 450M, made good progress despite hanging out in the run to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, awkwardly placed on heels near 700M, 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 4 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, hard ridden from 550M, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Commenced well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd early, took the lead after passing 1000M, led by half length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened and headed shortly thereafter.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1200M, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)

Steadied across from outside gate to race midfield away from rail. Shifted wider at the 500m before balancing 4.5L from lead entering final section. Hit top gear inside last 300m & made late ground to snare lead in last 50m.
Began well and strode forward to race at the leaders flank after 200m. Cornered less than a length form the lead before sprinting well to assume lead inside final 300m. Passed by winner in final 50m.

Began well and strode to lead before being steadied across to rail after 250m. Cornered under a length in front before being joined in the lead inside the final 300m. Boxed on strongly in late stages.

Had no early speed and steadied across to last after 150m. Continued to race rearward, conceding 9L at the 800m & entered straight conceding similar margin. Made significant headway in the final 400m from rearward position.

Began fairly before being ridden forward to make ground & race behind leading pair. Moved closer to leading pair before straightening 2L behind entering final section. Couldn't go with challengers inside the final 300m.

Shifted back behind runners after the start and raced rearward. Drifted back to the tail of the field at the 800m, 9 lengths from lead. Shifted very wide on cornering before making late headway down the middle of track.

Steadied across after the first 300m to race midfield before being left three wide without cover from the 1000m. Forced very when making ground near the 500m before balancing 6 lengths from lead. Held margin in final section.

Strode forward after the start to race behind leading pair away from the rail. Hard ridden passing the 600m and lost a length before straightening. Peaked on effort at the 350m and gave a few lengths late.

Began well before being restrained to midfield away from the rail. Ridden forward past the 600m when attempting to improve before balancing 8L from the lead at the top of the straight. Was always well back & didn't threaten.

Strode forward to be prominent early before being crossed and steadying to midfield after 200m. Stayed close to the inside on cornering when 3L from lead. Peaked on run at the 300m and yielded a few lengths late in the race.
Began well before easing into midfield position on the rail after the first furlong. Had clear running on cornering when 6L from the lead but couldn't run on in the final section.

Couldn't go with the early speed & was steadied across to race worse than midfield on the rail. Stayed close to the rail on the turn when conceding significant margin. Yielded a few lengths in last section & was well beaten.

Crowded for room on jumping & consequently raced towards the rear of the field. Raced a little wide but with cover in middle sections before cornering nearly 10L from lead. Failed to run on in final section & was well beaten.
