Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly after turning in, scored by 1-1/4L.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hard ridden after passing 400M, wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Jumped with them, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, angled out in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Clean jump from gate 12, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still last turning in, one-paced in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to win.
Pushed to hold the lead under pressure, harmed by the fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 100M.
At back, 2 wide, whilst hanging in severely pulled its bit out of its mouth, unable to be properly tested in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairy.
Slow away, took rail at rear, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Slow away, at back, no progress.
Never a factor.
Ridden along to race midfield, always niggled, wide on straightening, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Settled in box seat with nice early speed, travelled comfortably, responded solidly in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight, came line nicely.
Travelled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 400M, awkwardly placed in final stages, not fully tested.
Jumped nicely, ridden to take lead, commenced to improve passing 400M, gave ground passing 50M.
Taken back at start, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, finished OK.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, worked home one-paced.
Urged to race outside the lead, asked for effort passing 500M, came under pressure in the straight, weakened near 100M.
Steadied after start but was not able to obtain cover, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.

Steadied after start to race midfield away from rail. Shifted wider at the 450m before entering the last section 4.5L from lead. Sprinted well at 250m & continued on to snatch lead late. Trainer questioned re. improved perf.

Raced midfield away from rail shortly after the start and held position in middle stages. Made ground when shifting wider at 450m before cornering 2L from lead. Sprinted hard to assume lead at 200m before being headed late.

Steadied after the start and shifted across to race at the tail on the outside. Shifted out at the 450m before entering final section some 6L from lead. Made good headway in last 250m to be narrowly beaten.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners after the start to race at the tail. Was the last horse to corner and then shifted out on straightening before finishing off well in last 250m.
Steadied across to the rail approaching the 1200m and maintained midfield position approaching turn. Cornered close to the rail and made up a few lengths in the final 250m.

Shifted across to the rail in the first 250m and raced worse than midfield in middle stages. Shuffled back to second last, 6.5L from lead entering the final section before passing a few in the final 100m.
Began well and assumed leading role before being joined on the outside at the 1000m. Held the lead until being joined at the 200m & giving a few lengths late.

Strode forward to race near the lead before racing tight & bumping on multiple occasions after the 1200m. Was on leaders back before shifting three wide near the 450m. Straightened 2L from the lead before peaking at 200m.

Ridden forward after start to challenge for lead. Raced wide & worked hard until shifting outside the lead at the 1000m. Within a length of the lead on cornering before peaking on run at the 250m & tiring in the late stages.

Held the rail in midfield in the first section. Crowded midrace and lost ground before passing the 800m 3.5 lengths from lead. Cornered close to the rail before peaking on effort inside the final 200m.

Ridden hard after the start but failed to show speed & was steadied to race worse than midfield. Raced wide without cover from the 900m. Couldn't improve approaching the corner & yielded further ground in straight.

Raced near the lead before being bumped & tightened on numerous occasions after the 1100m. Shifted in to race with cover at the 900m before coming under pressure & yielding ground from the 600m. Was well beaten & must trial.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 400M, wide into straight, finished off strongly to score.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide turning, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, half length back on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, crowded early in straight then inconvenienced near 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat a length behind the leader thereafter, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently but wide, found rail near 700M, travelled well on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sat 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, crowded near 1000M, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Travelled in the box-seat, continued on nicely to the line to score by a neck.
Took cover, settled in midfield, wide but with cover, made nice ground and closed off strongly to the line.
Sent forward, took rail and led, ran on until weakened late, just hung onto 3rd.
Settled one-out one-back, continued on fairly to the line.
Jumped fairly only, at rear along the rail, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Urged and raced outside the lead, kept on until emptied at 100M.
Crowded start, settled in midfield along the rail, improved slightly only. (See Incident Report)
Taken back and raced at the tail, 2 wide, made ground in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 2 wide, made minor ground.
In midfield, along the rail, never threatened.
In front of midfield, wide however, weakened out from rounding turn. (See Incident Report)
Settled some 2L back in 3rd, came to challenge turning in and hit the front 200 metre out, held on under pressure to the line.

Broke well, settled within 4L of pace in 7th and then 6th in back straight, gained to 5th passing the Rock and 4th rounding home bend within 3L of the pace, ran on dourly under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in last few from the widest gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, widest runner turning in, ran on stoutly to just fail to get up on line.
Settled just worse than midfield from a wide gate, in similar position rounding home bend, ran on well in straight to be nearest at finish.

Settled for 3rd on the rail, carried backward a few times in back straight dropping to midfield onto home bend, saved ground turning in, ran on to hold some chance 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.

Moderate start, settled better than midfield within 4L of pace on the rail, shuffled backward a few times in back straight dropping towards the rear, tight between runners early in home straight, finished off the race well. (Lame)
Very awkward at the start and soon dropped to last few, kept on well in the run to the line.
Travelled wide without cover towards the rear, commenced move on the outside rounding home bend, kept on one pace without quickening in the straight.

Jumped best, taken back 3-wide without cover in better than midfield, gained closer from halfway out to join the leader on the bend, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, led on the first bend and obtained rails run passing the 900 metres, headed under pressure inside the 300 metres and weakened noticeably. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden positively to obtain rails run inside the leader, obtained cover in 2nd passing the 900 metres, dropped away quickly despite reminders from over 600 metres out. (Roarer)
Crowded on jumping, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, awkwardly placed near 1200M, moved closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3W with no cover, 2Ls or so back, moved closer after entering the back straight, sat outside the leader from 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.

Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, challenged from near 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, wider from 400M, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Shifted out shortly after start and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from gate 11, raced 2 wide in 2nd, crossed by rival near 700M, 3 wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle on the first turn, 4 lengths back in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, improved on turn, took the lead after passing 600M, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, sat a length behind the leader after entering the back straight, improved on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, found a 2 wide spot after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, still well back on turn, made little progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, still well back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 9 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, headed near 600M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 1200M, 6 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, steadied off heels near 800M, still well back on turn, emptied early in straight. (Lame right front leg.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Midfield, pace good, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Settled in front of midfield, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
At back, pace good, progressed steadily 350M, run ended 100M.
At back along the fence, pace good, held up most straight, made steady ground.
Box seat, pace good, blocked up 4-2, just held ground when clear.
At rear, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Midfield, trapped wide, made early move 600M, run ended 150M.
At back, pace good, ran on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward, pace good, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, emptied 250M.
Midfield, trapped wide, no progress in straight.
Never better than midfield.
Eased back, raced ungenerously, never competitive.
Eased back, never a factor.
Ridden to race in front of midfield, responded solidly in the straight, continued to make ground to score.
Settled midfield on rail, held up in the early part of straight, quickened passing 150M, finished solidly.
Travelled behind midfield, very wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Urged along after start, raced at rear, had difficulty to obtain clear running passing 400M, gained ground passing 150M.
Took box seat with nice early speed, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort near 500M, came line well.
Detached in early stages, kept on rail in the straight, worked home OK.
Ridden along to take lead, fought hard but gave ground near 150M.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, tried to improve but gave ground passing 150M.
Jumped sharply, raced in one back one off position, gave ground near 200M, failed to run on.
Began only fairly, improved to outside the lead passing 900M, weakened passing 300M.
Raced 3 wide in handy position, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, emptied near 300M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, checked at entrance to the straight, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, travelled keenly and difficult to settle in middle stages, faded out near 200M.
Showed speed to race forward before getting leaders back after 250m. Eased away from the rail on cornering before sprinting hard once balanced. Took lead inside 220m and raced away for solid win.
Began well before steadying across to race in midfield, one horse away from rail. Shifted out at the 250m before making good ground in the final furlong for second.

Strode to midfield after the start but raced three horses wide. Lay out around the home turn and lost ground before cornering very wide, 5 lengths form lead. Made good late headway in the final 250m to not be beaten far.

Began well before drifting back to race worse than midfield, 5 lengths from lead after the first section. Continued to race rearward before picking up ground in the straight, changing direction at the 150m & finishing well.

Slow to begin before mustering speed to settle just worse than midfield on the rail. Cornered on the rail before entering the final section 4.5L from lead. Made up a few lengths in the straight but didn't threaten winner.
Shifted back behind runners after the start and raced at the tail, conceding over 7 lengths after the first section. Cornered last before making up good ground in the straight.

Began fast and strode forward before being crossed, racing second on outside without cover. Strode up to get within a length of the lead before peaking on effort at the 250m and losing a few lengths late.

Crowded & lost ground after start, consequently racing just worse than midfield. Shifted wider at the 450m before cornering 4 lengths from lead. Checked & lost ground 250m before holding margin under no riding to the line.
Showed early speed to lead before crossing to rail after 250m. Cornered over 1 length clear in the lead before being joined at the 220m and giving ground when tiring in late stages.

Ridden forward and worked hard in first section before improving to third, three wide without cover passing the 800m. Continued to cover additional ground before peaking on run near the 200m & losing ground late.
Shifted across to rail when striding to midfield in first furlong. Travelled well when cornering close to the rail, 3 lengths from the lead before failing to challenge in the straight.
Shifted back behind runners after the start and raced a clear last. Continued to race at the tail on cornering and failed to make any ground in the straight.
Began smartly, showed good speed to take the lead on the stands rail, ridden after passing 350M, showed very good response, easily scored.
Jumped well, raced prominently near to the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on very well to the line, just no match for winner.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, near to the stands rail, closed off well to take a place without threatening. (Lost left front plate.)
Commenced well from gate 14, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced in the middle of the track, 2 to 3 lengths back, showed limited response in the final 400M, never a threat to the first few.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked on run near 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, closer to the middle of the track, peaked near 450M, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, only showed limited response in the final 400M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield, nearer to the stands rail, made no impression final 400M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear in the middle track, no cover throughout, showed no response to riding final 400M.
Began fairly, raced 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, peaked on run near 450M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, peaked on run near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear in the middle track, peaked near 500M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never competitive. (See Racing Incidents.)
Awkward and crowded at start, then taken back, in behind midfield 2 wide, worked home strongly and scored by a neck.
Raced just behind midfield along the rail, battled on nicely but couldn't hold on, finished a neck behind.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2 wide, worked home nicely to take 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, ran on and closed off well to the line.
Eased back and raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, made ground and ran on fairly.
Asked and raced in one-off one-back position, one paced and found no extra inside final 100M.
Settled just front of midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced. (Lame left front)
Taken back, travelled in worse than midfield 2 wide, continued run until emptied passing 150M. (Restricted movement in both front legs)
Raced in the box-seat, saw no daylight from 300M to 100M and therefore not properly tested.
Eased back and raced at the tail, 3-4 wide from 700M, hardly improved.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, emptied and headed at 200M.
At rear, wide and without cover, made no impression.
Rolled forward and sat outside the lead, stayed on until weakened near 200M. Disappointing and must trial. (See Incident Report)
Awkward start then taken back, and subsequently finished tailed out. Must trial.
Moderate start, niggled along towards the rear on the rail, sustained progress on the bend and ran on well in straight to assert authority inside the final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear, commenced move alongside eventual winner rounding home bend, ran on well and unable to peg back the winner the length of the straight.

Niggled along in midfield, improved to 3L back in 5th onto home bend, sustained progress from a similar position into the straight hitting the front briefly inside the 200 metres, swamped close to home.
Well there on the rail, hit the front upon straightening and only to be headed inside the 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Close up early, eased to 4th within 3L of pace onto home bend, came under pressure after straightening but failed to quicken to threaten.
Settled just better than midfield, slightly worse coming onto home bend, kept on same pace in straight.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, saved ground on the rail turning in, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Broke well, settled some 4L back in 5th 3-wide, became 6th and without cover rounding home bend, one-paced in the run to the line.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, crossed to the rail in front passing the 800 metres, stirrup iron reported to be broken at the 700 metres, led until swamped early in straight.
Well there, folded up under pressure inside the final 200 metres. (Bled)
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, soon found no extra.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden along, became last entering straight, no further impression.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back early, found rail after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back in the middle stages, improved on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1200M, closer on turn, 4 wide turning in, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, 3 wide from 800M, still 6 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, found a 2 wide spot after entering the back straight, struck heels and checked near 700M, 3 wide turning, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Began fairly from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced 9 lengths back at rear, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rivals turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked near 700M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, one paced in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 9 lengths or so back, closer on turn, 6 lengths behind at 400M, made little progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back, carried wider on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 1050M, carried wider after passing 600M, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1050M, bumped and checked near 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to score. (Rider dropped his right rein near 100M.)
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced 8 lengths back at rear, moved a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly to make frame without threatening the first few.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Commenced well from a middle draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 700M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.

Shifted out on jumping, raced prominently, a length behind the leader on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.)

Fast to begin, raced prominently but trapped wide early, slight taken back near 900M for some cover, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, recovered quickly to take the lead, led by a length on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, showed nothing in straight, finished last.
Began smartly from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Taken back from gate 11, raced wide with cover at rear, moved closer on turn, wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to take a place.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line, finished 4th.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, 3 wide from 700M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Moderately away, hampered early, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, kept on one-pace to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.

Began very awkwardly and bumped, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened after passing 150M. (Lame left front leg.)
Hampered start, raced at rear on rail, awkwardly placed near 650M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Hampered start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, in traffic after passing 250M, eased final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.

Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently but wide, shared lead after passing 700M, kept on very well after turning in, scored by 1/2L.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on well until peaked near 100M, headed thereafter, stayed on for 2nd.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, gradually moved closer after entering the back straight, no cover on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 100M, stayed on for 4th.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some progress early in straight, hesitated near 150M, closed off well thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same position on turn, made reasonable progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off one pace.
Began well, raced prominently, 3 wide, got cover near 700M, 1-1/2L behind on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Jumped well, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, moved forward 800M to take advantages of the slow pace, led 300M, overhauled 50M.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Slow away, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
At back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, made early move 700M, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, settled along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
At back, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace
Eased at start, took cover, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased at start, took cover, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 2-4 wide, little dash in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 400M, very wide on straightening, kept making ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Raced midfield, improve passing 500M, widest on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Ridden to race outside the lead, awkwardly placed near finishing line, not fully tested.
Began awkwardly then failed to muster speed, asked for effort passing 600M, widest on straightening, quickened passing 100M, came line nicely.
In early and middle stages travelled keenly and very difficulty to settle, improved into outright lead near 600M, finished OK.
Began awkwardly, hard ridden to race midfield, niggled near 600M, worked home one-paced.
Raced in handy position on rail, checked away from heels near 550M, tried to improve but only one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to ask for effort passing 700M, kept on rail to save ground rounding the home turn, awkwardly placed over concluding stages, not fully tested.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 700M, limited response in the straight, lame right front next day.
Urged along to take lead, steadied to allow a runner to cross passing 800M, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced at rear, tried to improve but near 200M was held up, not fully tested.
Near 1200M was left racing wide and without cover, settled in front of midfield, no response in the straight.

Ridden forward after start, shifted across to good position away from rail behind leading pair. Moved three wide at the 450m before striding up to share lead at 250m. Held narrow margin in last 100m & tough to the line.
Strode forward to good position on leaders back after 200m. Sprinted into narrow gap between runners at the 250m before moving up to share lead at 200m. Narrowly beaten.
Showed early speed & strode to lead, crossing to rail after 200m. Challenged after straightening before sharing the lead past the 250m. Boxed on well last furlong, first two a little too strong late.

Showed early speed to come across and share lead, before steadying to race outside the leader at the 700m. Strode forward to share lead shortly after straightening before peaking at 200m & giving a few lengths late.

Began awkwardly & consequently strode to midfield, three wide without cover. Improved position mid-race when continuing to race wide. Only 2L from lead passing the 400m before peaking late after tough trip.
Began fairly before holding the rail and racing in midfield. Moved away from rail on cornering when 2.5 lengths from lead, before failing to make any inroads in the last 250m.

Began well before being restrained back approaching the first turn. Continued to be steadied mid-race & conceded 5.5 lengths after first section. Cornered well back before making late headway in the straight. Rider questioned.

Steadied away from heels after the start & shifted back to the rail, settling worse than midfield. Four lengths from lead entering final section before cornering close to the rail and maintaining margin in straight.

Strode to midfield before shifting closer to rail passing the 900m. Raced near heels at the 650m & drifted further back, before cornering third from last. Shifted wider on straightening but only held margin in straight.

Slightly slow to begin before shifting behind runners to be last of the main bunch. Improved position when racing three wide past the 500m before cornering 3.5 lengths from lead. Peaked after straightening & yielded ground late.
Began well & strode forward before settling midfield, 3 lengths from the lead after the first section. Came under heavy riding passing the 450m before yielding many lengths in the straight.

Checked away from heels shortly after start and lost ground before becoming detached from remainder of field. Continued to race well back, made no ground in the straight and was beaten a long way. Must trial.
Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score by a neck.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, steadied off heels near 1050M, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began smartly, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, sent forward to race in 2nd after entering the back straight, 3/4L behind on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, settled 3 wide, 2 lengths back from 800M, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Sent forward to take rail and led, came out on top by a neck after battling spiritly with the 2nd to the line.
Pushed and settled to race outside the lead, battled with winner to the wire, missed out by a neck.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, ran home gamely but was no match to the first two.
Awkward start, raced in one-out one-back, continued on one paced to the line.
Urged, settled in front of midfield, wide and without cover however, stayed on until emptied at 150M.
Eased, then raced at the tail along the rail, ran on one paced to the line.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, showed some slight dashes but was one paced in general.
Failed to muster, then was in worse than midfield, 2-3 wide at turns, showed no turn of foot.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, found no extra after 200M.
Asked and took up the box-seat, gave no response in the straight.
Eased and raced at the rear, 2 to 3 wide, hung out and was difficult to ride from 600M. Must trial.
Just behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, lost ground in the straight.

Ridden positively from a wide draw, settled just off the pace 2-wide, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily to just prevail in the final 100 metres. (Questioned for improved performance)
Slightly slow out, travelled wide towards the rear, commenced move approaching home turn and ran on well between runners in home straight, did best work late.
Never far off in 3rd on the rail, held similar position into home straight, ran on to hold every chance 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Ridden along after moderate start, took up running after the first 200 metres, led until headed inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden forward from the widest gate settling wide in 4th some 2L back, came under pressure early on home bend, failed to quicken to threaten under strong pressure in straight.

Moderate start, improved steadily along the rail to forward of midfield settling in 6th in back straight, came under pressure entering home straight but could only keep on at the same pace without quickening.
Settled in midfield, widest runner turning for home, kept on well without quickening in the run to the line.
Settled well back, finished off the race well running past beaten horses in home straight.
Settled well back from a wide gate, came under pressure from 450 metres out, found no response.

Began well, niggling along just off the pace before gradually shuffled backward to rear of midfield coming onto first bend, renewed effort entering home straight but faded under pressure after straightening.
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, gained closer to 3L back in 5th in back straight, made short-lived effort around home bend but soon weakened after straightening.
Settled towards the rear, came under pressure coming onto home bend, dropped away quickly inside the final 300 metres.
Showed good early speed to be racing outside leader, quickened to the front 250M, kept on strongly for debut victory.
From wide draw got into a midfield position, driven wide 400M, closed off well to be nearest at the line. (Wound to LH fetlock.)
Never far off, moved closer to be tracking leaders turning in, fought on steadily to the line.
Settled behind midfield, 5.5L behind leader at 400M, came on strongly in the straight to just miss 3rd at the finish. Encouraging return from a break.
Began well, close up behind leaders, kept on well initially in the straight but effort levelled off final 100M.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately turning in, had to shift ground 100M when caught up behind weakening rival.
Switched off to last, 8Ls off the pace 400M, made some progress without threatening leaders.
Didn't show enough speed to be leading, caught wide no cover chasing the pace, didn't respond on straightening. (Jockey : didn't finish off the race having travelled wide no cover.)
From draw 1 pushed forward to take the lead, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, weakened away. (Lame RF leg.)
Began only fairly, pressed along to go closer, travelled keenly from 600M, 6th at 400M, faded final 250M.
Stumbled badly at the start, ended up 3-wide towards the rear, swung wide home, didn't finish off and never a threat.
Lacked early speed, fell back to near last, didn't respond to riding, never looked to threaten.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 650M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front near 150M, kept on well, headed close home.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, finished 3rd.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 450M, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 900M, carried wider on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, difficult to settle throughout, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened from 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, very wide into straight, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, raced tight near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1200M to race outside the leader, peaked on turn, crowded early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to score.
Settled outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, dominated from 400M, overhauled 100M.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, ran on strongly 300M.
Pushed early to hold the rail in midfield, lack room 400M, closed off well when clear whilst hanging out.
Eased at start, took rail, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, raced keenly and checked badly, little dash 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Eased at start, took cover, 2 wide at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Hard ridden but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide at back, no progress.
Eased back, never improved.
Pushed forward, soon emptied 400M.
Eased back, never better than midfield.
Ridden forward to race in front of midfield on rail, shifted out near 500M to improve, gained ground passing 200M, worked home solidly to score.
Fractious in barriers and slow out, settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn, responded strongly in the straight, missed by SH.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, battled nicely in the straight, made ground near 200M, finished strongly.
Jumped nicely, urged along to race behind the lead, asked for effort near 400M, responded nicely in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, placed pressure near 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, tried to improve on straightening, fought hard entire straight, made some ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, tried hard and made some ground passing 150M.
Ridden along, settled in one-back-one-off position, one-paced in the straight, blood trachea.
Raced at back, in the straight fought hard but only limited response.
Jumped well, pushed along for some distance and took lead near 800M, weakened passing 100M.
Travelled well in early and middle stages in handy position, came under pressure near 400M, failed to make impression.
Crowded on jumping, raced midfield on rail, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Slow to begin and settled at rear, very wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Urged to take box seat, faded out passing 300M, failed to run on.
Began fast and assumed lead. Crossed to rail after the first section, racing over 1L clear. Kicked clear inside final 300m and continued on for easy win.

Slow to begin before racing worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from rail at 750m before shifting the widest runner on cornering. Straightened 5 lengths from lead before making good late ground in final 300m.

Strode forward to race in third, without cover, 2L from lead after the first section. Moved up to challenge on cornering but could only get within a length passing the 300m before winner proving too strong late.

Raced in midfield, three wide without cover throughout middle sections. Improved steadily when wide entering the second section. A length from lead passing the 400m before boxing on late with winner well clear.
Raced in midfield with cover for majority of middle sections. Came under pressure upon cornering when 2.5 lengths from the lead before yielding a length in final 400m.
Enjoy economical run in midfield on the rail, under 3L from the lead after first section. Stayed close to the rail after straightening but could only maintain margin in final section.

Steadied across after the start to race worse than midfield away from the rail. Moved three wide when improving mid-race, conceding 4.5L at halfway. Two lengths from lead passing the 400m before peaking inside the last 150m.
Raced in midfield, between runners in middle sections. Shifted wider on cornering before entering final section 3.5L from lead. Crowded at the 125m before finishing fairly in late stages.
Began awkwardly and failed to muster speed, consequently racing in midfield on the rail. Four lengths form the lead after straightening and gave a length in the run to the line.

Settled next to last shortly after the start and held rearward position in first half. Moved three wide with cover at the 750m before cornering the widest runner, 4L from the lead. Peaked on run inside final 300m.
Strode forward before getting leaders back position after the first section. Hard ridden on straightening and gave ground in final section.
Steadied across behind runners after start before racing a clear last. Hard ridden at half-way and well beaten. Must trial.

Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1200M, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run near 100M, stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 600M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 600M, wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, 2 wide on turn, kept on well to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, angled out after passing 600M, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from 250M. (Lost right front plate.)

Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3Ls or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (Jockey reported his horse didn't travel comfortably at any stage.)
Raced in one-off one-back position, kept going and worked home gamely to score by 1/2L.
Worked forward to take the rail and led, looked likely until headed at 50M, ran on well to the line otherwise.
Settled to race in the box-seat, kept on going nicely to take 3rd.
Taken back to be at the rear, 3 wide with cover at turns, saved ground and closed off fairly.(See Incident Report)
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward, sat outside the lead, weakened passing 200M.
Jumped fairly only, at the rail along the rail, very one paced.
In about midfield, wide and without cover, emptied passing 200M.
Raced just behind midfield, along the rail, weakened badly approaching 300M.
Made all, drew 2.5L clear un-extended over 300 metres out, won easily.
Settled in 3rd, shaken up to gain 2nd inside the 400 metres, fought on under pressure but never able to trouble the winner.
Moderate start, soon picked up to 4th within 2L of pace, drifted further off the speed passing the 1200 metres some 3L from the front, fought on dourly inside the 300 metres to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind, did not find much room early in straight, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in rear, commenced move on the outside 600 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.
Chased the leader to straight, weakened. (Lame next day)

Settled just over 4L off the pace in 5th on the rail, angled out to challenge entering home straight, quickened to within 1L of eventual 2nd upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Away awkwardly, settled mid-division along the fence in a fast run race, 6th at 400M, responded strongly final 200M to lead inside 100M, won in track record time.
Eased back to race near last, 6Ls off the fast pace at 800M, improved wide round the bend, finished off well in straight but couldn't reel in winner.
Restrained behind midfield, 5-6Ls off the fast pace in middle stages, ran on well and had every chance in the straight, held by winner.
Crossed to the lead passing 1800M, sat in 2nd entering back straight, moved up to challenge for lead again home turn, kept on well in straight, not pace of first 3 late stages.
Began well from draw 2, tracked leaders in a strongly run race, came through narrow gap to challenge inside 300M, led from 250M till passing 100M, no extra close home.
Held up towards rear in a fast run race, 10th at 400M with 5Ls to make up, stayed on past beaten horses, no threat to leaders.
Away well, restrained to race in midfield, shifted out to 3-wide from 600M, couldn't quicken up entering straight, faded final 200M.
Shifted across from draw 11, settled 5-6Ls back behind midfield in a fast run race, remained same pace turning in, never near to challenge.
Dropped back from wide barrier, raced in last 10Ls off the fast pace early and middle stages, pressed along 600M out but didn't respond to riding, never factored.

Began well and ended up more forward than anticipated, 4th chasing leaders in fast run race, off the bridle 800M, lacked further response in straight, weakened away final 300M. (Jockey : strong tempo in mid-race didn't suit.)

Strode forward from draw 10, used a bit to make up ground before taking the lead from 1500M, set fast pace middle stages, soon tackled by rivals on straightening, couldn't sustain run passing 300M, faded away.
Held up midfield, 3-wide no cover from 1600M, gave ground from 700M, soon beaten and eased. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along early stages, caught 3-deep behind midfield, gave ground from 700M, soon out of contention.

Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on very strongly in straight to score by a nose.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, kept on very well to the line, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten. (Blood in trachea.)

Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on strongly early in straight, headed near 150M, stayed on well to the line, just beaten by a neck.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.

Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover,2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, bumped early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 750M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (Lost left hind plate.)
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, severely checked off heels near 1150M, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, steadied off heels near 800M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, wider from 550M, 6 lengths back turning in, bumped early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, no daylight early in straight and bumped near 300M, finished off very strongly when got clear run from 200M, won by 1/2L.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival on turn, kept on well until 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, bumped early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Fast into stride, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide and without cover, 3 lengths back, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.

Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 800M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back early, travelled keenly after 1000M, 4 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score by a neck.
Fast into stride, bumped early, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 550M, 1-1/2L behind the leader turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Jumped well, crowded early, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently but 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made some progress in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to may any progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, taken back to race at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Pushed to occupy box seat, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to obtain the rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Hard ridden early, in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, made steady ground 300M, run ended 100M.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Slow away, at back, 3 wide, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
At rear, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2 and checked, made ground when clear.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to sit outside the leader, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Trapped 3 wide just off the leaders throughout, emptied 250M.
Ridden after start, raced in front of midfield on rail, improved near 300M, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Ridden along to take lead then passing 1000M travelled keenly, asked for effort on straightening, responded strongly, missed by Neck.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 350M, wide on straightening, gained nice ground in the straight.
Hard ridden to maintain its position in early stages, settled midfield on rail, responded well in the straight, finished nicely.
Raced at rear, commenced passing 500M, battled hard on rail in the straight, finished nicely.
Settled at rear on rail, niggled throughout, fought hard in the straight, made up some late ground.
Jumped sharply, raced in box seat, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, near 650M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, weakened near 100M.
Raced in one-back-one-off position with nice early speed, tried to improve but no response.
Began awkwardly, niggled to race behind midfield, shifted out to improve on straightening, faded out passing 200M.
On jumping was crowded for room, then ridden along to race outside the lead near 650M, faded out passing 300M, failed to run on.
Began only fairly and then was crowded for room, raced at back, nothing in the straight.
Shifted across and raced in midfield away from rail. Moved wider passing the 450m before cornering 4 lengths form lead. Sprinted hard inside final 250m before continuing on for easy win.
Strode forward outside leader before continuing on to assume lead passing the 1100m. Raced clear on straightening before being headed inside the final 100m.
Strode to lead in first section before being headed and getting the leaders back passing the 1100m. Just behind leader on straightening and battled on the final 300m.

Ridden hard to race prominent before being left three wide without cover near leaders. Continued to work hard & improved to race outside leader at 900m. Hard ridden passing the 500m before fighting well late after tough trip.
Held the rail and raced in midfield. Drifted back mid-race and conceded 5L passing the 800m. Stayed close to the rail on straightening & made up a few lengths in the final 300m.

Hard ridden after start but couldn't gather speed & raced wide. Improved position after the 900m when ridden forward to stride up outside the leader at the 700m. Not far from lead before peaking at the 200m after tough trip.

Had no early speed and raced at the tail. Continued to race rearward, conceding nearly 7 lengths entering the last section. Passed a few in the run to the line but not a winning threat from back there.

Began fairly before racing in the second half of the field, three wide with cover. Steadied when racing wide passing the 450m before conceding 5L entering final section. Peaked on effort in final 150m.
Held prominent position in first section before being shuffled a pair further back mid-race. Hard ridden nearing the 600m and couldn't maintain position in the final 300m.

Drifted back to race rearward, between runners in middle sections. Shifted wider approaching 450m when 5 lengths from the lead & could only maintain that margin in the straight. Irregular heart rhythm post-race. Must trial.
Failed to show early speed before being steadied & shifted across to race at the tail. Came under heavy pressure passing the 500m before cornering last and failing to make any headway in late stages.

Began well and raced prominently before being crossed at the 1300m and getting leaders back. Shuffled a further pair back midrace. Shifted away from the rail on cornering but weakened out poorly in the final 300m.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Away with them, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just missed out in the head-bobbing finish.
Out in line, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to make frame.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 50M.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in 2nd, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, showed no early speed, raced very wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.

Away with them, raced prominently but wide in the early stages, slightly taken back near 1000M, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, peaked shortly after turning in, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out on jumping, raced prominently but trapped very wide, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began smartly, raced prominently but trapped wide, weakened gradually after passing 700M, emptied early in straight and eased.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, kept on very well to the line and scored by 3/4L.
In front of midfield initially, improved to be one-out one-back at 800M, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Travelled in the box-seat, worked home spiritedly and held onto 3rd.
Took cover then raced at the rear, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly to the line.
Asked, wide until shifted to outside the lead at 1000M, out of steam at 150M.
Settled in behind midfield, 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
Awkward start, recovered to be in front of midfield along the rail, slightly crowded at 250M, one paced nonetheless.
Bumped start, then taken back to be in worse than midfield, maintained one paced home.
Crowded start, then raced just behind midfield along the rail, one paced.
Eased back, raced at the tail 2 wide, did not feature.
Sat one-out one-back initially, raced ungenerously in the middle stages, shifted wide after 900M, lost ground in the straight.
Rolled forward into the lead, emptied passing 250M.

Settling just off the pace when steadied and dropped over 2L back in 5th passing the 1000 metres, soon recovered to former position by the Rock, saved ground turning in, sustained effort to prevail in the final stages.
Quickly improved from a moderate start to travel outside the leader, gained closer into the straight and hit the front briefly inside the 200 metres, caught close to home.
Broke well settling just off the pace in 3rd, inconvenienced inside the 600 metres, some 1L back in 4th entering home straight, kept on same pace without threatening.
Ridden to lead from a middle gate, headed when found no extra inside the final 300 metres.
Settling in midfield before shuffling further back from scrimmaging at the 1000 metres, gained midfield rounding home bend but unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Settled 4-wide without cover just better than midfield, came under pressure entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, remained well behind until saved ground turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.
Moderate start, soon picked up to rear of midfield in joint 6th, in similar position turning for home, kept on same pace without threatening.
Very slowly away, trailed the field most of the way and never seen with a chance.
Dropped steadily to midfield, travelling wide down far side, dropped out noticeably from around home bend. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped on terms, settled in mid-division 3-4Ls behind leader in a steadily run race, kept responding to riding passing 300M, did best work late to wear down leader just in time.
Away awkwardly, caught wide no cover before reaching leader 1100M, closed hard to wrestle the lead 100M only to be caught late.
Prominent behind leaders, loomed up to win 200M, kept on well to the finish just couldn't get there in time.
Pressed forward from draw 12, crossed to the lead 1400M setting steady pace, fought on well early and mid-straight, just couldn't hold off first 3 final stages. (Lame next day.)
Held up in mid-division along the 2-path, shuffled back to near the rear home turn, stayed on well enough over final 300M but comfortably held by leaders.
Bustled along early stages to find the rail, chased leaders in 4th, kept battling away to the line but never going the pace to challenge. (Lame next day.)
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, shuffled back to last midway, taken wide upon straightening, closed well but from too far back.
Began well, not hurried and settled worse than midfield 4.5L on the inside, in 8th spot 400M, couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaders.

From draw 1 restrained to race in midfield early stages, got shuffled further back after 1100M, took time to muster early straight, commenced to finish off 200M but got held up final 50M. (Jockey questioned.)
In mid-division, caught 3-wide no cover throughout, couldn't quicken with rivals on straightening, kept on fairly to line.
Began only fairly, held up towards rear, became difficult to settle 900M, swung 3-wide home turn, couldn't make much progress, boxed on fairly.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, severely checked 1400M, raced as the back marker before making a mid-race move, no extra turning in, gave ground form 250M.
