Brushed at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after passing 300M, easily scored.
Average to begin, positioned behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, made very good progress final 400M to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, nearer to the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, soon outpaced by the winner, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, positioned on the stands rail behind midfield, made minor progress in the final 400M to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader, near to the stands rail, peaked on run near 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced behind midfield nearer to the stands rail, 4 lengths or so back at 400M, made no progress thereafter.
Brushed at start, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked 400M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear in the middle of the track, weakened gradually after passing 350M, finished tailed off.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made good ground 400M, led 200M, however run ended 50M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace ,out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, too cover, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground 250M.
Eased to rear, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made some ground when clear.
Never better than midfield.
Eased back, favoured by the fast tempo, never improved.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 350M.
Never competitive.
Ridden forward to take lead, asked for effort near 350M, responded strongly to score.
Settled in box seat, improved on straightening, worked home solidly, missed by Neck.
Crowded on jumping, settled midfield, commenced to improve near 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Raced in front of midfield, battled hard in the straight, finished well, lame left front next day.
Raced behind midfield on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Fast out, raced outside the leader, fought hard but gave ground passing 100M.
Jumped well then taken back, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight, roarer.
Travelled outside the leaders, 3 wide and without cover, gave ground passing 300M.
Settled behind midfield, severely checked when crowded for room passing 900M, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly then ridden along to muster speed, settled midfield, no response in the straight.
Raced at tail, checked passing 900M, failed to run on in the straight, bled third occasion.
Began well, strode forward to share lead at half-way. Raced over a length clear passing the 250m mark before continuing on for comfortable win.
Settled in midfield against stand side rail. Shifted in for clear running passing the 150m before making good head-way in late stages. Two lengths back to third.
Showed early speed to be prominent before steading behind leading pair, 1 length behind at half-way. Battled hard on the outside rail but couldn't go with winner in final 300m.
Limited early speed and raced worse than midfield. 4.25L from lead entering the final section before making steady ground in the final 250m.

Showed early pace before racing between horses just behind leading pair. Only 1.5L from lead passing the 400m before peaking shortly after & giving a few lengths late. (Epiglottic entrapment reported post-race).
Strode to midfield between runners, less than two lengths from lead at half-way. Couldn't go with the winner from the 250m mark and tired in late stages.
Gathered speed after start to race in midfield between horses. Lost a few lengths passing the 650m mark before coming under heavy pressure shortly after. Gave a few lengths in final section.
Showed abundant speed to shift across and assume the lead in first half. Joined in the lead passing half-way before tiring out quickly in the final section.
Slow to begin and consequently raced near the rear of the field. Five lengths from the lead entering the final section before shifting inwards but making little impression in last 300m.
A touch slow away before making ground to midfield closest to middle of track. Hard ridden from the 450m giving a few lengths in the final 300m.
Began awkwardly & bumped before gathering speed to move forward and race 1.5L from lead at half-way. Tired out of contention from the 300m mark. (Mucus discharge post-race).
Had no early speed and raced a clear last. Shifted toward the middle of the track when conceding 7 lengths entering the final section. Gave further ground in the last 300m and was well beaten.
Crowded & checked shortly after the start and consequently raced near the tail. Conceded huge margin at the 400m and gave further ground in last section.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced at rear on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight but still beaten a long way.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked turning in, kept on evenly to final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, wider on turn, showed little response early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
On jumping stood flat-footed and lost ground, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Began well from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 2 wide, continued on nicely to the line and scored by a neck.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide but with cover, worked home nicely but couldn't hold off winner and finished a neck behind.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to take 3rd.
Awkward start, raced prominently but wide and without cover, took lead from 300M until emptied at 100M
Niggled along and settled to race outside the lead, kept on until emptied in final 150M.
Hampered after the start, raced in worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, continued on steadily to the line.
Eased and raced at the tail along the rail, made ground steadily though had an interrupted run in the straight.
Settled in one-off one-back position, remained in touch until the 250M.
Raced in the box-seat, kept on going till passing the 150M.
Bumped start, then eased to be at the rear 2 wide, found no extra at 250M.
Jumped awkwardly then crowded, recovered to be in midfield along the rail, emptied approaching 200M.
In midfield, 3 wide but with cover, gave ground from on straightening. (See Incident Report)
Asked to take the rail and led, emptied and faded approaching 300M.
Bumped start, then eased back, remained at rear and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Settled in rear of midfield and mainly in 5th on the rail in back straight, commenced move entering home straight, quickened well from 2L 4th into straight to assert authority over 250 metres out.

Began well, taken back to rear of midfield in 6th alongside eventual winner, commenced move on top of home bend and 5-wide entering home straight, quickened well early on but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Attempted to make all, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in last few, ran on well inside the final 300 metres down the centre of the track.
Trailed the field to the 350 metres, given reminders from home bend, made up good ground down the centre of the straight past well-beaten horses.
Settled 2L back in 3rd on the rail, slightly closer behind the leaders entering home straight, switched out for a run upon straightening, found nothing. (Tactic in home straight questioned)
Travelled wide in first few early stages, settled one back turning into back straight and chased the leader to home straight, dropped out under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Settled in last few, made short-lived effort early in home straight, had no more to give when tightened 200 metres out.
Settled some 3L back in 4th, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Positively ridden out the gate, crossed to lead along stands' rail from 800M, driven clear 250M, always well in control.
Reserved in midfield along stand's rail, ran on well from halfway, went 2nd near line on his first try over 1000M, but never a threat to the clear winner.
Tracked leader, outpaced by winner inside 400M, faded late and lost 2nd near line. (Bled.)
From draw 3 obtained a midfield spot 4Ls off the pace, kept on moderately over final 400M, just missed 3rd place.
Chased leader towards the stand's side, couldn't muster speed to challenge when driven along 400M, held ground to the line.
Raced near the rear 5Ls off the pace, ran on mildly from 500M passing well beaten horses, not reached leaders.
Niggled along to be close up behind the pace, couldn't keep up with leaders passing 400M, weakened steadily.
Settled 3-4Ls back in midfield, ridden inside 500M but kept on only same pace, weakened final 200M.
In mid-division, driven along halfway but lacked the necessary response, soon beaten.

Began awkwardly, squeezed after start, ended up behind midfield further back than intended, couldn't quicken inside 400M. (Jockey : not able to race in forward position may have attributed to disappointing performance.)
From draw 1 positioned not far off leaders early stages, outpaced from 400M, eased when no chance.
Raced in midfield towards the outside of group, couldn't sustain run passing 300M, weakened badly.
Outpaced in last, detached from field 600M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Towards the rear, struggled to keep up halfway, weakened rapidly to last, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same positon on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, bumped near 1400M, shared the lead with rival on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail after passing 1200M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover after passing 1100M, same position on turn, made some progress in straight.

Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight but still unable to obtain clear running until near 200M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to sit outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, brushed near 400M, finished off one pace. (Mucus in trachea.)
Began fairly, sent forward to take the 1 out 1 back position, there to turn, peaked on run near 250M, raced tight shortly thereafter, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped well, bumped early, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.
Threw its head at the start and lost ground, detached from the main group early, got back to it 800M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 600M, failed to make any progress in straight. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, carried wider after passing 600M, weakened after turning in, eased final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from 600M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, no clear running early in straight then crowded near 300M, finished off strongly thereafter to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1500M, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, blocked early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, saved ground to turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, 3 wide from 600M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked near 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.

Shifted across after the first furlong to race midfield on the outside. Two lengths from the lead entering the final section. Sprinted well once balanced, assumed lead at the 75m and continued on for comfortable win.

Showed speed to position at leaders flanks in the first section. Moved up to take lead at the 375m, raced a length clear inside the last furlong before being joined and past quickly by winner inside the final 75m.

Began well & raced in midfield but was left racing wide and without cover. Within two lengths of the lead on cornering and continued to make good headway before being passed quickly by winner inside the last 150m.

Shifted across from wide barrier before racing worse than midfield, 5L from the lead after the first section. Raced wide with cover around the home turn before balancing 3.5L from lead. Made some ground in run to the line.

Not fast away and had little early speed racing worse than midfield on rail. Stayed close to the rail on cornering when 3L from the lead, before shifting out at the 350m when making ground. Crowded & not tested late stages.
Showed early speed to assume lead and cross to rail after 350m. Relinquished lead at the 375m but fighting strongly until peaking inside the final 150m and yielding a few lengths late in the race.
Ridden forward after the start but left racing wide without cover, throughout middle sections. Tired out in last 350m after covering additional ground.

Began only fairly before making up ground to race just behind leaders after 300m. Came under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground over the final 300m. (May not have appreciated racing between runners  rider).
Began awkwardly & bumped before improving position to race in midfield 3.5 lengths from the lead at the 800m. Battled on after straightening before yielding a few lengths in the final 250m.
Steadied after the start & shifted across to race rearward after 200m. Shifted out after cornering when 5 lengths from the lead but failed to run on in the last section.
Began well and held early lead before being crossed and getting leaders back after 350m. Stayed close to the rail on straightening before tiring and giving many lengths in the final 300m.
Shifted across after the start and raced around midfield between runners in early and middle stages. Had clear running after straightening but commenced to give ground from the 375m.
Reared at the start & struck head, losing considerable ground. Tacked on to the tail of the field at the 800m before tiring out. Forgive run. (Blood in trachea post-race, must trial).
Began awkwardly and had no speed, consequently racing last of the main bunch after 200m. Hard ridden passing halfway and began yielding ground shortly after. Well beaten.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat a length behind the leader on rail, brushed the running rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, brushed the rail near 700M, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly. (Had overreach wound to the outside of the left front heel.)
Began well, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, hard ridden turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one pace to the line.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover in midfield early, found cover after entering the back straight but still 3 wide, peaked turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear with cover on the outside, no cover after passing 750M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, peaked turning in, showed no response in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, weakened turning in, emptied early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Hard ridden to hold rail, shared the lead at fast sectionals, ran on well to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
At back, trapped 3-5, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field along the rails, suited by the fast tempo, made good ground 200M.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, made minor ground 200M.
Pushed early, trapped wide in front of midfield, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Pushed early, midfield along the fence, no progress.
Never competitive.
Never a factor.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Settled in front of midfield, wide on straightening, battled solidly in the straight, made up some nice late ground.
Taken back at start from widest barrier, raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, quickened passing 200M, came line solidly.
Always hard ridden but still raced at rear on rail, made some late ground in the straight, rider questioned.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 450M, gained nice ground passing 100M.
Ridden to settle midfield on rail, made nice ground in early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Raced midfield, near 700M was left racing wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Settled in box seat, tried to improve passing 500M, gave ground passing 200M.
Urged along but failed to muster speed, settled at tail, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, no response in the straight, failed to make impression.
Trapped wide then improve to outside the lead near 700M, responded OK in the early part of straight, emptied near 100M, roarer.
Jumped OK then hard ridden to take lead, faded out near 200M, failed to run on.

Began well and showed speed to race outside the leader. Moved up to share lead on cornering before striding to the lead passing the 300m. Raced 2 lengths clear inside the final furlong and continued on for solid win.

Ridden forward to be prominent before getting on leaders back shortly after start. Presented with clear running on cornering before making steady headway and diminishing margin in the last 100m. Well clear of third.

Didn't have the early speed of others and consequently raced just worse than midfield on rail. Just over 3L from the lead on cornering before working home fairly in the straight with first two well clear of remainder.
Shifted across after the start to race midfield between runners, around 4 lengths from the lead at half-way. Steadied & shifted in on cornering before passing a few in the run to the line.

Had no early speed and was a clear last after 100m. Continued to race rearward, 3L behind second last runner after the first section. Cornered close to the rail and made up a length in the straight despite being well beaten.
Showed fast early speed to stride across in the lead. Joined in the lead on cornering before being headed inside the final 300m. Peaked on effort in the final 250m and gave a few lengths late.

Couldn't go the early speed and shifted across to race near the rear, nearly 5 lengths from lead after first section. Effectively last after cornering before making some headway and passing a few in the final 250m.

Began well and strode forward before being trapped 4 wide without cover for the majority of the race. Began losing ground passing the 500m before cornering very wide & tiring out further in the straight.
Began only fairly before mustering speed to midfield, racing three wide with cover. Cornered the second widest, 4 lengths from the lead but could not continue and gave ground in the straight.
Pushed forward after the start but raced three wide without cover throughout. Hard ridden approaching the 450m before giving ground in the final section.

Failed to muster speed after the start & consequently raced towards the rear. Continued to race rearward, conceding 5.5 lengths on cornering. Held up for clear running over & was untested in final 300m.
Began fairly before mustering speed to race between runners just behind leading pair. Commenced to yield ground form the 450m and was well beaten.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved after passing 700M, 4 wide turning, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to hold off a late charging rival.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, gradually improved after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, closed off well to take a place.
Began smartly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, positioned 7 to 8 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 400M, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out near 250M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 600M, showed some response after turning in, peaked on run near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Away well from gate 10, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, 3 wide from 1000M, gradually improved after passing 700M, wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, gradually improved after passing 900M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently but wide, found rail near 1000M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, headed 250M, gradually dropped away thereafter.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside in the early stages, moved to 2 wide after entering the back straight, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, challenged the leader turning in, weakened early in straight, dropped away thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, showed no response to riding on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Slotted in to be just in front of midfield, 2 wide, showed good kick from 300M to score impressively by 2-1/4L.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, kept on going but was no match to the winner.
Travelled in the box-seat, ran on fairly in the straight to take 3rd.
Raced prominently, 2 wide, kept on until couldn't keep up at 200M.
Sat behind midfield, wide and without cover throughout, pretty one paced.
Jumped only fairly, then raced at the tail, 3 wide with cover, did not feature.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, found nothing in the straight and eased down at 200M.
Bumped start, at rear along the rail, raced keenly in the middle stages, not competitive in the straight.
In behind midfield, along the rail, lost ground in the straight. (Lame right front)

Hard ridden from a wide gate, joined the leader coming out of back straight, gained slender advantage turning for home before kicking over 2L clear 200 metres out, just staved off runner-up's late challenge.
Settled mainly in midfield, ran on in straight to just fail to get up on line.
Settled well back after beginning from a wide gate, switched widest turning for home, ran on strongly to be nearest at finish.
Ridden positively from the widest gate travelling wide in first few, some 2L back in 4th turning for home, one-paced under pressure.
Slow out but soon recovered to within 2L of pace on the rail, gained 3rd rounding home bend but ran home one paced.
Soon dropped well behind despite ridden along, trailed the field to home bend, produced good late impression inside final 250 metres.
Ridden along in prominent position, within 1L of pace when steadied and lost ground coming out of back straight, made no impression in the run to the line.
Moderate start, dropped to last rounding home bend, made good progress inside final 300 metres.
Broke well, not far off early stages, dropped to midfield coming onto home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Broke well from a wide draw but taken back to midfield, inconvenienced and lost position rounding home bend, found nothing in the run to the line. (Blood in trachea)
Broke well to lead holding narrow advantage rounding home bend, headed into home straight and dropped away quickly over 200 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, gradually recovered under pressure towards the rear, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Tracked leader in a steadily run race, chased well on straightening, kept responding to riding and got there near the line.
Crossed to the lead passing 1400M, had uncontested lead, kept on well turning home, caught final stages.
Held up towards the rear over 8Ls behind leader early and middle stages, pressed along 600M, stayed on steadily to go 3rd near line but didn't pose any threat to first 2.
Settled behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, made steady progress from 500M, stayed on to take 4th, not reached first 2.
Never far off in 5th, moved up to 3rd 250M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to first 2, faded late stages to finish 5th.
Positioned in 6th just ahead of midfield, ran on mildly to line, never looked threatening.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot towards rear of midfield, 6Ls off the pace on settling, switched wide into straight, kept on fairly, no threat to leaders.
Not hurried on jumping from wide draw, 10Ls away in rear pair, gave limited response turning in, never reached leaders.
Towards the rear always, didn't travel, bustled along middle stages, fell back to last home turn, plodded past well beaten horses in straight.
Eased back to the rear, over 10Ls off the pace early stages, didn't respond passing 400M, never in contention.
Towards the rear early stages, moved closer to race in midfield 1000M, no closer than 3-wide throughout, lacked further response in straight and struggled to the line.
Caught wide no cover from early stages, strode closer to pace when proving difficult to settle from 1300M, weakened turning home.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, came under pressure 500M, not going the pace to challenge, had to swerve to avoid a fallen rider 250M, eased thereafter.

Placing: UR
Comment: Chased leaders, went amiss at 300M, dislodged rider.

Away with them, raced 3 wide at rear early, found a 2 wide spot 1200M, there to turn, moved closer after passing 600M, wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, made contact near 600M, wider turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take a place.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide at rear, improved after passing 700M, very wide into straight, peaked near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, crossed by rivals near 1100M, angled out turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, made contact near 600M, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, difficult to settle early, sent forward after passing 1400M, settled 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off one-pace.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, angled out after passing 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Slow to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, crossed by rival near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 600M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden early, at back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts after being held up 4-2.
Slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well for 2nd whilst hanging in.
Settled in front of midfield along the rails, lack room 4-2, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled 1 out 1 back, enjoyed the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M weakened.
Settled just off midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Pushed to take rail and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, suited by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, little dash when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, made early move 600M, emptied 250M.
Slow away, trapped 4 wide at back, moved slight forward 600M, emptied in straight.
Slow away, never a factor.
Eased back, never competitive.
Jumped sharply, ridden forward to take lead in one off position, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged, trainer questioned improved performance.
Jumped nicely, ridden to race inside the lead on rail, responded well, held it position to the line.
Settled in handy position on rail, tried to improve passing 500M, finished OK.
Slow out then ridden along to race midfield, fought hard and made some ground in the straight.
Urged along to race behind leaders, tried to improve but only one-paced in the straight.
Slow to begin, then ridden to settle midfield on rail, passing 200M was held up for clear running, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield, passing 200M was checked, after that made limited ground.
Travelled midfield, wide on straightening, in the straight fought hard but limited response.
Raced behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but no response.
Settled midfield, after 1000M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, commenced to improve passing 500M, passing 200M was severely checked, lame left front next day.
Taken back at start, no response despite been hard ridden in the straight, fade out passing 200M.
Hampered at start then settled at rear on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, weakened passing 300M.
Began awkwardly, raced greenly at tail, never in it, must trial.

Strode forward, away from the rail to race behind leading trio. Raced keenly near 900m before entering the second section 2.5L from lead. Sprinted well to assume lead inside the 250m before continuing on in final furlong.

Crowded & shifted back behind runners after start. Awkward near heals at 900m & checked at 800m. Cornered very wide when a clear last before hanging in badly at the 350m. Straightened in final 300m & finished hard.
Didn't have speed of others and raced midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail on cornering before balancing 3L from lead. Shifted out at the 350m before working home well in the late stages.

Steadied after the start to race in midfield away from rail. Ridden hard passing the 500m before having clear running on cornering when 3L from lead. Boxed on soundly in the straight & held margin to line.
Showed early speed to stride forward and race outside the leader. Moved closer to lead at the 300m before peaking on effort in late stages. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Began fast and held the rail and the lead. Lay outwards when taking the final corner before balancing 1L clear. Headed inside the final 250m before giving a few lengths in final furlong.

Checked & restrained after start, consequently racing rearward. Raced keenly & checked when near heels passing the 800m. Continued to race keenly ungenerously at half-way before cornering 5L form lead. Didn't threaten.

Began awkwardly & lost ground at start, consequently settling at tail. Raced greenly in middle sections & became unbalanced when making ground near the 650m. Sprinted to be within 3L at the 300m before peaking in late stages.

Began well, raced prominent to lead but wide & without cover. Continued wide run in middle sections before laying outward from the 650m and further wide on corner. Yielded ground in the straight & was well beaten.

Began awkwardly & lost ground before being hard ridden to make up ground and position on the leaders back after 250m. Moved up within 1.5L of the lead after straightening before tiring out in last 300m.
Shifted across after the start to race three wide with cover in midfield after first section. Came under pressure shortly after straightening before being badly crowded at the 300m. Well beaten.

Bumped & steadied after start, and raced worse than midfield. Taken wider passing the 800m & covered additional ground in second section. Severely crowded & checked at the 350m and played no competitive part thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Fast into stride, raced 3W better than midfield early, no cover from 900M, moved a bit closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 300M, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.

Slightly slow out and crowded, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 250M, made some progress thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide with no cover in midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, travelled well on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Taken back to race 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, eased final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, steadied off heels near 300M, dropped away thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final furlong.
Sent forward to take rail and led, kept on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, battled on gamely to hold onto 2nd.
Lost ground after start, recovered in midfield, wide but with cover, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Urged and settled to race outside the lead, dropped off slightly near 150M, continued on thereafter.
Asked before settling to race in the box-seat, kept on going to the line.
Raced just in front of midfield, wide and without cover, continued on to the line.
Crowded start, recovered to be behind midfield, 2 wide, one paced mostly but had no daylight late.
Taken back, at rear along the rail, maintained one paced to the line.
Eased then raced at the tail, 2 wide, saved no ground.
Lost ground after start, at rear and 2 wide, did not feature.
In about midfield, along the rail, weakened passing 250M.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, weakened badly approaching 200M. (See Incident Report)
Broke well and always travelling, settled just over 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, cruised to lead inside the 200 metres and won going away.
Broke well from a wide draw, ridden positively when wide before settling one off the rail in 2nd, hit the front 400 metres out but only to be outsprinted inside the final 200 metres.
With leaders on the rail, taken one back in 3rd for cover 1000 metres out, kept on steadily without threatening in the run to the line.
Unbalanced at start, ridden early before settling in midfield in 7th, switched off the rail for a run upon straightening, fought on steadily.
Broke well, settled just over 2L back in 5th, carried slightly further back coming onto home bend, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.

Moderate start, improved steadily to take up running on the rail over 1000 metres out, led until headed upon straightening, weakened under pressure inside the final 300 metres. (Jockey reported saddle shifted)
Sluggish at start, remained well behind to straight, switched out for a clear run after straightening, finished off the race nicely.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield from the widest gate, similar position into home straight, ran home one-paced.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield racing keenly over 1000 metres out, similar around home bend and into the straight, ran home one-paced.
Crowded at start and settled in last few, very wide rounding home bend and into the straight, made no impression. (Lame next day)
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Never better than midfield.
Slightly slow out, given reminders and soon picked up to 6th within 3L of the pace, slightly worse coming onto home bend, dropped out under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Ridden forward to midfield along the rail after moderate start, gave ground from around home bend.
Worked over from wide draw, led on rail from 900M, kicked hard in straight and kept going strongly to hold off rivals.
Away well, held up in mid-division, took time to get going early straight, did best work final 200M, went 2nd close home, nearest finish.

Steadied to near the rear for cover, switched wide 650M getting closer, lay in early straight, responded well when straightened, continued to challenge the winner but failed to get the upper hand, lost 2nd late.
Pushed up to occupy a prominent rail position just behind leader, kept on steadily in the straight but always held.
Travelled keenly behind leaders, had every chance from 400M, stayed on mildly but came up flat final stages.
Pressed forward to be racing outside the leader, stayed in touch until mid-straight, faded over final 150M.
Chased early pace, settled ahead of midfield entering home turn, on straightening stuck to the inside, couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaders.
Began well from draw 1, restrained to race behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, kept on same speed in straight, never a threat to leaders (Jockey : did not feel comfortable in action / Lame next day.)
Slightly slow away, held up 5Ls towards the rear, ran on fairly final 400M, not reached leaders.
Began only fairly and settled near last, 5Ls behind leader 400M, lost every chance when severely checked 300M. Never in the picture.
Switched off to last 8Ls off the pace early stages, still 5Ls to make up 400M, didn't respond to riding.
Began awkwardly, not for off leaders but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, weakened away turning home.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently near to the stands' rail, took the lead near 400M, kept on well thereafter, just held on.
Away with them, raced 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle of the track, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Shifted in on jumping and bumped, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Made contact on jumping, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off evenly to make frame.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle of the track, made good progress after passing 500M, peaked on run near 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader near to the stands' rail, showed limited response in the final 400M.
Moderately away, raced closer to the middle of the track, 2 lengths back, steadied near 300M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced at rear in the middle of the track, made some progress in the final 400M.

Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced closer to the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages, hard ridden from 400M, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Shifted out shortly after start and bumped, raced prominently in the middle of the track, peaked shortly after passing 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead in the middle of the track, peaked and headed shortly after passing 400M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced at rear nearer to the stands' rail, failed to make any progress in the final 400M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well from gate 14, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' rail, peaked on run near 500M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Began well, sat on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off strongly to take 2nd.

Shifted in on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 1100M, 2W with cover on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but still unable to hold off the first two.

Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, found rail 900M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, finished 4th.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail thereafter, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, wider from near 500M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Hampered start, raced 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, found a 2 wide spot on turn, angled out near 500M, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced very wide with no cover at rear, a bit closer on turn but still 3 wide, finished off one pace.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken very wide after passing 500M, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, showed no early speed, raced at rear throughout, never a threat. (Mucus in trachea.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Hampered start, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide in midfield, sent forward after passing 1050M, sat outside to the leader on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to score.
Lifted front feet on jumping and slightly slow into stride, positioned a length behind the leader, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 3rd.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly after passing 800M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed and weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 800M, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 10 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail, 12 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced very wide and without cover in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Commenced well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased to sit just off the leaders, pace good, drifted away 200M to score with ease.
Hard ridden to rake rail and shared the lead at good pace, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased at start for cover at rear, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 250M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden to share the lead at good pace, soon out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, no dash.
Hard ridden but not muster, midfield 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up at back along the fence, never improved.
Trapped 3 wide throughout, never better than midfield.
Never a factor.
Ridden along to take lead, responded solidly, kept making ground in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Settled midfield, niggled near 700M, wide on straightening, made up nice ground passing 100M.
Settled in box seat, improved to tight running near 200M, battled hard to the line.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, continued to gain ground when placed pressure in the straight, finished nicely.
Crowded on jumping then taken back, settled behind midfield on rail, niggled to maintain its position near 700M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 400M, one-paced, lame left front next day.

Near 1300M proved difficult to settle and checked away from heels, after that was left racing wide and without cover, near 900M was improved to race outside the lead, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled at rear on rail, fought hard and gained limited ground passing 50M.
Ridden to race in one off one back, after 1500M lost its left front plate, came under pressure near 400M, failed to run on.
Raced at back, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, faded out near 300M, failed to run on.
Economical run in midfield on rail, five lengths from the lead at half-way. Shifted away from the rail at the 400m, sprinted well to join lead at 150m. Drew away for easy win.
Strode to midfield away from rail. Ridden hard from the 500m when improving position before cornering widest. Made good headway in straight but winner was clear.

Shifted behind runners after the start and raced worse than midfield between runners. Drifted back in middle stages, conceding six lengths entering final section before making good headway from rearward position.
Held the rail early before settling on the leaders back after first section. Stayed close to the rail on cornering before peaking on run inside the final furlong.

Ridden forward to assume lead after 250m before crossing to the rail shortly after. Challenged in the lead between the 900m & 600m. Joined in the lead at the 150m before giving a length in late stages.

Had no speed & shifted across behind runners to race second from last. Continued at the rear, 10 lengths from lead at halfway. Shifted out on cornering before making good headway into huge margin in straight.

Hard ridden after start to push forward and race outside leader in first section. Obtained cover at the 800m when 1.5L from lead. Moved three wide at the 550m when improving before peaking on effort inside the final 200m.

Shifted across to midfield, three wide with cover in early section. Eased to get cover passing the 700m when 7L from lead. Made up some ground in straight but was never a threat. (Reported as "roarer" post-race, as previous).

Raced near lead before steadied after 200m to race in good position just behind leaders away from rail. Shifted wider passing the 400m when 2.5L from lead before weakening out final 200m. (Heat stress post-race).

Raced wide in first section before working very hard to improve & race outside leader from the after the 900m. Raced on equal terms with leader until 600m. Under heavy pressure on cornering & weakened out abruptly last 250m.
Steadied across behind runners before racing last & slightly detached after 300m. Over 12L from the lead at the 800m and didn't pose a competitive threat at any stage.
Slightly slow to begin and consequently raced last of the main bunch on the rail in the early stages. Began yielding ground from the 500m and was well beaten.
Made contact on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Crowded out start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Made contact on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Began smartly from the widest gate, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well until final 50M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Lost ground at start, settled behind midfield along the rail, ran home strongly inside final 150M to score.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, improved to box-seat at 600M, worked home nicely for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to take the rail and led, headed passing 150M but ran on.
Crowded start, sat at the rear initially, improved at 800M to sit outside the lead, stayed on till emptied at 100M.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, continued on to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, close off fairly to the line.
Sent forward, in box-seat until shifted 2 wide after 800M, stayed on until emptied for final 100M.
At rear initially, improved to be about midfield after 700M, wide however, improved slightly.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, travelled keenly throughout, was one paced.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, did not improve.
In about midfield, wide and without cover, lost ground in the straight.
At rear, long the rail, not competitive.
Began well from a middle gate sharing early pace, taken 1L back to 3rd passing the 800 metres, renewed effort and hit the front turning for home, held on well to the line.
Settled in rear of midfield from a wide gate, commenced move on top of home bend and one of the widest runners into straight, finished off the race well but without threatening.
Jumped best from the one draw, settled within 2L of pace in 4th on rail, baulked behind runners early in straight, kept on same pace under pressure without threatening closing stages.
Broke well, soon taken back to 5th within 3L of pace, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend to join the leaders into straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, settled in midfield on the rail, shifted out for a run after straightening, fought on steadily to the line.
Slowly away, trailed the field to the 800 metres, remained well back on the rail to home bend, saved ground turning in, finished off the race well.
Settled well behind, last and one of the widest into straight, made significant progress down the centre of the track.
Settled mainly in 6th or 7th, commenced move rounding home bend and 4-wide into straight, kept on well. (Blood in trachea)
Began fairly, worked steadily forward out wide to take up running passing the 800 metres, obtained rails run 600 metres out, found no extra when headed upon straightening.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, came under pressure out wide rounding home bend, plugged on under pressure in straight.
Ridden to the front early, ceded advantage over 600 metres out, weakened under pressure soon after straightening.
Never better than midfield.
Dropped back from draw 12, in rear 8Ls off the pace, widest into straight, ran on strongly despite shifting out under pressure final 200M, got up near line. (Jockey dropped left rein close home.)
Settled in mid-division, in 6th spot from 800M, quickened up well from 300M, just couldn't match the pace of winner late.
Rolled forward, emerged as leader 1300M, led steadily, kept finding passing 300M, only headed by first 2 late stages.
Taken back on jumping from draw 11, settled near rear 7Ls off the pace, driven wide 400M, worked home well down outside, just missed 3rd.
Slow to begin, recovered to race in midfield, 4Ls off leader home turn, into clear 250M, fought on to line but lacked the dash late.
Had a ground saving trip just behind leaders, kept chasing entire straight, tried hard but always held.
Strode forward to be stalking leader in a steadily run race, held ground to 150M, no extra late faded out of contention.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, battled on fairly down the inside, never likely.
Held up behind midfield, travelled 3-wide from middle stages, stayed on mildly turning home, no threat to leaders.
In midfield, caught wide from early stages and left with no cover from 1000M, showed little on straightening after a tough trip.
Began awkwardly, tracked leaders 2-wide, found no extra and faded away passing 250M, already out of contention when steadied 200M.
Held up behind midfield about 5Ls off leaders, failed to run on passing 400M, never a chance.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight to score by a head.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, made very good progress thereafter to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to make frame.

Lifted front feet on jumping and bumped, raced at rear on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 250M, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, made contact turning in, angled out early in straight and bumped, crowded near 200M, made little progress thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, there to turn, one-paced in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, made contact near 500M, bumped early in straight then crowded near 350M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter,
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Bumped start, pressed forward, shared the lead at slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Settled in front, favoured by the slow sectionals, ran on for 3rd.
Midfield, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Bumped start, at back, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, ran on well until 200M out of fuel.
Tried hard to keep up in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Checked at start, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
At back, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never better than midfield.
At rear, never improved.
Never competitive.
Never a factor.
Taken back at start, settled midfield, improved to 4 wide rounding the home turn, responded solidly when asked for effort, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, wide on straightening, issued a strong challenge near 200M, missed by SH.
Urged along after start, travelled comfortably in the lead, responded well in the straight, finished nicely.
Raced in box seat, commenced to improve on straightening, battled hard in the straight, finished well.
Raced at rear, near 1000M lay in, near 900M was checked and lost ground, gained ground when asked for effort in the straight, near finishing line shifted in away from heels and not fully tested.
Ridden along to race outside the lead, asked for effort passing 500M, gave some ground passing 200M.
Began only fairly, near 1000M lost its left hind plate, near 750M travelled keenly and raced close to heels, settled midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Began very awkwardly, settled midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Ridden along then raced in handy position, tried to improve passing 500M, one-paced, over concluding stages was not able to obtain clear running and was not able to be ridden out.
Broke well, ridden along to race in handy position, trapped very wide and without cover, limited response in the straight.
Settled at back, very wide rounding the home turn and widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, faded out passing 350M, must trial.

Began well, strode forward to race outside leader, half-length from lead. Cruised up to join lead under no riding at the 300m before exploding inside final furlong and drawing away for an effortless win. Fast time.

Began fairly before mustering speed, racing midfield on rail. Moved away from rail on cornering when 2L from lead. Couldn't go with winner passing the 250m but worked home well relative to others. Good debut.

Raced in midfield away from rail, 3.5L form lead after the first section. Shifted three wide passing the 500m before sprinting well in the straight & making solid ground relative to others. Winner well clear.
Had nice position on leaders back. Shifted out at the 350m before battling on well in the final 250m. Not beaten far behind placed horses.

Began fast and assumed lead after 100m. Less than 1 length clear entering the final section before being joined and headed inside the final 300m. Peaked inside the final 150m & gave a few lengths late.

Last one into stride before settling on the rail in the second last pair. Lay outwards mid-race and was checked away from heels after the 600m. Not far from lead entering last section before peaking on run in final 250m.

Steadied behind runners after start and raced a clear last after 250m. Continued to race rearward & conceded 4.5L entering the final section. Cornered last of all and couldn't challenge from rearward position.
Steadied after the start & shifted across behind runners to race at the rear. Continued to race rearward, conceding 4.5L entering the final section before failing to threaten in last 350m.
Shifted across when improving position to race on the outside, one pair from lead. Forced one horse wider on cornering before peaking on effort inside the final 400m.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 600M, finished off strongly to snatch win on the line in a 3 way ding dong battle.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, showed very good response after straightening, took the lead near 250M, kept on very well thereafter, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, wider turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 11 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made little progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out thereafter and finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, difficult to settle early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, headed near 500M, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out.
Settled to race in front of midfield, along the rail, showed good kick after 200M, ran on strongly to score by 1-3/4L.
Jumped well then taken back, raced in behind midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely to the line for 2nd.
Settled to race in box-seat, kept on going to the line to take 3rd.
Jumped fairly only, raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
Asked to go forward, led along the rail, found no extra and headed approaching 100M.
Eased, in worse than midfield along the rail, continued to make ground to the line.
Raced in one-off one-back position, awkward to heel at 400M and again at 300M, closed off okay thereafter.
Crowded start, then raced towards the rear 2-3 wide, made minor ground.
Travelled in about midfield, 2 wide, kept on one paced. (Lost left front plate)
Raced in front of midfield, wide but with cover, couldn't save ground. (See Incident Report)
Awkward start, recovered to be in midfield along the rail, slightly held up till near 300M, ran on until late.
Niggled along, prominent but wide and without cover, emptied approaching 200M.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, weakened near 300M.
Awkward start, remained at rear and finished tailed out. Must perform in a series of consecutive barrier trial.
Picked up quickly from moderate start to soon take up running, made all to win unchallenged. (Lame next day)
Broke well from a wide gate travelling wide and prominently in back straight, improved to 2nd 2-wide coming onto home bend, kept on one pace without quickening.
Never far off in 3rd on the rail, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate travelling keenly to 1000 metres, dropped to tail-end coming onto home bend, finished off the race strongly.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in midfield, ran on without threatening.
Began fairly settling in forward of midfield on the rail, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Moderate start, settled wide in last few, ran on well inside final 300 metres down the centre of the track.

Well there early stages, gradually drifted over 2L back in 4th approaching home bend, in similar position turning in, kept on under pressure before fading inside final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled well behind from the widest gate, remained in last few turning in, kept on in straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, improved along the rail to rear of midfield 1000 metres out, in similar position turning for home, kept on one pace.
Crowded at start, lost ground from midfield when crowded 1100 metres out, towards rear in 8th rounding home bend and into straight, soon faded.
Pressed along on jumping from wide draw, crossed to lead 850M, was tackled from 300M, kept finding to hold rival at bay.
Jumped on terms, moved up to track leader along 2-path, loomed a strong chance 300M, tried hard but couldn't reel in winner.
Niggled along to be chasing leaders along the 3-path, no cover from 900M, kept battling to the line but always held by first 2.
Slow to muster, ended up 3-wide in mid-division, ran on moderately on straightening, just missed 3rd but never looked like troubling the winner.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, raced as the back marker until making wide move 550M, kept up his work until 200M, no extra late stages.
Slightly slow out, held up behind mid-division on inside, ran on final 400M without menacing.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up at the back 5-6Ls from leader, brought wide 400M, stayed on fairly to line, no impression.
Settled down midfield along the fence, commenced to travel keenly 750M, just over 3Ls off the pace home turn, kept on same pace in straight, not reach leaders.
Away fairly, held up 3-wide towards the rear, wide into straight, gave limited response and only past a few beaten ones.

Settled just behind leaders, didn't respond to riding and gave ground noticeably turning home. (Unacceptable Performance / Trainer : would have the horse ridden more quietly wherever possible in future.)
Restrained in midfield, proved difficult to settle early stages, lacked further response in straight and struggled to the line.
Up with early pace then restrained to sit ahead of midfield, soon weakened on straightening, eased 150M when no chance.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on strongly to the line. (Lost right hind plate near 1350M.)
Commenced well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, bumped and unbalanced near 1400M, half length back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear final 200M.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight.
Shifted in on jumping and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, awkwardly placed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, hard ridden from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, improved from 500M, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 200M, made good progress thereafter to take a place, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, a length behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 1000M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, raced tight early in straight, finished off evenly.

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar positon on turn, raced tight early in straight, shifted out abruptly near 250M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, easy run on turn, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off one pace.
Away well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
