Began well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, improved from 600M, kept on strongly in straight, scored by 3/4L.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but still headed near 100M, finished 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, improved on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost right front plate.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, 3 wide from near 800M, moved closer on turn, hung in and difficult to ride in straight, failed to make any progress.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar positon on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, closed off well to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 200M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, pace good, just held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, pace good, ran on well to the line.
Eased at start, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, out of fuel 200M.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, pace good, no dash.
Never competitive at rear.
Never a factor.
Moderate start, settled midfield, improved passing 500M, steadied away from heels when being inclined to lay in passing 300M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled well, asked for effort near 300M, worked home solidly, missed by 1/2L.
Settled midfield on rail, improved passing 400M, wide on straightening, made ground passing 100M, finished nicely.
Raced in box seat, commenced to improve near 400M, battled well in the straight.
Settled behind the lead, niggled passing 500M, fought hard in the straight, worked home OK.
Taken back at start, passing 1600M was checked away from heels, raced behind midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at tail, passing 1300M was checked, commenced to improve passing 750M, one-paced in the straight.
Began only fairly, niggled to race in front of midfield, tried to improve near 600M, limited response in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, tried to improve near 600M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight, lame right for next day.

Raced at back, checked passing 1300M, mid-race improved to handy position but left racing wide and without cover, came under pressure rounding home turn, failed to make impression, lame left fore and right hind next day.
Passing 1600M was steadied when crowded for room, settled at rear on rail, came under pressure near 700M, failed to run on.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, niggled passing 500M, weakened badly passing 300M.

Crowded at the before gathering speed to race behind the leading pair away from rail. Moved three wide approaching the 400m when travelling strongly. Joined lead at the 200m before drawing away in last 100m for solid victory.

Showed early speed to run to the lead after 100m. Shared the lead passing the 750m until the bend. Skipped half-length clear on straightening before being joined at the 200m. Battled on well to hold second.
Began fast and strode forward, racing outside the leader. Went head and head with leader from the 750m until corner. Battled hard form after straightening but couldn't match winner.
Steadied after the start and raced worse than midfield. Continued to race rearward, over 6 lengths from lead passing the 400m. Shifted wider after straightening & made good headway in the last 250m.

Shifted across after start & raced between runners in midfield. Raced keenly in middle stages before checking away from heels near the 600m. Hung in after straightening before making up a few lengths late without threatening.
Began well and raced on leaders back from the 1100m. Hard ridden passing the 500m before staying close to the inside but yielding a length in the straight.
Ridden forward after the start but was left racing three wide without cover in midfield from the 900m. Continued to cover additional ground but managed to maintain margin in final section.

Hard ridden and mustered speed in first 100m to get good position between runners, 2L from lead after first section. Drifted a length further back, conceding 3 lengths at the 400m before failing to run on in straight.
Began awkwardly & consequently raced in midfield, holding the rail position. Around 4L form the lead when cornering close to rail before yielding ground in the straight.

Lifted feet and lost considerable ground at the start before making up some ground to be 6.5L from lead after first section. Stayed close to inside on cornering but gave a few lengths in straight and was well beaten.

Made first corner awkwardly consequently racing three wide with cover, just worse than midfield. Commenced to lay out passing the 500m, cornering extremely wide losing considerable ground. Played no part in the straight.

Shifted across behind runners after the start & raced rearward. Drifted to last approaching the 900m before yielding further ground in middle stages. Was 8L from lead past the 400m & never closer in last section, well beaten.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Began well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield in the early stages, sent forward after entering the back straight, settled outside leader, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well to take a place.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from near 400M, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, got cover from near 700M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, still 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, still 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear early, sent forward after entering 1200M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off impressively inside final 100M to score.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead at 600M, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Travelled in about midfield, 2 wide, worked home well to take 3rd.
Asked then travelled in the box-seat, ran on fairly in the straight.
Eased back, raced in worse than midfield 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
Bumped start, settled in about midfield 2 wide, continued on to the line.
Bumped start, then eased to be in worse than midfield, wide and without cover however, made minor ground.
Sent forward to take rail and led, headed when couldn't find extra at 150M.
Settled in one-off one-back position, stayed on until emptied passing 200M.
Crowded start, taken back and at tail, did not improve.
At rear, along the rail, made slight dash early in the straight only.

Soon dropped to last few despite ridden along, remained in 10th into the straight, came under pressure upon straightening and responded well inside final the 200 metres to assert authority closing stages.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, widest runner turning for home, fought on dourly down the centre of the track to just fail to peg back the winner.
Travelled in midfield, baulked for a run after straightening, fought on steadily without threatening inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, remained prominent 3 wide without cover to the straight, fought on to hold every chance until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled keenly in 4th just about 2L off the pace, held every chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Moderate start, took up running from 900 metres out, led the field until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Began well and close up early, settled just off the pace in 5th on the rail, ran home one-paced under pressure.

Sluggish and given reminders early stages, reached the main body of the field over 1000 metres out, given reminders 600 metres out and again when entering home straight, ran on past beaten horses down the centre of the track.
In front until ceded advantage about 900 metres out, chased leader into home straight, dropped out tamely. (Questioned for disappointing performance).
Never better than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, one-paced.
Settled wide in last few from the widest gate, dropped to last into straight, no further impression.
Quickly into stride from draw 1, led at fast pace, found another gear passing 300M, pulled clear from runner up mid-straight, well in control.
Chased leader, tried hard in straight but couldn't quicken up as well as winner, held ground final 200M. Easily accounted for rest.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, driven out nearing 400M, stayed on for distant 3rd, no threat to first 2.
Began well from draw 10, restrained and fell back to a position towards the rear, made ground over final 300M, just missed 3rd, well beaten by first 2.
Dropped back from draw 11, settled last over 8Ls off the pace, swung widest home, stayed on for non-threatening 5th.
Jumped well, settled ahead of mid-division, didn't quicken over the final 300M.
Eased to near last, over 8Ls off the pace on settling, ran past beaten rivals in the straight only, never near to challenge.
Chased leader, couldn't keep up turning in, faded final 200M. No impression.
Fractious in barriers, began awkwardly and lost ground, towards the rear further back than usual, gave limited response on straightening. Never a factor.
Bustled along after the start, never travelled, pushed to 4th entering home turn, couldn't sustain run passing 250M.
Away well, restrained to race in midfield, felt the pinch passing 250M, couldn't go on.
Began awkwardly and slow to begin, ended up behind midfield further back than usual, failed to respond turning home, dropped out mid-straight.

Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Commenced well, showed good speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored, impressive.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out near 550M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Began well, positioned 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, carried wider after passing 600M, showed no response early in straight, eased final 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 400M, ran on to score.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Slow away, at rear, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, trapped 4-5 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M despite all negative racing situations.
Pressed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M weakened.
At back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash in straight.
Checked at start, too cover at rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, weakened 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Never competitive.
Trapped 3 wide in front throughout, emptied 450M.
Ridden to race in one-off-one-back position, asked for effort on straightening, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Began awkwardly then taken back, raced at tail, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, passing 300M rider lost his right rein, made nice ground passing 150M, finished solidly.
Ridden along from wide barrier, settled outside the lead, responded nicely in the straight, finished well, missed by 3/4L.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, fought well in the straight.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, raced at back, made up nice late ground.
Began only fairly then was steadied when crowded for room, raced behind midfield on rail, gained some ground passing 200M.
Travelled behind midfield, tried to improve on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at back, very wide rounding the home turn, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Urged along and settled in box seat, placed pressure but gave ground passing 250M.
Urged along to take lead, placed pressure in the straight but weakened near 200M.
Failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, raced at back and always niggled, no response in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, fade out near 200M, irregular heart rhythm, must trial.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield, weakened badly near 200M, must trial.
Jumped well, slow to muster speed despite being aggressively ridden, travelled wide and without cover, must trial.
Stumbled after start before gathering speed to race prominent to the lead near the stand side. Improved to share the lead at the 200m before drawing away inside the final furlong for easy win.

Began fast and assumed lead in early stages. Drifted out towards the outside rail mid-race when travelling strongly. Joined in the lead inside the last furlong and battled hard but found winner too strong.
Showed early speed to stride forward and race one length from lead in early & middle stages. Hard ridden at the 350m when two leaders kicked away before battling on over last 250m to hold third.
Showed early speed when holding the near side rail, racing 2L from the lead at half-way. Hard ridden from the 400m and finished off well in a race well spread from first to last.
Settled in midfield and always within two lengths of the lead at half-way. Hard ridden entering the final section before peaking on effort inside the final 150m.
Didn't have early speed despite being hard ridden after the start & settled next to last. Continued to be pushed along in middle stages before passing a few late but still being well beaten.
Didn't have the early speed of others and raced near the tail in early stages. Conceded over 5 lengths entering the final section and was well beaten with first two over 5L clear of remainder.

The last into stride and shifted across towards the stand side after the start. Improved passing half-way when conceding around four lengths to leader. Drifted back before the 400m before tiring out in final 250m.
Began well before settling in midfield only 3L from lead early. Hung in towards the center of the track in middle stages before tiring out from the 350m.
Showed some early speed when racing near outside rail, only one length from the lead after 250m. Drifted back midrace before yielding substantial ground from the 450m onwards.
Didn't have the speed of others and raced near the tail immediately after the start. Came under heavy pressure passing half-way and began giving ground from that point. Well beaten. (Must trial).
Had limited early pace and raced in a group at the tail in early stages. Began yielding ground from the 550m and was beaten a long way (Must trial).
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 550M, finished off very strongly to score. (Thumps.)

Average to begin, raced prominently but 3 wide in the early stages, made contact near 1100M, then slightly taken back to race 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Away nicely, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 900M, half length back on turn, hard ridden from 300M, took the lead after passing 200M, ran on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Moderately away, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn but still the last, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Clean jump, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 900M, led by half length on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened thereafter.

Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, positioned a length behind the lead on turn, made contact near 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Jumped well, raced prominently but wide, made contact near 1100M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, raced tight near 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, trapped wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, improved from 600M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slotted in to race in midfield, 2 wide, ran home gamely to score by 3/4L.
Travelled in about midfield, along the rail, battled on nicely to the line to take 2nd.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, made nice ground and closed off fairly.
Asked to be prominent, wide however, stayed on till 100M. (Lame right front)
Rolled forward, sat inside the lead along the rail, ran on till emptied passing 100M.
Sent forward and led, 2 wide, found no extra and headed near 200M.
Crowded start, remained at rear along the rail, made slight ground.
Raced one-off one-back, emptied passing 300M.
Bumped start, at rear, never competitive.
Settled in midfield on the rail, travelled keenly onto home straight, baulked for a run early in straight, quickened well inside final 100 metres to snatch victory final stride.
Broke well, shared early pace before taking one out one back, hit the front under pressure about 300 metres out only to be pipped at post.

Jumped fairly, improved steadily along the rail to reach 4th some 2.5L back coming onto home bend, gained closer turning into straight, quickened to hold some chance over 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Inconvenienced at start, settled within 3L of pace in 5th, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in last few, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure in straight.

Broke well from the widest gate settling wide in midfield, drifted back under pressure towards the rear come out of back straight, wide without cover rounding home bend, kept on same pace in straight.
Shared early lead out wide in back straight, disputed lead around home bend, hit the front momentarily after straightening, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 300 metres.
Broke well, settled in midfield, yielded ground entering straight, made no further impression.
Jumped awkwardly settling well back, dropped to last rounding home bend, kept on past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing considerable ground, remained well back, made no impression in straight.
Ridden to slender lead on the rail after beginning from the one draw, headed shortly after straightening, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres. (Mucus in trachea)
Never far off from leaders, well positioned to strike 500M, quickened up to take lead nearing 150M, well in control final stages.
Switched off to rear in a race run in good tempo, just over 5Ls to make up at 400M, stayed on strongly to go 2nd late stages in a career best performance.
Travelled well in mid-division, shifted away from fence 400M, finished off well to claim 3rd, couldn't reel in winner.
In 3rd, responded well when asked passing 400M, briefly led mid-straight, run peaked 100M, faded to 4th late stages.
Chased leader in a race run in good tempo, briefly took over 300M, had his chance, faded mid-straight.
Dropped back to rear 5-6Ls off the pace, ran as well as he could in straight, held by much higher rated rivals.
Led at good pace, headed 300M, no extra and weakened badly.
Held up behind midfield, caught wide no cover from early stages, couldn't go on turning home, soon beaten.
Settled behind midfield, came under pressure 600M, didn't respond to riding, soon left behind to finish last tailed off. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.

Shifted out shortly after start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well after turning in, just unable to hold off the winner near 100M, finished 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 200M, nearest on line.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, crowded near 850M, carried wider turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, got closer on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, made no progress in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, showed good speed to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Hampered start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off one pace.
Hampered start, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield early, taken back after passing 1200M, found a 3 wide spot with cover near 1000M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, weakened from 300M.

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle near 1000M, sent forward after passing 650M, took the lead near 500M, very wide into straight, kept on very well in straight to score.
Commenced well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1050M, 2 lengths back on turn, improved from 600M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1000M, improved from 600M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, improved from 600M, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, travelled keenly near 1200M, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 200M, finished off strongly when clear thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, improved from 650M, very wide into straight, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.

Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1400M, travelled well to turn, challenged by rivals turning in, headed near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.

Fast into stride, unable to slot in early, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, 2 wide turning, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 600M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, weakened early in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 1300M, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Began well from widest barrier to lead before being joined at the 750m. Hung out when cornering when narrow leader before kicking 1L clear inside the final furlong. Dug deep in late stages to hold challenger.

Shifted across to midfield after the start before getting cover from the 900m when racing three wide. Sprinted fast after straightening before hanging in when making good ground in late stages. Just missed.

Began well & strode forward to race outside the leader. Continued to share the lead on cornering before failing to go with winner inside the 300m. Inconvenienced close to the line after fighting on bravely in last furlong.
Gathered speed after start and shifted across to race behind the leader. Cornered close to rail when one length from lead and continued to battle hard in late stages. Not beaten far.
Settled worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Continued to race wide in middle sections before cornering 5 lengths from the lead. Made good headway in the straight from rearward position.
Began only fairly before mustering some speed to race in midfield on the rail. Entered the final section four lengths form the lead before making up a length or so without threatening.

Not the fastest away but gathered speed to race in midfield between runners. Raced keenly passing the 900m when less than 3 lengths from the lead. Ridden hard from the 500m before making up a few lengths in the final 250m.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on the rail, three lengths from lead throughout early & middle sections. Stayed close to the rail on straightening and maintained margin in then run to the line.

Began awkwardly & lost ground after start before improving around the field to race three wide without cover, settling outside the leaders from the 750m. Peaked on run inside the 300m before battling away after tough run.

Began only fairly and consequently raced worse than midfield between runners. Continued to race rearward, six lengths form the lead on cornering. Made up a few lengths in the straight but was always well back & not a threat.

Obtained midfield position away from the rail in early section. Steadied near the 900m when pace slowed. Cornered two lengths from the lead before peaking on run inside the 300m & giving a few lengths late.

Not fast to begin & raced rearward, 6 lengths form the lead in early and middle sections. Shifted away from the rail at the 600m but couldn't make headway into substantial margin in last section. (Lame right-hind post-race).

Steadied back behind runners after the start and settled a clear last after 200m. Cornered with only one behind and conceded over 8 lengths entering the final section. Couldn't improve in the run to the line.

Steadied after the start and shifted across to get cover, settling second from last. Shuffled back to last in middle stages before coming under pressure passing half-way. Cornered last & made little impression in straight.

Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off strongly to score by a length.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 900M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 3rd on line.

Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, took the lead near 750M, 2 wide turning, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, missed 3rd on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, hard ridden on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 700M, a length or so back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off one pace.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, weakened early in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, very wide into straight, showed nothing in straight, finished last.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, made all.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden to sit outside the lead, held ground for 3rd.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide at back, dashed strongly 300M.
At back, 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail at back, no dash in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up at back, on the fence, never improved.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden throughout but never traveled, emptied 500M.
Settled midfield, niggled after 800M, improved rounding the home turn, quickened passing 100M to score.
Urged after start, near the 2100M and again near the 1900M was hampered, raced behind the lead on rail, gained ground when placed pressure in the straight, finished solidly.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 700M, made up some ground passing 150M.
Ridden along, then was hampered near the 2100M and lost running near the 1900M, settled midfield on rail, asked for effort near 400M, responded nicely in the straight.
Began only fairly, near the 1700M was hampered, settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn, made some ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, tried to improve near 400M, worked home one-paced.
Raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Reared and lost ground at start, raced at tail, niggled passing 700M, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight, stalls test.
Began awkwardly, lost its left front plate after the 2100M, ridden along to take lead, niggled near 500M, weakened passing 200M.
Settled behind midfield, made the turn near 1700M awkwardly, near 1050M was left racing wide and without cover, fought hard in the straight then weakened near 100M.
Taken back at start, always back, widest on straightening, failed to run on.

Hard ridden from start before settling away from the rail behind the leading trio. Moved three wide when making ground passing the 450m. Sprinted well to assume lead inside the 150m before continuing on for comfortable win.

Showed speed after the start, raced wide early before shifting across outside the leader passing the 800m. Made ground after straightening, assumed lead nearing the 200m before fighting hard but over run in late stages.

Steadied away from heels & consequently raced third from last on the inside. Ridden forward in middle stages to improve, 6L from lead at half-way. Crowded at 250m before getting clear late & finishing well in the final 150m.
Settled in midfield, away from the rail 3.5 lengths from the lead after the first section. Hard ridden form the 450m before shifting out on cornering & making steady ground in the last 150m.

Ridden forward after start and settled second on the rail, before getting cover behind the leader near the 700m. Moved away from behind leader on cornering before peaking on effort inside the last furlong.

Ridden forward from widest barrier before shifting across to midfield, three wide with cover. Four lengths from the lead entering final section before steadying away from heels on cornering. Maintained margin in straight.

Showed early speed to stride to lead on the outside before crossing to the rail near the 700m. Raced a length clear on cornering before being joined near the 250m. Peaked on run in last furlong & gave ground last 150m.

Strode forward before hanging out at the first turn and racing very wide near the lead. Shifted back to race three wide from the 800m. Continued to lay outwards rounding the turn before giving ground in the straight.

Not fast in early stages and settled worse than midfield away from the rail, some six lengths from lead at the 800m. Continued to race rearward approaching the turn and made little impression on the straight.

Had little early speed before improving after the first 300m to race in midfield on the rail. Continued to make ground, 3.5 lengths from lead at half-way. Hung in badly at the 275m before giving ground inside the last 250m.

Steadied and shifted across after the start to race second last on the outside. Continued rearward over 7 lengths from lead at the 800m. Cornered close to the rail but failed to improve in the straight & was well beaten.
Steadied after the start and raced a clear last a long way from the lead throughout early & middle stages. Never threatened to improve position & was well beaten.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, sent forward after passing 750M, took the lead near 500M, led by half length turning in, kept on very well in straight to score.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 700M, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 450M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1150M, travelled well to turn, headed near 500M, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail in the early stages, 2 wide from 900M, peaked on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, slightly inconvenienced near 1600M, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Stumbled at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, very wide into straight, weakened from 300M.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Prominent, wide and without cover however, pulled away at 200M, ran home easily to score by 1-3/4L.
Raced in about midfield, 3 wide with cover, battled on well to the line for 2nd.
Settled to race just behind midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and close off fairly to the line.
Jumped into the lead along the rail, headed by winner passing 200M but stayed on okay.
Raced at the tail, 2 wide, improved slightly in the straight only.
Travelled in one-off one-back position, began to close off until found no clear passage from 200M to 100M. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, weakened approaching 100M.
Raced in the box-seat, stayed on till emptied passing 150M.
Eased then raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover, didn't save ground.
Sat towards the rear, along the rail, not competitive.
In behind midfield, along the rail, never featured.
Settled just better than midfield, switched wide to challenge turning into home straight, ran on well to assert authority inside final 50 metres.
Settled behind tear-away leader on the far side, hit the front from tiring leader turning into home straight, outsprinted by eventual winner inside final 50 metres.
Settled in 3rd, some 1L back turning for home, kept on under pressure without quickening.
Crowded at start settling in last few, commenced move rounding home bend, widest runner into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in 4th on the rail, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled mainly in midfield from a wide gate, in similar position entering home straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled behind midfield, circled the field over 600 metres out to join 3rd some 1L back entering straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Rushed up to lead from a wide gate, went some 4L clear in front on the far side, came back to the field but still leading around home bend, dropped out under pressure in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, produced some late impression closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled just worse than midfield on the rail, dropped to second last when pace quickened 600 metres out, made no impression in straight.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Outpaced in detached last early stages, still over 6Ls to make up turning home, sprinted through along the inside and produced the fastest 400M finish of the night to secure the win close home.
Settled midfield 4Ls back, responded well leaving the bend, hit lead 150M but couldn't match winner's sprint late.
Eased back to near the rear, 5Ls off the pace at 400M, made stealthy progress over final 250M for minor placing.
Bustled along after the start, moved up to 2nd prompting the pace, battled for the lead from 300M, briefly led mid-straight, peaked late stages and swamped by first 3.
Jumped well to be tracking leaders along the fence, chased hard until finding no extra inside 100M.
From draw 12 taken across behind runners after the start, settled near last, widest straightening, made good ground over final 300M.
Restrained after the start, held up behind mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, chased steadily on straightening but never really threatened.
Caught wide no cover in midfield on jumping from draw 11, gave limited response passing 300M making no impact.
Awkwardly away, settled behind midfield along rail, couldn't muster the speed to challenge from 300M, never figured.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to a more forward position chasing leaders, had his chance on straightening, peaked on its run final 150M and swamped by rivals.
Jumped well but unable to cross, ended up 3-wide no cover chasing leaders, only battled upon straightening, faded mid-straight.
Positively ridden to take lead along the fence, set steady pace to straight, headed 200M and weakened away to finish last.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 700M, took the lead near 550M, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored. (Lame right front leg.)

Began smartly, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross 1350M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, commenced move 700M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened thereafter, stayed on for 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, angled out near 650M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Made contact on jumping, taken back to race at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 1350M, led by a length in the middle stages, headed by rivals turning in, weakened early in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Pushed to share the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 200M to score with ease.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, held ground for 3rd.
Just behind the leaders, lack room 400M, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, hampered 400M, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
At back, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 150M.
Pressed forward, favoured by the slow tempo, weakened 250M.
In front of midfield, no dash in final stages.
Eased to sit in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
At back, no progress.
At back, never improved.
Never a factor.
Never competitive.
Settled in box seat, travelled comfortably, improved passing 500M, responded strongly and finished unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 450M, gained nice ground passing 300M.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed then taken back, always niggled, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield 3 wide with cover, wide on straightening, battled well in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, placed pressure passing 550M, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back from widest gate, raced at tail, gained some ground passing 150M.
Fast out then raced outside the lead, asked for effort near 500M, gave some ground passing 200M.
Urged to race in one-back-one-off position, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
At the start lost its right front plate, settled midfield, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly and then was crowded for room, raced at rear on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn, no response when placed pressure in the straight.
Settled at back, no response when asked for effort, failed to run on.
Raced midfield on rail, tried to improve but no response, weakened near 250M.
Urged along after start, passing the 1100M was left racing wide and without cover in handy position, faded out passing 300M.
Jumped nicely, took lead with nice early speed, made the home turn awkwardly, weakened badly near 350M.
Obtained good position away from rail behind leading pair. Sprinted well after straightening, shared lead inside the final 200m and just got the bob in a two horse battle in final furlong.

Strode forward after start before improving to race outside the leader from the 850m. Moved up to gain the lead at the 300m before being joined at the 200m. Narrowly beaten after stirring battle in final furlong.

Ridden forward for first furlong before racing midfield, 4 lengths from lead after first section. Made up ground in second section to be closer on cornering. Sprinted well after straightening & made steady headway last 350m.
Didn't have the speed of others and drifted back, six lengths from lead after first section. Made up ground in middle stages before working home evenly from rearward position in the straight.
Began well before being steadied and shifting to midfield away from rail. Forced three wide nearing the 500m before straightening just over a length from lead. Peaked on effort inside the 200m.
Had no early speed and settled third from last, six lengths behind after first section. Made up some ground along the rail in middle section before maintaining margin in straight without threatening.
Began well and strode to lead, crossing to rail near the 850m. Headed in the lead approaching the 300m & gave yielded ground in the final 250m.
Had no early speed, settled last and hard ridden to keep in touch for much of the early and middle stages. Continued at the tail on cornering and couldn't improve margin in the straight.
Strode forward before getting crossed and racing on the leaders back from the 850m. Less than two lengths from the lead passing the 400m but tired out noticeably in the last 300m.
Steadied at start and shifted behind runners, settling second from last. Five lengths from lead entering the last section but failed to run on and was well beaten.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide slightly worse than midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, hit the front near 300M, kept on very well thereafter, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 900M, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield early, found a 2 wide position near 900M, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out from near 550M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1100M, travelled well to turn, headed after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 200M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rivals to cross near 1100M, 3 lengths back on turn, carried wider turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Inconvenienced start, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight, made little progress in straight.
Inconvenienced start, raced at rear throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled to race outside the lead, gradually pulled away from 200M, ran on to score impressively.
Raced in one-out one-back position, ran home gamely to take 2nd but was no match.
Settled to race in the box-seat, battled on to the line to take 3rd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, stayed on until weakened passing 100M.
Shifted across to race in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly to the line. (See Incident Report)
Eased, raced at the rear along the rail, made good ground in the straight.
Bumped start, recovered to race prominently, wide and without cover however, was one paced.
Taken back, raced at the rear 2 wide, made minor inroad.
In about midfield, along the rail, did not make ground in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground in the latter stages.
Bumped start, in behind midfield, 3 wide at turn, showed no response. (See Incident Report)
Taken back, at rear wide but with cover, did not feature.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, not competitive.
Awkward start, sat in behind midfield, wide but with cover, never in it. (Overreach wound to the inside of the right front heel and lame right front)
Settled in midfield, awkwardly placed coming onto home bend, soon came to challenge upon straightening and ran on to hit the front 200 metres out, just held on to the line.
Ridden early before settling 3-wide without cover and mainly in 5th within 3L of pace, came within 1L of leader turning in and fought on dourly to just to fail to get up on line.
Ridden along not far off in 4th, raced keenly on heels coming on to home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Slowly away, gradually picked up along the rail to be midfield racing keenly coming onto home bend, improved to within 1L of pace over 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Hampered at start dropping to last few travelling wide most of the way, ran on steadily down the centre of the track. (Lame next day)
Jumped best from a wide gate, gradually shifted across and settled alongside the leader, kept on under pressure until swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Soon ridden to the front from a wide gate, obtained rails run after the first 200 metres, held narrow lead until overhauled inside the final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, hampered when last over 1000 metres out, saved ground on inside turning for home, fought nothing under pressure.
Settled wide without cover in midfield, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Settled wide in last few from a wide gate, remained similar to straight, never a danger.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Not far off to straight, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Bled)
Jumped well from wide draw, tracked leaders 2-wide, quickened up well 350M to lead mid-straight, headed 100M out but rallied back to regain lead close home.
Began only fairly, held up behind midfield 6Ls on settling, chased well when driven out 400M, briefly in front 100M but winner fought back. Clear from rest.
Guided to a midfield position along the 2-path, driven along 550M, stayed on mildly to claim 3rd before line but no impression on first 2.
Close up behind leaders, 5th on home turn, kept battling on straightening but couldn't match finishing pace of first 2 mid-straight, held 3rd till last stride.
Switched off to the rear after the start, 10Ls off the pace on settling, still last at 400M, worked home well but too far back to threaten the runaway first 2.
Dropped back from draw 13, held up towards rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, made good progress early straight, flat final 100M.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, ended up towards the rear, swung wide into straight, made some ground but never close enough to challenge.
Pressed forward to be sharing the lead along the fence, headed near 250M, faded.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, failed to muster speed passing 400M, kept battling away without threatening.
From draw 1 moved up to be tracking leaders, no clear run early straight, failed to run on when clear.
Pressed forward to be sharing the lead on outside, had little left and gave ground from 350M, eased final 200M as jockey felt the horse may have been galloped on.
Dropped back from draw 10, 2nd last entering home turn, taken to outside straightening, had little to offer, never figured.
Began only fairly, moved up to a midfield spot along the rails on settling, going one paced when severely checked 250M losing momentum, eased final 150M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 550M, finished off strongly to score.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 250M, finished off strongly thereafter to take a place.

Made contact on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back in the middle stages, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, restrained near 1400M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 450M, made no progress in straight.

Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, commenced moved after passing 600M, very wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away with them, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, easy run on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Out in line, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 700M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail better than midfield, checked off heels near 900M, difficult to settle on turn, failed to quicken in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 550M, weakened early in straight.

Strode forward to handy position between runners, behind the leading trio. Had clear running after straightening before making ground to share the lead at the 250m. Continued on in last furlong for narrow win.

Ridden forward before working hard outside lead three wide without cover throughout early & middle stages. Fought bravely in the straight & continued to make ground before missing narrowly on the line.

Shifted across behind runners from wide gate and raced at the tail. Continued rearward before shifting wide on cornering. Conceded six lengths on balancing before storming home in late stages to be close up.

Had limited early speed and raced just worse than midfield between runners. Drifted back, cornering third last, five lengths from lead. Finished strongly in the last 250m to be beaten only one length.

Had no speed after start & raced near the tail throughout early & middle stages. Six lengths from the lead on cornering before making solid headway in the straight despite having restricted room at the 100m.

Wasn't fast away but held the rail and raced on the leaders back throughout. Cornered on the rail before shifting out at the 275m when 1L from lead. Hampered at the 75m & lost a length but still wasn't beaten far.

Began well but was steadied after 100m and shifted back behind runners, 3.5L from lead. Shifted wider on cornering and made up some ground inside the 250m before peaking late. Steadied near line & wasn't beaten far.

Shifted across to race in midfield away from the rail shortly after start. Improved into clear running between horses inside the 250m before being badly checked and losing ground at the 75m when 1.5L from lead. Forgive.

Bumped at start before gathering speed to press forward and race outside leader. Moved up to share the lead at the 350m before being headed inside the final furlong and giving a few lengths in late stages.

Hard ridden at start and had early lead before racing wide & restraining right back to third last by the 800m. Continued racing wide in middle stages before making up a few lengths in straight without threatening.

Pushed forward but raced wide without cover behind leaders. Raced tight at the 750m before continuing wide without cover until the 600m. Three lengths from lead on cornering and didn't run on despite being steadied late.
Didn't jump fast but gathered early speed to assume lead after 150m. Joined in the lead at the 350m before peaking on effort inside the 200m and weakened badly in last 150m. (Must trial).
Shifted across to midfield but raced four and five horses wide without cover. Under three lengths from lead entering the final section before peaking shortly after and giving ground in the last 300m.
Had limited speed and raced near worse than midfield on the rail. Stayed close to rail on cornering when only 3.5L from lead before weakening out and being well beaten.

Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 to 3 lengths back, moved closer after entering the back straight, took the lead near 600M, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, hard ridden on turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Average into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, closer in the middle stages, wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 to 3 lengths early, slowed the tempo in the middle stages, headed by rival near 600M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
At back, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, led 250M, overhauled 150M.
Pushed forward, pace good, ran on well until 200M emptied.
Eased at start, took rail, pace good, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, pace good, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at good pace, under pressured 600M, out of fuel 300M.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, pace good, emptied 400M.
Urged along to race in box seat, niggled near 400M, quickened passing 150M and scored unchallenged.
Taken back at start, near 700M was left racing wide and without cover, raced midfield, wide on straightening, made up nice late ground, finished solidly.
Jumped sharply then ridden along to take lead, asked for effort passing 350M, finished nicely, lame left front next day.
Hard ridden along to race in front of midfield, over the final 200M hung in and difficult to ride and was not able to ridden out, must trial.
At the start was badly crowded for room, raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, worked home nicely.
Settled midfield on rail, battled hard in the straight, finished OK, lame left hind next day.
After start was ridden along then near 900M steadied to obtain cover in midfield, made the turn near 550M awkwardly, made some ground in the straight.
Urged along to race behind the lead, placed pressure but gave ground passing 200M.
Hard ridden but no early speed, settled behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight, failed to make impression, OVE.
At the start was bumped and lost ground, raced at tail, hard ridden but no response in the straight, OVE.
Travelled at rear, always niggled but no response, failed to run on.

Gathered speed under hard riding to shift across to the lead near the 950m. Challenged in the lead on cornering before kicking back strongly inside the final furlong to score narrow but impressive win.

Ridden forward to be prominent early before crowded and steadied at 900m and racing 2L from lead. Moved closer before shifting three wide at the 400m and issuing challenge. Closed well in last 150m to just miss.
Didn't begin fast but gathered speed to race midfield away from rail. Improved when shifting wider on cornering before making steady headway in the straight to not be beaten far.
Improved position after the start to race outside the leader by the 750m. Moved up to challenge for the lead on cornering before peaking on effort inside the last 150m and giving a few lengths late.
Held the rail in midfield and raced 3L from lead after first section. Moved away from the rail approaching the turn before maintaining margin in the straight. Sound debut.
Not fast early and raced just rear of midfield between runners. Moved closer mid-race before crowded near 550m and losing a length, consequently only managing to maintain margin in final section.
Steadied from outside barrier and shifted back to last. Continued rearward, nearly seven lengths from lead entering final section before making up a few lengths in the straight without threatening.
Was wide with cover in early & middle stages when racing worse than midfield. Made the turn awkwardly when 5 lengths from the lead and couldn't make any headway into that margin in the straight.

Steadied and shifted across behind runners at start, settling a clear second last. Continued rearward, nearly 6 lengths from lead passing the 400m before failing to run on in the straight. (Lame right hind leg post-race).

Ridden forward for first 100m before steading and drifting back to a rearward position when racing wide. Continued wide and at the rear, over six lengths from lead on turn before maintaining that margin in straight.

Began fast and held lead early before hanging out near the 1000m and then headed in the lead shortly after. Came under pressure on straightening before giving substantial ground in the straight. (Must trial).
Not fast to begin but improved to midfield on rail in first furlong. Cornered close to the rail when over 5 lengths from lead before yielding significant ground in the straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, improved on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1050M, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 1000M, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Commenced well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground to turn, angled out near 400M, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out near 450M, bumped turning in, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed to cross near 1050M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, awkwardly placed near 450M, bumped turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider on turn, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average into stride, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 350M, very wide into straight, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, wider turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
In midfield on rail initially, shuffled back and shifted 2 wide near 800M, held up near 250M, ran home nicely once cleared to score.
Bumped start, raced just in front of midfield 2 wide, worked home well to take 2nd.
Raced at the tail, made the turns 2-3 wide, saved ground and ran on strongly to the line.
In behind midfield and raced keenly, shifted wide and improved after 800M, showed dashes, closed off fairly.
Failed to muster, settled in midfield along the rail, held up near 300M, one paced nonetheless.
Urged then worked forward to obtain the rail and led, found no extra and headed at 150M.
Stumbled at start, settled in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, did not threaten.
Raced towards the rear, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight.
Eased, in worse than midfield early but wide, improved near 700M when taken wider, showed nothing.
Rolled forward, settled to race in the box-seat, held up near 300M, showed nothing. (See Incident Report)
Pushed and raced outside the lead, stayed on until emptied near 150M.
Eased, in midfield but wide initially, improved to race prominently by 700M, gave ground in the straight.

Moderate start from a wide gate, ridden forward to reach close-up 3rd 3W without cover 800M out, came to dispute lead coming onto home bend, fought on dourly the length of the straight to gain upper hand close to home.
Soon took up running after beginning from a wide gate, led on the rail before joined rounding home bend, fought on dourly until finding no extra about 50 metres out.
Close up early, gradually dropped to worse than midfield despite ridden along, gained closer to wide without cover in midfield going up the Rock, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in last few on the rail, finished off the race well despite briefly baulked 100 metres out.
Midfield early stages, checked and shuffled back to worse than midfield turning into back straight, widest runner turning for home, finished off the race well near the centre of the track.
Broke well, soon taken some 2L back to 5th, dropped slightly further back when pace quickened on home bend, made steady late progress in the run to the line.
Settled in midfield, shuffled slightly backward rounding home bend, produced good late impression from behind midfield inside final 250 metres, tightened close to home. (Tactic questioned)
Began from a wide gate, ridden forward before settling up with the pace, shuffled back to 3rd rounding home bend, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Moderate start, settled about 3L back in 6th on the rail, found nil after straightening.
Moderate start, settled in last few, never a danger.
Ridden early, settled just off the pace on the rail, weakened under pressure inside the 400 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Tracked leaders, pushed to a 3-wide spot 800M, pressed forward 450M, quickened to lead 200M, kept on well to the line holding off the late challenge of 2nd.
Held up in mid-division on settling, switched wide 450M to challenge, chased well and loomed a threat 150M, bumped by winner inside 100M, held.
Didn't show sufficient early speed to cross from draw 10, restrained to race in the rear, 7Ls off the pace on settling, ran on well final 300M to claim 3rd near line, not reach first 2.
Showed speed to be leading early stages, restrained to sit behind leader from 1100M, no clear run early straight, kept on well but steadied close home. Could have been 3rd.
Settled behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, widest straightening, kept grinding away for 5th.
Eased back from draw 11, raced towards the rear throughout, 5Ls off leader 400M, stayed on without threatening.
In mid-division, left racing wide with no cover 650M, made early move to joint leaders, run ended 150M, weakened away. (mildly distressed post-race.)
Taken across behind runners, settled towards the rear along the fence, gave limited response on straightening, never figured.
Jumped well to be tracking leaders along the fence, in touch until weakened near 200M,
Caught wide making first turn, moved up to be joint-leader 850M, battled for lead early straight, no extra passing 200M, weakened noticeably.
Caught wide no cover early stages, pressed forward to lead from 1100M, came under serious pressure 500M, gave ground on straightening.
