Began smartly, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled keenly in the early stages, same position on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, ran on evenly to the line, finished 4th.
Slightly slow out and made contact, recovered to race 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.

Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced 2 to 3 wide slightly behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, similar position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Commenced well from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Took rail easily and led at good pace, hung on until 100M weakened.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, pace good, made steady ground in straight.
Slow away, at back along the fence, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, made minor ground 300M.
Slow way, pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, weakened 250M.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Pushed to take box seat, pace good, emptied 300M.
Eased back, trapped very wide, never improved.
Never a factor.
Shared lead in one-off the outside rail, kicked off passing 250M, scored unchallenged.
Shared lead on outside rail, asked for effort passing 400M, finished well.
Niggled to share lead in the middle of track, improve passing 450M, finished OK.
Settled at back, for the majority of the race hung in, one-paced when placed pressure, bled.
Settled at rear, tried to improve near 550M but only limited response.
Travelled in forward position, placed pressure near 500M, limited response.
Raced at rear, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden forward to share lead in 3 wide off the outside rail, weakened passing 500M, irregular heart rhythm.
Urged along but no early speed, raced at tail on outside rail, failed to make ground, must trial.

Midfield between runners in early stages before steadying & drifting back at 900m. Cornered tenth, but only 3L from lead entering the final section. Sprinted well to assume lead inside the 150m & continued on for easy win.

Mustered speed after start to race in midfield, three wide with cover. Moved wider on cornering, dashing well to share lead inside the last furlong before being joined shortly after. Over 1L clear of third on the line.

Not fast and settled worse than midfield on the rail. Improved position in middle section before cornering 3L from lead. Held up near the 300m & again at the 250m before finishing off nicely in late stages for minor prize.

Steadied after start and shifted across to race worse than midfield between runners. Steadied at the 850m & lost a length. Next to last on cornering before making up a length in the straight without threatening.

Showed speed after the start before being crossed and getting good position behind leading pair after 400m. Moved three wide on cornering, moved up to share lead at 200m before peaking in last furlong.
Steadied after start to get good position in midfield between runners. Close to lead entering final section before hitting the line only evenly in the straight.

Steadied at start, shifted across from wide barrier to race at the tail. Shifted very wide passing the 500m when still at the rear. Conceded 4.5L passing the 400m and maintained that margin to the line.
Hard ridden after the start but failed to muster speed and raced worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Conceded 4.5L entering the final section & maintained that margin to the line.
Showed early speed to challenge lead before shifting across to race outside leader after 400m. Shared the lead from the 800m mark before peaking on effort inside the last 300m & giving ground late.

Ridden forward after the start but left racing three wide without cover from the 1000m. Continued to cover extra ground in middle stages before cornering only 1.5L from lead but weakening out shortly after.

Steadied after the start and shifted across to the tail of the field. Hung out & lost ground near the 700m, consequently cornering a clear last. Shifted out in the straight but failed to make any headway in the run home.
Ridden hard to assumed lead after 250m before crossing to the rail shortly after. Challenged in the lead from the 800m before being headed shortly after straightening & weakening in straight.

Began well but couldn't hold out leading challengers before racing on the leaders back from the 1000m. Held up momentarily after straightening when 1L from lead before peaking at the 300m & yielding significant ground late.

Bumped at the start and lost ground before mustering speed to improve along the rail to midfield. Stayed close to the rail on cornering but had no response after the 400m mark and gave substantial ground thereafter.
Shifted in at start, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, awkwardly placed 1000M, found a 2 wide position near 900M, angled out after passing 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line, no threat to the winner.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide turning, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, missed 2nd on line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, crowded near 900M, easy run on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on rail, travelled keenly to turn, shared lead turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail near 850M, angled out after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider after passing 600M, weakened gradually after turning in, finished last.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 2 wide, kept on going and took lead in the final strides, held on to score.
Raced in one-off one-back position, battled on and looked likely until caught in the last 50M.
Settled to race towards the rear, 2 wide, ran on gamely to take 3rd despite laying out in the straight.
Set forward to take rail and led, headed passing 300M, continued on one paced.
Settled to race at the rear, wide and without cover, improved and close off fairly.
Rolled forward and settled to race in the box-seat, showed no turn of foot but ran on.
Travelled at the tail, stayed 2 wide, saved ground and closed off to the line.
In behind midfield, 2 wide throughout, stayed on until emptied late.
Raced just in front of midfield, along the rail, remained one paced.
Missed start badly, at rear along the rail, saved no ground. (Lame right front)
In behind midfield, along the rail, made no threats.
Slow to jump the ridden, settled outside the lead, faded on straightening. (Blood in trachea and lame left hind)

Settled just over 2L off the pace in 4th from a wide gate, responded well under pressure inside final 250M to hit the front shortly after, just held off runner-up's challenge while drifting out away from the whip closing stages.
Travelled in midfield, quickened well under pressure inside final 300 metres to just fail to peg back the winner while shifting out away from him.

Ridden to lead early, taken one back to settle just off the pace over 1000 metres out, remained in similar position to straight and baulked in the straight until passing the 200 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden positively among the leaders after beginning from the widest gate, took up running on the rail over 1000 metres out, led until headed under pressure just inside the 200 metres.
Settled behind midfield in 7th, ran on steadily in straight without threatening.
One of the leading trio in early stages, settled 1L back in joint 2nd approaching home bend, improved to dispute lead turning into straight, yielded ground gradually inside final 250 metres.
Gradually taken back from a wide draw, travelling wide without cover in last few, widest runner turning for home, produced good late impression in the run to the line.

Slightly slow out, soon picked up to forward of midfield in 5th just over 3L back on the rail, hampered coming onto home bend, re-gained 5th some 2L back entering home straight, weakened after straightening.
Soon taken back to last few, last into the straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Taken back to last from a wide gate, trailed the field to the 700 metres, made headway along the rail approaching home turn, made no further impression in the straight.
Began moderately, settled mainly in 8th towards the rear on the rail, gave ground from approaching final turn. (Irregular heart rhythm and swelling over tendon next day)
Began only fairly, settled down 3-wide in midfield, chased steadily to find front nearing 100M, knuckled down well late to repel the persistent 2nd.
Reserved behind mid-division 5Ls off the pace, angled wide 500M and responded well to pressure, challenged winner from 300M out, tried hard but couldn't gain the upper hand.
Crowded for room at start before recovering to race behind midfield, shifted away from fence 500M, kept finding the line well, got up for 3rd just in time.
Strode forward to be tracking leader along the fence, angled out into clear 350M, there to challenge but only battled to the line, just held 4th in blanket finish for minor honors.
Began awkwardly, restrained to race towards rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, worked home well but came from too far back. Just missed 4th.
Caught wide early moved up to track leader 2-wide, took over from top of the straight and led to near 100M, faded late stages to finish 6th.
Up with early pace, raced keenly, shuffled back to midfield passing 1000M, held up early in straight, ran on mildly final 300M. Never seriously threatened.
Emerged as leader passing 1000M, led steadily, headed top of the straight, battled on, got out-finished from mid-straight.
From draw 1 held up in midfield along the fence, couldn't muster the speed to challenge inside 400M, didn't threaten.

Away awkwardly, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, couldn't accelerate passing 400M, never likely. (Jockey lost use of right stirrup iron early stages and unable to be as prominent as had been intended.)
Niggled along to be chasing leaders in 4th, ridden out 450M but couldn't finish off in the straight, soon gave way.
Restrained from wide barrier, settled down in rear, on straightening failed to let down when pressured.
Steadied early stages too be racing towards the rear, under pressure from 600M and gradually weakened out of contention.
Dropped back to the rear 8Ls off the pace on settling, couldn't go on passing 400M. Never involved.
Away well from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly in the early stages, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Slowly away and hampered, recovered to race behind midfield on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.

Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, awkwardly placed near 1100M, hard ridden turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, raced tight early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter and scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, raced tight early in straight, kept on very well thereafter to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.

Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made very good progress when clear thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 850M, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, moved closer on turn, wide into straight, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, bumped near 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away well, raced 2 wide right behind the lead, there to turn, awkwardly placed and bumped near 500M, checked early in straight, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, closer turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 900M, improved on turn, took the lead near 500M, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began fairly, positioned on rail, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away with them, raced behind midfield, 2 to 3 wide, carried wider after passing 1000M, 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently on rail, travelled well to turn, headed near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Bled.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 800M, moved a bit closer on turn, raced tight near 400M, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked turning in, raced tight near 400M, showed no response early in straight, eased thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well to win.
Stumbled at start, at back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, head gears came loose from 800M, dashed strongly 300M despite all negative situations.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing effort 300M.
Took rail and led easily, clocked slow sectionals, hung on until 150M overhauled.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout just off the leaders, held ground in straight.
At rear, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased to take box seat, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, weakened 300M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, soon emptied 500M.
Settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 750M, wide on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Urged along, raced midfield, passing 1400M was left racing wide and without cover, improved to handy position passing 900M, responded well in the straight.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 800M, gained nice ground in the straight, finished well.

Failed to must speed despite being ridden along, made contact with a runner and became badly unbalanced passing winning post on first occasion, travelled behind midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Urged to race outside the lead, asked for effort passing 500M, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced at tail, placed pressure near 900M, worked home one-paced.
Travelled midfield, near 500M lay in, failed to run on.
Niggled to race in box seat, tried to improve near 600M, weakened badly near 100M.
Hard ridden to take lead, tried to improve passing 600M, weakened passing 300M.

Made contact with a runner and became badly unbalanced passing winning post on first occasion, raced behind midfield on rail, faded out passing 200M, restricted action with swollen both front fetlocks next day.
Urged along and raced behind leaders, failed to maintain its position despite being ridden near 800M, failed to run on, must trial.
Ridden from widest barrier, raced in handy position, until passing 800M travelled wide and without cover, weakened near 300M, must trial.
Showed speed, raced on leaders back after being crossed at the 900m. Race tight on straightening before sprinting well to lead at the 275m and continuing on for easy win.

Didn't begin fast, mustered speed after start to race between runners, 2L from lead. Raced tight on cornering, couldn't go with winner passing the 350m before battling on well to hold second, well clear of third.

Didn't have the speed of others and raced in midfield on rail, 3.5L from lead after first section. Lay outwards rounding the turn before shifting out at the 250m and passing a few in late stages without threatening first two.

Had no early speed and raced a clear second last after 300m. Continued rearward and conceded over 8L when last and very wide entering the final section. Made significant late headway from impossible position in on speed race.
Began fast, assumed lead before crossing to rail at the 900m. Headed in the lead at the 275m before peaking shortly after and giving ground in the last furlong.
Began awkwardly and lost ground before improving to midfield, 4L from lead after first section. Drifted back in middle section, balancing 5L from lead before making little impression in straight.
Crowded after start and consequently raced a clear last in first 400m. Stayed close to the rail on cornering but failed to make any headway into 5L margin in the last section.

Hard ridden after the start to improve and race outside the leader from the 750m. Just over a length from the lead on cornering before peaking on run inside the last 250m & yielding many lengths late in race.
Steadied after the start but was left racing four wide without cover with only two runners behind. Continued very wide in middle section and couldn't go on in the straight & was well beaten.

Raced in midfield, three wide with cover. Cornered awkwardly, bumped and lost ground at the 700m. A clear second last on cornering, long way from lead, and failed to get into the race at any stage. Well beaten on the line.
Race in midfield, three wide with cover. Shifted wider nearing the 450m before balancing 4L from lead. Tired badly in the last furlong & was well beaten.

Showed some early speed to stride forward before being left three wide without cover from the 700m. Not far from lead on cornering before peaking on effort shortly after and giving significant ground in the straight.
Jumped with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half length back on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, wide into straight, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
In worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, battled home strongly to score by 1/2L.
Prominent before taking cover to be one-out one-back, worked home well to take 2nd. (See Incident Report)
Raced prominently, but wide and without cover, showed good kick at 200M, emptied late but held on to 3rd.
Settled to race at the rear, along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, kept on going to the line.
Slow to jump, recovered to race in the box-seat, emptied inside final 100M.
Raced just in front of midfield, wide and without cover, stayed on but found no extra late.
Hard ridden, settled midfield 3 wide, kept on one paced in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Ridden then took cover in behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, did not improve but ran on.
At the tail, went wide at turns, did not threaten.
Asked and settled to race outside the lead, stayed on until near 250M only.
Sent forward to lead on the rail, weakened out near 300M.
Moderate start, soon improved to close-up position 3-wide without cover, hit the front on top of home bend and hung on well under pressure.
Broke well, settled just over 2L back in 6th, slightly worse in 7th turning into straight, ran on to reach 2nd 200 metres out.
Soon dropped to tail-end despite ridden along, commenced move rounding home bend and widest runner turning in, finished off well to grab 3rd late.
Settled just worse than midfield from a wide gate, wide into straight, finished off race nicely.
Lacked pace and soon dropped to last few despite ridden along, saved ground on inside turning for home, produced good late impression under pressure inside final 200 metres.

Slowly away, soon recovered to one back positon on the rail, struck heels, blundered badly and lost 2L coming on home bend, recovered to 1L 3rd turning in, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, ridden along in prominent position, came under pressure entering home straight, soon faded.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate losing ground, settled well behind and trailed the field into straight, produced good late impression closing stages. (Jockey riding came under notice)
Soon ridden to lead, headed approaching home straight, folded up quickly.
Niggled along in rear of midfield, saved ground turning in, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Began well from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover prominently to about 300 metres, folded up quickly.
Took up the lead going into first bend, led uncontested travelling strongly, driven 350M and strode clear mid-straight, comfortably.
Pressed forward from draw 14 to be sitting on leaders' heels, couldn't quicken as well as the winner passing 300M, kept on for clear 2nd. (Jockey : abnormal breathing noise.)
Away well from draw 1, chased leaders along the fence, not pace to challenge the first 2 on straightening, fought neck to neck with rival for 3rd placing over final 200M, gained upper hand late.
Aggressively ridden on jumping from draw 11, caught wide no cover behind leaders, outpaced by first 2 passing 400M, fought neck to neck with rival for 3rd place, conceded late.
Given a patient ride, settled worse than midfield 7Ls away, pushed out 400M, did not finish well enough to threaten.
Eased back to the rear early stages, waited with until passing 600M, still last at 400M over 8Ls to make up, stayed on down outside passing beaten horses.
Lifted his front feet on jumping and lost ground, ended up racing in midfield along the fence, boxed on same pace final 300M, no impression.
Began awkwardly, recovered to be travelling just ahead of midfield, kept on same pace in straight, never in the reckoning.
Jumped on terms, restrained to race in midfield, on straightening went past a few without any threat to leaders.
Switched off to the rear after jumping from wide draw, 8Ls off the pace making the final turn, couldn't quicken. Never figured.
Held up behind midfield 6-7Ls off leader in a steadily run race, under pressure from the corner and couldn't rally. Never involved.
Fractious in stall beginning very awkwardly, shifted across behind runners to be racing near last, 7Ls back making home turn, wide into straight, never got going.
Settled down midfield, never more than 4Ls away, kept on same pace early straight, dropped away 200M.
Tracked leaders in 5th, travelled only fairly in the race, dropped right out on straightening. (Jockey : appeared not to concentrate when racing amongst runners. / Lame next day.)

Moderately away, raced prominently, took the lead after passing 500M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the stands rail, kept on well to the line to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead on the stands side, headed after passing 500M, peaked on run near 300M, ran on evenly thereafter, missed 2nd on line.
Began awkwardly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands side, peaked on run near 400M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, peaked near 500M, weakened thereafter.
Stumbled at start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Lost left front plate.)
Eased to sit in midfield, however trapped 3 wide, moved forward from 1000M, closed off strongly and scored.
Settled behind midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, blocked 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steady when clear.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
At rear, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 350M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Never competitive.
Raced inside the lead with nice early speed, asked for effort passing 500M, quickened near 100M to score.
Moderate start, travelled midfield, improved passing 450M, responded solidly, missed by 1/2L.
Settled behind leaders on outside rail, asked for effort passing 500M, passing 200M was taken out behind heels, responded nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, lay out over concluding stages then was checked, not ridden out.
Niggled to take lead on outside rail, placed pressure near 300M, came under pressure passing 100M.
Ridden after start but no early speed, raced at rear on rail, made up some nice late ground.
Began awkwardly, raced midfield, passing 600M lost ground when reluctant to hold its position, worked home one-paced.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield, lay out passing 600M, checked at 100M when disappointed for running, finished OK.
Hard ridden but no early speed, raced midfield on outside rail, gained some ground passing 100M.
Slow out then checked and lost ground when tightened for room, settled at back, passing 600M was checked and shifted in to avoid heels, limited response when asked for effort.
Raced at rear, always niggled, no response when placed pressure.
Began very awkwardly, raced at back in middle of the track, no response.
After start raced ungenerously, settled behind midfield, no response when placed under pressure.
Raced at back, always ridden to maintain its position, never in it.
Ridden forward after start and race midfield on rail. Shifted out shortly after straightening when 3L from lead before sprinting well to assume lead inside the final 50m.

Began well from outside draw, strode forward in the lead before crossing to rail near 1200m. Raced over 1L clear on cornering and kicked strongly in the straight before being caught inside the last 50m. 2.25L clear of third.

Improved after start to settle midfield between runners. Drifted back in middle sections before easing wider passing the 500m, cornering wide, 4.5L from lead. Good headway in the last section without threatening first two.

Drifted back after first furlong to race just worse than midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail approaching the 500m before balancing under 4L from lead. Passed a few in the straight but effectively maintained margin.
Shifted across to get good position away from the rail behind leading pair. Shifted 4 wide passing the 500m before peaking on run inside the last 250m.
Strode forward to be prominent before racing on leaders back from the 1200m. Couldn't go with leader inside the 400m and yielded 3L inside the final section.

Had no early speed and was hard ridden to maintain position when racing a clear last after 100m. Came under pressure passing the 500m before passing a few in the straight. Never likely from rearward position.

Began awkwardly, failed to muster speed and raced rearward. Continued rearward cornering next to last, over 5L from lead. Awkwardly placed near heels at the 300m but failed to make any impression in later stages.
Hard ridden to improve after start and raced outside leader form the 1200m. Came under heavy pressure passing the 500m and gave ground in the straight.

Strode forward after the start but was left racing wide without cover in midfield after the first section. Improved position mid-race to corner 2.5L from lead before giving significant ground in the straight after tough trip.

Steadied after start and shifted across to midfield after the first section. Moved three wide with cover near the 950m before coming under heavy pressure near the 500m. Hung in when giving significant ground in the straight.

Lost significant ground at the start & consequently raced rearward early. Forced 4 wide passing the 950m and left without cover thereafter. Improved position in middle stages before tiring out from the corner after tough run.
Began smartly, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced 2W better than midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, 3W turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, wider on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, inconvenienced near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, held up till 150M, finished off nicely thereafter to score by a head.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, worked home nicely but was unable to hold off the winner late.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground and ran on strongly to the line.
Raced in about midfield, 2 wide throughout, saved ground and ran on okay.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, in touch until couldn't find extra for final 150M.
Slotted in to race in midfield, 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, kept on until emptied late.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward and took up the box-seat, couldn't find extra for final 200M.
In behind midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Awkward start, at rear along the rail, hardly improved but continued on to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, emptied passing 300M. (Blood in trachea and lame left front)
Checked after start, at rear 2 wide, never threatened.
Slow to jump, always at the tail, never a factor.
Taken well back from a wide gate and waited with, responded well inside final 250 metres to assert authority close home.

Moderate start, settled well behind dropping to last rounding home bend, soon came under pressure after straightening, made up good ground down the centre of the track to reach 2nd inside final 50 metres.
Hard ridden early settling not far off 3-wide without cover in 5th, similar turning in, ran on to hold some chance 200 metres out but only to be outsprinted shortly after.
Moderate start but soon picked up to within 3L of pace on the rail in 6th, remained similar into home straight, kept on well under pressure.
Shifted back to last few from a wide gate, remained towards the rear and went wide into home straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Ridden hard to take up running 1200 metres out, obtained rails run passing the 1000 metres, kicked over 1L clear after straightening, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 100 metres.

Moderate start from a poor gate, settled behind midfield wide without cover, made steady headway rounding home bend and wide into straight, looked quickening when no clear run inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, ridden to forward of midfield in 7th, in similar position entering home straight, did not find much room early on, kept on same pace without threatening.
Settled in midfield, slightly worse rounding home bend, came under pressure after straightening, kept on at the one pace.
Brief lead early, taken one back on the rail to 3rd, came to challenge after obtaining a clear run early in straight, faded under pressure 150 metres out while hanging in.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled in midfield on the rail, awkwardly placed and checked from heels rounding home bend, towards the rear into straight, made no impression after straightening.
Began well, settled just off the pace mainly just over 2L back in 4th, poised to challenge upon straightening but soon weakened under pressure.
Broke well from the widest gate but taken back, wide without cover before rolled forward to 1L back 1000 metres out, soon dropped out of contention under pressure after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered towards the rear along the rails, cropped two bad checks rounding home bend, made no impression at rear of field in the straight.
Lost ground at start, ended up in rear pair along inside, over 4Ls to make up turning in, not clear run 250M, chased strongly final 200M, got up near line.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, 5Ls off the pace in the rear, last turning home, ran on well over final 300M, lay out final 100M, just denied.
Jumped well from draw 1 to be tracking leaders, responded well to pressure in straight and kept on steadily to line, just held by first 2.
Began fairly, held up in midfield along the fence, chased hard final 400M to just miss a placing. (Lame next day.)
Strode forward to be leading at good pace, opened up 2L lead 300M, kept on well only caught by first four 50M from home.
Settled 3-wide behind midfield, gave brief response early straight, couldn't muster the speed to be closer passing 200M.
Dropped back from wide draw, given a patient ride out the back along 3-path, ran on fairly in the straight without ever looking likely.

Lost ground at start, settled near rear further back than intended, checked 300M and didn't recover, went to the line one-paced. (Jockey cited inexperience was primary reason for disappointing performance.)
Began well, retrained to sit in 5th spot, pushed along 600M but failed to make ground in the straight.
Never far off the pace, 3-wide no cover chasing leaders home turn, labored early straight, out of contention 300M.
Chased leader, couldn't go on passing 400M, eased mid-straight. (Irregular Heart Rhythm / Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score, really impressive.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, recovered quickly to sit 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, blocked near 150M, not ridden out thereafter.
Taken back to race 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly for a short distance after 800M, 3 wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Minor laceration to the inside of the right hind heel.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, bumped early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1400M, sat right behind the leader thereafter, easy run on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, bumped early in straight, then showed some response before checked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, wider after passing 700M, made contact turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, made contact near 950M, wider on turn, one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked 200M then inconvenienced after passing 150M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, checked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Hampered start, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1400M to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.

Shifted across to midfield away from the rail after the start. Moved wider on cornering before sprinting very strongly once balanced. Assumed lead inside the final 250m before racing away for easy win.

Mustered speed after the start to race in midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail at the 550m before balancing four lengths form the lead. Made solid headway into second inside the furlong but no match for winner.

Shifted back behind runners to race second from last, 12L from a fast early speed in first section. Third from last on cornering before finishing off strongly in the straight after conceding big margin from rearward position.

Shifted across after the start to good position in midfield away from rail around 4L from lead. Moved three wide passing the 800m before cornering second widest and finishing off evenly in the last section.
Strode forward in early stages before steadying behind leaders near the 1100m. Two lengths form lead on straightening, moved up within a length at the 200m before peaking late in the race.

Steadied after the start and shifted across from wide barrier to race at the tail. Was a clear last on cornering before making up 4 lengths in the final section and passing some tired runners in late stages.

Strode forward to race behind leading quartet away from the rail after the first section. Eased three wide approaching the corner before moving within a length of the lead at the 300m before peaking shorty after.
Didn't begin fast and raced in the clear in midfield, over 8L from the lead at halfway. Came under pressure passing the 500m before passing a few tired ones in the straight without ever threatening.
Had no early speed and raced third from last, over 10L from lead after first section. Hard ridden before cornering and only really held margin in the straight.

Hard ridden in early stages to stride to the front after 200m. Continued to work hard to cross to rail at the 1200m when setting very fast early speed. Continued to hold the lead approaching the 200m before tiring late.
Worked very hard after the start to stride forward and cross outside a very fast tempo near the 1100m. Couldn't go with the leader inside the final 350m & tired out further inside the last furlong.
Held the rail in midfield, three lengths form the lead after 600m. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before peaking on effort & giving ground in the straight to be well beaten.
Strode forward to contest lead early before being crossed and racing on leaders back from the 1200m. Came under pressure shortly after straightening and tired inside the final 300m.
Had no early speed and settled in the final four, over 10L from lead after 400m. Steadied and drifted back nearing the corner before tailing out in the straight to be well beaten.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on strongly in straight, scored by 3/4L.
Began well, raced in 2nd, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight but always held by the winner.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, hampered near 1000M, no cover on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, hampered near 1000M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield, hampered and carried wider near 1000M, 4 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 9 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, showed no early speed, raced wide at rear, 9 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 to 3 wide better than midfield, hampered near 1000M, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.

Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, severely hampered near 1000M, positioned on rail behind midfield in the middle stages, showed no response early in straight, eased after passing 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased back, took cover, moved to 3 wide and improved steadily, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
Pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well until 150M weakened.
Pressed forward, sat outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, led 400M, emptied 150M.
Slow to muster, took rail at back, not suited by the slow pace, ran on only fairly.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, weakened 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
At back, 2-3 wide, moved forward 900M to take advantages of the slow tempo, however emptied 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at slow sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, continued to gain ground near 200M, worked home strongly to score.
At the start bumped a runner and became unbalanced, raced behind midfield, improved near 500M, made nice ground passing 200M, finished solidly.
Ridden with nice early speed to race behind the lead, placed pressure near 400M, finished nicely.
Settled in front of midfield, fought hard in the straight, gained ground passing 100M.
Ridden along to take lead, tried to improve passing 450M, worked home one-paced.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced, raced behind midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Slow out and raced at rear, widest on straightening, battled hard but only limited response.
Taken back at start, tried to improve on rail in the straight, limited response.

Bumped & unbalanced before steadying across to the tail. Improved position on cornering, conceding 5L at the 400m. Sprinted strongly passing the 350m & continued to make headway before striking lead in late stages.
Unbalanced at start before mustering speed to race on leaders back. Moved away from the rail passing the 400m, assumed lead inside the final 200m before being over-run in the late stages.
A touch slow to begin before gathering speed and holding the rail in midfield. Cornered close to the inside before shifting out at the 350m and making solid late ground to snare third.
Raced to midfield between runners in early section, 4.5L from lead passing the 800m. Shifted wider on cornering before making steady headway in the straight to be close up.
Began fast, crossed face of field when leading, settling on rail after first section. Over 1L clear on cornering, joined inside the final furlong and gave a length or two in late stages.

Steadied after the start and shifted back to a rearward position. Held the rail when 5.5L from the lead passing the 800m. Stayed close to rail entering final section before maintaining margin to line.
Showed some early speed to race away from the rail, 1L from the lead in first section. Hung outwards after straightening before peaking on effort passing the 300m & giving a few lengths late.

Steadied across from wide barrier before drifting back to last approaching the 800m. Continued to race rearward before cornering widest, 7.5L from lead. Passed a few in the straight while maintaining margin from leader.

Ridden forward after the start but trapped three wide without cover, before improving to race 1L form the lead approaching the 800m. Continued wide path in middle stages before weakening out in the final section.

Began awkwardly & bumped before making up some ground to midfield, when three wide with cover. Moved wider on cornering when 3L from lead before giving ground prior to the 200m. Not tested last furlong.

Settled in midfield, three wide with cover, 4L from the lead at the 800m. Moved wider when improving passing the 600m before cornering 6L form lead. Made no headway in the straight and was well beaten.

Began well but had no early speed and drifted back to settle worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Hard ridden approaching the corner when over 7L from lead before giving further ground in the straight.

Began awkwardly before being shifted across behind runners and racing third from last after 400m. Shuffled back to last when under pressure on cornering before yielding further ground in the straight to be well beaten.

Showed some speed to be prominent before steadying between runners, 3L from lead at the 800m. Came under heavy pressure to hold position passing the 650m before yielding significant ground from the 550m. (Must trial).
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 300M, kept on very strongly to the line, impressive.

Bumped on jumping, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, taken wide early in straight, bumped near 250M, finished off very strongly thereafter to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 900M, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 3rd without threatening.
Began only fairly and bumped, awkwardly placed near 1100M, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced very wide in midfield, made contact near 850M, 4 wide turning, kept on well early in straight, bumped heavily near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off one pace.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 850M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, peaked on run near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 800M, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 4 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to be in midfield 2 wide, ran on spiritedly to the line to score by a neck.
Raced in front of midfield, wide and without cover however, worked home nicely to take 2nd.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, continued on well to the line.
Eased then slotted in to race in behind midfield 2 wide, saved ground and continued on fairly.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, showed no turn of foot.
Raced just in front of midfield, on rail, slightly held up early, ran on fairly to the line thereafter.
Rolled forward to take rail and led, kept on until run ended at 150M.
Taken back, raced at the tail on rail, continued to the line.
In midfield, wide but with cover, one paced in the straight.
Jumped only fairly, settled in midfield along the rail, was one paced.
Eased to be in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover, saved no ground.
Taken back, at rear 3 wide at turn with cover, did not feature.
At rear, 2 wide, never improved.
In box-seat, emptied approaching 250M.
Jumped awkwardly but soon took up running on stands rail, briefly headed halfway out, won unextended.
Never far off, fought on steadily to reach 2nd over 150 metres out but never threatening.
Broke well settling just off the pace, not far off in 6th on stands rails 400 metres out, soon came under pressure to challenge, reached distant 3rd 100 metres out without threatening first two.
Jumped fairly, soon came to share the pace hitting front briefly 400 metres out, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres.
Began well settling just off the pace, unable to quicken under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to the rear despite ridden along, made up late ground past well-beaten runners in closing stages.
Soon dropped towards the rear despite ridden along, ran home one paced under pressure.
Towards the rear most of the way, found nothing under pressure.
Moderate start, settled in forward of midfield some 3L back on the rail, weakened under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled in last few, made headway down the centre of the track to reach 11th some 6L off the pace 400 metres out, made no impression in the final stretch.
Not far off to halfway, folded up quickly inside final 400 metres.
Settled in midfield, made no impression in the closing stages.
Never a factor.
Settled in midfield, faded out of contention inside final 400 metres.
Settled mid-division, travelled strongly into contention, quickened well under top weight to lead inside 200M, kept on late to hold off pursuing rivals.
Held up midfield along the fence, awkwardly placed early straight, into clear 300M, chased hard to go 2nd near line, couldn't reel in winner.
Settled behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, responded well turning home to be chasing winner but always held.
Strode forward as expected, led uncontested, kept on well early straight, headed passing 200M, fought on till late stages, lost 2 placings near line.
Held up 2nd last given a patient ride, saved ground on inside, peeled out passing 300M to challenge, kept coming to finish just behind the placegetters.
Stayed back from the outside gate, over 8Ls away in last middle stages, peeled wide 550M, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Chased leaders, didn't quicken passing 400M when put under pressure, failed to finish off. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation for disappointing performance.)
Chased leaders in 4th, didn't respond to riding early straight, soon out of contention.
Tracked leader 2-wide, out-sprinted from 350M, dropped out.
Behind mid-division, under the pump from 550M, already a spent force passing 300M.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, easy lead on turn, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.

Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, missed 2nd on line.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run near 100M, stayed on well, lost two places close home.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, blocked near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight peaked near 200M, weakened steadily thereafter.
Shifted on at start and bumped, raced wide with cover at rear, angled out 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 1000M, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began very awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, a bit closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, found rail near 900M, angled out after passing 550M, made very good progress in straight to score by a neck.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame without threatening the first few.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield, 2 wide turning, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began very awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider turning in, made little progress in straight.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 550M, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1050M, 2Ls back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 200M. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 250M.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length behind the leader, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on very strongly to the line, scored by 2 lengths.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 2nd.
Away well from gate1, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 600M, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back to race 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, checked off heels near 550M, brushed the rail 350M, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace in straight.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 700M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Pushed to cross in front, enjoyed the slow sectionals outside the lead, closed off strongly 300M to win.
Pushed to take rail in the lead, settled in box seat 600M, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, moved forward 800M to take the advantages of the slow sectionals, led 600M, overhauled 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Pushed early to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, lack room 400M, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
On heels early, eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed to obtain box seat early, shuffled back 800M, held up 5-3, no dash when clear.
Tailed out early, harmed by the slow tempo, lack dash.
Eased back, took rail, over-raced badly, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, buffered for room 400M, emptied 350M.
Jumped nicely, settled in handy position on rail, improved passing 500M, quickened solidly passing 100M to score.
Travelled midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, widest on straightening, made up nice late ground, missed by HD.
Fractious in barrier and slow to begin, settled at back, commenced to improve passing 600M, continued to gain ground in the straight, worked home solidly, missed by Neck.
Near 1200M was left racing wide and without cover, then improved its position to outside the lead near 900M, asked for effort near 400M, made ground passing 100M.
Taken back from widest barrier, raced at tail, commenced to improve passing 500M, wide on straightening, gained ground passing 100M.
Hard ridden to take lead, allowed a runner to cross and took box seat passing 1000M, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, responded well in the straight.
Taken back at start, tried to improve passing 400M, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Raced in front of midfield, wide on straightening, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, battled hard in the straight but only limited response.
Hard ridden to take forward position, settled in one-back-one-off, weakened passing 100M, failed to make impression, rider questioned.
Ridden forward with nice early speed, improved to lead passing 1000M, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged along but failed to muster speed, raced behind midfield, passing 800M checked away from heels when travelled keenly, no response in the straight.
Mustered speed to race behind the leader on the rail. Stayed close to the inside on straightening, moved up to join lead nearing the 100m before drawing away for comfortable win late.
Hard ridden after start to share lead before racing outside the leader passing the 800m. Continued to be close to the lead in the straight before finding winner too strong late.

Strode forward to be prominent to lead before steadying to race behind leading trio away from rail. Held up for running after straightening and again crowded when making steady headway near the 100m. Finished close up.
Shifted across after start, racing midfield on rail 3L from lead after first section. Stayed close to the rail in the straight before making up a length relative to leader in the dash to the line.
Mustered speed after the start to share the lead before continuing on to hold outright lead passing the 800m. Joined inside the last furlong before giving two lengths late in the race.

Steadied and shifted across from outside barrier to settle at the rear, three wide with cover. Continued rearward, 7L from the lead passing the 400m before making steady headway after straightening without threatening.
Bumped & unbalanced before hard ridden in first furlong to hold midfield position. Hard ridden approaching the 400m when 2.5L from lead before holding similar margin in the run to line.

Strode to midfield before being steadied after 250m to obtain cover, 3.5L from the lead after the first section. Moved three wide passing the 400m before cornering widest and maintaining margin in the straight.

Strode forward to challenge for lead before steadying and racing three wide without cover outside leaders. Moved up to join a line of three at the 400m before peaking & tiring in the last furlong after tough trip.

Steadied after first furlong and shifted back to obtain cover settling 5L from the lead after 400m. Hard ridden when attempting to improve passing halfway before holding 6L margin in the final section.
Shifted across to the rail after the start when racing at the tail. Hard ridden approaching the 400m when 6L from the lead and failed to make any headway in the last section.

Had no speed and raced next to last in first section. Hard ridden approaching the 550m when losing ground. Conceded 10L passing the 400m and continued to give further ground after straightening to be well beaten.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3w in the early stages, 2w from near 600M, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, ran on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Out in line, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 850M, 3 wide turning, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, kept on well early in straight, steadied approaching 50M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, made contact near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3w early, 2w from 850M, allowed rival to cross near 600M, 2Ls back on turn, kept on well early in straight, raced tight 200M, steadied 50M, not ridden out thereafter.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly until crowded near 100M, eased thereafter.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed after passing 150M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 2 wide, swung widest and battled on gamely to score by 3/4L.
Eased and found cover in just behind midfield, 2 wide, showed good dashes and continued nicely to the line.
Rolled forward and raced the box-seat, ran on fairly to the line.
Settled to race in front of midfield, along the rail, kept on going to the line.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, ran on to the line.
Eased then settled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved slightly.
Jumped only fairly, then failed to muster, in worse than midfield along the rail, made slight ground.
Ridden before taking cover in midfield, 2 wide, did not improve.
Eased and raced at the rear, along the rail, did not save ground.
Raced in one-off one-back position, found no extra near 150M.
Rolled forward, obtained lead on rail at 1000M, headed when found no extra passing 200M. (See Incident Report)
Ridden and settled outside the lead, stayed on until emptied at 200M. (See Incident Report)
Settled not far off in 4th, quickened well to lead 100 metres out, won readily.
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th or 5th, wide into straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Ridden along in close-up 3rd along the rail, held same into the straight, hit the front briefly inside the 200 metres, unable to sustain effort.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, widest runner turning for home, ran on well inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from the one gate, settled some 3L back in 5th or 6th on the rail, soon came under pressure after straightening, kept on until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Ridden to dispute lead, gained slender advantage at the 700 metres and led until finding no extra 200 metres out.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear, made some late impression closing stages.
Taken back to rear from the widest gate, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Settled in last few, never seen with a chance.
Jumped best and ridden positively from a wide gate, held narrow lead before headed at the 700 metres, dropped out from amongst the leaders upon straightening. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Failed to muster despite ridden along, trailed the field throughout virtually.
Broke well but soon dropped to rear of midfield, saved ground on inside turning for home, weakened under pressure shortly after straightening. (Bled)
Held up in midfield 5-6Ls back, kept to inside on straightening, ran on well to wrestle the lead 50M, clung on from fast finishing 2nd at the line.
Began only fairly, settled down midfield in 6th about 4Ls off the fast pace, brought wide into straight, finished off strongly, just missed.
Away swiftly from draw 1, led them at fast pace, kept on well in straight only to be caught by first 2 near line.
Away with them, 5th on settling, had inside run throughout, chased leaders steadily on straightening but always held.
From draw 12 taken across behind runners, held up towards the rear in a fast run race, 6Ls off 400M, stayed on well down outside, just missed 4th.
From wide draw ridden along for considerable distance to cross runners to its inside, tracked leader from 1100M in a fast run race, kept on same pace turning home, out-finished 200M.
Held up behind midfield 5-6Ls back, brought wide home, lay in under pressure in straight, closed off only fairly. No threat.
Settled towards the rear in a fast run race, 6-7Ls back in middle stages, pushed along 450M, couldn't muster the speed to challenge.
Taken across behind runners, settled near last 9Ls off the good pace, wide into straight, failed to finish off.
Went forward, chased leaders 2-wide in fast run race, run ended shortly after straightening, out of contention 250M.
Restrained to race in the rear in fast run race, over 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, swung widest into straight, made no progress.
Pressed forward to be tracking leaders in a fast run race, couldn't quicken early straight, failed to finish off. (Jockey: pace in middle stages did not suit but nonetheless disappointing.)
