Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, showed very good response, easily scored.
Away well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide after passing 700M, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, wider from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off one pace in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Jumped with field, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Failed to muster at rear, pace good, improved around the field 800M in 4-5 wide, dashed well 300M to score.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, held ground in straight for 3rd.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on well until 200M weakened.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 5-3, made steady ground when clear.
At rear, on the fence, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
At back, 2-3 wide, pace good, checked badly 500M, made ground 250M.
At back along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Hard ridden but never muster, trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, out of fuel 300M.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden to share the lead at good pace, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden to keep up, trapped 3-4 wide, faded 500M.
Pressed forward, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, dropped off 700M.
Ridden along to race in handy position, asked for effort near 400M, issued challenged passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Raced inside the lead, commenced to improve passing 400M, near 100M rider dropped his whip, finished solidly.
Urged along to race behind lead on outside rail, placed pressure passing 450M, approaching 100M rider dropped his whip, worked home nicely.
Settled midfield on outside rail, responded nicely when asked for effort passing 400M, finished well.
Raced behind midfield, fought hard passing 400M, gained ground passing 100M.
At the start stumbled, raced at rear on outside rail, niggled to maintain its position passing 800M, made up some ground passing 150M.
Began awkwardly, bumped inside gate and lost ground, settled at rear, fought hard but only one-paced.
Settled midfield near middle of track, one-paced when placed pressure near 400M.
Travelled behind leaders, limited response when asked for effort.
Raced behind leaders, near 700M lay out across heels, gave ground passing 150M.
Began only fairly then was crowded for room, took lead with nice early speed, weakened near 200M, blood trachea.
After start was crowded for room, near 700M was again crowded for room, raced at back, no response when asked for effort.
Settled in handy position, commenced to give ground passing 550M, failed to run on.
Began awkwardly, bumped a runner and became badly unbalanced, raced at tail, failed to run on.
Shared lead in early staged before being crossed and racing on leaders back from the 950m. Sprinted well to assume the lead nearing the 300m before continuing on to score easy win.

Enjoyed economical run in midfield on the rail, 2.5L from lead after 400m. Shifted away from the rail approaching the 550m before working home well in the final section for second. Winner well clear, margin to third.
Ridden forward in first 250m before assuming lead and crossing to the rail near the 950m. Joined in the lead at the 300m before being left in the wake of the winner.

Began fast from wide barrier before being restrained right back last after 100m. Improved position in second section, cornering 4.5L from the lead. Passed tiring runners in the straight but never a winning factor.
Shifted across to midfield position on the rail, over 7L from the lead passing the 800m. Moved wider on cornering before passing a few late without threatening placed runners.

Began well before easing out of speed battle to settle midfield, 4L from lead after 400m. Moved three wide approaching the 500m before balancing 3L from lead. Peaked on effort passing the 300m & gave a few lengths late.

Not fast away before mustering speed to race in midfield on rail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering when 4L from lead. One paced and couldn't improve passing the 350m before tiring & giving ground in final 250m.

Unbalanced after start before steadying & shifting back the tail. Drifted further back, 11L from the lead passing the 800m. Passed a few when working home evenly but was still well beaten behind dominant winner.
Improved after the start to race in midfield around 5L from lead after first 400m. Moved wider passing the 500m before yielding another 4L to the lead in the last section.

Shifted across from outside gate to midfield away from rail. Moved three wide passing the 600m before easing away from heels on turn. Six lengths from lead on straightening before yielding further ground in straight.

Drifted back after start to race in final trio passing the 800m. Taken very wide passing the 600m before cornering widest, 5L from lead. Eased down in late stages & was well beaten. (Uncomfortable action during race).

Steadied and shifted across behind runners to race near the rear. Checked away from heels when pushed wide passing the 650m before cornering last 7L from lead. Made no headway in straight & was well beaten.
Strode to good position away from the rail, two pairs behind leader. Came under pressure approaching the bend and yielded significant ground after straightening to be well beaten.

Share lead before being crossed and racing third on the outside passing the 900m. Failed to hold prominent position from cornering & yielded significant ground before being eased down in latter stages. (Must trial).
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, took the lead after passing 500M, kept on very strongly in straight, easily scored.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, positioned on rail better than midfield, travelled well to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider after passing 600M, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield, a bit closer turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, unbalanced near 1200M, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Rolled into the lead with ease, gradually pulled away from 300M and won comfortably by 2-3/4L.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, worked home well to finish 2nd.
Steadied after start, shifted to rail and raced in about midfield, ran on well inside final 200M to take 3rd.
Asked and settled in one-off one-back position, ran on fairly to the line.
Niggled along to take up the box-seat, continued on until emptied in final stages.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 2 wide, one paced early then closed off fairly late.
Taken back, at rear 3 wide but with cover, showed some dashes in the straight.
Hard ridden and sat outside the lead, gave ground from around 300M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 2 wide, did not threaten.
Eased back, raced at the tail 2-3 wide, did not feature.
In about midfield, wide but with cover, found nothing. (See Incident Report)
Slow to jump, remained at rear along the rail, lost ground in the straight.
Went forward and was prominent, wide and without cover however, gave ground prior to straightening.

Jumped awkwardly, settled not far off the pace in 6th on the rail, gained closer turning in, quickened under pressure to hit the front inside final 300 metres going 2L clear 200 metres out, just held on.
Settled in last few, made significant progress down the centre of the straight to just fail to get up on line.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear, ran on well inside final 300 metres to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along in midfield, slightly worse approaching home turn, finish off the race well inside final 250 metres.
Settled well behind, switched out for a run 300 metres out, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Close up early, drifted steadily backward on home bend to be 7th some 4L off into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Amongst leaders 3-wide, taken 2L back to 4th 3-wide around the bend, quickened under pressure to reach 2nd at the 200 metres before fading shortly afterwards. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled better than midfield about 3L off the pace, drifted slightly backward 4-wide rounding the bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Travelled very wide in midfield from a wide gate, slightly worse coming onto home turn, kept on at the same pace under pressure in the run to the line.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, remained very wide without cover with leaders throughout back straight and rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Slowly away, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Jumped well, shared early pace on the rail, hit the front briefly after straightening, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from wide gate, settled wide in forward of midfield, obtained rails run in 8th coming onto home bend, saved ground turning in, gradually faded under pressure.
Broke well, shared early pace in back straight, drifted one back to 3rd rounding home bend, lost further ground after straightening.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored, very impressive.
Fast into stride, positioned on rail better than midfield, angled out after passing 600M, finished off well to take 2nd, no chance with the easy winner.

Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and lost 2nd after passing 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, angled out near 550M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began very awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, unbalanced near 1000M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress when clear final 200M.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, carried wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Made contact on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, 3 wide from 800M, weakened turning in, finished last.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, travelled well to turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Commenced well from a wide draw, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just missed by a neck.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.

Crowded out start and unbalanced, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground to turn, commenced move after passing 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly.

Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Stood flat-footed and missed the start, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, no clear run until final 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide and without cover, slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide at rear, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, no clear running early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed good response early in straight, blocked 300M, switched in thereafter and finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, 2 wide after passing 800M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take a place.

Away well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead and set a fast tempo, led by 3 lengths turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong, headed final 50M, just stayed on for 4th.
Began well, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 950M, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide turning, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear after passing 200M.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 800M, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide in the early stages, found a 2w spot near 1050M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, peaked on run early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 150M.

Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 wide on turn, commenced moved after passing 600M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Away well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight.

Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored. (Lame left front leg.)
Began smartly, taken back to race 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take 3rd without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, made good progress when clear final 50M.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, taken wide after turning in, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Bled.)
Bumped start, raced prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Hard ridden to sit 3 back on the fence, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to occupy box seat, pace good, led 250M, overhauled 100M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
At back along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, weakened 150M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 250M.
At rear, 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, no dash in straight.
Hard ridden early but never muster, trapped 4 wide, no progress.
Began awkwardly then ridden along to race midfield, always niggled, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled well, responded nicely in the straight, missed by Neck.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, wide on straightening, gained nice late ground.
Raced midfield, improved passing 600M, wide rounding the Home Turn, responded nicely in the straight.
Urged to race outside the lead, commenced to improve near 600M, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground near 50M.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, tried to improve passing 600M, wide on straightening, one-paced.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, ridden passing 800M to maintain its position, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, travelled at back on rail, limited response when asked for effort in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but no response, failed to run on.
Raced behind leaders, no response when asked for effort, weakened in the straight.
Raced at rear, came under heavy pressure prior to the 600M, eased down in the straight, lame left front next day, must trial.
Hard ridden and mustered speed to race outside the leader passing the 900m. Moved up to assume lead approaching the 250m before sprinting away strongly to record big margin win.

Had soft run in midfield on the rail, 3L from the lead after the first section. Stayed close to rail on cornering, crowded at 250m before finishing off evenly in last 200m to grab second in a group well behind winner.

Shifted across passing the 900m to get nice trail away from the fence, on the back of the winner. Continued to track winner into the turn before being left behind prior working home evenly in the last 250m.

Strode forward to be prominent before shifting to the rail and onto the leaders back nearing the 900m. Hung in at the 250m when 2L from the lead before finishing off fairly to finish in a cluster behind big margin winner.

Slow to begin and was a clear last immediately after the start. Continued rearward and was over 8L from the lead passing the 400m before making up significant ground in the straight to finish just behind placed horses.

Not fast into stride and raced worse than midfield on the rail in early section before improving to be 4L from lead passing the 400m. Moved into clear running but didn't really threaten in the straight.
Had no early speed and drifted back to second last away from the rail after the start. Continued rearward before passing a few in the straight but was never a real factor.
Raced in midfield away from the rail, 4.5L from lead after first section. Moved three wide approaching the 400m before failing to run on in the straight.
Failed to muster speed and raced worse than midfield away from rail. Conceded 5.5L to lead entering the final section and failed to make any headway in the run home.

Shifted across from wide barrier to race midfield away from the rail, 3L from lead after first section. Close enough to lead on cornering before peaking & yielding ground shortly after straightening. (Blood in trachea).
Had no early speed and raced third from last on the rail in first 800m. Seven lengths from lead entering the last section and failed to make any headway in the straight to be well beaten.

Showed good early speed to assume the lead. Held narrow margin on cornering before being headed at the 250m & giving substantial ground thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm, blood in trachea. Must trial)

Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, 2 wide turning, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, awkwardly placed near 500M, commenced move after passing 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide after passing 900M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, wide into straight, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Out in line, positioned 5 to 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider after entering the back straight, sent forward after passing 700M, shared lead on turn, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead and set a fast tempo, challenged by rival turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 1100M, weakened after entering the back straight, eased after passing 600M, finished tailed out.
Sent forward, maintained lead on rail, ran on and held off a very late challenge to score.
Settled in one-off one-back position, closed off gamely, missed by a short-head.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, bumped at 350M, ran home well for 3rd.
Crowded after start, raced just behind midfield 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
Went forward and raced outside the lead, stayed on until weakened near 100M.
Settled just front of midfield, 2 wide, bumped at 350M, closed off fairly.
Crowded after start, in worse than midfield along the rail, showed some dashes.
Eased then raced towards the rear, 2 wide, saved some ground.
Asked and took box-seat, one paced and emptied near 150M.
At rear, along the rail, improved slightly in the straight. (Lame left front)
Taken back and at tail, 2 wide, made minor ground.
In midfield, along the rail, did not threaten.
Niggled along wide in midfield, taken slightly back for cover at the 900 metres, remained in similar position into straight, responded well to just get up on line.
Settled in midfield on the rail, switched out to challenge entering home straight, hit the front 100 metres out only to be caught close to home.
Very wide in midfield early stages, taken back to the rear after the 1000-metre bend, commenced move entering home straight, finished strongly down the centre of the track to fail narrowly.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning in, ran on well inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Ridden from a moderate start before settling 3-wide in 4th over 2L back, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield from the 700 metres, produced some late impression down the centre of the track inside final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled handily in 3rd, ran home one-paced.
Shared pace 2-wide most of the way, gained slender lead rounding home bend and held the same into straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Jumped fairly, closer up before steadied and lost position about 900 metres out, gave ground under pressure rounding home bend.
Ridden forward to share the lead, hung on for close 2nd on the rail rounding home bend, weakened under pressure after straightening.
Crowded and lost position early settling in 9th on the rail behind midfield, made no impression in the run to the line.
Began from a wide gate, soon dropped to last few despite reminders, never seen with a chance.
Shifted across behind runners, raced near last 6-7Ls away, wide on straightening, quickened up smartly to lead 150M, kept on strongly final stages for 3rd win of the season.
From wide draw eased back after the jump, raced as the back-marker early stages, kept to inside rounding home turn, kicked home well straightening, held by winner final 150M, well clear from rest.
Held up near the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, 3-wide entering back straight, swung widest home, stayed on steadily to claim 3rd near line without reaching top 2.
Pressed forward, travelled keenly 1200M when racing outside leader, vied for lead early straight, briefly led 200M, couldn't hold off first 2 inside 150M, lost 3rd close home.
Settled behind mid-division along the inside, 7th at 400M, worked home steadily without ever looking likely.
Chased leaders, no closer than 3-wide throughout, kept on same pace in straight after tough trip, never threatened leaders.
Pushed along to take up running along the fence, was taken on by rival entering back-straight, lost lead 250M then weakened away.
Settled down in 7th spot, 3-wide behind midfield, brought wide home, couldn't quicken, never a threat.
With leaders early stages then eased back to be 2Ls off the pace on settling, only laboured in straight. Never a factor.
Restrained to race behind midfield, 4Ls off the pace in 8th spot, couldn't go on passing 300M, eased when no chance. (Lame RF leg).
Chased leaders, wide no cover from 1100M, raced keenly and moved forward to be joining leaders 3-wide, run ended soon after straightening as hard run took toll.
Chased leaders along the fence, came under heavy pressure 500M, bumped by rival 250M and unbalanced but already beaten at that point.

Made contact on jumping, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, moved closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover, slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no match to the winner.
Began well, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back after passing 1050M to race behind midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced prominently on rail, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Made contact on jumping, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off one pace.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, 3 wide throughout, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly to score.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace, closed off strongly 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden but not muster, at back along the fence, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M.
Settled in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Trapped 4 wide throughout, emptied 400M.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide, never improved.
Slow away, never a factor.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, soon emptied 500M.
Began only fairly, settled midfield on rail, shifted out to one off position to improve passing 800M, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Settled midfield, asked for effort near 600M, responded solidly in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, in the early part of straight was held up running, gained nice ground near 150M.
Ridden along for some distance to take lead, placed pressure passing 400M, fought nicely in the straight.
Began awkwardly then taken back, raced at rear on rail, asked for effort on straightening, made up nice late ground.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, battled hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along after start, raced in front of midfield, lay out rounding the Home Turn, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced behind leaders, tried to improve near 500M, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Urged to race inside the lead on rail, placed pressure near 300M, gave ground near 100M.
Ridden along to settle in front of midfield, wide on straightening, emptied near 200M.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, hung out and lost ground rounding the Home Turn, no response in the straight, must trial.
Urged along but travelled wide and without cover in handy position, gave ground in the straight, must trial.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, did no travel at any stages, finished tailed out, must trial.

Shifted across to race in midfield on the outside. Moved three wide when travelling strongly passing the 600m. Sprinted fast after straightening, cruised to lead at the 150m before going on for effortless win.
Steadied after the start and raced worse than midfield between runners. Ridden hard passing the 475m before cornering over 5L from lead. Finished hard inside the last 250m to not be beaten far.
Began well before quickly getting trail behind leader. Moved over heels when travelling strongly, striking lead at the 300m before being joined and over-run inside the final 150m.
Had little early speed and raced in the final trio along the rail. Continued on the inside, 5.5L from the lead on cornering before passing a few late but maintaining margin to the line.
Ridden forward before working hard to get up outside the leader near the 700m. Cornered one length from the lead before peaking on effort inside the final furlong & giving ground late.
Steadied after the start before racing in midfield on the rail. Hard ridden on cornering when only 3L from the lead before peaking inside the last furlong.
Raced worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Shifted very wide on cornering, before balancing 6L from the lead. Passed a few in the run to the line despite being well beaten.
Had no early speed and raced at the tail. Continued at the rear, over 8L from lead on balancing and never improved after straightening.
Showed early speed to assume the lead. Raced over 1L clear in the middle stages before being headed at the 300m and yielding many lengths in the straight.
Ridden forward before steadying at the 900m, then left three wide without cover approaching the 600m. Five lengths from the lead on cornering before weakening out significantly in the last section.
Steadied after the start and shifted across to race at the tail after the first furlong. Was a clear last on cornering, 9L from the lead and failed to make any headway in the straight.
Strode forward to be prominent before getting one out, one back passing the 700m. Began yielding ground from the 600m and was beaten a significant margin. (Must trial).
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled comfortably to turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.

Away well, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, angled out after passing 450M, closed off well to take a place. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Jumped well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 700M, half length back turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, taken back to race 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, bumped the rail near 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, steadied to obtain cover near 800M, angled out after passing 500M, weakened early in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield, weakened turning in, eased early in straight.
Raced one-out one-back, showed good kick approaching 300M, continued on to score impressively by 3-3/4L.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, worked home nicely for 2nd despite racing greenly in the straight.
Eased then ridden to be just behind midfield, 2 wide, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Eased and raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved and closed off fairly.
Travelled in just behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground and ran on nicely to the line.
Settled to race in the box-seat, continued on one paced to the line.
Urged to take rail and led, maintained lead until headed passing 200M, weakened late. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward, raced outside the lead, stayed on until near 200M then weakened.
Bumped start, recovered to be in front of midfield along the rail, one paced until awkward to heels late.
Awkward start, raced in midfield 2 wide, bumped after 400M, saved no ground.
Dragged back, at tail and shifted 3 wide near 700M, did not threaten.
Taken back and remained at rear, 2 wide, did not feature.
Eased, at rear but wide and without cover, not competitive.
Bumped start, at rear along the rail, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move angling off the rail approaching home bend, quickened well to take command 300 metres out.
Settled in last few and waited with, switched out for a run shortly after straightening, finished off the race strongly but never going to trouble the winner.
Settled in midfield, slightly worse coming onto home bend, switched wide into straight, fought on well under pressure down the centre of the track, lost 2nd late.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, in similar position turning for home, baulked for a run early in straight, obtained run 300 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.

Moderate start, settled towards the rear, hampered on the rail at the 900 metres, saved a lot of ground turning in, baulked for a run until the 200 metres, switched out and kept on well closing stages.
Well there, re-gained narrow advantage outside of leader rounding home bend, kept on until headed 300 metres out.
Broke well from a wide draw, shifted in for cover travelling within 2L of the pace, came to challenge on straightening holding some chance, found no extra 200 metres out.
Jumped best, settled just off the pace on the rail, baulked for a run in straight, made no impression closing stages.
Travelled wide without cover in prominent position, soon weakened out of contention after straightening.
Reared at the start and lost considerable ground, detached early stages until joining the back end of the field rounding home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Ridden forward to lead 1100 metres out, obtained rails run shortly after but soon narrowly headed rounding home bend, folded up quickly on straightening.
Soon dropped to last few, saved ground on the rail turning in, made no impression in straight.
Travelled wide in midfield, yielded ground on home bend.
Settled in forward of midfield, dropped out of contention on home bend.
Quickly strode to the lead, joined by rivals from 700M setting fast pace, pushed out inside 400M, drew away for another convincing success. (Distressed post race.)
Chased leaders in a fast run race, kept working well to the finish but always held by the determined winner.
In midfield 3Ls away from the leading trio in a fast run race, fought hard final 400M to go 3rd 100M out, couldn't get closer to first 2.
Jumped well, restrained to sit behind midfield, stayed on steadily over final 500M, not reached leaders.
Pressed forward to join leaders passing 700M setting fast tempo, stayed close until 300M, effort levelled off from there.
Held up behind mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, responded only fairly when placed under pressure, struggled to make any impression on the run home.
Moved up to be vying for lead passing 700M, stumbled inside 400M, no match from there, weakened away.
Raced along the stands' side, never far off from leaders, couldn't muster the speed to challenge when shaken up nearing 400M, plodded home only.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled down behind mid-division, stuck on fairly to the line, lacked any dash.
In mid-pack towards the outside of group, 4-5Ls off the fast pace halfway, couldn't finish off inside 400M.
Close up to leaders, couldn't kick on passing 400M, faded away. (Bled).
Lost ground when crowded for room after start, ended up last, lay in under pressure for majority part of the race, made no progress over final 400M.
Outpaced early stages, 7Ls off the pace in a near last position at 400M, failed to run on.
Towards the rear always, couldn't keep up passing halfway, made no impression on its debut over possibly inadequate trip.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, finished off well to score by a neck.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight, just could not hold off the first two late. (Rider dropped left rein near 300M.)
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle after passing 1000M, 3 wide with no cover on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide and without cover, better than midfield, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, angled out after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, checked off heels near 900M, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening, ran on evenly to final 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide behind midfield, crowded near 900M, found rail 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off one pace. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield early, carried wider after passing 900M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (Lost right front plate near 600M.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced very wide at rear, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Bustled along after the start to be chasing leaders, took a while to get going leaving the bend, did best work final 200M, got up before line.
Jumped on terms, crossed from draw 10 to track leader, picked up well to lead 150M, caught by winner before line.
Pressed forward from widest gate and crossed to the lead before turn, driven out 250M but couldn't shake off rival, headed 150M, one paced final stages.
In mid-division just over 4Ls off leader, pressed along 450M, stayed on steadily without threatening.
Scrubbed along after the start, stayed close behind leader, couldn't finish off final 300M, kept on same pace only.
Eased back after the jump, moved closer to a midfield spot middle stages, caught wide no cover from 700M, worked steadily to the line but never a threat.
Pressed along to stay in touch with leaders, came under pressure home turn, battled on same pace in straight, no threat to leaders.
Failed to muster speed, raced towards the rear about 10Ls off the pace middle stages, gave limited response turning home.
Didn't show much speed early stages, towards the rear over 10Ls off the pace on settling, couldn't pick up in straight, made no impression on AWT debut.
Settled towards the rear, in 8th spot 9Ls off the pace at 400M, failed to get into contention, eased when no chance.
Dropped back to last, over 13Ls off the pace turning home, failed to improve, never in the picture.
Settled near last, over 10Ls behind leader home turn, never involved.

Held the rail in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Stayed close to the inside on corning, 4L from the lead. Made steady headway & improved into tight running in the last 75m before diving through late for narrow win.

Steadied at the start before improving along the rail approaching the 800m. Made gradual ground from the 300m when racing inside winner. Switched into tight room before diving through in last few strides to miss narrowly.
Began fast and assumed lead before crossing to the rail approaching the 1000m. Dashed over 2L clear inside the final section and continued to hold the lead until passed in last few strides.
Mustered speed after the start to race in midfield away from the rail. Moved wider on cornering before straightening 4L from the lead. Closed hard inside the final 250m to be beaten small margin.
Strode forward from outside barrier before shifting into one out one back near the 950m. Moved three wide on cornering before making steady headway to be close behind in a blanket finish.
Settled third from last between horses, conceding over 6L passing the 800m. Moved wider on cornering before finishing well in final section from rearward positon to be close up on the line.
Began well before drifting back to last shortly after the start. Next to last on cornering, 6L from the lead before making good headway over the final 250m to be narrowly beaten.
Mustered speed after the start to improve to midfield on the rail. Shifted out on cornering before making steady headway in the final section to finish close behind.

Wasn't the fastest into stride before mustering speed to settle midfield between runners. Hard ridden on cornering when 4L from the lead before making steady headway in the final section to be close behind in blanket finish.

Strode forward before being crossed and racing on leaders back from the 1000m. Raced keenly passing the 900m. Couldn't go with the winner after straightening before peaking & giving a few lengths in the final 100m.
Ridden forward to midfield when racing a little wide, five lengths from the lead at half-way. Ridden hard on cornering before peaking on effort inside the last 250m and giving a few lengths late.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners to race at the tail. Cornered widest and conceded 8 lengths on balancing before making no head-way in the final section.
Hard ridden after the start to improve and race in third on the outside without cover. Came under pressure immediately after straightening & gave significant ground in the final section.

Drifted back to worse than midfield when racing wide and without cover throughout early & middle stages. Continued wide path approaching the corner before yielding ground from the 450m to be well beaten.

Jumped well from the widest draw, showed good early speed to race prominently, 2 wide, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by 1-1/2L.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, stayed on for 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, a length or so back on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Moderately away, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Away with them, raced wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, no early speed, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Eased to sit 1 out 1 back, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, made early move 800M, ran on well for 2nd.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased at start, at rear, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 500M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at back, benefited by the fast sectionals, no progress.
At rear, hard ridden to keep up with the field, suited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, soon emptied 500M.
Settled behind the lead, placed pressure near 500M, near 150M was inconvenienced, finished strongly to score.
Urged along to take lead in one-off position, near 50M was bumped and became unbalanced then raced tight, worked home solidly.
Hard ridden after start, then was steadied to obtain cover near 800M, settled midfield, near 350M was awkwardly placed, finished solidly.
Ridden along to race inside the lead on rail, responded nicely in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, approaching 200M and passing 200M was awkwardly placed, near 50M was checked when crowded for room, not fully tested.
Began only fairly, ridden but no early speed, settled at rear on rail, made some ground in the straight.
Slow out, raced toward the rear, wide on straightening, lay out after 200M and the remainder of the race, gained ground near 50M.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, rider's whip was knocked off near 75M, finished OK.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, tried to improve passing 500M, finished one-paced.
Raced in handy position, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, emptied near 250M.
Began awkwardly, raced at back, always niggled to maintain its position, failed to run on.
Raced behind midfield on rail, niggled passing 800M to maintain its position, no response in the straight.

Crossed nearing the 1200m & obtained nice run on leaders back. Travelled strongly between runners approaching the 400m, before sprinting well once balanced. Assumed lead in last few strides to record narrow win.

Strode forward before getting one out, one back passing the 1200m. Dashed forward to assume lead passing the 600m before racing 3L clear on cornering. Held lead inside the final 50m before being caught late.

Strode to midfield away from the rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved three wide passing the 500m when improving before cornering 3L from the lead. Made steady headway in the straight to be close behind first two.

Shifted across to the rail after the start, racing in midfield. Moved away from the rail when taken out passing the 500m before straightening 5L from the lead. Made up some ground in the final 250m without threatening.
Had no early speed and consequently raced rearward. Continued rearward entering the final section before making steady headway and passing a few in the straight.

Fractious in barriers, lifted feet & slow to begin. Mustered pace to race midfield on rail. Raced tightly, 600m to 500m before cornering 5L from lead. Battled on after straightening but was never a real factor. (Must trial).

Shifted across behind runners to race in second half. Moved three wide before improving position passing the 800m to be 1L from lead at the 600m. Peaked shortly after straightening & gave a few lengths in last furlong.

Steadied and shifted behind runners to race in final trio leaving the straight. Moved wider passing the 400m when conceding 6.5L to the lead. Held margin in run to line and was never a likely contender.
Strode forward to race outside the leader approaching the 1100m. Three lengths from lead when racing second on the turn before tiring out and losing ground in the straight.

Shifted across to race in midfield away from rail. Moved three deep approaching the 600m before tracking wider into the turn. Widest runner, 5L from the lead on straightening before peaking on effort shortly after.
Steadied after start and shifted back to last leaving the straight. Over 3L behind the second last horse passing the 400m and failed to make any headway into significant margin in the last section.
Strode forward to assume lead approaching the 1200m. Headed passing the 600m before yielding ground from that stage and was a well beaten last. (Must trial).

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, commenced move after passing 800M, took the lead 600M, led by 2 lengths on turn, kicked clear early in straight, in command final furlong, eased final 50M.
Hampered start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, made some headway in straight to take 2nd on line, never a threat to the winner.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead until headed near 600M, 2 lengths back on turn, ran on evenly in straight, lost 2nd close home.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 600M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, fought on until weakened final 50M.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from near 650M, 7 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 1100M, peaked on turn, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on rail, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 800M, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped start, settled to race in box-seat, worked home nicely and scored with something in hand.
Bumped start and raced at the rear, on rail, closed off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, emptied and headed at 100M.
Raced in about midfield, 2 wide, made ground and continued on nicely to the line.
Steadied to find cover in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly to the line.
Bumped start, settled one-off one-back, one paced and weakened near 150M.
Prominent, however wide and without cover, was one paced.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, stayed on until emptied near 150M.
Bumped start, in midfield along the rail, showed no turn of foot.
Bumped start, in worse than midfield 2 wide, never threaten.
Slow to jump, at tail, not a factor.
Missed start badly and lost ground, did not take any active part. Must trial. (See Incident Report)
Broke well settling not far off the pace, travelled well in 2L 3rd from the 800 metres, commenced move shortly after straightening and took command over 200 metres out.
Settled in rear from a wide gate and waited with, saved ground on the rail turning for home, snuck up on rail to claim 2nd inside final 100 metres.
Broke well and ridden along, came to join the leader from the 800 metres, unable to quicken with the eventual winner inside final 300 metres.
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from the widest gate, remained similar into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Crowded at start, niggled along in rear of midfield most of the way, fought on steadily without threatening.
Towards the rear, produced some late impression in the run to the line.
Settled in midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening, made modest progress early in straight, found no extra inside final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled within 3L off the pace mainly in 4th from the 800 metres, saved ground entering home straight but soon faded out of contention.
Hampered at the start, raced wide without cover towards the rear, widest runner swinging for home, kept on at the one pace without quickening.
Always well behind, swung very wide into home straight, made no show.
Led or disputed lead to home straight travelling keenly in early stages of the race, weakened noticeably in straight.

Placing: PU
Comment: Dropped out of contention shortly after start.
Dropped back from wide draw, given a patient ride 8Ls behind leader, niggled along 600M and swung widest home, closed off determinedly, got up just in time for 5th win in a row.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, made good progress passing 300M, led 100M out, caught just before line.
Away well enough, stayed in touch behind pace, travelled smoothly into straight, loomed a strong chance 300M, stayed on steadily to line, got 3rd just in time.
Bumped at the start, ridden along to obtain prominent spot just off the pace, moved up to press leader 700M, led them going into straight, kept on well until late stages when swamped by first 3.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, shifted out to 3-wide entering back straight, moved closer from 600M, wide into straight, closed off well to claim 5th not beaten far.
Jumped well to be track leaders along the fence, held every chance turning in, not finishing pace of first few over final 200M.
Urged along from draw 11 but took time to muster, caught 3 wide no cover just off the pace, battled on same speed passing 400M, well held by leaders.
Reserved behind midfield 5-6Ls back, in 10th spot entering back-straight, pressed along 450M, failed to finish off.
Caught 3-wide in mid-division, 4Ls off the pace on settling, fought on same pace in straight, never likely.
Strode forward, crossed to the lead before first bend, soon came under pressure when pressed by rival 700M, failed to respond to riding rounding home turn and in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled down midfield along the fence, 4Ls to make up 400M, couldn't go on in the straight, weakened away.
Failed to muster speed, ended up near last 6Ls off leader, couldn't keep up rounding home bend, soon behind. (Restricted action both hind legs day after racing.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide after passing 700M, wider on turn, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, bumped early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late, just beaten by a neck.
Away well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take a place.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 800M, commenced move after passing 450M, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently on rail, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide after passing 600M, shared lead turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, bumped early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, raced in restricted room near 700M, found rail near 500M, showed no response after turning in, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, weakened from 600M, eased early in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
