Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 650M, wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score. (Minor laceration to the right hind fetlock.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, stayed on for 2nd.

Clean jump, raced prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 1200M, found cover shortly thereafter, travelled well on turn, angled out near 500M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Commenced well from the widest draw, raced in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, made some headway in straight without threatening the first few.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, moved closer turning in, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, Steadied off heels near 900M, hard ridden after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, a bit closer turning in, made little progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, kept on one pace in straight.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 1100M, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden forward, enjoyed the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, held ground for 2nd.
At rear, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Took rail and led easily at slow sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Eased to rear, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden early, in front of midfield no dash.
At back, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Slow away, at back, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Pressed forward, emptied 300M.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, ran on fairly when clear.
Never a factor.
Never competitive.
Settled at tail, widest on straightening, issued challenged near 200M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Taken back at start, after 1000M was left racing wide and without cover, settled at rear, wide on straightening, finished solidly, blood trachea.
Rolled forward, raced in box seat, placed pressure near 450M, responded nicely in the straight, rider questioned.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield, near 200M became badly unbalanced when crowded for room, worked home nicely.
Jumped nicely then ridden along from widest gate to take lead, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Jumped well, passing 1000M was left racing wide and without cover behind midfield, responded OK in the straight.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 500M, responded well in the early part of straight, one-paced after 200M.
Raced toward rear, passing 300M was checked when disappointed for running, finished only one-paced.
On jumping was crowded then ridden along to maintain its position, raced behind midfield on rail, fought hard but finished one-paced.
Urged along after start, settled outside the lead, placed pressure in the straight but gave ground passing 150M.
Began only fairly and raced at back, tried to improve near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Urged along after start, after 1000M was left racing wide and without cover in handy position, passing 300M was checked when crowded for room, weakened passing 200M.
Began only fairly, settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but gave ground passing 300M, failed to run on.
Urged along to race in one-back-one-off position, emptied passing 200M, failed to run on.

Settled slightly worse than midfield, away from the rail, 8L from lead after the first section. Made ground in second section before improving between runners at the 300m and dashing away for solid win.
Shifted into midfield away from the rail, 5L from lead passing the 800m. Shifted into clear running between horses inside the last 200m before finishing strongly to be close second.

Raced in midfield on the rail, 4L from lead after first section. Shifted away from rail passing the 600m before sprinting to share the lead at the 300m. Joined inside the last furlong before fighting on late.

Shifted across to race in midfield away from the rail. Three lengths from lead after cornering before being held up & crowded until the 300m. Shifted out at the 250m and finished well in the last furlong. (Rider questioned).
Crowded & lost ground after the start and consequently raced rearward. Continued rearward, nearly 5L from lead on cornering. Made steady headway in final 300m to not be beaten far.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners to race second from last. Cornered in a last place before shifting wider and making up decent headway from a rearward position.

Strode forward to race in first four away from the rail. Became unbalanced and hung outwards throughout the middle section. Cornered wide when handy to lead before peaking on effort inside the final 150m.
Showed speed after the start to hold the lead. Headed in the lead inside the 300m before tiring & giving a few lengths late in the race.

Showed early speed to push forward & race in third position before improving to race on leaders back at halfway. Moved over heels on cornering and continued to be close to lead until peaking at the 250m & giving ground late.

Began awkwardly & lost ground before improving position to just worse than midfield, 8.5L from lead at the 800m. Stayed close to rail on cornering when 5L from lead, before holding margin in the run to the line.

Steadied and shifted across behind runners after start and settled a clear last after 300m. Continued rearward, 6.5L from lead entering the final section before making up only a length in the run home.

Shifted across to midfield but raced wide & without cover until the 600m. Hard ridden prior to the 500m and gave ground in the final section. (Abnormal breathing noise, blood in trachea, vet exam req.).
Showed early speed to push forward and race outside the leader. Was a length from the lead passing the 400m before giving ground past the 300m and weakening out in the late stages.

Shifted across behind runners after the start & raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Six lengths from the lead on cornering before giving significant ground to be well beaten last. (Mucus in trachea, must trial).
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Shifted out on jumping, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the rival on line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, closed off well to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, steadied off heels near 700M, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover better than midfield, checked off heels near 1150M, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Fast into stride, raced wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 200M. (Rider lost the use of his stirrup iron on jumping.)

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 800M, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Sat just behind midfield, wide but with cover, worked home nicely and held on to score by 1/2L.
At tail, shifted 2 wide prior to 900M turn, made nice ground and ran home gamely to take 2nd.
Raced in about midfield, along the rail, kept going and closed off nicely to the line for 3rd.
Taken back and raced at the rear, wide but with cover, made ground steadily to the line.
Sent forward and took rail, led by a margin initially, headed at 100M but ran on.
Raced just in front of midfield, along the rail, closed off to the line. (Rider dropped rein at 350M)
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, stayed on till 100M and found no extra.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, raced tight near 200M, closed off okay thereafter.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide and without cover, was one paced.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced and eased late.
Raced behind the lead, sat 2 wide, kept up until emptied passing 300M. (See Incident Report)
At rear, along the rail, did not threaten.
Eased, raced at the rear, wide but with cover, not competitive.
Niggled along, failed to find cover, wide in midfield, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Settled behind midfield, commenced move after straightening, quickened well to assert authority close to home.
Handy settling just off the pace on the rail, kept on steadily without threatening.
Broke well settling just better than midfield, just over 3L back in 5th into the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled 3-wide without cover just worse than midfield, in similar position turning into home straight, fought on steadily to claim 4th late.
Settled wide in midfield, gained slightly closer wide around home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, trailed the field around home bend and into straight, kept on well to the line.
Hampered at start, travelled well behind, saved ground entering home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, kept on at the one pace without quickening. (Tactic questioned)
Travelled mainly 3-wide without cover in midfield, ran home one-paced under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Soon took up running, obtained rails run inside the 1000 metres, led until finding no extra over 250 metres out.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Broke well, soon dropped to rear of midfield, made no impression in home straight.
Hampered shortly after start, travelling keenly when checked off heels inside the 1000 metres, wide into home straight, ran home one-paced.
Ridden positively from the widest gate settling next to the leader coming onto home end, gradually weakened under pressure after straightening.
Dropped back to race towards the rear in a fast run race, in 8th spot 5Ls back at 400M, ran on strongly to join leader 150M, gained upper hand close home. (new class record.)

Restrained to race behind mid-division, moved closer home turn to be just over 3Ls off the pace at 400M, quickened up nicely to lead 150M, soon joined by eventual winner, went down narrowly after a tussle. Clear from remainders.
Up with early pace, sat behind leaders passing 1200M, picked up well to lead 300M, got outsprinted by first 2 final 150M.
Bustled along to be chasing leaders in 4th, moved up to challenge early straight and loomed a chance 300M, couldn't match finishing pace of first 2 final 150M, faded late.
In midfield along the fence, battled on same pace in straight, never looked likely.
Settled towards rear, well off the pace middle stages, made some progress in straight but too far back to threaten.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, gave brief response early straight, couldn't go on final 200M.
Led early stages, taken on by rival from 1200M setting fast pace in 2nd quarter, track leader to straight, vied for lead to 300M, no extra.
Switched off to the rear, over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, swung wide 600M, couldn't muster the speed to challenge.
Chased leaders early, proved difficult to settle, took outright lead passing 1100M setting fast pace in 2nd quarter, headed inside 300M, weakened rapidly.
Settled near last, well off the pace middle stages, failed to run on leaving home turn, never involved.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off strongly to score by 3/4L.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner final 50M.

Taken back from a wide draw, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, finished off strongly to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)

Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide at rear, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line. (Laceration to the outside of the right front cannon.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 5Ls back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, no clear running early in straight, crowded near 350M, made some progress when clear final 150M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 4 wide at rear, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, 3 lengths or so back, closer turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, crowded early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover in midfield early, moved closer after passing 1000M, 1-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out from near 550M, closed off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck.

Jumped well, bumped early, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on well after turning in, briefly headed near 250M, fought back, ran on well but unable to hold off the rivals close home.
Began well from a tricky gate, bumped early, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, moved closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, found cover after passing 1100M, travelled well to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground throughout, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced slightly behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, hard ridden after passing 550M, wide into straight, weakened gradually in straight.

Shifted across behind runners & raced third from last. Continued rearward, conceding 4.5L entering the final section. Sprinted fast passing the 250m before making late ground to steel the lead in final stride.

Improved after the start to race midfield away from rail. Eased wider on straightening before sprinting fast passing the 300m to assume the lead at 150m. Continued strongly to the line before being caught in last stride.

Showed some early speed to improve to race on the back of the leader. Presented with clear running after straightening before joining a line of four inside the last furlong and boxing on well to be close behind.

Began fairly before holding the rail and improving to midfield. Sprinted well between runners passing the 300m before joining a line of four inside the final furlong and fighting hard to be a narrowly beaten.

Pushed forward from wide barrier before continuing to improve to race outside leader at the 900m. Shared lead in middle stages before sprinting clear on straightening. Held lead until 150m before shifting & losing ground late.

Steadied and shifted behind runners, settling worse than midfield away from rail. Moved three wide with cover passing half-way before balancing 4L from lead. Made solid headway in final 300m to not be beaten far.

Began awkwardly before drifting back in first section. Improved position in middle stages cornering on the rail, 2L from lead. Crowded at the 400m & again in final 100m before not tested late. Improved without threatening.
Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout early & middle stages. Cornered the widest, 3.5L from lead and maintained that margin in the run to the line.

Raced three wide without cover from the 850m when under 2L from the lead. Forced wider on cornering before moving closer to the lead inside the 300m. Tightened & checked at the 250m before yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Shifted across to the rail behind runners and raced at the rear. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before balancing 4L from the lead. Could only maintain margin in final section.
Not bustled and raced in midfield between runners. Cornered 3.5L from the lead before failing to threaten in the final section.

Ridden forward to be prominent before getting cover one out, one back near the 850m. Moved three wide on cornering before coming under heavy pressure shortly after straightening. Gave significant ground over final 300m.
Steadied from outside gate and shifted across behind runners to race at the tail. Continued at the tail when over 6L from the lead on straightening before losing a further 10L in the straight.
Gathered speed after the start and assumed the lead after 150m. Joined in the lead at the 850m before being headed and yielding significant ground from the 400m. Well beaten.

Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out near 600M, showed good response after turning in, took the lead near 100M, kept on well to hold off the challenger.

Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 150M, just narrowly beaten.

Began fairly, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths or so back, carried wider after passing 600M, closer turning in, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 700M, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, kept on evenly early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, last turning in, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, crowded early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, moved closer on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Eased at start, 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M to score.
Eased at start, 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 250M for 2nd.
Eased to rear, took rail, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 150M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, blocked 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Pushed to take lead and clocked slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow pace, weakened 200M.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
At back, on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room in straight, ran on ok.
Failed to muster, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, out of fuel 250M, hampered 100M.
Pushed early but not muster, 2 wide in front of midfield, weakened 250M, hampered 100M.
Midfield, emptied 400M.
Jumped well, settled outside the lead, gained solid ground when asked for effort passing 400M, finished strongly to score, blood trachea.
Raced at tail, commenced to improve passing 850M, wide rounding the home turn, responded nicely in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled midfield, placed pressure passing 550M, made up some ground passing 200M, finished well.
Travelled nicely in the lead, asked for effort on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Began well, raced in box seat, travelled keenly in middle stages, limited response in the straight.
Travelled at back on rail, kept on rail rounding the home turn to save ground, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced in handy position, fought hard in the straight, gave ground passing 100M.

Began well, strode forward to race second on the outside. Obtained cover passing the 600m when racing in third. Sprinted well after straightening, assumed lead passing the 300m, drew away inside last furlong for tidy win.
Held position in midfield on the rail for early & middle sections. Eased out inside the final 350m before making steady headway in final furlong to snare second.
Not fast early and drifted back to race in final three. Moved wider passing the 500m before making good late ground inside the final 300m to be close behind.

Ridden forward after start before settling forward of midfield, only 2L from lead after first section. Followed the winner into the bend before boxing on well in the last section to just miss out on minor placing.
Away only fairly before drifting back to race worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Straightening 3.5 lengths from the lead before making stead ground to finish just behind.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on the rail throughout early sections. Moved into clear running after straightening and finished off evenly in the run to the post.
Had economical run in midfield between runners. Shifted out and bumped approaching the 300m when attempting to make ground before finishing off evenly in late stages.
Steadied after the start and shifted across to midfield when racing three wide. Balanced 3.25L from the lead and maintained that margin in the run to the line.
Strode forward before being crossed and racing on the leaders back from the 900m. Handy to the lead entering the final section before peaking on run in the last furlong & yielding a few lengths late.

Began awkwardly before shifting across behind runners & racing second from last. Hard ridden to improve approaching the 600m before cornering 7 lengths from lead. Passed a few tiring runners late but was never a real factor.

Raced in midfield early before drifting further back in middle stages. Five lengths from lead on cornering, shifted back towards the rail in the straight but couldn't make sufficient ground to challenge.

Raced wide early before ridden forward and improving to race up outside the leader approaching the 650m. Shared the lead approaching the 300m before peaking on run and giving ground inside the last 250m.
Began awkwardly, lost ground after the start and raced a clear last. Continued at the tail, conceding 7.5 lengths entering the final section before maintaining that margin in the run to the line.

Showed customary early speed after the start, shifted across to the rail in the lead after 250m. Joined in the lead inside the last section before tiring & yielding many lengths in last 300m. (Mucus in trachea post-race).

Average to begin, raced 2w in midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, showed very good response after turning in, hung in badly final 100M, hampered rival and took the lead 50M, scored by 3/4L. (Objection by 2nd, overruled.)

Began smartly, sent forward to take the early lead, allowed rival to cross 1000M, enjoyed the easy run on turn, angled out after passing 500M, kept on very well in straight, took brief lead 100M, headed and hampered 50M, finished 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well after turning in, headed and inconvenienced near 50M, finished 3rd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar positon on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Bounded in the air on jumping, difficult to settle early, raced wide with no cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, found cover near 900M but still 3 wide, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 8 lengths back, there to turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, carried wider after passing 500M, weakened gradually in straight. (Lost right front plate at 600M.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, on centre track, battled on nicely to score by a neck.
Prominent, on centre track, took lead at 150M but couldn't hold off winner at final 50M.
Raced on the outside rail in behind midfield, made ground and continued on well for 3rd.
Sat towards the rear, stand side, shifted to centre track at 350M, saved ground and ran on strongly.
Raced behind the leads, stand side, continued fairly to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, stand side, made ground.
Crowded at start, in worse than midfield stand side, ran on one paced to the line.
Settled to race off the lead on stand side, stayed on until the 200M.
Crowded at start, went forward to take the outside rail and led, ran on till 200M only. (See Incident Report)
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield stand side, one paced and emptied at 150M.
Travelled at the rear, stand side, closed off fairly late.
Raced in behind midfield, on centre track, weakened at 250M.
Hampered after the start, sat behind the lead on outside rail, no turn of foot and held up in final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in front of midfield stand side, run ended at 300M.
Settled in last few from a wide gate and waited with, commenced move passing the 400 metres, ran on well under pressure to snatch victory close to home.
Jumped fairly, settled 2-wide in midfield in 5th some 3L back, similar into home straight, ran on under pressure to hit the front inside the 200 metres only to be collared final few strides.
Ridden in first few early, settled just behind the leaders in 3rd one off the rail, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, in front early stages before shifting backward to settled between the race leader and the rail, kept on under pressure until fading inside the final 300 metres.
Moderate start, wide in midfield early stages before moving up to take slender lead 2-wide, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to the straight, briefly baulked on straightening, finished off the race impressively inside the final 200 metres.
Slightly slowly away, niggled at early before settling towards the rear in 7th on the rail, fought on steadily in straight but never threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled just worse than midfield in 6th 2-wide, came under pressure after straightening but could make no impression throughout.
Moderate start, settled just better than midfield in 4th on the rail within 3L of pace, weakened under pressure shortly after straightening.
Jumped on terms, chased leaders 2-wide, loomed up early straight, quickened to lead 250M, kept on well closing stages to hold off a late challenge.
Settled behind midfield in 7th place, 5Ls off leader making home turn, worked home strongly down the straight, nearest finish.
Bustled along to be chasing leaders, couldn't quicken as well as the winner from 400M but fought on under hands and heels riding to take 3rd.
Switched off to race towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on well to claim 4th near the post.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, just over 6Ls off the pace top of straight, stayed on well towards the line. Encouraging debut.
Away well enough, restrained to race ahead of midfield, 5th at 400M, kept on steadily early and mid-straight, outpaced by pursuers final stages.
Took some time to muster speed early stages, moved up to press leader from 1000M, battled on same pace in straight, swamped by rivals 100M.
Slow away, recovered to race behind midfield, brought wide 400M to challenge, ran on only fairly, no threat to leaders. (Jockey unable to explain disappointing performance.)
Dropped back to race towards the rear, wide on straightening, ran on only fairly. (Jockey : hung out for majority of the race and made abnormal breathing noises.)
Quickly into stride, crossed to lead setting good pace, headed 250M, couldn't sustain run, weakened noticeably passing 150M.
Travelled keenly in midfield, lay out home turn, kept on same pace on straightening, faded final 200M.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, settled in last over 8Ls off the good pace, didn't respond and soon left behind by rivals passing 300M.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on very well to hold off the challenger, scored by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, raced behind the lead, 2 away from the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well but always held by the leader.
Out in line, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, gradually moved to the middle of the track after passing 450M, finished off strongly to take a place.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, raced at rear, near to the middle of the track, made very good progress final 400M to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Severely checked at start, raced at rear on the stands rail, still 7 lengths behind at 400M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands rail, awkwardly placed off heels and unbalanced near 650M, hard ridden after passing 400M but failed to make any progress.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths or so back, 3 away from the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 450M but only showed limited response, weakened from 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact on jumping, raced at rear, nearer to the middle track, showed limited response final 400M.
Away with them, raced behind midfield, 2 to 3 away from the stands rail, showed no response to vigorous riding final 400M.
Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on run near 350M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle of the track, peaked on run near 500M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out after passing 800M, moved closer on turn, led 400M out, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail after passing 1000M, moved closer on turn, angled out from 550M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced wide with no cover at rear, improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced at rear on the rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing near 600M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 950M, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 900M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began fairly from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 250M, finished off strongly to score by 1-3/4L.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, slightly improved after passing 650M, 4 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival after passing 750M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a middle draw, showed limited early speed, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward thereafter to race outside the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from near 500M, taken wider in straight and finished off evenly.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked and crowded early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, peaked on turn, kept on one pace to 100M, eased thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, showed no early speed, raced wide at rear, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight. (Heat stress post-race.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, taken back to raced 2 wide at rear, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Took rail easily and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Eased to sit in midfield, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Box seat, lack room 4-2, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit just off the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 250m.
At rear, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Crowded on jumping, settled towards rear, improved near 400M and kept on rail in the straight, worked home strongly to score.
Urged for some distance and settled in box seat, asked for effort passing 400M, responded solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Settled in handy position on rail, commenced to improve near 450M, battled well in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled in midfield, placed pressure passing 400M, came home nicely.
Began awkwardly, settled towards rear, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 200M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but finished one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve near 600M, worked home one-paced, blood trachea.
Raced in front of midfield, lay in in early stages and early part of straight, passing 300M was badly hampered, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, tried to improve near 600M, lay in in the early part of straight and difficult to ride, limited response.
Travelled midfield on rail, badly held up for running in the early part of straight, near 300M was checked, finished only fairly.
Fractious in the barrier, ridden along for some distance to take lead, gave ground passing 300M, Stalls Test.
Slow out then detached despite being ridden along, no response in the straight, lame left front next day.
Raced behind midfield, placed pressure near 600M, no response in the straight.
Urged along to race behind leaders, always niggled, severely checked passing 300M, finished tailed-out.
Shared lead early before obtaining lead outright after 350m. Raced over a length clear shortly after straightening before continuing on over the final 300m to score comfortable win.

Shifted across at start before improving to midfield between runners. Momentarily crowded nearing the 800m when 3L from the lead. Chased hard after straightening but could not bridge the margin on the easy winner.
Steadied across behind runners after the start and raced near the tail. Conceded 5L on straightening before shifting out shortly after and making good headway over the final 300m.

Strode forward getting a nice position on the leaders back. Stayed close to the inside on straightening but couldn't maintain contact with the leader in the run to the line. Battled on creditably late.

Showed some speed after the start to improve and race right behind the leading trio in the first section. Held position be close behind passing the 300m mark before peaking on run shortly after and giving a few lengths late.

Ridden hard early before steadying & shifting across from outside gate to settle rearward. Covered a little extra ground in second section before conceding significant start on straightening. Passed a few in the run home

Obtained midfield position between runners after start. Steadied and lost a length when crowded passing the 800m. Shifted wider on cornering when 4 lengths from the lead before failing to make an impression in the run home.

Ridden forward to be prominent before settling three wide outside leading pair. Continued to race wide without cover before laying outwards on cornering. Straightened 2 lengths from the lead before peaking in the final 300m.

Challenged for the lead before steadying and racing at the leaders girth after 350m. Put under pressure shortly after cornering when the leader kicked clear. Bottomed out passing the 300m mark & tired out in the last furlong.

Steadied after the start & shifted across to the tail of the field. Raced 6.5L form the lead after the first section before being hard ridden from the 650m. Stayed close to the inside on cornering, failed to make any headway.
Not fast away before settling in the final trio. Checked away from heels yielding ground steadily over the final 250m.

Ridden forward before shifting across to race four wide in midfield. Drifted further back passing half-way before coming under pressure shortly after. Balanced 5L form the lead before yielding further ground in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out near 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 800M, bumped near 500M, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, wider after passing 600M, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Began well, showed good speed to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well after turning in, peaked near 200M, weakened and headed thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, wider from 600M, same margin back turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, sat right behind the leader on turn, bumped near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Stumbled at start, unable to slot in, positioned 4 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide after passing near 700M, closer turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Bounded in the air on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight. (Abnormal breathing noise.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Sat in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on nicely and held off late challenge to score by a head.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly to the line. (See Incident Report)
Slotted in to race in midfield, 2 wide, continued on until inconvenienced at final 75M.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, one paced but ran on.
Settled to race in about midfield, along the rail, kept on going to the line.
Travelled at the rear, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, was one paced until checked late.
Eased and settled to race in worse than midfield, 2 wide, kept on going until eased in the final strides.
Bumped start, then eased back and raced at the tail 2 wide, never improved.
Eased at start, raced at the rear along the rail, did not challenge in the straight.
Hard ridden out of the gates, sat one-off one-back, eased near 350M, run ended thereafter.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, emptied passing 350M.
Rolled forward and was prominent, however trapped wide all the way, found nothing.
Jumped fairly only, recovered to lead on the rail, weakened prior to 300M. (See Incident Report)
Settled in midfield, commenced move on straightening, responded well under pressure to hit the front over 100 metres out, hung on well.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, ridden forward to take up running coming out of back straight, kicked 1L clear early in straight, unable to sustain effort and headed over 150 metres out.

Broke well, settled just off the pace, drifted back to 2.5L 5th rounding home bend, baulked for run briefly after straightening, fought on steadily inside 300 metres but unable to sustain effort close to home. (Tendon injury)
Settled wide towards the rear, ran on well under pressure to be nearest finish despite forced to switch for a run 150 metres out.
Broke well and led early, ceded advantage to settle 1L off the pace on the rail, switched out to challenge on straightening, kept on until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Ridden in first few early stages, gradually settled in forward of midfield in 6th, travelled wide round home bend, ran on well under pressure inside the final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start from a wide gate, worked his way forward out wide to join the 2nd rounding home bend, in similar position into home straight, one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Slightly slow out, soon recovered along the rail to about 3L oft the pace in 7th, steadied behind heels coming onto home bend, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, finished off the race well down the centre of the track. (Tactic questioned)
Began fairly, settled in last few, fought on steadily without threatening, hampered close to home.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, remained well behind to the straight, kept on well for a nice debut.
Jumped awkwardly, settled not far off the pace in 4th in back straight, lost position entering home straight, soon faded under pressure.
Jumped well, tracked leaders along the fence, into clear passing 400M, quickened up well to wrestle the lead 100M out, kept on to the line.
Bustled along after the start to maintain a midfield position, 4Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on well to claim 2nd near line, nearest finish.
Chased leader 2-wide, ridden to take lead passing 200M, headed by winner 100M, lost 2nd before line.
In touch tracking the pace in 4th spot, kept on steadily in the straight but always held by first 3.

Driven along, crossed to the lead before the turn, came under pressure 300M, headed inside 200M, weakened towards the line. (Blood in trachea / Jockey : did not handle the pressure when racing on the AWT first time.)
Taken across behind runners early stages, held up behind midfield, ran on same pace final 300M, never a threat to leaders.
Along the inside never far off from leaders, ridden and outpaced from 350M, soon out of contention.
Began awkwardly, settled 2nd last, over 10Ls off the pace 400M, made no real progress passing a couple beaten runners only.
Driven along from draw 12 but failed to muster, caught very wide and without cover in midfield, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled in last over 10Ls off the pace, failed to make any impact turning home, never in the picture.
In mid-division along the 3 path, bumped rival at 450M, struggled from there. (Jockey : did not feel comfortable in its action after becoming unbalanced home turn.)
Held up behind midfield, caught wide no cover during race, couldn't keep up from 600M, weakened away to finish tailed off. (Unacceptable Performance).
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 100M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by 3 lengths.
Moderately away, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd on line.

Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on very well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, soon no extra, lost 2nd close home.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Away well from a wide draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, checked near 300M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, travelled keenly near 700M, 9 lengths back turning in, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped well from a middle draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.

Began well, raced prominently but trapped wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 900M, 3/4L back on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed shortly thereafter, weakened final 100M.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, steadied off heels near 1050M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from near 1000M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 900M, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still 7 to 8 lengths back, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 10 lengths or so back, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently but wide, found rail after passing 950M, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began smartly, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross near 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out 400M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly and awkwardly placed near 1300M, wider on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 8, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Sat just off the leaders, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace, just behind the leaders along the fence, ran on well for 3rd.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Slow away, at back, favoured by the fast pace, however blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
At back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made ground.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Ridden along with nice early speed to take lead, travelled nicely, held ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Began well then rolled forward from widest barrier, until passing 900M travelled wide and without cover, raced behind leaders, gained ground near 150M, missed by Neck, rider questioned tactic.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve near 600M, then after 600M was bumped and taken wider, wide on straightening, worked home strongly.
Taken back at start, passing 900M was left wide and without cover, raced midfield, improved passing 600M, battled well in the straight.
Rolled forward to race outside the lead, fought hard in the straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Settled toward rear, asked for effort passing 550M, wide on straightening, made up some ground passing 100M.
Raced in box seat, placed pressure on straightening, gave ground near 50M.
At start was bumped then taken back, raced at tail, placed pressure passing 600M, widest on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled at rear on rail, niggled near 700M, shifted out to improve in the straight, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail round the Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Crowded on jumping, travelled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but only limited response.
Settled in front of midfield, lost left front plate after 800M, no response in the straight.

Shifted across to the rear after the start. Ridden forward to improve passing the 700m before cornering wide, 2 lengths from lead. Sprinted hard on straightening, assuming lead inside last furlong. Easy win (track record).

A touch slow to begin before settling worse than midfield on the rail. Continued rearward, 4 lengths from the lead passing the 400m. Cornered close to the inside before finishing off well in the straight to be close behind.
Raced in midfield on the rail throughout early and middle stages. Made steady headway after straightening to finish just behind.
Raced in midfield away from rail, 5 lengths from the lead at half-way. Moved wider approaching the corner before passing a few in the run to the line from a rearward position.

Strode forward in early stages before racing on leaders back passing the 1200m. Followed two leaders into the turn before racing near heels at the 300m. Peaked shortly after and only battled on in the final furlong.

Ridden forward before improving to race second on the outside passing 1200m. Moved up to share lead approaching the 400m before being joined & headed past the 275m. Gave a few lengths late after racing on fast mid-race speed.

Ridden forward from the start to assume the lead. Raced over a length clear in middle stages, when setting fast mid-race sectionals. Joined in the lead approaching the 400m and tired out inside the final 250m.

Failed to muster speed after the start and raced at the tail. Continued to be ridden along passing the 1000m when becoming slightly detached. Clear last entering final section and was well beaten. Never a factor.
Obtained nice trailing position away from the rail in midfield. Ridden along passing the 500m mark before yielding ground from the corner. Well beaten.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, found rail near 400M, kept to inside after straightening, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Stumbled at start, raced prominently on rail, travelled comfortably to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Slightly slow out and bumped, recovered to sit 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 400M, made some progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried very wide turning in, ran on one pace in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, led by half length on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Sent forward to take the rail, led all the way to score by 1/2L.
Settled in one-off one-back position, kept going and ran on nicely for 2nd, finished 1/2L behind.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, fought on gamely to the line to take 3rd.
Jumped smartly, asked then rolled forward to sit outside the lead, kept on going to the line.
Took cover in worse than midfield, 2 wide, travelled keenly initially, saved ground and closed off nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, maintained one paced only.
Slotted in behind midfield, 2 wide, finished off only fairly in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, stayed on one paced to the line.
Raced in the box-seat, about 4-1/2L off, showed no turn of foot.
Taken back, at the tail along the rail, saved ground steadily.
Jumped fairly only, raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, improved slightly.
Settled at the tail, 2 wide, lay in in the straight, did not threaten.
Virtually made all setting a steady pace in back straight and briefly headed 500 metres out, drew over 2L clear under pressure into the straight, hung on well to the line.
Settled just worse than midfield 2-wide from a wide gate, commenced move out wide from the Rock, came under strong pressure after straightening, ran on to reach 2nd 100 metres out.
Broke well, settled 2-wide in midfield, commenced move 3-wide from approaching the Rock reaching 4th just over 2L back on the bend, fought on under pressure to be 2nd briefly inside the 200 metres.
Restrained to travel off the pace, drifted backward approaching the Rock and checked coming onto home bend, swung wide for home and ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Travelled in rear, made steady progress early in back straight before intensifying its pace to hit the front briefly 500 metres out, soon weakened from 2nd into home straight.

Broke well from a middle gate, settled in midfield but failed to obtain cover, improved steadily early in back straight to join the leader 800 metres out, became 3rd at the 500 metres, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, settled 2-wide just off the pace in 3rd, gradually drifted back to 6th come 4L back approaching home bend, kept on same pace under pressure.
Settled in rear of midfield on the rail, gradually shuffled backward to last few in back straight, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Travelled in rear despite niggled along early stages, remained in similar position to home straight, produced good late impression in the run to the line.
Settled in last few, wide rounding home bend and into straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Travelled in midfield, raced keenly in slackened pace early in back straight, in similar position rounding home bend, kept on well to the line.
Broke well and ridden early, settled just off the pace on the rail, yielded ground from approaching home bend.
Always in touch, in 5th place making the final turn, finished off strongly to lead near 100M, gamely held on from 2nd and 3rd late stages.
Never far off from leaders, in 4th place making the home turn, finished off well down center of track, just failed.
Slightly slow away, improved to be racing in midfield along the 2-path 4Ls away, fought on well from 300m out, just held by first 2.
Settled down behind midfield, made steady headway final 300M without threatening the top 3.
Switched off to race in last after jumping from wide barrier, 8Ls away at 400M, fanned wide into straight, closed off steadily down outsider.
Tracked leader along the 2-path, moved up to challenge 400M, responded well and led mid-straight, run ended 100M, weakened badly final stages. (minor wound to RH pastern.)
Jumped on terms from draw 1, reserved in midfield along the rail, gave limited response turning in, no threat from 200M.
Steadied to obtain cover early stages, held up near the rear 7Ls from leader, kept on same pace in straight, never threatened.
Driven along to obtain a trailing position behind leader, vied for lead briefly early in straight, soon no extra and weakened. (Jockey unable to explain for the disappointing performance.)
Soon led, took them along steadily, headed passing 300M, weakened over final 150M
Dropped back from wide draw, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, couldn't close off the race, soon left behind by rivals passing 300M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, always towards the rear, didn't respond to pressure 400M, never in the picture.
