Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, headed early in straight, rallied on, just beaten by a neck.

Jumped with them, positioned 2w, 2ls back, commenced move after passing 600M, 3w turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, ran on one pace thereafter. (Jockey lost use of right stirrup iron early.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 650M, 4 wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 600M, peaked turning in, kept on one pace in straight.
Bounded in the air on jumping, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 750M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Took rail easily, led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Eased back, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow sectionals.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed forward, suited by the slow tempo, however soon emptied 250M.
Jumped well then ridden along to take lead, travelled nicely in the lead, worked home strongly to score.
Urged to settle in box seat, asked for effort passing 500M, responded solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Began only fairly then taken back, settled behind midfield, placed pressure near 500M, quickened passing 200M, finished nicely.
Raced midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, kept improving on rail in the straight, finished OK.
Raced in one-back-one-off position, placed pressure passing 500M, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Settled midfield, after 1000M travelled wide and without cover, gave ground passing 150M.
Slow out and in the early stages raced detached despite being niggled along, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, tried to improve but no response.
Ridden along to race outside the lead, came under pressure near 600M, gave ground in the straight.
Raced midfield, tried to improve passing 600M, weakened near 300M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure passing 600M, emptied near 300M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, weakened near 200M, must OVE.
Shifted across to midfield away from the rail, three deep with cover. Sprinted well passing the 250m, moved up to share lead inside the 50m, continued on late for win.

Obtained position in midfield between runners. Steadied passing the 900 when pace slowed before moving three wide shortly after. Made gradual headway in the straight to share the lead inside the last 50m before headed late.

Raced in fourth, on the rail, two lengths from lead passing the 800m. Shifted around heels passing the 350m, assumed the lead inside the final 150m before being over-run in late stages. Narrowly beaten.

Didn't begin fast before improving after the start to midfield between runners. Steadied passing the 900m. Shifted out into clear running approaching the 400m before making steady headway in the last section.

Improved after the start to race second in the clear after 200m. Hung outwards when joining a line of three on cornering. Continued to share the lead approaching the 150m before peaking in late stages.

Hard ridden first 150m to hold midfield position on rail. Steadied passing the 900m, before over-racing in the middle section. Three lengths from the lead on cornering & made up a length in the last 150m. (Bled).

Strode forward before being crossed and racing in the first four away from the rail in first section. Continued between runners when 2.5 lengths form lead on straightening & maintained that margin to line.

Shifted across worse than midfield after the start before being inconvenienced & force back to second last passing the 900m. Continued rearward on cornering before making up a few lengths from the back without challenging.
Showed early speed to come across to lead. Steadied the speed approaching the 900m. Joined in a line of three in the lead on cornering before weakening out in the final 150m.
Taken back from wide barrier to race in final trio. Inconvenienced passing the 900m, consequently racing wide with cover in the middle section. Made up a length in late stages but was never a threat.

Strode to midfield, three wide without cover in early section. Improved quickly approaching the 700m to race wide outside leaders from the 600m. Peaked on run inside the 300m & gave ground in final furlong.

Had no early speed and settled near the tail on the fence. Improved along the rail before being inconvenienced in middle stages. Continued near the tail on straightening & was never a factor in the run to the line.

Shifted back to the tail of the field shortly after the start. Steadied passing the 850m before moving wider shortly after. Cornered the widest runner, 5.5 lengths from lead & made no headway into that margin in final 400m.

Steadied after the start & settled at the rear on the fence. Improved marginally passing the 800m before being pratted & forced back to a clear last at the 650m. Conceded big margin on cornering & couldn't improve thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield early, closer on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rival turning in, kept on very well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began well, positioned 3 wide, 3 lengths back, no cover throughout, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, closer on turn, finished off well to take frame without threatening.

Began fairly and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, crowded near 1000M, 2w on turn, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, awkwardly placed and carried wider near 850M, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, recovered to race 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made little progress in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn but still the last, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Settled one-off one-back, hampered at 950M, ran on nicely in the straight and held on to score.
Sat just in front of midfield, along the rail, badly hampered at 950M, closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made ground and ran on gamely for 3rd.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward into the box-seat, held up early and disappointed for running passing 200M, ran on.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, ran on to the finish.
Raced at the rear after crowded at start, shifted 3 wide at 700M, made ground steadily.
Settled in front of midfield, wide and without cover, ran on to the line.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, checked at 950M, ran on fairly to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, run ended at 200M.
In midfield, 2 wide, one paced and crowded momentarily near 100M.
At the tail and stayed one-off the rail, did not threaten.
Ridden to lead from a wide gate, obtained rails run over 1000 metres out, kicked clear under pressure 200 metres out, won confidently.
Travelled keenly in midfield, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to reach 2nd 200 metres out but without threatening.

Reared after loaded, slightly slow out, travelled towards the rear on the rail, switched out for a run after straightening, obtained clear passage over 200 metres out at the centre of the track, finished off the race well.
Settled just worse than midfield, obtained a run shortly after straightening, ran on under pressure despite shifting ground inside final 200 metres.
Settled not far off the pace in 5th on the rail, drifted slightly further back rounding home bend, saved ground turning in and baulked briefly after straightening, kept on same pace under pressure.
Broke well from the widest gate, travelled very wide without cover in forward of midfield, made rapid headway rounding home bend, kept on steadily in straight without quickening. (Tactic questioned)
Driven up to dispute lead early, settled one back on the rail rounding home bend, kept on until swamped for 2nd inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, settled about 2L off the pace mainly 4th or 5th, kept on same pace without quickening in the run to the line.
Settled 3-wide in last few from a wide gate, remained similar into home straight, shifted wider for a run on straightening, ran home one-paced. (Tactic questioned)
Settled wide behind midfield, widest runner turning in, one-paced in straight.
Jumped fairly, niggled along wide in forward of midfield in back straight, lost position approaching home turn, made no impression in straight.
Close up under pressure early stages, came to dispute lead early on home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, never a danger.
Stumbled badly at the start, soon recovered to be 2nd tracking clear leader, moved strongly into contention 500M, led 350M and strode clear mid-straight, kept going strongly never in danger.
Began awkwardly, moved up to race in 3rd just over 3Ls behind clear leader, worked home well final 400M but always held by winner.
Dropped back as expected, over 8Ls off the pace early and middle stages, driven along and wide from 600M, ran home final 400M fastest.
Jumped on terms, settled down midfield 5Ls behind clear leader, kept on steadily final 400M but never a serious threat to leaders.
In mid-division, 6th place making home turn, only battled over final 350M, not threatened. (Blood in trachea.)
Began only fairly, held up behind midfield 6-7Ls off the pace, kept on moderately turning home, never troubled leaders.
Sent forward, established clear lead from 1200M, headed near 350M, weakened away mid-straight.
Dropped back to near last early stages, 7Ls off the pace half-way, failed to respond when driven along near 400M, never near to challenge.
Away well from draw 1, in 4th spot never far off from pace, came under pressure 500M, weakened mid-straight.
Taken back on jumping from wide barrier, always well back 8Ls from leader, switched wide 500M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, no cover form 1400M, struggled to keep up 500M, first to be beaten turning in.
Moderately away, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Crowded on jumping, positioned 2w, 1-2Ls back, bumped near 1000M, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the rival late.

Average to begin, sat 2-3Ls behind the leader on rail, enjoyed the easy run on turn, made good progress early in straight, bumped shortly after passing 300M, crowded 200M then steadied 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, slightly taken back after passing 950M, positioned 3 wide at rear on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress until encountering traffic problems final 100M, not fully tested.
Bumped start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 600M, made some headway early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, made contact near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, trapped very wide with no cover in midfield, found cover near 650M but still 3w, 5-6Ls back turning in, no clear running early in straight, made little progress when clear thereafter. (Lost right front plate near 1000M.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly from 900M, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, bumped near 1000M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed good speed to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, kept on very well in straight, scored by 1-1/2L.
Slowly away, soon recovered, raced 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, angled out after passing 600M, closed off well to take 2nd. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, outpaced by the winner early in straight, kept on evenly to final 50M, weakened and lost 2 places close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Jumped with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, angled out and made contact near 450M, peaked near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Out in line, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, made contact early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from near 800M, wider turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, wide on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, gradually dropped towards rear under pressure on turn, showed nothing in straight, eased final furlong. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide at rear, moved closer in the middle stages, no cover throughout, peaked turning in, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very strongly in straight and scored.
Jumped well, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening the winner.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, steadied off heels near 700M, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced wide with cover behind midfield, wider after passing 450M, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, slightly better than midfield, no cover throughout, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Slow away, hard ridden throughout to keep up with the field, made steady ground 300M to score by a narrow margin.
Eased to sit in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M whilst hanging in.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, overhauled 250M, ran on for 3rd.
Behind midfield, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 150M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 150M.
Just off the leaders, out of fuel 150M.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 100M.
Pushed early, at back, no dash.
At rear, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast tempo, soon weakened 400M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden early, never competitive.
Travelled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, asked for effort near 500M, kicked off passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Pushed along to take lead, travelled comfortably, responded nicely in the straight, worked home solidly.
Settled in one-off-one-back, improved on straightening, worked nicely in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, briefly held up at 400M, made up nice ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, placed pressure on straightening, gradually gained ground in the straight.
Raced 3 wide towards rear, widest on straightening, made some ground passing 150M.
Moderate start, settled midfield, battled hard in the straight, made limited ground near 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, gave ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, placed pressure in the straight but no response.
Began only fairly, settled midfield on rail, weakened passing 150M.
Jumped nicely then sent forward to race outside the lead, emptied near 200M.
Travelled wide and without cover in handy position, lay out passing 700M, came under pressure near 600M, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at rear on rail, no response.
Moderate start, raced in box seat, faded out passing 400M, must trial.
Mustered speed to assume lead after 100m. Continued on, crossing to rail passing the 750m. Raced over 2 lengths clear on straightening & held comfortable lead in the run to the line.

Began fast before being steadied and getting trailing position behind leading pair. Sprinted well after straightening & continued to make steady ground, closing within one length on the line. Winner too far clear.

Began well but was then steadied & shifted across to rearward position. Moved wider passing 600m before passing the 400m mark 8 lengths from lead. Made significant headway in last section after conceding big start.
Began fairly before being hard ridden to hold midfield position away from rail. Hard ridden on cornering before picking up in late stages to close the margin in final 100m.
Mustered speed to race in forth position on the rail. Stayed close to the inside, three lengths from lead on cornering & maintained that margin in the run to the line.

Shifted across to midfield, but was left four wide without cover throughout. Drifted further back approaching bend before entering last section 8 lengths from lead. Passed a few late but could make no headway on winner.
Steadied after start before improving to midfield, wide and without cover. Hung outwards in middle stages when cornering before losing a few lengths in the final 300m.
Began awkwardly before being shifted across behind runners to the tail. Was a clear last on cornering, nearly 10 lengths from lead and despite passing a few tired ones late was never a factor.

Steadied after the first furlong and raced in the final three, wide with cover. Improved slightly between runners approaching the bend but could not go in in final section. Steadied near line but was always well back.

Showed speed to challenge for early lead before being headed and eventually crossed passing the 750m. Came under heavy pressure on cornering when over 2 lengths from the lead before weakening out final section.
Began awkwardly before racing between runners, just worse than midfield. Was hard ridden passing the 550m before yielding significant ground in the last section. Never likely.
Last to begin before holding the rail & improving to midfield after 300m. Lost ground at the 700m bend before continuing to yield further ground from half-way. (Abnormal breathing noise, must trial).
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, raced tight near 950M, 2 wide on turn, angled out after passing 500M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Away well, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 600M, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 1000M, a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, checked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, similar position on turn, took the lead near 300M, kept on evenly until headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, recovered to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 950M, gradually dropped to rear on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
In just behind midfield, on stand side, burst through at 100M, closed off strongly thereafter to score.
Settled to race behind the leader, on the outside rail, worked home gamely for 2nd.
Sat behind the leaders, on stand side, ran on well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, recovered to share lead on centre track, ran on fairly to the line.
Raced in the lead, on stand side, found no extra for final 100M.
In midfield, on centre track, kept on one paced to the line.
Sent forward, shared lead on stand side, showed no turn of foot.
Crowded start, in behind midfield, stand side, closed off fairly from final 200M. (See Incident Report)
Prominent, on centre track, stayed on until weakened at 200M. (See Incident Report)
At rear, on centre track, did not improve and eased at 100M. (Blood in trachea)
Crowded start, recovered in midfield, stand side until shifted to rail at 500M, not competitive.
Urged but remained at the tail, stand side, never a factor.
Raced close to the rear, on centre track, dropped off from 350M.
Settled mainly 2L off the pace in 4th, quickened well under pressure to lead over 100 metres out, just held on.
Ridden to soon take up running setting a steady pace, kept on but unable to defy winner's strong late challenge.
Settled mainly in rear of midfield in 6th, came under pressure to challenge entering home straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Slowly away, travelled in last few racing keenly approaching home bend, wide into the straight and finished off the race well near the centre of the track.
Raced keenly wide in midfield, moved forward to track outside the leader inside the 1200 metres, kept on same pace from one back 2nd into home straight.
Taken back gradually to travel last and wide, widest runner turning for home, kept on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Never far off on the rail, baulked when joint 3rd after straightening, weakened inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in rear from the widest gate, remained similar turning for home, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Slowly away, soon recovered to rear of midfield on the rail in steady pace, faded gradually in home straight.
Settled ahead of mid-division, 4Ls behind leader in fast run race, let down strongly 300M, pounced to the lead 100M out, won going away in class record time.
Went forward to be tracking leader in a fast run race, took over inside 400M, finished off well, caught by winner 100M out, kept on to hold 2nd.
Slow to begin, held up near last 9Ls off the fast race, closed off quickest over final 400M to claim 3rd. Clear from rest.
Held up towards the rear in 10th position, 8Ls off middle stages, driven along 500M, made ground through the field but no impression on leading trio.
Jumped on terms, reigned back to be racing towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, ran on mildly and safely held by first 3.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, kept on evenly passing 400M but lacked a turn of foot to challenge leaders.
From wide draw dropped back to race in last, 10Ls off the pace early and middle stages, made some headway final 400M but never near to challenge.
Chased the pace in 3rd, moved up on leaders passing 600M, kept battling early straight, run ended 200M, faded away.
Emerged as leader passing 1300M, led at fast pace to straight, headed passing 400M, soon no extra and dropped away.
Held up midfield 6Ls off leader in a fast run race, couldn't quicken when driven along 500M, failed to make any impression.
Dropped back on jumping from wide draw, settled midfield 6Ls off leader, failed to improve in straight after racing wide and no cover throughout.
Jumped fair to be settling in midfield 6Ls off the pace, only battled in the straight, made no impact.
Steadied to obtain cover early stages, held up near the rear 9Ls back, struggled home.
Steadied early stages for cover, proved very difficult to settle 1500M, towards rear 3-wide, failed to close off and soon left behind, tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, missed frame on line.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, carried wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, trapped wide and without cover behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back turning in, taken wide in straight and made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Average to begin, raced in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take a place.
Began smartly from gate 12, sent forward to race prominently, travelled comfortably on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the first few late.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, hampered near 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Out in line, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1200M, took the lead near 900M, headed turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, crossed near 800M, angled out and made contact near 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear final 200M.

Began well from gate 9, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, crowded near 1000M, similar position on turn, carried wider and made contact near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position in the middle stages, no clear running after turning in, eased final 150M.

Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer in the middle stages, finished off strongly to score by 3/4L.

Clean jump, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer on turn, angled out after passing 450M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M, finished 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, kept on evenly thereafter to take a place.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently early, allowed rival to cross 1250M, sat 2Ls behind the leader in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 500M, 4w turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly and made contact shortly after start, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1600M, settled 2 wide in 2nd thereafter, peaked turning in, one paced in straight.
Average to begin, unbalanced early, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Hard ridden forward, settled just off the leaders, 2 wide, ran on well to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 300M, made steady ground when clear.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly 200M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed to take the rail and share the lead, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Slow away, hard ridden to share the lead at fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 100M.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 100M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Settled midfield on rail, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Jumped sharply, ridden to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home solidly.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, responded solidly in the straight, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure on straightening, battled well in the straight.
Urged along to race outside the lead, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Travelled in box seat, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, tried to improve passing 400M, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced in front of midfield, came under pressure near 500M and weakened near 200M, must trial.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, niggled near 600M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, steadied away from heels near 100M, no response.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, wide on straightening, weakened in the straight.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover in midfield, faded out near 150M.

Enjoyed good run on leaders back in early & middle stages. Travelled strongly & moved away from rail approaching the 400m before sprinting strongly to obtain the lead at the 150m. Continued on for strong win.

Shifted back behind runners to race at the tail in early stages. Made sweeping mid-race move to assume the lead approaching the 600m. Continued in front until being joined and past at the 150m. Battled on well late.

Raced in midfield on the rail in early & middle stages. Drifted further back in middle sections before cornering nearly five lengths from lead. Stayed close to the inside in the straight & made good headway in the final furlong.
Ridden forward after start before getting nice spot away from rail behind leading pair. Shuffled a pair further back approaching the turn and maintained margin in the dash to the line.
Crossed after the start and steadied to race in midfield on the rail. Three lengths from lead entering the final section and effectively maintained that margin in the final 400m.

Shifted across to midfield away from the rail. Ridden forward to improve from the 600m before conceding 4 lengths entering the final section. Made up a length in the last 400m but was never a real threat.

Showed early speed to lead, crossed to rail nearing the 1300m. Joined an headed in the lead passing the 600m before kicking back to share the lead on straightening. Peaked & weakened out in last furlong.

Strode to midfield away from rail. Moved three wide approaching 750m on back of improving runner before being left wide without cover from the 600m. Shifted the widest on cornering before yielding a few lengths in straight.

Strode forward to race in second, 1L from lead, away from rail leaving first section. Obtained cover passing the 600m before being pushed 4 wide on cornering. Peaked on effort at the 250m & weakened out thereafter.
Reared at the start & lost ground before making up deficit to settle last. Continued rearward, nearly 8 lengths from the lead passing the 400m mark and couldn't make any headway late. Never a factor.

Shifted across after start & raced worse than midfield away from rail. Moved wider & was improving mid-race before being checked passing the 600m & losing ground. Five lengths from lead at 400m & couldn't make any headway.

Had no early speed & consequently raced third from last on the rail. Shuffled back to last approaching the 650m before coming under pressure shortly after. Long way from lead entering the final section & failed to improve.
Bumped start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 50M, weakened gradually thereafter, missed 2nd on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, got cover after entering the back straight, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.

Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg.)
Average to begin, raced very wide and without cover in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 100M. (Bled.) (Lame left front leg next day.)

Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide behind midfield, taken back after entering the back straight, raced 2w at rear in the middle stages, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, stepped up inside final 100M and caught leader late, scored by 1/2L.
Sent forward, shared lead on the rail, held on until the closing stages, had to settle for 2nd.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, worked home well for 3rd.
Sent forward, took cover in one-off one-back prior to the 600M turn, ran on fairly.
Taken back, raced at the tail along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly well.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, continued on one paced.
In front of midfield, wide and without cover however, ran on fairly to the line.
Raced in just behind midfield, 2 wide, made late ground after shifted out to centre track.
Took cover, in behind midfield along the rail, was one paced.
Fractious prior to the start, eased back after the jump, at tail 2 wide, did not improve. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden forward, shared lead 2 wide, emptied passing 200M.
In box-seat, did not improve, weakened and eased out approaching 150M. (See Incident Report)
Soon ridden up to vie for early lead, taken back for 2nd spot on the rail 800 metres out, renewed effort after straightening, gained upper hand inside the final 100 metres.

Worked his way across from the widest gate to settle just off the pace in 3rd, raced keenly and lost position 800 metres out, some 2L back in 5th coming onto home bend and 4th into the straight, fought on steadily to miss narrowly.

Jumped fairly in forward of midfield early stages, improved steadily to one back in 3rd about 700 metres out, saved ground on inside turning for home, fought on steadily to hold every chance but unable to sustain effort late.
Broke well from a wide gate to lead, obtained rails run passing the 900 metres, led until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Moderate start, settled worse than midfield, ran on well down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Niggled along in rear on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend and switched out for a run entering straight, finished off the race strongly down the centre of the track.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to rear of midfield, similar into home straight, produced good late impression closing stages.

Settled 3-wide just better than midfield, made headway at the Rock to be wide in 3rd rounding home bend, lost position entering home straight and never recovered. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield, slightly closer up rounding home bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Hampered after a moderate start and dropped to last, trailed the field to home straight, saved ground turning in and kept on past beaten horses.
Jumped awkwardly but soon recovered to within 3L of pace in 4th, lost position approaching the Rock dropping to 7th in midfield onto home bend, wide into straight and one-paced.
Settled well back from a wide gate, last and wide turning into straight, one-paced.
Jumped on terms, settled in 4th/5th, quickened up well to lead nearing 150M, forged clear to score.
Never far off from the pace, switched wide 450M making his move, chased solidly to the line but couldn't reel in winner.
Pressed on early stages to be tracking the leader, driven along 450M, fought on steadily from the corner, not finishing pace of first 2 final 150M.
Close up to leaders early stages before easing back to race in midfield, on straightening battled away steadily down the inside, only just missed out on a podium finish.
Held up behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, let down well early straight and loomed a danger, effort levelled off final 100M.
Driven forward as expected, had uncontested lead, driven out 350M, headed mid-straight, weakened and lost several placings final 100M.
Settled down in mid-division, had ground-saving trip, fought on steadily in straight, raced tight late and not ridden out closing stages.
Not hurried after an awkward start, 8Ls away near the rear, made up some ground final 300M but not reached leaders.
Taken across behind runners, settled last almost 10Ls off leader, gave limited response in straight, ran past well beaten horses only.
From draw 1 drifted back to race towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, kept battling on at same pace on straightening, never threatened.
Dropped back from a wide draw, held up near last and wide no cover from 1200M, struggled to keep up with rivals 400M, soon beaten.
Bustled along after the start, tracked leader from 1200M, first one to come under pressure, hard pressed from 550M, weakened noticeably mid-straight.
Began smartly from gate 1, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, angled out near 400M, kept on evenly in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 3 wide without cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off one pace.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced very wide with no cover at rear early, found cover near 800M, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, unbalanced near 750M, there to turn, weakened early in straight.

Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover better than midfield, bumped near 1000M, 2 wide turning, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.

Jumped with them, raced 2W, 1-1/2L back, got cover from 800M, same margin back turning in, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner 50M, finished 2nd.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, closed off well to take 3rd without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, raced wide with cover at rear, found rail near 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Rider dropped whip near 250M.)
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, failed to make any progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race very wide with no cover at rear, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, bumped near 1000M, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, blocked near 200M, eased shortly thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, sent forward to race prominently but wide, took the lead near 900M, shared lead with rival on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle early, struck heels and badly blundered near 650M, eased shortly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right front leg with a swollen tendon next day.)
Settled just off the leader, closed off strongly 300M to score.
At back, lack room early straight, dashed strongly when clear.
Box seat, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
At back, dashed strongly 250M.
At back, trapped wide, made steady ground 300M.
Secured more prominent spot, lack turn of foot in straight.
At back, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, ran on fairly in straight.
Failed to muster, midfield, trapped wide, never improved.
Took rail and lead easily, soon out of fuel 250M.
Midfield, no progress in straight.
Pressed forward, emptied 300M.
Never better than midfield.
Eased back, never competitive.
Taken back at start, improved passing 400M, responded strongly to score.
Settled at tail, responded nicely when placed pressure passing 400M.
Settled on outside rail behind midfield, after 300M had difficulty to obtain clear run, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden to share the lead, commenced to improve near 400M, worked home nicely.
Raced behind leaders, near 750M was momentarily ease away heels, fought hard passing 400M, finished OK.
Niggled to take lead on outside rail, asked for effort near 350M, finished fairly.
Settled toward rear, shifted in to improve passing 400M, came home one-paced.

Shifted across behind runners before improving to midfield away from rail. Travelled well, 4L from lead passing half-way. Clear running at 350m, sprinted quickly assuming lead inside the 100m & continued on for easy win.

Showed early speed to assume the lead after 150m. Broke over 1 length clear passing the 400m before continuing in lead until being joined and passed inside the last 100m. Ran well, no match for winner.

Steadied after the start and shifted back to race third from last. Continued rearward, over six lengths from the lead on straightening before finishing fast in the final 250m to snare third in the shadows of the post.

Raced in first few early before improving in the second section to race in second outside leader. Ridden up passing the 500m before dropping off leader on straightening. Battled hard in last section to hold fourth.
Began well before being steadied and drifting back to midfield, three wide with cover. Six lengths from the lead on cornering, made up a length in the run to the line but was never a threat.
Wasn't fast to begin and settled worse than midfield on the rail. Continued at the tail, third from last on cornering before passing a few in the dash to the line without threatening.

Began awkwardly & had no early speed , racing towards the tail of the field. Shuffled back to last before cornering over 8 lengths from the lead. Shifted wider inside the 400m before making some headway without threatening.

Lost ground at the start before failing to muster speed & racing a clear last. Continued rearward, 9L from lead at halfway. Next to last on straightening before passing a few in last section. Never likely after beginning.

Began well before steadying to midfield, three wide with cover early. Continued wide with cover before shifting wider on straightening when 4L form lead. Peaked inside the 300m and gave ground in late stages.
Gathered speed after the start before settling in midfield away from rail. Peaked on effort shortly after straightening and yielded ground in the final furlong.
Strode forward and enjoyed soft run on the rail behind the leader. Hard ridden approaching the 600m & yielded ground after straightening. Well beaten.

Began fast before steadying to midfield, racing four wide without cover early stages. Shifted three wide passing the 800m & continued without cover thereafter. Hard ridden into the turn before yielding ground in final 300m.

Settled in midfield on the rail, less than 4L from the lead in early stages. Crowded at the 700m before cornering 5L from lead. Momentarily held up near the 350m but could make no headway & weakened significantly thereafter.
Strode forward to race in second before being crossed and racing with cover, 2L from lead at half-way. Hard ridden approaching the turn before yielding significant ground in the last section.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground in the middle stages, angled out turning in, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2 wide on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no chance with the clear winner.

Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter, missed 2nd on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Made contact on jumping, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, no cover after passing 1000M, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, a length or so back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider turning in, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 300M.
Steadied after start, remained at the tail along the rail, held up till 300M, took inside run and closed off strongly to score.
In front of midfield, along the rail, battled on gamely but couldn't hold off the winner, settled for 2nd.
In midfield, trapped wide however but with cover, continued on nicely to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, in worse than midfield along the rail, badly held up until 200M, closed off nicely after that.
Travelled in about midfield 2 wide, stayed on well to the line.
Taken back, raced at the rear 2 wide, saved ground and ran on to the line.
Bumped start, in around midfield 2 wide, no daylight from 300M to 200M, closed off fairly thereafter.
Failed to muster, in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, steadied at 350M, ran on thereafter.
Raced in one-off one-back position, stayed on till about 200M.
Asked and raced in the box-seat, one paced and emptied passing 200M.
Bumped start, sat in front of midfield, wide and without cover however, not competitive.
Bumped start, in just behind midfield along the rail, stayed on until 200M when slightly held up.
Sent forward, took rail and led, lay out throughout and emptied at 300M. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden, sat outside the lead, gave ground from 350M.
Jumped fairly, settled close up with the pace, commenced move entering straight and soon asserted authority.
Broke well from a wide gate, ridden amongst the leaders in back straight, obtained rails run over 900 metres out and led until headed turning in, just held on for 2nd.
Moderate start, settled in midfield on the rail in back straight, saved ground on home turn, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Travelled 3-wide mainly over 2L back in 4th early stages, obtained 2-wide position with cover coming onto home bend, left flat-footed on straightening but produced good late impression closing stages.
Moderate start from the one draw, settled just off the pace in 3rd, kept on same pace without threatening.
Broke well, settled just off the pace, gradually shuffled back to rear of midfield 3-wide onto home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind from the widest gate, did best work late.
Settled in last few, came under pressure after straightening, one-paced without quickening.
Lacked pace despite ridden early, remained well behind to straight, never a factor.
Never better than midfield.
Went forward to be disputing the lead on inside, led going well passing 300M, was challenged by runner up final 150M but held on always.
Chased leaders on inside, switched out to challenge 350M, pushed winner all the way to the line but always held.
Pushed along early stages, stayed in touch with leaders throughout, chased on steadily from 300M but not reached first 2.
Held up in a position ahead of midfield, 4Ls to make up top of straight, stayed on mildly over final 300M, no serious threat to first 3. (Lame RF leg.)
From draw 12 raced in midfield 3-wide, no cover from 700M, kept on evenly in the straight, never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Dropped back towards the rear, settled in 11th spot just over 6Ls off leaders, stayed on final 400M making mild progress but never threatened.
Up with early pace before easing off to sit behind leaders passing 800M, had his chance early straight, faded over final 150M.
Driven forward from draw 14, caught wide until crossing to a 2-wide spot 600M, held narrow lead turning in, headed nearing 300M, weakened steadily mid-straight.
Failed to muster after beginning slowly, settled near last 8Ls away, gave limited response turning in, never factored. (Bled.)
Began awkwardly, held up in midfield, failed to pick up when ridden out 400M, ran home same pace, never a threat.
Settled down behind midfield, 3-wide home turn, driven but made no progress over final 400M.

Reared abruptly at the start losing a significant amount of ground, got back to the tail of the field 700M, ran past a couple of beaten rivals in the straight. Slow start costly. (To consecutive barrier trials.)
Eased back on jumping from wide gate, always towards rear, driven along 450M, struggled home.
From draw 1 held up in midfield along the fence, outpaced passing 400M, soon beaten.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, switched to inner early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide better than midfield, found cover near 700M, commenced move after passing 600M, peaked shortly after turning in, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, carried wider near 500M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off one pace.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, slightly hampered near 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, shared lead with rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong.

Moderately away from gate 13, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1000M, raced 3 wide, a length or so back in the middle stages, weakened from 600M, finished tailed off.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run in the middle stages, angled out turning in, hit the front early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line, scored by 3 lengths.
Bumped start, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly throughout, angled out turning in, made some headway in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 800M, angled out turning in, no clear running near 300M, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield early, 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 6 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off one pace.
Average to begin, taken back to race 3 wide, 6 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, 1 out 1 back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, blocked near 150M, eased thereafter.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
