Bumped on jumping, showed good speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, a length behind the leader, moved closer on turn, kept grinding to the line but always held by the winner.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.

Crowded out start, positioned 5 to 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.

Shifted out on jumping and made contact, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 850M, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, commenced move after passing 800M, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Pushed to take the rail and led at good pace, hung on to win.
Eased to secure box seat, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, moved to 3 wide around home turn, dashed well 300M.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
At rear, along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Eased to rear, took cover, 2 wide, pace good, made ground in straight, lack room 150M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, on heels 250M, weakened.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, moved forward 600M, soon out of fuel 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, made early move 700M, emptied 300M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 650M, wide rounding the Home Turn, quickened passing 200M to score.
Settled towards rear, asked for effort passing 800M, wide on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Hard ridden to race behind leaders, placed pressure passing 500M, gained nice ground in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, in the straight made up some nice late ground.
Raced in handy position on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Sent forward to take lead, allowed a runner to cross passing 800M, gave ground near 100M, lame left front next day.
Stumbled on jumping, improved to outside the lead passing 900M, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 200M.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, then ridden along to race in front of midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Slow out then taken back from the widest gate, no response when asked for effort in the straight.
Raced at rear, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Trapped wide then improved to lead passing 900M, weakened near 300M.
Settled midfield, ridden to maintain its position near 1100M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, faded out near 200M.
Urged along to race behind leaders, came under pressure passing 600M, emptied in the straight, must trial.
Settled in front of midfield, came under pressure passing 600M, emptied passing 300M, must trial.

Raced in midfield, between runners, 3L from lead approaching the 800m. Shifted out after straightening before sprinting quickly, assuming lead inside last 150m & continuing on strongly for impressive win.
Ridden forward to assume early lead, before challenged & headed approaching 900m. Held the rail and kicked back to assume lead on straightening, continued in lead until being passed inside last 150m.

Steadied & shifted across behind runners, settling near the tail. Continued at the rear, before moving very wide on straightening, over 5L from lead entering final section. Made solid late headway last 400m, close behind.

Limited early speed before racing midfield on the rail. Moved away from rail approaching 650m before shifting second widest on bend. Balanced 3.5 lengths from lead before making late headway without threatening winner.

Not bustled after start & raced worse than midfield between runners. Drifted rearward, entering final section 3.5L from lead. Ran on steadily before making up a length in final 250m. (Rider questioned, see incident report).

Ridden forward to be prominent before steadying to get trailing position behind leading trio. Cornered close, just over 1L from lead before peaking on effort at the 300m & yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Had no early speed and raced at the tail on the inside. Continued at the tail, 4.5L from lead on straightening, passed a few in the run home but finishing over 7L off winner.
Steadied after the start, shifted back to race worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Pushed very wide on cornering when 4L from the lead & could make no impression in the last section.
Had limited early speed and got back to race in final three. Began to make steady ground on the inside from the 500m, before being badly checked at the 200m mark & playing no part thereafter.

Hard ridden after the start before improving to take the lead away from the rail from the 900m. Re0joined in the lead on straightening before peaking on run and yielding ground in the final 350m. Well beaten.
Strode forward to be prominent before being crossed & racing midfield between runners. Moved wider approaching the 500m before yielding ground from the 400m mark. Well beaten.

Didn't begin fast but mustered speed to race midfield, wide & with cover. Hung outwards around the turn before losing ground on cornering. Yielded substantial ground in final section & was well beaten.

Mustered speed after the start to obtain good position on leaders back. Only a length form the lead on cornering but gave significant ground in the final section to be beaten a big margin. (Irregular heart rhythm post-race).

Showed good early speed from wide barrier to shift across & race outside leading pair when three wide without cover. Began yielding ground from the 500m mark & was beaten a big margin. (Unacceptable performance  must trial).
Commenced well from a wide draw, taken back to race 7 lengths back at rear, found rail near 800M, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made very good progress in straight to score.
Clean jump, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back, 2 wide turning, hit the front near 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, angled out after passing 700M, 3 wide turning in, closed off well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Clean jump from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out early in straight and made contact, finished off well without threatening, just missed 3rd on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, closer on turn, made good progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress, blocked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, brushed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Bled.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Away well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, unbalanced near 1100M, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, taken back to race 3 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, travelled keenly in the early stages, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Jumped with them, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, slightly better than midfield early, moved closer in the middle stages, still 3 wide without cover, weakened from 500M, eased early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, detached from the field after passing 800M, eased turning in, finished tailed out.
Midfield but wide early, prominent by 1200M, wide and no cover throughout, continued nicely and held on to score by 1/2L.
Travelled just in front of midfield, wide but with cover, ran on gamely to take 2nd.
Eased back and raced at the tail, saved ground and closed off nicely for 3rd.
Bumped start and remained at the rear, saved ground and continued to the line fairly.
Raced in just behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, showed no turn of foot.
Settled to race in the box-seat, was one paced and emptied for final 150M.
Bumped start, in behind midfield 2 wide, did not feature in the straight.
Sent forward to take rail and led, weakened and headed at 250M.
Raced in one-off one-back position, emptied half way down the straight.
Awkward start, recovered to be in front of midfield, 2 wide, was not in it.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, not competitive in the straight.
Settled outside the lead, in the straight finished tailed out. Must trial.
Taken well back from a wide gate and waited with, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest runner turning into straight, finished off race strongly to assert authority over 100 metres out.

Raced wide in last few after beginning from the widest gate, commenced move rounding final bend to be 1L ahead of eventual winner turning in, ran on well under pressure but outsprinted closing stages.

Broke well to lead early, settled just off the pace in 3rd coming off first bend, remained in similar one-out-one-back position to home straight, ran on to hold some chance 200 metres out but didn't last. (Tactic questioned)
Settled within 3L of pace in 6th just better than midfield travelling wide throughout, came to challenge entering straight reaching 2nd over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort.
Travelled wide in worse than midfield after beginning from a wide gate, gained slightly closer coming onto home bend, kept on steadily in straight without quickening.
Picked up steadily from a moderate start to settle 3-wide close-up in 3rd, ran on to hit the front upon straightening only to be collared inside the final 100 metres.
Moderate start from a wide gate, settled behind midfield in 10th near the rail, dropped to last few turning in, only went past well-beaten horses.
Settled well behind, kept on past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Lacked early speed and given reminders, travelled in last few before dropping to last into home straight, only ran past well-beaten horses late.
Settled not far off the pace in 5th on the rail, in similar position turning for home, weakened noticeably inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, improved steadily to take up running 2-wide turning into back straight, obtained rails run coming onto home bend but soon flattered, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled in midfield near the rail, came under pressure rounding final bend, weakened steadily on straightening.
Recovered swiftly from an awkward start to be up with the pace on the rail, came under pressure entering home straight but folded up quickly.
Settled in rear of midfield, dropped out tamely in home straight.
Jumped well, eased back to sit in midfield passing 1100M, angled out 4-wide 500M, quickly moved up to lead 350M, was strongly challenged by the runner up from 200M but fought well to hold on.
Settled down in mid-division, tracked the path of the eventual winner going into straight, launched a serious challenge final 200M, just held.
Began well from draw 1, up with early pace until 1000M, tracked leaders turning, ran on steadily on straightening, not pace of first 2 final 200M, held on for 3rd just.
Jumped on terms, eased back towards the rear, brought widest 450M, stayed on well, just missed 3rd.

Stood flat-footed after the start and lost significant amount of ground, refused to stretch out early stages, 6Ls off leader 400M, made good progress from rear despite laying in over final 400M, nearest line. Slow start costly.
Crossed to race 3-wide in mid-division, swung wider 500M, kept on evenly to the line but never going the pace to challenge.
In touch tracking leading trio, checked early straight then badly held up until 200M, unable to make much progress when clear.
Began fairly, bustled along to hold a midfield spot along the fence, had no clear run from straightening and unable to be fully tested at any stage.
Slowly away, drifted back to race towards the rear 5Ls back, kept on steadily turning home, shifted in when placed under pressure in straight, faded final stages.
Dropped back to a position near last, ran past beaten horses in the straight, awkwardly placed late stages, not ridden out near finish.
Driven after the start to be racing outside leader, battled on early straight, weakened over final 150M, lost ground when hampered final 50M.
From wide draw, eased back to a 3-wide position towards rear of midfield, gave brief response on straightening, weakened final 200M.
Pressed forward, established narrow lead nearing 800M, swamped by rivals 350M, well beaten at 200M, eased.
Moved forward from draw 11, caught 3-wide outside leader, struggled from 400M, soon dropped out of contention.
Jumped nicely, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, stayed on for 2nd.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced 2 to 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly for a short distance after passing 800M, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from near 800M, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped well, taken back to race at rear, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide, 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Out in line, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Quickly into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, angled out 550M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, 2 wide from 550M, finished off evenly.
Away well, sat right behind the leader, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, eased final 150M.

Made contact at start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked on run near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, headed close home.
Away well from a wide draw, raced prominently but 3 wide, took the lead after passing 700M, 2 wide turning, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 to 4 wide, slightly better than midfield, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, took inside run after straightening, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position in the middle stages, awkwardly placed rounding the home turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide, slightly worse than midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, showed no response in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 600M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, drifted away 300M, hung on well to score.
Settled in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Slow away, at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 4 wide, made early move from 1000M, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 300M.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 500M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, emptied 500M.
Eased back, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
At back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Never a factor.
Took rail easily, led at fast sectionals, dropped off rapidly 600M.
Settled midfield, improved passing 450M, issued challenge near 150M, finished strongly to score.
Travelled nicely in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, worked home solidly, missed by HD.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 600M, battled nicely in the straight.
Raced in handy position, asked for effort near 350M, gained nice ground in the straight.
Urged along to take lead, made nice ground in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Jumped fairly, raced midfield on rail, responded well in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Travelled keenly in early and middle stages outside the lead, weakened passing 150M.
Ridden along after start then steadied and tried to obtain cover, settled 3 wide midfield, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Slow out, raced at back on rail, gave ground passing 250M.
Jumped sharply then hard ridden but failed to muster speed, travelled wide and without cover outside the leaders, weakened passing 400M.
Showed speed after the start to improve & race outside leader. Continued to hold outright second place before making continual late ground to snare lead in final 50m.
Showed early speed to assume the lead. Raced a lengths clear on straightening and continued in the lead until being passed inside the final 50m.

Shifted across to midfield after the start, racing away from rail, 3.5 lengths from lead. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before shifting out at the 250m and making solid late headway thereafter.
Steadied after the 1000m mark, drifting back to midfield, three wide with cover. Shifted wider on straightening and made up a length or so in the final 300m.
Strode to midfield between horses, two lengths from lead at the 800m. Just over 2 lengths from the lead passing the 400m before peaking on effort shortly after straightening. Well held.
Enjoyed good run on the leaders back. Couldn't keep in touch with leader entering the final section before weakening & yielding ground in the final 300m.

Shifted behind runners after the start & raced at the tail of the field. Improved position passing the 750m & made up a few lengths in second section. Five lengths from lead on straightening & could only maintain that margin.

Steadied & shifted behind runners to race near the rear. Shuffled back to last at half-way before conceding 7 lengths entering the final section. Could only maintain margin in the straight & was never a factor.

Limited early speed & raced in midfield on the rail in first section. Ridden along approaching half-way before drifting further back. Over 6 lengths from lead on cornering & yielded further ground in straight. Well beaten.

Steadied after the start and raced third from last away from rail. Drifted back to last, 8 lengths form the lead entering the final section. Yielded further ground in the straight & was beaten a big margin.

Strode forward to race prominently, three wide, two lengths from lead. Hard ridden passing the 600m and began yielding ground thereafter. Beaten a significant margin (Unacceptable performance  must trial).
Away well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, 3 wide turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line.
Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, commenced move after passing 450M, wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still 5 to 6 lengths behind turning in, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide from 600M, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, trapped wide early, found rail after passing 1200M, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, took the lead 1100M, found rail after entering the back straight, travelled well to turn, headed 250M, weakened thereafter.

Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 1100M, 1-1/2L back in the middle stages, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, raced tight and made contact early in straight, checked near 150M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away from gate 9, raced prominently but trapped 4 wide early, slightly taken back after passing 1300M, sat 3 wide better than midfield in the middle stages, sent forward 700M, 2nd on turn, weakened early in straight.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, kept going and caught leader to win just prior going to the line.
Raced in the box-seat, gave a brave run but couldn't hold off the winner in the final strides.
In midfield initially, gradually improved from 800M onwards, wide throughout, ran on well to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, battled on gamely until couldn't find extra for final 100M.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on until flattened in final 100M.
Raced in one-off one-back position, stayed on until flattened passing 150M.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, unbalanced and lost ground at 800M, was one paced. (See Incident Report)
Eased then shifted to the rail, raced in worse than midfield, pretty one paced in the straight.
Missed start badly, remained at the tail, did not feature.
Fractious at start, at rear throughout, did not threaten.
In behind midfield, raced greenly, not competitive.
Settled mainly in midfield, switched out to challenge entering home straight, asserted authority over 150 metres out.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish but never threatening.
Settled one back 2-wide, similar when 3rd 600 metres out, held good chance under pressure early in straight, outsprinted when inconvenienced closing stages.
Gradually improved to take up running 1200 metres out, led until headed 600 metres out, re-gained lead on inside turning for home, unable to sustain effort and swamped 150 metres out.
Settled mainly in midfield or just worse, towards rear when wide entering home straight, made some late impression down the centre of the track.
Began from a wide gate, settled just better than midfield and wide most of way, inconvenienced 600 metres out, made steady headway in the run to the line.
Began from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover and keenly 1000 metres out, made rapid progress from 900 metres to lead 600 metres out, found no extra when headed shortly after straightening.
Settled one back in 3rd in the rail, became 4th two back 600 metres out, soon faded after straightening.
Trailed the field most of the way, saved ground on inside turning in, only went past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Never seen with a chance.
Away well, crossed to race in mid-division, brought wide 450M, let down strongly to take lead passing 150M, kept on well.
Began fairly, held up in midfield 3Ls off the pace, responded well on straightening, joined by eventual winner 150M, out-battled final stages.

Dropped back to be racing towards the rear, 4Ls off leader turning for home, commenced to close off well from 200M, hampered by rival 100M and not able to be properly tested to the line (Finished 4th, placed 3rd after enquiry.)

From wide draw eased back near last, made early move 600M circling the field, stayed on well down outside of track but shifted in badly over final 100M causing interference to a rival. (Finished 3rd, demoted to 4th after enquiry.)
Jumped on terms, moved closer tracking leaders passing 800M, vied for lead early straight, outpaced by leaders final 150M.
Began fairly, settled towards the rear, lost ground 600M, ran on steadily on straightening. Passable debut.
Not hurried, raced as the back-marker until turning home, stayed on past one paced rivals but no threat to leaders.
Away fairly from draw 1, moved up along the rails to lead from 950M, joined by rival early straight, stayed in contention until 150M then weakened away.
Began fairly, rushed forward to be racing outside the lead, peaked on its run 250M, plodded home.
Tracked leaders 3-wide, couldn't quicken when asked 300M, faded mid-straight.
Chased leaders, driven 350M but didn't respond to riding, weakened out of contention 200M. (Jockey : horse didn't appear to be comfortable first time running at Happy Valley.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, found rail near 650M, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck. (Rider momentarily dropped right rein near 150M.)
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out near 400M, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Clean jump, showed good early speed, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from the widest draw, trapped 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, peaked shortly after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off one pace.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 2 wide better than midfield, found rail near 1000M, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made some progress early in straight, blocked final 50M, not ridden out thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Jumped well from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Away well, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Led easily at advantages slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Settled in front, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Midfield, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground for 3rd.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Midfield, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Checked shortly after the start, settled in prominent spot, favoured by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Checked shortly after the start, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 100M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early, midfield, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden early, never better than midfield.
Checked start, never competitive at rear.
Hard ridden throughout, never responded.
Pushed forward, raced ungenerously, soon emptied 350M.
Settled in handy position, placed pressure on straightening, worked home strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail to save ground rounding the Home Turn, quickened passing 200M, finished solidly.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, checked away form heels near 700M, lay out passing 700M, widest on straightening, gained nice ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made up solid late ground.
Urged along to take lead, lay out near 700M, worked well in the early part of straight, one-paced after 200M.
Jumped well, ridden to settle midfield, 3 wide with cover, made up some ground passing 100M.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover when sharing the lead, in the straight asked for effort but only one-paced.
Crowded after start then raced towards rear, improved to midfield near 800M, passing 200M was steadied and lost ground when disappointed for running.
Sent forward with nice early speed, raced outside the lead, gave ground near 150M.
Raced behind leaders on rail, limited response when placed pressure in the straight.
Raced at tail, niggled passing 700M, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, lay in passing 800M, came under pressure passing 700M, weakened passing 250M.

Mustered speed after the start to assume lead in first furlong. Raced a length clear in middle stages before holding that margin on straightening. Continued on inside the final furlong & went on for solid win.

Began well, steadied shortly after to race in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide passing the 700m before improving to be within 2L on straightening. Worked home strongly in last section but couldn't reel in the winner.
Strode forward before shifting across to race on leaders back from the 1100m. Moved away from the rail on cornering before making up a length on the winner in the straight. Close behind.

Raced prominent early before being crossed & drifting to midfield on rail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering when 2.5 lengths from lead, before yielding a length in the straight when boxing on for 4th.

Drifted back after start before shifting across worse than midfield, three wide without cover from the 1000m. Continued wide run into turn before straightening 4L from lead. Worked home evenly in straight without threatening.
Gathered some speed after the start to race in midfield on the rail. Drifted away from rail after straightening but could only maintain 4L margin in dash to line.

Crowded & checked at the start & consequently hard ridden to hold position near tail. Came under hard riding again approaching the 500m, before cornering 5L from lead. Couldn't make any headway in last section.

Steadied & shifted across from wide barrier, sharing last position on the rail. Continued at the rear, 8 lengths from lead on straightening before passing a few tiring runners in dash home. Well behind winner.

Steadied after the start & shifted across to race at the tail. A clear last entering the last section, 7 lengths from lead. Passed a few in the run to line but was never a genuine threat & was well beaten.

Steadied after the start before racing keenly when taken back near the rear to obtain cover. Continued a wide path, with cover in middle stages. Six lengths from lead in straightening & made no impression in straight.
Showed early speed to stride across and race in second on the outside. Over 1L from lead on straightening peaked on run at the 300m mark and gave ground thereafter.
Race din midfield away from rail, six lengths from lead passing the 800m. Hard ridden from the 550m and gave ground in the straight.
Obtained nice position in 4th away from rail. Hard ridden approaching the 500m before yielding ground shortly after. Well beaten.

Crowded at start before being taken back towards the rear between runners. Shuffled back to second last on straightening, 6 lengths from lead before weakening out significantly in last section to be a long last.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, angled out after passing 300M, took the lead near 150M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by a narrow margin.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just missed by a narrow margin.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from a middle draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight. (Lost left hind plate near 1000M.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, angled out after 500M, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left front leg.)
Commenced well from a tricky gate, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, found rail near 1000M, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, carried wider on turn, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from the widest draw, trapped very wide early, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield after passing 950M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Bumped start, sat towards the rear 3 wide but with cover, dashed through nicely to score by 1-1/4L.
Sent forward, settled to race outside the lead, took 2nd after holding off some late challenges.
Eased shortly after the start, at tail, wide but with cover, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Raced in midfield, wide and without cover, made ground steadily to the line.
Settled to race in the box-seat, kept on going to the line.
Raced in one-off one-back position, showed no turn off foot.
Taken back, at rear along the rail, showed slight dash early in straight, one paced thereafter.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, was one paced in the straight.
Asked after the jump, took rail and led, weakened and headed passing 250M.
Awkward start, settled in midfield but wide, not competitive.
In midfield initially, wide and without cover, gave ground from near 700M.
In midfield, dropped off from 600M, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, quickened well under pressure to hit the front 200 metres out.
Inconvenienced at start settling in last few, saved ground on inside turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind the pacemakers, left over 5L off the speed in 3rd rounding home bend, quickened well in straight to hit the front momentarily over 200 metres out, kept on same pace.
Settled in forward of midfield on the rail, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in last few, ran on well down the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, trailed the field to 200 metres, finished off the race well.
Jumped well, settled mainly in midfield, lost position coming onto home turn, baulked behind runners early in straight, kept on under pressure.
Settled in worse than midfield from a wide gate, wide rounding home bend and into straight, ran home one-paced.
Broke well, settled better than midfield, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres. (Lame)

Pressed forward from the widest gate to take up running 1300 metres out, obtained rails run when 2L clear shortly afterwards, narrowly headed approaching home turn, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.

Began well from a wide gate, restrained up with the pace before settling just over 2L back in 2nd on the rail, improved to hit the front over 500 metres out, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly 200 metres out.
Strode forward to be tracking leaders in 3rd, quickened up to draw level with leader 300M, kicked on well to line holding off late challenge of 2nd and 3rd.
Hugged rail from draw 1, settled midfield, held up slightly early straight, had every chance from 350M, tried hard to line but couldn't reel in the winner.

Slightly slow away, taken across behind runners and settled towards the rear, held up early straight, picked up well when gap opened up 200M, nearest finish. (Jockey questioned re his riding early straight.)
Tracked the pace along the rail, kept on evenly turning in, never able to challenge leaders.

Jumped on terms, caught wide no cover 1400M, strode on and led from 900M along the 2-path, joined by rival 350M, run peaked final 150M and weakened to finish 5th. (Jockey questioned re his riding position.)
Reserved behind mid-division, raced keenly early stages, pulled wide to challenge on straightening, made ground final 300M but never close enough.
Never far off from leaders, couldn't finish off well enough entering the straight, out of contention 200M.
Switched off to race at the rear, bustled along 550M, stayed on mildly on straightening, held up 150M and no clear run 100M, not ridden out to the line.
Dropped back for cover, ended up racing 3-wide towards the rear, moved closer to a midfield spot middle stages, driven wide into straight, kept on only one paced to line.

Reined in after the start, slotted into a 3-wide spot in midfield, moved closer to leaders nearing the turn, no cover from 850M, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, peaked on his run 200M and weakened.
Commenced fairly, held up in midfield 4-5Ls back, plodded on same pace from 400M, eased off at the 100M when well beaten.
Turned its head when the start was effected losing significant amount of ground, held up in rear 8Ls behind leader, never near to challenge. (To Barrier Trial.)
Restrained after the start, held up near last in a 3-wide spot 7Ls off the pace, still well back on the corner, failed to respond under pressure, never in contention.
Positively ridden out the gate, led until 900M, scrubbed along to hold position 550M, soon weakened on straightening, finished tailed out (Unacceptable Performance.)
Clean jump, tracked leaders, 2 away from the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, took the lead near 250M, kept on very strongly to the line.
Made contact on jumping, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back, nearer to the middle of the track, made good progress in the final 400M to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Began well, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back behind the leader on the stands rail, no clear running from near 300M, made good progress when clear final 100M, no threat to the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from gate 14, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed some response until blocked near 150M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, near to the stands rail, hard ridden 300M, peaked shortly thereafter, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently on the stands rail, ridden after passing 300M, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced in midfield at the middle of the track, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, made little progress in the final 400M.
Made contact on jumping, raced at rear in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 500M, finished off evenly.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced in the middle of the track, 4 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 500M, only showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (Lame right front leg.)
Hampered shortly after start, raced behind midfield, 2 to 3 away from the stands rail, commenced move after passing 500M, only showed limited response, peaked 250M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, positioned in midfield, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield, near to the stands rail, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out 450M, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.

Slowly away, raced 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, closer on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 250M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, closer on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, crowded near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail 1000M, travelled keenly and checked off heels near 700M, angled out after passing 500M, no clear running in straight, not able to be properly tested.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Moderately away, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, finished off one pace.
Began smartly from a wide draw, showed good speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 to 4 wide at rear, found cover near 900M but still 3 wide, angled out turning in, weakened early in straight.

Commenced well, raced 2W, 3Ls or so back, moved closer after entering the back straight, 3W from 700M, challenged the leader on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line, scored by a narrow margin.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 12 lengths back, sent forward after entering the back straight, 2 wide in midfield on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, sent forward after passing 700M, 3 wide in midfield on turn, closed off well to take a place.

Away with them, positioned on rail, slightly better than midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 400M, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter to make frame.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, last turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, ran on evenly until final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, sat a length behind the leader, saved ground to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 3 wide turning, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled just off the leaders, 2 wide, drifted away 200M to score.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, closed off strongly when clear.
Pushed early, took cover in front of midfield, 2 wide, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 100M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield along the rails, blocked most straight, not tested.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up at the back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 200M, held up 100M.
Slow away, at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased at start, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 600M, issued challenge near 150M, finished strongly.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort passing 500M, responded nicely in the straight.
Taken back at start, improved passing 700M, shared lead in 3 wide position rounding the Home Turn, worked home solidly.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort near 500M, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Sent forward with nice early speed, settled behind leaders, made up some ground near 50M.
Slow to begin and raced at tail, fought hard in the straight, gained some ground passing 50M.
Raced towards rear on rail, asked for effort but only one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, passing 1000M was left racing wide and without cover, improved near 600M, gave ground passing 50M.
Jumped nicely, ridden along to take lead, placed pressure passing 500M, gave ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, tried hard but only limited response in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover in early stages, near 1000M improved to outside the lead, weakened passing 100M.
Raced midfield, widest on straightening, weakened near 150M.

Shifted across from outside gate to get soft run in midfield on rail. Appreciated strong mid-race tempo, 5L from lead at half-way. Stayed hard on inside rail in straight, made continual headway, striking lead at the 100m.

Steadied, raced second last in early stages. Improved position from half-way, racing wide, 1L from lead passing the 400m. Shifted in at 275m, assumed lead shortly after, continued in lead until passed at 100m. Clear of 3rd.

Crowded shortly after start & taken back to last. Ridden with whip nearing half-way when over 9L from fast lead. Continued to be hard ridden & was clear last on straightening before making significant late headway to 3rd.

Held the rail, racing leaders back early before shuffled to midfield. Raced on leaders back once again when 2.5L from lead entering final section. Badly crowded at near the 250m before finishing off fairly in last furlong.

Strode forward to lead early before being headed & racing on leaders back from the 1000m mark. Moved closer to lead on straightening before being badly crowded & unbalanced at 275m. Yielding a few lengths thereafter.

Didn't have early speed and drifted back to third form last on rail. Continued rearward, 4.5L from lead entering final section. Moved wider approaching the bend but could only maintain margin in straight.

Steadied and raced worse than midfield away from the rail in early & middle sections. Hard ridden passing the 500m before being pushed very wide on cornering. Didn't really run on in straight & was never a factor.

Steadied leaving straight & shifted across to good position in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide to improve approaching 500m before being forced wider on cornering. Gave little after straightening & was well beaten.

Ridden forward, racing outside lead before improving to lead after the 1200m. Very fast third section when racing over 1L clear in middle stages. Joined in lead at 275m, badly hampered shortly after & dropped out in last 150m.

Enjoyed nice run away from rail, one pair behind leaders. Hard ridden passing the 500m to shift three wide and improve before cornering 3.5L from lead. Yielded substantial ground in the straight & was well beaten.

Ridden forward after the start to race forward, worked hard to improve to 3rd, one horse away from rail approaching 1000m. Began yielding ground approaching the 450m & was beaten before straightening. Eased down in straight.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off very strongly to score. (Minor laceration to the right hind fetlock.)

Began well, checked off heels near 1600M, raced 2 wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 850M, took the lead 750M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, bumped near 1500M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.

Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, bumped near 1500M, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just missed 3rd.
Began well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 1050M, headed near 850M, 2nd on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after passing 850M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1050M, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear early, 3 wide after entering the back straight, angled out 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stage, hard ridden after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.

Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1500M, sat outside to the leader after the first turn, allowed rival to cross 750M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back and raced at the rear, 2 wide, worked home nicely to score by 3/4L.
Awkward start and lost ground, in behind midfield along the rail, burst through late to take 2nd despite crowded at 50M and raced tight prior to the line.
In the box-seat, stayed on well until straightened by rider at 50M, caught late and missed 2nd.
Taken back, in worse than midfield, 2 wide, switched widest in straight, closed off nicely to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, headed approaching 50M then bumped, couldn't be ridden out thereafter. (Lame right front)
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, closed off fairly despite crowded at 50M.
Crowded start, recovered to be in font of midfield, left wide and without cover at 600M, closed off okay.
Awkward start, sat outside lead until shuffled back at 600M, continued one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, stayed on until running into trouble near 50M.
Midfield but trapped wide initially, improved to share lead by 600M, weakened gradually from 200M.
In midfield, 2 wide, one paced and was awkward to heels at 100M.
Eased and raced at the rear, no clear running in the early part of the straight, saved minor ground. (Bled from both nostrils)

Jumped fairly from the one draw settling just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, travelled keenly when pace slackened in back straight, switched out for a clear run over 200 metres out and gained upper hand close to home.

Soon recovered from a moderate start from a wide gate improving steadily wide in back straight to join the leaders on home bend, gained slender advantage under pressure 200 metres out only to be caught close to home.
Broke well but soon dropped to midfield in 7th, switched wide turning for home, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Settled worse than midfield from a wide gate, came under pressure and wide entering home straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, settled just off the pace in 2nd before hitting the front narrowly entering home straight, found no extra when headed 200 metres out.
Broke well and ridden forward from a wide-ish gate to lead with a steady pace on the rail passing the 1000 metres, headed coming onto home turn and steadily faded.
Jumped awkwardly and stumbled dropping to behind midfield in 8th despite niggled along, remained similar on the rail to home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th within 3L of pace, saved ground on inside turning for home, faded gradually under pressure.
Jumped well, shuffled back to 5th over 2L off the pace, gradually faded under pressure after straightening.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, switched wide into home straight, produced good late impression down the centre of the track.
Taken back from the widest gate and trailed the field to home straight, saved ground turning in, found nothing.
Jumped awkwardly, always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Not hurried, raced towards the rear until 500M then switched out making smooth headway on outside, hit lead passing 250M, drew right away to win by dominant margin.
Began awkwardly, settled last 6Ls off the pace, driven along 450M, wide into straight, stayed on to go 2nd 50M, no threat to runaway winner.
Held up in midfield, 4Ls off the pace at 800M, made rapid headway on outside from 550M to join leaders, kept on steadily to line, not winner's pace over final 200M, lost 2nd 50M.
In mid-division, caught wide no cover from 1100M, made his move 550M, vied for lead until 200M, one paced final stages.
Shifted across behind runners, towards the rear 5Ls back, shuffled back to last 650M, ran on mildly in the run home, never a threat to the runaway winner.
Pressed forward, led passing 1300M, taken on by rivals 400M, fought and stayed in contention until 200M then faded towards the line.
Niggled along to be tracking leaders along the 2-path on settling, shuffled back to midfield spot 500M, battled on to 150M, no extra final stages.
Hugged rail from 1500M, tracked leaders to the straight, fought hard to keep up with rivals early straight, run ended 150M and weakened.
Settled down behind midfield along the inside, kept to inside on straightening, failed to respond to pressure, no impression from 250M.

Crowded for room on jumping, caught wide no cover and raced keenly from 1300M, strode forward to race outside leader, first to come under pressure inside 500M, weakened badly to finish tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out after passing 600M, raced tight early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to score.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, angled out after passing 550M, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, commenced move after passing 550M, took the lead near 250M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover, slightly behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, made some headway in straight.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 250M, kept on evenly to final 50M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from gate 12, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield early, 3 wide after passing 1000M, moved closer in the middle stages, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, wider turning in, made little progress in straight. (Bled.)
Began smartly from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, 2 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.(Bled.)
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, awkwardly placed 650M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, showed nothing in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned 3 wide with cover, 6 lengths or so back, hung out near 800M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden forward, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Hold the rail and led at fast sectionals, raced keenly, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up with the front runners, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to secure a midfield spot, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Very slow away, took rail at back, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 250M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly in straight.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack turn of foot.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Never competitive.
Slow away, soon obtained prominent position, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Took back at start, raced at tail on rail, wide on straightening, quickened near 100M to score.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield, responded strongly in the straight, missed by SH.
Raced behind midfield, gained ground passing 100M, finished nicely.
Jumped well, took lead with nice early speed, asked for effort on straightening, worked home well.
Travelled behind midfield, made ground in the straight, checked closing to the line.
Sent forward to settle outside the lead, fought hard but worked home one-paced.
Settled in box seat, fought hard but gave ground passing 200M.
Raced at rear, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.

Began fast & showed early speed to lead before shifting closer to outside rail. Continued to hold slender lead passing half-way before pulling away inside the final 250m. Held sole challenger in late stages.
Strode forward after the start to race prominently to the lead in the center. Drew away with leader inside the final furlong before being unable to get past. Well clear of third.

Mustered speed & improved along stand side rail to be within 1L of lead at half-way. Drifted further back before coming under heavy riding entering last section. Made steady late headway in final furlong.
Drifted back, slightly worse than midfield passing half-way. Raced 3.5L from lead entering the final section, passed a few in run to line when maintaining that margin relative to winner.
Strode to midfield, two lengths form the lead at half-way. Shifted in when under heavy riding at the 250m before finishing off soundly in final furlong.

Showed speed after start to improve & race within 1L of lead early. Moved up to share lead near the 500m before coming under heavy pressure at 400m. Weakened out in final section. (Unacceptable performance  must trial).

Began awkwardly & then didn't have the pace of others, racing worse than midfield before improving to midfield in middle stages. Came under hard ridding passing the 450m before yielding a few lengths to finish midfield.

Didn't have the early speed of others & raced second from last in early stages. Drifted back to a clear last, 5L from the lead entering final section. Passed a few tiring runners in the run to the line but was well behind.

Bumped & lost ground at start, consequently settling in the center of the rack at the rear. Continued rearward, 4.5L from the lead entering the final section. Made no significant headway in late stages & was well beaten.
Mustered speed after the start & shifted across to race within a length of the lead at half-way. Came under heavy pressure passing the 500m & gave significant ground in last section.

Crowded & stumbled at start, consequently racing rearwards. Moved closer when racing on stand side rail in middle stages. Peaked on effort upon entering the final section & yielded ground in final 300m to be well beaten.
Began fast before being steadied to race behind the leader in early stages. Drifted further back passing half-way before beginning to yield ground from the 450m. Well beaten.

Improved after the start to race in midfield between runners after 250m. Shifted out when yielding ground nearing the 300m before weakening further in final 250m. Tired badly to run last. (Lame post-race).
Moderately away, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 600M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 1000M, bumped near 650M, gradually improved thereafter, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to make frame.

Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly and bumped near 650M, 3 wide thereafter, no daylight early in straight, made good progress once cleared passing 150M, no threat to the first few.

Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside early, switched 3 wide with cover near 1200M, commenced move after passing 700M, very wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.

Hampered at start, recovered quickly, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross after passing 1200M, there to turn, wider from 550M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, headed after passing 300M, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 1000M, travelled keenly 900M, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Out in line, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths or so back, travelled keenly near 700M, very wide turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 600M, very wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, found a 2 wide position near 1000M, commenced move 600M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 600M, shared lead turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 150M.
Taken back, raced in worse than midfield along the rail, closed off nicely in the straight to score by 3/4L.
Settled to race in midfield, wide and without cover, kept on nicely but couldn't match the winner's effort.
Raced in the box-seat, ran on well to the line to take 3rd.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off only fairly.
Sent forward, took rail and led, out of steam and headed approaching 150M.
Travelled in behind midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, stayed on till steadied passing 100M.
Sat behind midfield, along the rail, mostly one paced. (Lame left front)
Went forward, settled to race outside the lead, weakened passing 150M.
Began only fairly, in front of midfield along the rail, showed no turn of foot.
Settled one-out one-back, raced keenly near the 1000M, did not close off. (See Incident Report)
Crowded start, at the tail along the rail, wasn't in it.
Raced closed to the rear, 2 wide, no progress. (See Incident Report)
Taken back, at rear 2 wide, showed nothing. (See Incident Report)
Settled in midfield on the rail, baulked for a run after straightening, quickened well once clear over 250 metres out, asserted authority inside the 100 metres.
Crowded at start, travelled 3-wide and keenly in midfield most of the way to straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from a wide gate to soon take up running, led the field until narrowly headed inside the 200 metres, kept on well to the line.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few to the straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Well there, improved to dispute lead over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Crowded at start, soon recovered to better than midfield 3-wide in 6th just over 2L back, kept on same pace without quickening.
Ridden early before settling one back on the rail, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from the widest gate, gradually taken back towards the rear but remained wide without cover throughout, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, pulling his way forward when steadied and lost position passing the 1000 metres, dropped to last few coming onto home bend, made up good ground near the centre of the track.
Began well before settling 2L back in 5th, hampered over 250 metres out, kept on steadily without threatening.
Travelled in rear of midfield, baulked for a run after straightening, kept on well to the line.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, trailed the field into home straight, ran on and never nearer.
Travelled wide without cover in first few, came under pressure to join the leader entering home straight, soon weakened.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Held up behind mid-division in 7th place, driven wide 500M, picked up strongly to be vying for lead passing 200M, gained upper hand near line.
Settled 3Ls off the pace in midfield, travelled well into straight, responded strongly from 400M, vied for lead with eventual winner over final 200M, just held.
Restrained behind leaders, shifted out passing 600M to commence improving into the race, vied for lead early straight under top weight, couldn't match pace of first 2 final 150M.
Crossed to lead from 1300M, set steady pace until pressed by rivals home turn, fought on but not finishing pace of first 2 inside 200M.
Chased leaders, moved up 4-wide to join leaders 500M, fought on steadily to line but safely held.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, swung widest 500M, stayed on fairly, no threat to leaders.
Held up in midfield along the inside, kept on same pace turning home, never able to challenge leaders.
Settled down behind midfield 4-5Ls back, pushed along 600M but never going the pace to challenge.
Pressed forward, travelled keenly outside leader, faded passing 300M, soon out of contention.
Dropped back to race near last 6-7Ls behind leader, didn't pick up when asked top of straight, never in contention.
Steadied early stages, raced in last 7Ls off the pace, came under pressure 600M, failed to go past a rival.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner.
Quickly into stride, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.

Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few. (Sustained a laceration below the right stifle.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off one pace in straight.
Began well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began very awkwardly and stumbled, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed little response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 12, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from near 900M, travelled well on turn, hit the front near 250M, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line to take a place.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide and without cover at rear, a bit closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Mucus in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, angled out early in straight, showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, only showed limited response, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
