Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, angled out 500M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began smartly from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, closed off well to take a place.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 450M, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased after passing 100M.

Began well from gate 9, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, sent forward after passing 1150M, positioned 2 wide in 2nd in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, peaked near 500M, weakened and dropped to rear turning in, eased final 100M.
Hold the rail and shared the lead easily at good pace, drifted away 200M to score.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, pace good, made ground 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead at good pace, weakened 200M.
At back, along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, no progress in straight.
At back, 2-3 wide, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
Slow away, took rail at back, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, emptied 300M.
Slow away, never progressed at rear.
Never a factor.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, wide rounding the Home Turn, quickened passing 200M to score, trainer questioned.
After start was crowded, settled behind midfield, improved to outside the lead passing 600M, responded solidly in the straight, missed by Neck.
Taken back at start, improved passing 750M, fought well in the straight, finished nicely.
Moderate start then urged along to take lead, fought hard in the straight, finished well.
Settled behind midfield on rail, near 1000M became awkwardly placed and lost ground, near 550M was checked, raced tight near 50M and not fully tested.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made up some ground passing 200M.
Raced in one-off-one-back, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, near 1000M was checked, near 550M was again severely checked, limited response in the straight.
Travelled midfield, tried to improve near 600M, gave ground passing 200M.
Took box seat with nice early speed, near 1000M became unbalanced, near 550M was severely checked and lost ground, weakened passing 150M.
Jumped sharply then sent forward, raced outside the lead, near 450M lay out when giving ground, emptied passing 250M.

Began well, strode forward to lead after start. Increased speed in 3rd section, continuing in lead, broke away with one challenger near turn. Sprinted away from challengers inside final 250m & was soft on line. Dominant.

Strode forward, nice run on leaders back throughout. Continued in 3rd before dropping a length further behind as speed quickened near corner. Finished strongly in straight to snare second, well behind dominant winner.

Strode forward raced second on the outside, at the flanks of leader. Continued in second before racing clear of remainder of field with leader nearing the turn. Couldn't go with dominant winner in final 250m but held third.

Raced in midfield away from rail, 3.5 lengths from lead at half-way. Drifted a length further back from lead entering final section as leaders kicked clear. Maintained margin in dash to line in race not run to suit.

Shifted across to the rail shortly after the start, racing in midfield, three lengths from lead after first section. Drifted a length further back from lead entering final section. Weakened out in final 250m, well held.

Steadied after the first 150m and shifted back to second last away from rail. Moved three wide approaching the 450m to improve before entering final section six lengths from lead. Couldn't make any headway in the straight.

Steadied after the start and shifted across to race at the tail of the field. Was a clear last on cornering, over 7 lengths from lead and was never likely from that position given sectional times and race shape. Not a factor.

Steadied in early stages and shifted behind runners to race third from last on rail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering when six lengths from lead before yielding further ground in the straight, beaten over 10 lengths.

Enjoyed good run away from rail, one pair behind the leaders. Came under heavy pressure approaching the 450m & dropped out of contention from that point, finishing a long last. (Irregular heart rhythm  must trial).

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 900M, sat right behind the leader thereafter, easy run to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began well from gate 12, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, crowded near 1000M, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame. (Blood in trachea.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, hampered near 1000M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress early in straight, not enough room final 100M, not able to be ridden out.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 550M, still well back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 800M, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Began fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Jumped well, settled to race outside the lead, ran on comfortably and won with something in hand.
Travelled in front of midfield, wide but with cover, ran on well for 2nd.
In midfield, 2 wide, bumped at 150M, made nice ground in general.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, made ground steadily.
Prominent, maintained one horse off the rail, was one paced in the straight.
Hampered after start, settled in worse than midfield along the rail, made slight ground.
Taken back, raced at the tail along the rail, improved slightly only.
Eased then raced at the rear, wide but with cover, did not improve.
Travelled in behind midfield, wide but with cover, wasn't in it.
In midfield, along the rail, found nothing in the straight.
Sent forward to take rail and led, weakened approaching 200M. (Bled)
Hard ridden and raced prominently, trapped wide however, faded in straight. (Lame right front)

Broke well, travelled 3-wide in midfield around first bend, shifted slightly backward for cover into back straight, renewed effort rounding home bend and wide into straight, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out.
Jumped fairly, settled in last few, switched out for clear run 200 metres out, finished off the race strongly to just fail to get up on line.

Ridden to first few early stages, tight between runners and drifted back to 4th early in back straight, renewed effort on top of home bend holding good chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled in midfield, carried slightly back on the rail rounding home bend, did not find much room in critical stage of straight, fought on well to the line.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly in forward of midfield, commenced move on outside rounding home bend, held some chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away, settled in rear on the rail, commenced move going up the Rock and continued to circle the field rounding home bend, widest runner turning in, sustained headway to be nearest at finish.

Began well, travelled wide in first few around first bend, improved to join the leader early in back straight and hit the front rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled in better than midfield on the rail, steadied for a run entering home straight, unable to sustain effort under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Taken well back from a wide gate, trailed the field most of the way to home straight, saved ground on inside but baulked for a run until the 200 metres, fought on well to the line.

Failed to muster and soon dropped to midfield, inconvenienced on the rail making first bend, remained towards the rear thereafter, kept on same pace without quickening in home straight. (Lame next day)

Pressed forward from the widest gate travelling wide in midfield rounding first bend, improved to lead and cross for the rail about 700 metres out, led until headed into home straight, dropped out tamely.
Began well, led until ceding advantage for 3rd over 700 metres out, came under pressure entering home straight, hung in badly and lost position early in home straight.
Quickly away to be leading along the fence, quickened up tempo home turn, skipped clear early straight, kept on well final stages to hold runner-up at bay.
Tracked leaders, awkwardly placed 400M-300M, switched lane, stayed on well to be nearest at the line.
Chased leaders along the inside, had every chance turning in, safely held in the run home.
Guided to a rail spot in midfield, just over 3Ls behind the pace at 400M, tried hard but couldn't get any closer to leaders.
Caught wide no cover early stages, strolled forward from 800M to be tracking leaders entering home turn but remained wide, run ended mid-straight, one paced final stages.
Settled near last 5-6Ls off the pace, had plenty to do top of straight, ran on steadily for non- threatening 6th.
Jumped on terms, eased back to race in midfield, couldn't go on in the straight, no impression on leaders.
From widest draw taken back for cover early stages, settled behind mid-division 3-wide, made limited progress final 300M. Never threatened.
Bumped at start, taken back to race near the rear, couldn't finish off on straightening, made no progress.
From wide draw eased back to race in last, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, ran on same pace in straight never able to challenge.
Pressed forward to be racing outside the leader, outpaced passing 400M, gave ground early straight, eased final 150M.
In midfield early stages, raced keenly when racing without cover, moved closer to leaders halfway, couldn't quicken from 400M, plodded home.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead near 100M, kept on very well to hold off the challenger late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at rear, moved closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.

Commenced well, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover behind midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 3 wide turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, slightly improved after passing 450M, very wide into straight, weakened gradually in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 450M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 450M, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently early, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Clean jump, trapped very wide early, slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from near 750M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide in midfield early, steadied off heels near 750M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently on rail, travelled well to turn, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 250M.
Slightly slow out and made contact, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (Mucus in trachea.)
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked slow sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room in straight, dashed well.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Eased at start, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Ridden along to settle behind leaders, commenced to improve near 700M, issued challenge near 200M, worked home strongly to score.
Urged along to take lead, responded solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Raced towards rear, asked for effort passing 700M, wide round the Home Turn and on straightening, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, travelled at back on rail, asked for effort near 400M, gained some ground passing 200M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, made ground in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 600M, worked home one-paced.
Raced at back, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight, lame right front next day.
Raced at tail, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Raced towards rear, tried hard but no response in the straight.
Pushed along to race in box seat, came under pressure passing 700M, gave ground in the straight.
In the early stages was left very wide, passing 900M improved to outside the lead, emptied near 300M.
Raced wide and without cover in early and middle stages in midfield position, faded out passing 300M, must trial.
Settled midfield, weakened near 300M, finished tailed out, must trial.

Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail. Shifted away from the rail when making ground approaching the 400m. Sprinted quickly after straightening, assumed lead inside the 100m and ran away late for very easy win.

Strode forward to assume lead before crossing to rail near the 1300m. Held 1 length margin when leading in middle stages. Passed quickly by winner inside the final 100m before digging in deep to hold second.
Strode forward before racing on leaders back from the 1300m. Stayed close to the inside rail on straightening and battled away strongly to run third.
Pushed forward to race in second away from the rail. Moved closer to the lead on straightening before peaking inside the last furlong and giving a few lengths in late stages.
Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Moved wider approaching the corner when 3 lengths form the lead but failed to make sufficient ground in the straight to challenge.
Shifted across behind runners after the start and raced second from last. Moved wider nearing the turn before balancing the widest runner, 4.5 lengths from lead. Maintained margin in final section.
Steadied and shifted to the rear of the field after the start. Was a clear last passing the 400m, and despite running the second fastest last section, could not play a role in finish.

Failed to muster usual early speed before shifting across to race in midfield away from the rail. Pushed three wide approaching the 400m before peaking on effort on straightening. Gave ground in last 300m.
Shifted across to the rail in the first 100m and raced worse than midfield on rail. Continued near the rear entering the final section before weakening out to be well beaten.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, wider turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced in midfield, found rail near 750M, moved closer on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out 250M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, blocked near 300M, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, unable to obtain clear running until near 150M, made good progress thereafter to make frame.
Away with them, no early speed, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some headway early in straight, peaked near 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on rail, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide for the majority of the race, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.

Away well from gate 11, unable to slot in early, trapped wide in midfield, found a 2 wide spot near 750M, commenced move after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, crowded near 250M, ran on one pace thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, crowded near 200M, eased thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, showed no response early in straight, not ridden out thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide with no cover in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Raced in the box-seat, burst through at about 100M to score by a head.
Settled in one-out one-back position, continued spiritedly to the line for 2nd.
Urged and settled to race outside the lead, ran on fairly to take 3rd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, found no extra and headed near 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, wide but with cover, showed good dash to make ground until about 100M.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, found no daylight in the straight, not tested.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, continued one paced to the line.
Detached early, then was ridden to make up, was one paced in the straight.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear and wide, crowded at 700M, did not improve.
Jumped awkwardly and was detached early, never in it. Must trial.
In midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly, in worse than midfield 2 wide, unbalanced at 800M, never a factor.
Moderate start, ridden to just better than midfield in 4th over 3L off the speed, improved to one back in 3rd entering home straight, sustained effort to hit the front close to home.
Rushed up to hold 2nd on the rail, shifted one back coming onto home bend, switched 2-wide for a run approaching home turn, hit the front upon straightening, swamped close to home.
Ridden to lead, obtained rails run after the first 100 metres, led until headed upon straightening.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, gained closer turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

Gradually drifted towards the rear, hampered and dropped further back 800 metres out, after travelling travelled wide throughout made up good ground inside the final 250 metres to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well but soon dropped to midfield despite ridden along, came wider into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Taken back from the wide gate, trailed the field to the straight, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres, steadied for a stride late.
Travelled wide throughout, gradually dropped towards the rear after the start, produced some late impression in home straight.
Settled some 3L back in 3rd early stages, gained closer to the speed despite joint 4th into home straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon taken across for rails run at the rear of the field, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Crowded after a moderate start, settled just worse than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly into midfield, improved 3-wide to reach 2L 3rd around home bend, folded up quickly inside the final 400 metres after travelling wide throughout.
From low draw got into a trailing position behind leaders, quickened up smoothly 300M, led 200M out, well in control final 100M.
Taken across behind runners from draw 14, raced near last in first half of the race, made early move passing 700M, made good progress to take 2nd close home, held by winner.
Up with early pace, steadied to obtain cover behind leading pair passing 1400M, had every chance turning in, briefly went 2nd inside 100M, edged out to 3rd in photo finish.
Began awkwardly, reserved in midfield 8th spot, ran on steadily without reaching top 3, got up 4th close home.
Caught wide early stages, crossed to share lead on outside from 1300M, kept battling turning in, not pace of rivals over final 200M.
Positively ridden, shared lead on inside from 1300M, battled on early straight, headed near 200M, no extra and weakened badly towards the line.

Dropped back to the rear as expected, over 10Ls off leader on settling, switched out to make early move passing 800M, improved to be 6Ls behind at 400M, couldn't sustain run mid-straight, one paced final stages.

Positioned ahead of midfield, settled in 6th from 1400M, failed to quicken early straight, crowded for room 300M, no impression over final 200M. (Jockey : didn't appear to run out the distance first time on the AWT.
In mid-division 6Ls back, scrubbed along 600M, kept on same pace to line, never able to challenge.
Tracked leaders, 5th on settling, pushed along 600M, run ended 300M, weakened away.
Patiently ridden near last, 10Ls off the pace entering home turn, driven out 500M, made no real progress.
Towards the rear over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, bustled along 600M but didn't go on. Never in the picture.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, came under pressure 550M, failed to respond to riding, soon behind.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear, shuffled further back passing 500M, soon beaten turning in, never involved.
Bumped on jumping, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score by a head.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner on line.

Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed near 450M, angled out early in straight, bumped near 300M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, blocked and snatched up close home.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, showed some response early in straight, bumped near 300M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, one pace in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 850M, 3 wide turning, took the lead near 350M, kept on very well in straight to score.
Taken back from gate 8, positioned on rail behind midfield in the early stages, angled out after entering the back straight, 4 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Slowly away, recovered, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 750M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.

Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked after passing 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, commenced move after passing 800M, 4 wide turning, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 750M, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed near 350M, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to 800M, challenged by rivals on turn, headed near 350M, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 800M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Took rail easily and led at fast sectionals, drifted away 300M to score with some in hands.
Pressed forward, sat off the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide just behind the front runners, held ground for 3rd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 200M.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Slow away, took rail at back, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Hard ridden but failed to muster, midfield along the fence, never improved.
Never mustered, no progress.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 300M.
Sent forward then raced behind leaders, improved passing 550M, worked strongly in the straight to score.
Took lead with nice early speed, travelled nicely, placed pressure near 400M, worked home solidly, missed by Neck.
Ridden to race outside the lead, asked for effort near 400M, battled hard in the straight, missed by Neck.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 800M, responded nicely in the straight.
Began only fairly then was crowded for room, near 1500M was checked, settled behind midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Raced towards rear, placed pressure near 700M, gradually made ground in the straight.
Moderate start, raced midfield, worked home one-paced, close to finishing line was steadied away from heels.
Taken back at start then raced behind midfield on rail, kept rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start and raced on rail, improved passing 550M, wide rounding Home Turn and on straightening, no response in the straight.
Jumped well, raced in handy position on rail, niggled passing 800M, weakened passing 200M.
Raced at rear, tried to improve passing 700M but no response, must trial.

Had good passage, better than midfield, racing in second pair passing half-way. Stalked leaders, 2L form lead entering final section. Made continual headway after straightening until snaring lead in closing stages.

Enjoyed soft passage in just better than midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail on cornering, made continual headway until sharing the lead at the 75m before over-run in closing stages. Narrowly beaten.

Ridden forward after the start before shifting across & racing on the leaders back passing the 1300m. Continued to track the leader on straightening before staying close to the rail & grinding away well to be close up third.

Strode forward to be prominent in third away from rail early. Improved passing the 800m to race at flanks of leader. Moved up to share lead inside the last furlong before being overhauled in late stages. Not far behind.

Ridden forward from outside gate obtaining lead at winning post, then shifting across to rail passing 1300m. Continued 1L lead before being joined passing 800m. Held lead until being joined inside last furlong. Close behind.
Not bustled and held rail position in midfield, 4 lengths from lead at half-way. Stayed close to rail on cornering, before shifting out at the 250m and making up a few lengths to not be beaten far.
Steadied and shifted across to midfield, racing 4 lengths from lead at half-way. Moved a length closer entering the final section before peaking on effort & only maintaining margin in final 250m.

Eased after the start before shifting across, worse than midfield. Improved slightly in second section before coming under heavy riding passing the 400m. Made up a few lengths in last section but still beaten over 3L.

Eased after the start & shifted back to second last passing winning post. Continued rearward, conceding 6.5 lengths entering the final section under heavy riding & couldn't make sufficient ground to be a factor.
Reared at start & lost significant ground before improving along the rail to settle with 4 behind passing the 1200m. Pushed along from the 500m & was never a threat beaten around 5L.

Bumped & unbalanced at start before steadying & shifting behind runners to last. Continued at the back, under heavy pressure, 9L from lead entering final section before weakening out further in straight. (Lame post-race).

Bumped & unbalanced after start before steadying passing the winning post to race second from last. Stumbled when ridden along in last position near the 450m, before being eased out of the race shortly after. (Must trial).
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position to turn, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 2nd.
Clean jump, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, just missed 3rd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 350M, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, found cover near 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a little bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, half length back, same position to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 3 wide, better than midfield, no cover after passing 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in the box-seat, continued on nicely in the straight, scored by a neck.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, ran on gamely to take 2nd.
Sent forward, took rail and led, kept going until weakened inside final 100M.
Asked and settled outside the lead, ran on until flattened passing 100M.
In front of midfield along the rail, travelled keenly in the middle stages, ran on one paced.
Travelled in behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Raced just in behind midfield, 2 wide, closed off fairly to the line.
Crowded start, raced at the rear along the rail, improved slightly. (Lame left front)
Eased after start, raced at the tail along the rail, closed off fairly only. (See Incident Report)
In one-off one-back position, lost ground in straight, not competitive.
At the tail, 2 wide, swung widest in straight, saved no ground.
Sat towards the rear, 2 wide, did not feature.
Settled well behind and waited with, commenced move rounding home bend and widest into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to just get up on line.
Settled just over 3L off the pace in 4th and then slightly closer up in 5th, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, hit the front narrowly 100 metres out only to be pipped at post.
Began well from the one draw, settled some 4L back in 5th on the rail, commenced move over 600 metres out reaching 2nd into the straight, held every chance but outsprinted close to home.
Travelled in midfield on the rail, saved ground on inside entering home straight, fought on steadily under pressure but narrowly missed the place-getters.
Taken back for cover in just worse than midfield, commenced move on top of home bend and wide into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Ridden up to 3rd on the rail, settled about 2L off the pace in back straight, came to challenge under pressure entering straight holding every chance until finding no extra inside the final 100 metres. (Lame)
Jostled at the start but taken well back from a wide gate, saved ground on inside making final bend, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from a wide gate eventually taking up running 2-wide over 800 metres out, led the field until finding no extra under pressure just inside the 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled 2-wide mainly in midfield in 6th, switched out for a run entering straight, ran home one paced.
Jumped fairly settling in last few, saved ground on the rail turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.

Pressed forward from the widest gate to lead over 1200 metres out, travelled awkwardly before ceding advantage for 2nd early in back straight, held similar position until finding no extra on straightening.

Placing: PU
Comment: Settled in last few, dropped out from the 600 metres. (Bled)
Drifted back to obtain cover early, settled near last, had ground saving run along the inside, improved to 8th at 400M, quickened through narrow gap 150M to lead close home.
Held up behind mid-division about 5Ls off the pace, made forward move along 3-path middle stages, challenged for lead 200M, not pace of winner final stages.
Scrubbed along early stages to take up handy spot, early move 600M to challenge for the lead, stayed in contention until nearing 100M, fought on to hold 3rd.
Settled down midfield along the inside, switched out 600M to challenge, chased on steadily to go 4th close home.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, never far away from leaders, bustled along 550M, battled on without threatening.
Jumped well, crossed to the lead passing 1600M, joined by rival 1100M, quickened up tempo 600M, ran on well early straight, headed 150M, weakened.
From draw 12 steadied early stages to obtain cover, crept closer passing 600M, ran on fairly upon straightening, made no impression.
Reserved in midfield, 4-5Ls off the pace on settling, shuffled back to near rear 600M, switched out 350M to challenge, stayed on only fairly.
Driven early stages to be tracking the pace, held 3rd until 650M, soon pushed along, run ended 250M, faded.
Slow to begin, ended up racing in last 9-10Ls off the pace, couldn't close off over final 300M.

Began awkwardly, settled down behind midfield, pushed wide back-straight, under serious pressure home turn and already beaten top of straight. (Jockey : unable to offer explanation for disappointing performance.)
Caught wide early stages from draw 11, rolled forward to join leader 1100M, came under pressure 600M and struggled to hold his position, was a spent force turning for home.

Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside early, got cover after passing 800M, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M, finished off well to score by a neck.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide early, found rail near 750M, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, blocked near 100M, not able to be properly tested.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 600M, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out near 600M, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from 800M, 4 wide turning in, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, unable to obtain clear running in straight, crowded near 50M, not able to test properly.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off one pace in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 wide turning in, showed no response in straight, eased final 150M.
Slow away, under pressure throughout, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Shared lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 50M overhauled.
Slow away, at back, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground.
Eased back, favoured by the fast pace, held up badly 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Pushed to share the lead at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
At back, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, soon gave ground 400M.
Pressed forward, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Jumped nicely, near 950M was checked, settled in handy position, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Ridden along then race behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, asked for effort passing 500M, gained nice ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, made ground passing 100M.
Urged along to settle midfield on rail, placed pressure and worked home one-paced.
Began only fairly, travelled midfield, lay out in the early part of straight, finished one-paced.
Pushed along and raced outside the lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Jumped sharply, ridden along from widest barrier then took lead passing 900M, tried hard but weakened near 150M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure but no response, blood trachea.
Taken back and raced at tail, asked for effort but no response in the straight.
Sent forward and raced in box seat, passing 300M was checked and near 100M was again checked, after that faded out in the straight.
Showed speed after the start to stride to lead. Continued in the lead on straightening before racing 2 lengths clear inside the final 100m. Won with something extra in hand late.

Hard ridden after start before improving to race one pair from lead. Hard ridden when coming off bit past 750m. Continued to be hard ridden on cornering before digging deep in the straight to snare second in the last 50m.
Ridden hard in first furlong before shifting across to the rail in midfield. Raced just over 3L from the lead after the first section. Closed off nicely in the straight to finish close behind.
Began awkwardly before mustering speed to race outside the leader. Kicked clear with the leader after straightening before peaking on effort inside the last 150m. Close up, solid debut.

Steadied after the start & shifted across from wide barrier to race third from last away from rail. Conceded significant margin on cornering before finishing strongly in the last section from disadvantaged position.

Steadied from wide barrier & shifted across behind runners settling second last, 6.5 lengths from lead after first section. Continued at rear, a long way from winner before making creditable late headway from poor position.

Didn't have the early speed of others & raced just worse than midfield, away from rail. Conceded over six lengths from leader entering the final section before making up steady late ground to finish not far behind.

Began well before being steadied right back to last after first furlong. Became detached shortly after, trailing the field by some 10 lengths approaching the corner. Halved margin in last section but was never in race.

Began only moderately before holding the rail & racing just worse than midfield, 5 lengths from lead after first section. Hard ridden approaching the bend & couldn't improve on 6 length margin in last section.

Ridden forward before racing three wide without cover in early stages. Moved closer to the rail near the 600m when 2 lengths from lead. Hard ridden on bend before weakening out in final 300m. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Bumped at the start & lost ground before improving to race in midfield away from rail. Travelled well on straightening before weakening out of contention in the last section. (Irregular heart rhythm post-race, must trial).

Began well before steadying and shifting across to race on leaders back after 150m. Was 3.5 behind the leader entering the final section before yielding significant ground in the final 300m. Well beaten.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide turning, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Away well, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight, just missed frame.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 700M, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly. (Mucus in trachea.)

Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, moved closer after passing 1000M, 2 wide on turn, angled out 550M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on rail, angled our near 800M, finished off evenly.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 650M, kept to inside early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned on rail in midfield, awkward around turn, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, sat right behind the leader, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Settled to race in the box-seat, peeled away from 150M, scored comfortably by 1-3/4L.
Awkward start, in behind midfield along the rail, saved ground and closed off nicely to take 2nd.
Was prominent, 2 wide, continued on fairly for 3rd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, headed passing 200M, showed no turn of foot.
Eased back, raced at the tail along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Settled just in front of midfield, along the rail, was one paced.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, closed off fairly to the line.
Raced at the rear, 2 wide, improved slightly.
In midfield, along the rail, was one paced in the straight.
Pushed before settling to race at the rear, 2 wide, did not improve.
Sat just in front of midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot and faded out.
In midfield, 2 wide, showed nothing in the straight.
Broke well, settled one back on the rail, came to challenge after straightening, ran on to gain upper hand final strides.

Jumped only fairly from the widest gate, took up running and crossed for rails run about 1300 metres out, led until joined on top of home bend, went over 1L clear after straightening only to be caught close to home.
Held up in midfield on the rail, slightly worse when pace quickened around home bend, snuck back up to 6th some 3L back by saving ground on the inside turning in, ran on quite well.
Ridden early before settling wide in midfield, drifted backward rounding home bend and became last into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Slow to begin settling in rear on the rail, shuffled back to last rounding home bend, saved ground on inside turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in forward of midfield, kept on steadily without quickening in home straight.

Niggled at in last few dropping to last about 1400 metres out, made rapid progress round the field on home bend, fought on steadily from towards rear into home straight but found no extra closing stages.
Raced keenly while taken back to last few when wide without cover, made swift progress to join the leaders rounding home bend, kept on in straight until fading gradually inside the final 300 metres.
Travelled wide in last few, made swift progress rounding home bend to be 4-wide with leaders into straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
Well there, gradually weakened after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Settled just worse than midfield, raced keenly approaching home bend and lost position, one of last few into straight, ran home one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled just ahead of midfield, 6th at 800M, chased hard turning for home, got up just before line.
Hard pressed early stages, settled just outside leader, kept responding to pressure in straight, wrestled the lead nearing 100M, caught by winner close home.
From draw 10 slotted into a 2-wide spot in midfield, 4Ls to make up top of straight, ran on steadily over final 300M to go 3rd near line, held by first two.
Went forward, raced keenly after obtaining the lead early stages, kept on well early straight, caught nearing 100M, faded to 4th.
Chased leaders along the inside, looked to have more to offer but got held up from 200M, not properly tested to the line.
From wide draw dropped back to last about 9Ls behind leader, brought wide to challenge, still last at 200M, closed off fastest to be nearest at the line.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, loomed to challenge top of the straight but run ended passing 200M, one paced to the line.
Settled down midfield, lay out home turn and in the straight, kept on same pace to line.
Towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, made some progress on straightening but never able to challenge leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled near last along the inside, failed to quicken when asked from 450M.
Crowded for room on jumping, soon taken across to the fence and settled behind midfield, lacked further response on straightening, never threatened.
Close up tracking the pace setters, came under serious pressure 500M out, dropped right away on straightening.
Held up behind midfield 5-6Ls from leaders, couldn't quickened early straight, got tired passing 200M, faded to last.

Jumped well from gate 10, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1300M to race in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, hard ridden 400M out, took the lead near 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Quickly into stride, showed good speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner 150M, stayed on for 2nd. (Minor laceration to the right hind pastern.)
Began well from gate 1, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after passing 800M, wider turning in, bumped early in straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, bumped early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.

Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Mucus in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened after passing 150M. (Lame right hind leg with a haematoma over its right shoulder.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight, finished tailed out. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Lame right hind leg next day.)
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd on line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.

Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, commenced move after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, positioned 3 wide better than midfield, raced tight near 900M, no cover on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, travelled keenly after passing 800M, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, blocked near 200M, ran on evenly when clear final 100M.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 1100M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Moderately away, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened after passing 200M, eased shortly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Commenced well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, found rail near 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (Lame right front leg.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Small wound to the right hind pastern.)
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, checked near 750M and 550M, 9 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, checked off heels near 200M, eased thereafter.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail 700M, awkwardly placed 450M, hard ridden after turning in, only showed limited response, then shifted in abruptly near 200M, eased thereafter.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily around the field 400M to score.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Box seat, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well until 100M emptied.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight, on heels 100M, made steady ground.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Eased at start, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on ok.
Midfield along the fence, emptied 250M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Travelled in box seat, asked for effort passing 300M, responded strong in the straight to score.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, rider dropped right rein near 100M, made up some nice late ground, missed by Neck.
Took lead with nice early speed, placed pressure passing 400M, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, gained solidly ground passing 150M.
Near 900M was very awkwardly placed and lost running, settled in front of midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Sent forward, wide and without cover until 650M, took rail passing 500M, gave ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, raced at tail on rail, improved passing 700M, responded well in the early part of straight, one-paced passing 150M.
Jumped OK then failed to muster speed despite ridden along, travelled at rear, one-paced in the straight.
Slow to begin, settled midfield on rail, niggled near 400M, gave ground passing 200M.
Ridden forward, race behind leaders, weakened in the straight.
Jumped well, settled behind midfield, near 650M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, faded out in the straight.
Enjoyed good run in transit on the leaders back throughout. Stayed hard on the inside rail before sprinting through to share lead at the 250m. Drew away in last furlong for cozy win.

Shifted back to second last away from rail after start. Steadied from heels approaching the corner when 5 lengths from lead. Shifted out to clear running at the 250m before finishing strongly to snare second in last stride.
Steadied after the start and shifted back to race in last position on the rail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before making steady headway in the last 300m to be not far behind winner.

Shifted across behind runners after the start & raced worse than midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail passing the 1000m. Shifted the widest runner on cornering before making late ground to be close behind.

Slow to begin before shifting to the rail & improving to midfield. Three lengths from lead entering the final section, before shifting out at 300m when making ground. Worked home fairly in final 150m, not be beaten far.

Strode to midfield before being left wide without cover from the 800m. Improved position in middle stages, before entering the final section 1L from lead. Bumped heavily on straightening & yielded a few lengths thereafter.

Strode forward before getting nice run away from rail, one pair behind lead. Shuffled a pair further back at half-way, before moving wider approaching the 450m. Moved closer nearing final 200m before emptying out late.

No early speed & drifted back worse than midfield. Moved 3 wide with cover after the 1000m before ridden hard to improve nearing half-way. Moved closer when racing wide nearing turn before yielding a length in the straight.

Raced wide in midfield early before improving position to race outside lead passing the 900m. Shared the lead from the 800m before coming under heavy riding at the 450m. Peaked on run at 250m & gave a few lengths late.

Ridden forward after the start before crossing to the rail passing the 1300m when leading. Challenged near the 850m before sharing lead from that point. Peaked on effort at the 250m before yielding a few lengths thereafter.

Began well, strode forward before racing outside the leader from the 1300m. Crossed nearing the 800m & raced with cover, 1 length from lead. Bumped & unbalanced on straightening before weakening out thereafter. Well beaten.

Drifted rearward after the start when racing wide with cover. Continued rearward 5.5 lengths form the lead at half-way. Was a clear last entering the final section & yielded significant ground in the 400m.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 1350M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, 2 wide turning, showed good response in straight, took the lead 50M, ran on well but headed close home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer on turn, finished off well to make frame.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, peaked on run near 100M, headed and weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress. (Rider dropped right rein near 75M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved closer on turn, showed some response in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race at tail, 11 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, weakened from 600M, eased after turning in.
Raced in box-seat, led outright from 150M, kept on to score. (See Incident Report)
In front of midfield, on rail, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, ran on well for 3rd.
Sat one-out one-back, battled on to the line.
Took cover, in behind midfield, 2 wide, closed off fairly.
Forward and led on the rail, stayed on till weakened at 150M.
Raced close to the rear, 2 wide, saved ground.
Jumped only fairly, midfield on rail, one paced.
Behind midfield, on rail, ran on fairly until late.
Bumped start and taken back, 2 wide, didn't threaten.
Began slowly, remained at rear, on rail, hardly improved.
In midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in straight.
Taken well behind, commenced move 700 metres out, circled the field rounding home bend, widest runner into straight, ran on well to hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.

Taken back towards the rear from a wide draw, lost position approaching the Rock, commenced move rounding home bend, hung in under pressure early in straight, produced good late impassion closing stages.
Ridden to over 2L back in 4th 2-wide, improved to 1L 2nd half-way out, sustained progress to hit the front into straight, headed inside final 200 metres.
Pressed forward to settle on the rail just behind the leader, became 3rd half-way out, saved ground on inside turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
Settled not far off the pace mainly in 4th, dropped to midfield coming onto home bend, kept on same pace without quickening in the run to the line.
Began fairly from a wide gate, ridden to soon take up running, crossed to the rail passing the winning post the first time, led until headed shortly after straightening.
Given reminders after sluggish start, last into straight when saved ground turning in, made short-lived effort inside the 200 metres.
Moderate start from the rail draw settling in midfield, lost position 700 metres out, re-gained midfield on inside turning in, made no impression. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled in midfield to home straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Broke well, awkwardly placed and carried backward to behind midfield around first bend, baulked behind runners after straightening, soon weakened.
Prominent from the outset, travelled strongly outside the leader on straightening, soon took over, drew clear passing 200M, won easily by dominant margin.
From draw 10 dropped back gradually to settle towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, ran on well to take 2nd close home without threatening the easy winner.
Eased back on jumping from widest gate, held up last 6Ls off the pace, widest into straight, closed off well to go 3rd near line.
Slotted into a 3-wide position in midfield, 3.5Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on mildly to just miss 3rd at the line but no impression on runaway winner.
Began awkwardly, soon raced keenly, wide no cover from 650M, in 4th spot making home turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Went forward, established narrow lead 700M, soon headed on straightening, held on to 2nd until final stages, swamped by rivals late.
Began only fairly, held up in midfield along the fence, kept on same speed turning for home, no threat to leaders.
Caught wide behind midfield from draw 11, failed to run on over final 300M.
Never far off, 5th on settling, 3Ls behind at 400M, ran on same pace in straight.
Up with early pace, track leaders from 600M, run ended 200M, no extra and weakened. (Mucus)
Settled down behind midfield but further back than anticipated, 4Ls off the pace 400M, no clear run 250M but failed to quicken after, no threat.
Dropped back to race near last, driven top of straight but gave limited response only, awkwardly placed final stages, not ridden out to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover on turn, finished off strongly to score by a nose.
Began fairly, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.

Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 150M, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take a place.
Away well, raced prominently, took the lead after passing 900M, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 150M, kept on well thereafter to make frame.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 700M, 3/4L back on turn, kept on very well in straight, just missed frame.
Clean jump, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide after passing 500M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, showed no early speed, positioned 4-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
