Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after turning in, easily scored, impressive debut.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight, lost 2nd close home.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly, recovered to sit right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Slowly into stride, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 3 to 4 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to show any response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced very wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily to score.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden early, midfield, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well until 150M emptied.
Hard ridden early, in front of midfield on the fence, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Eased at start, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground 250M.
Settled in midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Eased to rear, took rail, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Very slow away, suited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Raced in front of midfield, quickened passing 200M, worked home strongly to score.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort near 400M, finished solidly, missed by Neck.
Raced towards rear, improved near 500M, responded solidly in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, in the early part of straight had difficulty obtaining clear running, gained nice ground passing 200M.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along after start and settled in one-back-one-off position, shifted out away from heels near 200M, finished one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, near 200M was steadied when disappointed for running, made some ground over concluding stages.
At the start was crowded, then was hard ridden to take lead, tried hard but gave ground passing 150M.
Raced behind midfield, passing 900M was checked, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Travelled keenly outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, near 200M was crowded for room and lost running, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly then taken back, raced at back on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, limited response in the straight.
On jumping was crowded for room, travelled at rear, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
On jumping was crowded for room, raced at tail, wide rounding the Home Turn and widest on straightening, made no ground in the straight.
Wide and without cover throughout in midfield, faded out near 200M.

Improved after first section to race in midfield away from rail in middle stages. Travelled strongly nearing turn, moving closer at the 400m. Sprinted fast to assume lead inside the 250m before drawing away for easy win.

Crowded on jumping before racing to midfield three wide. Steadied & shifted closer to rail by nearing the 1100m. Followed winner into the straight when 3 lengths form lead before closing strongly to snare second.

Ridden forward to be prominent early before being crossed at the 1000m & racing on the leaders back thereafter. Stayed on the rail on straightening, assumed lead at 300m before battling on gamely for 3rd in closing stages.

Steadied & shifted across behind runners from wide barrier, settling second from last. Moved wider when ridden forward to improve from the 600m before cornering very side & making good late ground from difficult position.
Had no early speed and raced in final three horses on the rail. Hard ridden from the 600m before straightening second widest. Finished of reasonably well but was never a winning factor.

Crossed shortly after the start before enjoying good run in midfield on rail. Stayed close to the rail on straightening before being crowded & unbalanced near the 250m. Failed to run on once clear in late stages. (Bled).

Had no early speed & raced worse than midfield away from rail. Hard ridden to hold position passing the 1000m before drifting back to second last at half-way. Maintained margin in final but was never likely.

Began well & strode forward before racing in third on the rail in early stages. Looked to travel strongly when only 1.5 lengths from lead at the 400m before failing to run on in the last 300m. Well held.

Shifted back behind runners after the start, settling a clear last in first section. Continued rearward, third last entering the final section. Passed a few tiring runners in the dash home but was never really involved.

Shifted across after the start to get good position in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide when improving past the 700m. Moved up less than 1 length from lead at the 400m before tiring out quickly in last 250m.
Began well & was ridden forward before getting good position away from rail behind leading pair. Moved up outside the leader on straightening before yielding significant ground in final 250m.

Showed speed after the start to lead, before continuing on to cross to rail approaching the 1100m. Continued over 1 length clear in middle stages before being joined & headed on straightening. Weakened out badly final 300m.

Began awkwardly before racing near the rear between runners. Shuffled back to a clear last passing the 1000m. Was a clear last approaching the turn, 8 lengths form lead & made no impression thereafter, beaten a long way.

Maintained position on the rail, racing in midfield, six lengths form the lead at half-way. Stayed on the inside, 4.5L from lead entering the final section but yielded substantial ground in the last section. Long last.
Towards the rear early stages before taking closer order mid-race, put in a strong challenge final 200M, led final 50M.
Tracked leaders along stands' rail, switched out to challenge nearing 300M, ran on gamely, just held.
Always prominent, hard driven passing 400M, kept on well to the line, just held by first 2.
Held up in midfield, 3.5Ls behind at 400M, kept finding to the line but always held by leaders.
Began awkwardly, sat just off the pace, led 300M out, kept on well until 100M when caught by rivals, faded towards the line.
Missed break, recovered to race in midfield, 2Ls behind at 400M, chased hard but held ground final 100M. (Deemed to have afforded a fair start after Stewards Enquiry.)
Soon crossed and led along stands' rail, pressed along halfway, couldn't hold off pursuers 200M, one paced final stages.
In midfield, bustled along halfway, took time to muster speed, did best work closing stages.
Settled in rear of main group, made minor progress when driven along 400M, never reached leaders.
Held up midfield on outside of group, outpaced from 400M, didn't respond to riding.
Never far off leaders, switched to center of track halfway, couldn't go on under pressure, run ended 250M.
Began awkwardly, soon detached in last, ran past well beaten rivals only. Never in the picture.
Prominent just behind leaders, outpaced halfway, weakened badly final 200M. (Blood in trachea.)
Up with early pace, couldn't hold his spot halfway, soon dropped out and weakened to last.
At rear, wide but with cover, shifted widest on straightening, closed off strongly to score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward, settled one-out one-back, ran on nicely to take 2nd.
Eased and raced behind midfield, wide but with cover, closed off well to the line for 3rd.
Settled in the box-seat, ran on one paced.
At rear, along the rail, made ground, ran on well to the line.
Ridden forward to take rail and led, kept up until weakened at 100M.
Jumped awkward, at rear 2 wide, improved and closed off fairly.
In behind midfield, along the rail, kept on until checked at 200M, not properly tested.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, stayed on until checked and lost running at 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, wide but with cover, did not improve.
Sat in behind midfield, 2 wide, wasn't in it.
In behind midfield initially, improved along the Back Straight, very wide at turn, gave ground gradually.
In midfield, wide but with cover, not competitive.
Prominent but wide throughout, gave ground from on straightening. (See Incident Report)
Began fairly, gradually improved to dispute the lead, hit the front from the tiring leader on straightening, hung on well to the line.

Niggled at early before settling just off the dueling pair of front-runners, just over 2L back turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening. (Reported saddle shifted at the 500 metres)
Jumped fairly, settled behind midfield, some 8L off the speed turning for home, finished off the race well.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail to home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start, ridden along towards the rear, made up late ground inside final 300 metres.
Travelled just better than midfield, some 4L back in 4th into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Bumped at start losing ground, travelled keenly early improving steadily to midfield, made up some late ground in straight.
Ridden to maintain prominent position early, gradually dropped to forward of midfield approaching home bend, ran home one-paced.
Never better than midfield. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in last few, made some late impression down the centre of home straight.
Taken back from a wide gate for rails run, trailed the field to the straight, never nearer.
Ridden positively from the widest gate, soon gained slender lead and gradually obtained 2-wide position coming onto home bend, unable to sustain effort on straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover from the 1100 metres, made no impression in the run to the line.
Tracked leader in a steadily run race, moved up alongside leader 500M and going very well into 300M, quickened up strongly when asked, raced away to win comfortably.
Began well from draw 1, held up in midfield 3-4Ls back, awkwardly placed top of straight, responded well to pressure, got up for 2nd close home but came too late to trouble winner.
Tracked leaders along the fence, driven along 450M, inclined to lay out under pressure but stuck to task well to take 3rd.
In touch behind leaders, had every chance turning in, kept on steadily to the line for moderate 4th.
Jumped on terms, crossed to the lead 1200M setting steady pace, joined by eventual winner from 500M, headed 200M, lost several placings close home.
Held up behind mid-division 6Ls off the pace, saved ground on inside throughout, driven out 300M but not going the pace to challenge leaders.
Began awkwardly, dropped back towards rear 6-7Ls away, stayed on without threat to leaders.
Settled near last, hampered 600M, switched wide to challenge in straight, made minor progress only.
Chased leaders early, shuffled back to midfield position 900M, came under pressure 650M, soon hard driven, kept on same pace to line.
Slow to begin, ended up near last along the fence, failed to run on final 400M.
Settled last 8Ls off the pace, brought wide 600M, ran on only fairly to the line, never in the picture.
Held up in 3-wide spot midfield, wide no cover after 800M, couldn't go on passing 350M, no impression.
Towards the rear of midfield along the 3-path, wide into straight, failed to make ground over final 400M. No danger.
In midfield, checked and dropped towards rear 600M, soon behind on straightening.

Raced in midfield between runners, 4.5 lengths from lead after first section. Moved wider nearing the corner, sprinted fast passing the 400m. Assumed lead at the 150m before drawing away for easy win in closing stages.

Raced worse than midfield away from rail, 6 lengths from lead after first section. Followed winner into corner before balancing 4 lengths form lead. Made continual headway in straight, running into second inside final 50m.
Ridden forward after the start before racing outside the leader. Assumed the lead upon straightening before being headed and passed inside the final 150m. Not beaten far.

Shifted across behind runners after start & raced third from last early stages. Moved wider approaching the corner. Balanced up the widest, 5 lengths form lead before finishing strongly in last section. Not far behind.
Had no early speed and shifted behind runners to race rearward. Continued rearward, 5.75 lengths form lead passing the 400m before finishing strongly over the final 300m to not be beaten far.

Held the rail in midfield, 5 lengths from lead after first section. Moved away from the rail passing 600m before shifting further on straightening. Three lengths from lead entering final section & maintained margin on line.

Crowded & bumped at start before shifting across to the rail, racing worse than midfield. Moved away from rail on cornering before being held up & shifting back inwards. Held margin in final section & was never a real threat.

Strode to midfield before racing three wide without cover in early & middle stages. Continued wide before being hard ridden nearing turn. Over four lengths from lead entering final section & held margin in straight.

Held the rail after the start and raced on the leaders back. Checked near the 1500m losing a length. Continued on rail, 2.5 lengths from lead entering final section before weakening out in final 300m. Well held.

Pushed forward passing the 1600m before racing wide, without cover in middle stages. Improved position passing 1000m, racing into third near the 800m. Peaked on effort shortly after straightening & weakened out thereafter.

Ridden forward before obtaining trailing position behind leading trio away from rail. Raced tight at 400m before being crowded & losing ground at 200m. Not tested last furlong but didn't look to be a threat prior to incident.

Gathered speed after start before racing third, wide outside two leaders. Steadied & shifted closer to rail approaching the 1300m. Hard ridden on cornering ,2 lengths from lead before weakening out significantly thereafter.
Shifted back behind runners & raced at the tail of the field. Was a clear last on cornering, around 10 lengths from lead and made no ground in last section. Well beaten.

Ridden forward after the start & assumed the lead after 250m. Propped & lost momentum near 1500m before regaining the lead shortly after. Headed in lead upon straightening before weakening significantly in last section.
Jumped on terms, sat just ahead of midfield, chased well on straightening, hit led 150M and fought off the persistent challenge from 2nd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 6 lengths back on the inside, 2 wide turning, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out near 500M, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Began well from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.

Shifted in at start, sat 1-2Ls behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly and checked off heels near 850M, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M then bumped 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, bumped near 100M, weakened thereafter.

Commenced well from gate 12, showed good speed to take the lead, allowed rival to take the lead near 1000M, travelled well on turn, retook the lead early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 600M, blocked early in straight, showed minor response thereafter, weakened after passing 150M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, just ahead of midfield, slightly taken back after passing 1100M, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened gradually after turning in, eased final 150M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide at rear, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced prominently but trapped wide early, sent forward after passing 1150M, took the lead near 1000M, 2 wide on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well on turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, finished off well to take a place.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, made good progress thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Jumped well from the widest gate, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, commenced move after passing 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover, just ahead of midfield, wider turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Fast into stride, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing effort 300M.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, however trapped 3 wide, moved forward 1200M to take advantages of the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, checked badly 250M.
Pressed forward, checked early, box seat, lack room most straight, ran on fairly.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, took cover, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed fairly.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, quickened when asked for effort passing 300M, scored unchallenged.
Pushed along after start, raced in front of midfield on rail, responded solidly passing 200M.
Travelled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 200M.
Jumped well then ridden along to take box seat near 800M, fought well in the straight, blood trachea.
Moderate start, settled at rear, made up some late ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly then taken back, settled at tail, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield, at 200M was crowded and hampered, finished one-paced.
Raced in handy position, after 600M was buffeted between runners, gave ground passing 200M.
Settled behind midfield, held up in the early part of straight, near 300M was checked when attempting to improve, continued to be held up near 150M.
Began only fairly, raced at back on rail, limited response in the straight.
Urged along for some distance to take lead near 800M, faded out passing 100M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn and straight, held up over final 100M.
Pushed along to race outside the lead, faded out near 200M.
Raced in front of midfield, severely checked near 850M then was left wide and without cover, checked again at 200M, finished tailed out.
Enjoyed nice run in midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail just prior to straightening, sprinted fast passing the 350m, assumed lead passing the 200m mark before dashing away for easy victory.
Began fast and ridden hard to assume lead, maintaining 1 length break passing the 800m. Headed at the 200m mark before battling away well to hold second. Winner well clear.
Had no early speed and consequently raced at the tail of the field. Was a clear last on cornering, some 6 lengths from lead before making solid late headway to run into third in closing stages.

Not bustled after the start and raced in midfield between runners, 5.5 lengths from lead at the 800m. Held up approaching the 300m before getting clear shortly after & finishing off well in the last 250m.

Obtained good position in midfield away from rail. Move three deep passing the 600m before entering final section just over 2 lengths form lead. Worked home fairly to finish just behind placed horses.
Showed good early speed before racing in second behind the leader. Continued on the leaders back in the last section & battled on fairly well in closing stages. Only 1 length behind second.
Had no early speed before improving to midfield on the rail. Three lengths off lead entering the last section, shifted wider at the 300m but finished off only moderately in final furlong.

Raced in midfield but was very wide before improving from the 1100m to race outside the leader passing the 850m. Moved closer to lead nearing the corner before peaking on effort at the 250m & yielding ground thereafter.
Steadied after the start and shifted across to race worse than midfield between runners. Continued rearward, 5 lengths off lead on cornering & made no impression in final section.

Shifted across after the start & raced worse than midfield away from rail, 7L from lead at the 800m. Was held up after straightening & again on multiple occasions in the last 300m. Well beaten but should have finished closer.

Raced wide in midfield, before being left without cover from the 850m when five lengths from lead. Continued wide in middle stages before cornering 3.5L behind. Weakened out in last section after covering extra ground.
Steadied after the start and raced in final trio between runners. Moved wider nearing the corner before balancing a clear second last. Made no headway in last section & was well held.

Steadied after the start & taken back to rear. Improved position when racing wide & with cover in the middle stages. Five lengths off lead passing 400m but failed to run on & was well beaten. (Must trial-poor performance).
Pushed forward to race third away from rail before getting cover 1,1 near the 850m. Was hard ridden passing the 500m before yielding significant ground in the last section. Well held last.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, found cover after passing 900M, same position on turn, angled out near 450M, finished off evenly.

Jumped with them, raced 2w in midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 4 lengths or so back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 12, taken back to race at tail, hard ridden after passing 700M, still 7 lengths behind the leader at 400M, finished off well without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, a bit closer in the middle stages, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 900M, carried wider turning in, showed limited response in straight.

Out in line, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide, just ahead of midfield early, sent forward after passing 1100M, settled 2 wide in 2nd from 900M, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, no clear running near 300M, failed to make any progress when clear thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Sat box-seat, sprinted home nicely after getting a saloon passage on the inside rail, scored by 3/4L.
Hard ridden to sit outside lead, kept rolling to the line to take 2nd.
Pushed hard to take rail and led, showed no kick and headed by winner at 200M.
Behind midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly.
Eased back, at tail on rail, closed off fairly late.
In midfield, 2 wide, kept up until weakened gradually passing 200M.
Bumped start, then eased back, at rear 2 wide, was never a match.
Settled in 4th over 6L off the pace early in back straight, commenced move passing the 900 metres, joined the lead 3-wide approaching home straight, asserted authority shortly after straightening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend to be just off the pace turning in, fought on steadily under pressure but unable to peg back the winner the length of the straight.

Began well setting over 4L back in 3rd early stages, gained closer to the tiring pacemaker approaching home bend, switched off heels for a run inside the final 300 metres and fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, commenced move and the widest runner rounding home bend, made up good ground under pressure to reach 2.5L 3rd briefly inside the 200 metres, found no extra closing stages
Taken back from a wide gate and trailed the field to home straight, commenced move approaching the home turn, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled in last few, saved ground on inside turning in, did not find much room over 200 metres out and forced to check shortly afterwards, never recovered.
Ridden early to vie for lead, took up running on top of first bend, led until headed upon straightening, folded up quickly.
Towards the rear early stages, gained closer to pace approaching home bend when travelling 4-wide, folded up quickly upon straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Jumped moderately from the one draw but quickly recovered to the front, ceded advantage for trailing position on top of first bend, came to challenge approaching home straight but only found nil, weakening when hampered 200 metres out.
Positively ridden, crossed to the lead 900M, led at good pace, drew away from field 350M, kept on strongly for a dominant win over much higher rated rivals.
Close up in 4th, driven 350M, moved up to 2nd 200M, chased hard to line but not making progress on the runaway winner. Promising return nevertheless.
Held up towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace home turn, ran on well to go 3rd nearing 100M.
Taken back from widest draw to race in the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, closed off fastest down outside to claim 4th before line.
Dropped back, settled near last along the fence, made mild progress final 400M, no impression on leaders.
Jumped on terms, settled down behind mid-division, kept on evenly final 300M. Encouraging return after a long absence.
Away well, held up in midfield 4Ls off the good pace, held ground in the run home. Never able to challenge.
From draw 12 settled 3-wide behind midfield, no cover from 900M, kept on same pace in straight, never reached leaders.
Began fairly, rushed forward to be racing just off the leader, gave brief response early straight, lost 2nd 200M, weakened towards the finish.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4Ls back, came under pressure when pace quickened rounding the home turn, found disappointingly little when asked turning in, no impression on leaders.
Dropped back to race near the rear, still over 6Ls to make up 400M, failed to make ground in the straight.
Chased leaders in 3rd, couldn't go on early straight, dropped away rapidly passing 300M to finish last, tailed off.

Placing: PU
Comment: Pulled himself up after travelling a short distance, took no part in the race.
Commenced well, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter, took 2nd last stride.
Began awkwardly and bumped, unable to slot in, trapped very wide and without cover, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, lost 2nd last stride.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, showed good speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well early in straight, hard ridden after passing 200M, peaked near 100M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced very wide at rear, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight. (Rider dropped whip near 300M.)
Bumped start, raced wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 800M, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide, just ahead of midfield, checked near 750M, 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move from near 650M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 700M, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to take a place.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground to 600M, 2 to 3 wide turning in, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, sat 1to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide turning in, unable to obtain clear running until final 50M, made some progress thereafter.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out near 500M, made some progress early in straight, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, wider after passing 700M, closer turning in, one pace in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, crowded near 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.

Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.

Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, 3 wide and moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, hard ridden from 400M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, sent forward after passing 1050M, settled 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back in the middle stages, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly. (Bled.)
Began smartly, sat 2 wide better than midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Roarer.)

Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear early, 3 wide from near 900M, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (Lame right front leg next day.)

Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 6 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 200M and 100M, ran on one pace. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Hard ridden to take the rail, clocked slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on strongly 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, checked 450M, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, run ended 100M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the slow sectionals, held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Slow away, at back on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, ran on ok.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, raced ungenerously, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, never competitive.
Took lead with nice early speed, responded strongly when asked for effort, scored by 5L.
Sent forward, raced behind leaders, ran on well in the straight.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 700M, widest on straightening, quickened near 100M.
Settled midfield on rail, near 550M became unbalanced and passing 500M was awkwardly placed, worked home well.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 600M, finished one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, fought hard but only one-paced, lame left front next day.
Niggled along, travelled wide and without cover until after 600M, weakened passing 100M.
Raced in handy position, placed pressure but gave ground passing 100M.
Began awkwardly then taken back, raced at tail, no response in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, faded out near 100M.
Raced midfield, came under pressure near 700M, finished tailed out.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Pushed to race in box seat, went amiss approaching 100M.
Began well before steadying & racing on leaders back from the 1300m. Moved up to assume the lead at the 200m before continuing on in closing stages to score well.

Bumped at start before being steadied & racing third from last in early stages. Moved wider to improve passing the 450m before cornering the widest runner. Finished hard in last 300m to close into second in final few strides.

Ridden forward after start before getting cover in forth, away from rail by the 1250m. Moved three wide approaching the final section, 3 lengths from lead. Sprinted well inside final 250m before being caught late for second.
One of the slowest away before maintaining midfield position on rail. Moved wider at the 400m when 4 lengths from lead. Made steady late ground in the straight to be close behind.

Ridden forward before obtaining good position on rail, 2.5L form lead after first section. Continued on the rail, 3 lengths from lead entering last section. Made up a length in the dash home & wasn't far behind.
Obtained position in midfield away from rail. Was 5.5 lengths from lead passing the 400m before making up over 3 lengths in the straight to finish in midfield. Not beaten far.

Bumped & start before being allowed to drift across just worse than midfield & away from rail. Well back entering the last section, stayed close to inside rail in the straight & made steady ground to finish midfield.

Ridden forward to assume lead passing winning post, crossing to rail approaching the 1300m. Continued in lead, over 1L clear passing half-way. Headed in the lead at the 200m before yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Slow to begin before shifting across to rail & racing just worse than midfield. Continued in midfield on cornering but couldn't really improve position in run to line. No threat.

Steadied from outside barrier & shifted back to last. Continued at the tail making the corner when over 7 lengths form lead. Made up a few lengths relative to winner but could only manage to beat two home.

Steadied after the start& shifted behind runners to race second from last. Continued a long way from lead entering the final section, stayed close to the inside in the straight but made no impression and was well beaten.
Ridden hard after start before improving position to race to second from the 1250m. Came under heavy pressure passing the 500m & yielded significant ground in the final section. Well beaten last.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after turning in, finished off strongly to score.

Began well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, showed good response after turning in, took brief lead near 150M, headed shortly thereafter, ran on well to take 2nd.
Away with them, sat 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped near 500M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Slow to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, bumped near 500M, showed limited response after turning in, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden after passing 600M but only showed limited response, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Jumped well, checked after 100M, settled in just behind midfield along the rail, ran on gamely to score from 200M.
Taken back, at rear along the rail, closed off nicely once fully cleared passing 150M.
In front of midfield, along the rail, kept rolling to take 3rd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, stayed on till emptied at 100M.
Bumped start, improved into lead by 600M, 3 wide at turn, bumped at 200M, showed no turn of foot.
Sent forward, shared lead 2 wide, emptied passing 150M.
Eased and raced at the rear, 2 wide, steadied at 250M, improved slightly.
Bumped start and taken back, at tail and 3 wide with cover at turn, did not threaten.
Urged then prominent early, then eased and settled midfield with cover, was one paced.(Blood in trachea)
In midfield, 2 wide, steadied at 200M, one paced nonetheless.
Prominent, wide and without cover till 600M, didn't improve and checked at 200M.
Always prominent, 2 wide, run ended when checked at 200M.

Broke well, amongst the leaders early before shifting back to trailing position in 3rd on the rail, switched out to challenge entering home straight and hit the front over 250 metres out, hung on well to the line.

Badly crowded at start dropping well behind, travelled keenly behind runners coming off the Rock, switched out for a run entering home straight, made significant progress down the centre of the track and did best work late.
Badly crowded at the start losing ground, recovered steadily under pressure to be better than midfield in 4th over 3L back, came wide into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began fairly from the one draw, settled in forward of midfield on the rail in 5th, saved ground on the inside turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield in 6th, ran on under pressure in straight but never threatening.
Travelled just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning for home, kept on steadily without threatening.
Began from the widest gate travelling wide without cover in rear of midfield, remained in similar position into home straight, produced some late impression closing stages.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, trailed the field from approaching the Rock, saved ground on the inside turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Failed to muster early stages despite ridden along, lost position passing the 600 metres, made no impression thereafter.

Driven forward from a wide gate to duel for lead, persevered with quick pace to gain slender advantage approaching home bend, held similar 2-wide position into straight and soon weakened. (Jockey warned)
Pressed forward from a wide gate, obtained rails run while sharing the quick pace to the Rock, remained under pressure from the outside runner until tiring noticeably in home straight.
Moderate start, travelled towards the rear 3-wide early in back straight, gradually dropped to last into home straight, made no show thereafter.

Positively ridden out the gate, crossed to join leader on outside passing 1300M, tracked pace from middle stages, driven to lead 250M, strongly challenged by rivals late, just held on in photo finish.
Held up midfield along the fence, angled out into clear 250M, pressed winner strongly final stages, just denied.
Settled behind mid-division early stages, took closer order passing 700M, chased steadily in straight, held in a 3-way photo finish.
Chased leaders on inside, found clear passage on inside on straightening, ran on steadily to the line, not pace of first 3 final 150M.
Soon taken across to the fence, reserved towards the rear 5-6Ls away, held up for running passing 200M, ran on well to the line.
Strode forward from inside draw, disputed lead with rival, battled on to 200M, faded towards the finish.
Dropped back from wide draw, raced as the back-marker early stages, crept closer from 700M, driven wide 500M, stayed on mildly towards the line.
From draw 12 unable to get closer than 3-wide, in mid-division throughout, stayed on fairly over final 300M. No impression on leaders.
Scrubbed along after the jump, unable to slot in early stages, caught wide no cover until 900M, disputed lead to straight, weakened away 250M.
Not hurried, taken back to race near the rear 5-6Ls back, driven along 500M, made no real progress in straight.
Settled ahead of midfield, shifted out 3-wide to improve position 700M, pushed wider by rival home turn, soon under pressure, weakened passing 250M.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, held up at the rear 7Ls off the pace, struggled to keep up home turn, soon left behind by rivals.
Bumped start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to join leader on line.

Jumped with them, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, same margin back on turn, commenced move after passing 450M, hit the front near 150M, kept on well thereafter, just able to hold on for dead heat.

Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, just ahead of midfield, closer on turn but still 3 wide with no cover, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail after passing 700M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Out in line, positioned 3 wide, a length behind the leader early, 2 wide from 700M, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.

Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter. (Sustained a small laceration to the outside of the left hind fetlock.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, struck on heels and stumbled early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back early, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Moderately away from gate 10, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, allowed to cross after passing 800M, challenged turning in, headed and weakened early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, took the lead near 300M, kept on well to the line, scored by a narrow margin.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 750M, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Made contact at start, sat 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sat right behind the leader, there to turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 800M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 4 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Slow away, at back, dashed strongly 300m for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Slow away, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Pushed early, in front of midfield on the fence, just held ground in straight.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M, on heels 100M.
At back, along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 250M, lack room 200M.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 300M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 400M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-5 wide, ran on fairly, on heels 200M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Took lead on outside rail with nice early speed, quickened near 200M, scored by 4L.
Settled midfield on outside rail, made up nice ground near 100M.
Raced behind the pace, gained ground passing 300M when asked for effort, finished well.
Lifted its legs and began only fairly, raced towards rear, passing 300M rider dropped his whip, gained ground passing 150M.
Settled in forward position, fought well when placed pressure.
Jumped nicely, settled behind the lead on rail, worked home one-paced.
Raced inside the leaders in the middle of track, fought hard but only one-paced.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced at tail and always niggled along, made some ground near 200M.
Settled midfield, near 400M was held up for running, one-paced.
Raced midfield, passing 400M had difficulties to obtain clear running, limited response passing 100M.
Ridden along for some distance to obtain forward position, did not travel comfortably, lay out in latter stages, weakened near 200M.
Niggled to race in forward position, placed pressure but gave ground passing 200M.
Settled in forward position, weakened passing 300M.
Raced at rear, always under pressure, faded out passing 200M.

Shifted across to race rearward, away from the rail. Commenced to improve passing the 700m before entering the last section very wide, with cover, 3L form lead. Sprinted well to assume lead at the 100m & was strong late.

Raced just worse than midfield, three wide with cover in early stages. Pushed very wide passing 700m before balancing less than 2L from lead. Sprinted well to assume lead inside last furlong before headed late. Clear of 3rd.

Enjoyed good run in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide passing 700m when improving before cornering five-wide. Made solid headway to share the lead near the 200m before being easily passed by first two. Held third.

Steadied after start & shifted behind runners to the tail. Third last on cornering, 4 lengths from lead entering final section. Shifted back towards the rail at the 350m before making good late headway to fourth.

Mustered speed & shifted across to race outside leader. Steadied & obtained cover in fourth passing the 900m. Moved three wide passing 600m, improved to second entering final section before peaking in closing stages.

Strode forward, raced on leaders back in early stages before being shuffled a pair further back approaching the 1000m. Shifted away from the rail at the 400m when 2L from lead before finishing off fairly in closing stages

Strode to midfield in first section before improving position to race in second, away from the rail by the 1000m. Came under heavy riding on cornering before peaking on effort at the 300m & yielding a few lengths thereafter.

Steadied after start & shifted across to race forth from last on the rail. Moved wider passing the 600m before balancing 3 lengths from the lead entering the final section. Finished off fairly in the final 300m. No threat.
Had no early speed & raced near the tail on the fence. Second from last entering the last section, nearly 6 lengths from lead before passing a few in the closing stages.

Strode forward to race just behind leaders early before being shuffled a pair further back passing half-way. Continued in midfield only 2.5L from lead entering the final section before failing to get any closer thereafter.

Raced wide in midfield before being without cover from the 900m. Moved closer approaching the corner before entering the last section 1.5L from lead. Remained close behind at the 200m before tiring late after wide passage.
Raced wide near the lead in early stages before improving after the 1200m mark to take lead shortly after. Raced over 1L clear on cornering before peaking on effort & weakening out in last furlong.

Showed speed after start before striding to lead in early stages. Relinquished lead & racing on leaders back from 900m. Had clear running at the 350m & continued to be close behind before being checked at 150m.
Held the rail in midfield, six lengths form the lead at half-way. Came under heavy riding passing the 950m mark before yielding significant ground in the second half of race. (Must trial).

Jumped well, trapped very wide in midfield, found cover from 800M but still 3 wide, commenced move after passing 500M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 200M, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began well from gate 11, raced 3 wide, slightly better than midfield, no cover from 750M, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide, slightly behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.

Began fairly, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly in the early stages, got cover after passing 750M, a length behind on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide from 750M, led narrowly on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Sent forward, led on rail, ran on all the way to score.
Crowded start, at rear, wide but with cover, saved ground and closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled to race in box-seat, stayed on well to the finish to take 3rd.
Awkward start, in midfield, wide but with cover, ran on well to the line.
Slotted into behind midfield, stayed 2 wide, improved and continued on fairly.
Eased and raced at the tail, stayed off the rail, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Bumped start, in behind midfield, wide but with cover, found no daylight until 200M, closed off only fairly.
Pushed after start, sat one-out one-back, did not threaten.
Crowded start, recovered to be in front of midfield, wide and without cover, no turn of foot.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, emptied at 200M out.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, found nothing.
In midfield, along the rail, out of steam at 300M. (See Incident Report)
Eased, at rear, wide but with cover, never in it.
Urged, settled outside lead, faded after straightening. Not competitive, must trial.

Broke well but soon taken back towards the rear and waited with, saved ground on the inside turning for home, quickened well inside the final 300 metres to take command over 100 metres out, won readily.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, finished off the race well down the centre of the straight, did best work late despite hanging in under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield, dropped slightly further back when given reminders approaching the home turn, made significant progress between runners inside the final 250 metres.

Taken back for rails run after beginning from a wide gate, snuck up to midfield after the first 200 metres, remained similar into home straight, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Taken back to last from the widest gate, trailed the field to home straight, made significant progress inside the final 200 metres.

Bumped at the start from a wide gate, ridden forward before settling 1L back in 2nd after the first 300 metres, hit the front under pressure over 350 metres out only to be swamped inside the final 150 metres.

Jumped fairly amongst the leaders, gradually drifted about 6L back in 6th or 5th, similar entering home straight, ran on to reach within 2L of lead for 3rd over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort.
Ridden to forward of midfield along the rail after an awkward start, settled about 5L back in 5th or 6th to home straight, made moderate progress under pressure without threatening.
Settled in midfield, one paced under pressure in home straight, beaten when tightened 150 metres out.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate settling well behind, switched wide into home straight, ran on near the stands rails, never nearer.
Not far off early stages, taken back to 4th some 3L back for cover approaching the home bend, remained similar turning in, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 150 metres.
Taken back from a wide gate for rails run settling in 10th some 10L off the pace, switched out for a run entering home straight but not able to quicken, beaten when tightened 200 metres out.
Soon took up running setting quick middle sectionals, headed when no extra inside the final 350 metres.
Quickly recovered after bumping at the start to settle 2L back in 3rd, remained similar to straight, kept on under pressure until fading inside the final 250 metres. (Jockey reported saddle shifted)
Quickly into stride, tracked leaders in 3rd, going well turning into straight, quickened to the front nearing 200M, drew nicely clear winning comfortably.
Held up along the fence in midfield, 6th at 800M 4Ls off the pace, stayed on well to go 2nd 50M out, no chance with easy winner.
Dropped back after the jump, unable to slot in from draw 11, caught very wide home turn, ran on well over final 300M to claim 3rd near line.
Began only fairly, settled towards the rear, had wide trip, crept closer 600M, kept on steadily turning home, just missed 3rd.
Driven forward, took outright lead passing 800M, headed by winner nearing 200M, no extra final 100M, lost several places close home.
Chased leaders in 4th, found no extra on straightening, never a threat to leaders.

Pressed forward, vied for early lead before settling down behind leader, driven 400M but didn't respond to riding, weakened away mid-straight. (Jockey : not able to finish off the race after being challenged in the lead.)
Held up behind midfield, 6-7Ls behind leader home turn, ran past beaten horses in the straight. No impression on leaders.
Badly unbalanced when crowded for room on jumping, settled 3-4Ls off the pace in 5th, struggled passing 400M, soon out of contention.
Dropped back from wide barrier, held up near last on inside, 6Ls to make up 400M, failed to make ground.
Slowly into stride, detached from field early stages, always back, never ran on.
Began awkwardly, never better than midfield the trip, 8th at 400M, weakened passing 300M to finish last.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 650M, finished off very strongly to score.

Began smartly from gate 14, raced 3w with no cover, better than midfield, moved closer after passing 750M, bumped 650M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable hold off the winner.

Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide in midfield early, no cover from 950M, commenced move after passing 800M, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, just stayed on for 3rd.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 1100M, 4 wide turning, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, just behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, awkwardly placed early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn but still the last, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 800M, moved a bit closer on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Had a small cut to the left hind cannon.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, 4 wide from 750M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Quickly into stride, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, sat 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead but trapped wide early, found rail near 800M, peaked and headed turning in, weakened early in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, there to turn, commenced move after passing 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Crowded out start, recovered to race prominently, 3 wide, no cover throughout, kept on well after turning in, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress in straight.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, weakened thereafter.

Clean jump, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide early, taken back to race 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide from 700M, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 to 4 lengths back, carried wider from 550M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Stood flat-footed and missed the start, detached from the main group early, got back to it near 900M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace. (Rider dropped whip near 100M.)
Reared at the start and struck head, detached early, gradually recovered to latch onto back of group just before halfway, 4 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position in the middle stages, hung out turning for home, weakened early in straight.
