Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, led by half length turning in, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line and scored.
Slightly slow out, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to take a place.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, outpaced and became detached from the field early, gradually recovered but still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, produced good late impression in the run home.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 4 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, failed to make any progress.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, closed off well for 2nd.
Took rail and lead easily, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Bumped start, at back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Box seat, pace good, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, lack room in straight, made steady ground.
Eased to sit in front of midfield on the fence, pace good, no dash in straight.
Bumped start, eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on ok in final stages.
Behind midfield along the fence, pace good, emptied 250M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, dropped off quickly 600M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, improved passing 600M, wide on straightening, quickened near 100M, finished strongly to score.
Settled towards rear, asked for effort near 500M, widest on straightening, made up nice late ground, missed by Neck.
At start was bumped then taken back, placed pressure passing 300M, responded well in the straight.
At start was inconvenienced then taken back, near 200M was checked when crowded for room, gained some ground near 50M.
Ridden along to take lead, commenced to improve passing 500M, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Raced behind midfield, travelled keenly, moved to outside the lead near 600M, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort near 600M, weakened passing 100M.
Settled in front of midfield, only one-paced in the straight.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure passing 700M, gave ground near 100M.
On jumping was crowded, settled midfield on rail, improved near 600M, weakened passing 200M.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, commenced to improve near 1000M, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 700M, faded out passing 300M.
Strode forward to race second away from rail, over 1 length from lead at half-way. Moved up to assume lead approaching the 400m, kicked clear after straightening & held challenger in closing stages.

Began only fairly before shifting to rail, racing in midfield after start. Moved away from rail on cornering, shifted back in near the 200m when making ground before continuing to close hard in concluding stages to just miss.
Raced in midfield away from rail, 4 lengths form lead in early stages. Moved closer to lead after half-way before straightening just over a length from lead. Finished off fairly to hold third.
Nice position in midfield on rail in early & middle stages. Stayed close to inside rail nearing corner, raced tight on straightening before making up a length in closing stages to not be beaten far.
Stumbled at start & lost ground, raced at rear. Stayed close to inside on cornering when still racing last, before making late headway between runners from rearward position.

Drifted back shortly after start to race forth from last away from rail. Moved three wide with cover passing the 1200m mark. Moved wider on cornering when three lengths from lead before maintaining margin in last section.
Drifted back after start and raced third from last on rail. Continued near the rear entering the final section, and despite making up over a length in last 300m was never a genuine threat.
Raced in midfield, three wide without cover throughout. Ridden hard to move closer passing the 500m before peaking on effort at the 200m & weakening in closing stages after wide trip.
Shifted behind runners after start & raced second from last. Next to last on entering the final section, made up a length relative to winner but was never a threat.
Began fast, early leader before racing on leaders back from the 1600m. Only 1.5L from lead entering final section but weakened out in last 300m. May not have appreciated further distance.

Began well before drifting back to midfield away from rail in first section. Came under heavy riding approaching the 500m. Only 3 lengths from lead passing the 400m before weakening thereafter. Well held.

Strode from outside gate to lead before crossing to rail nearing 1500m. Raced over 1L clear of second at half-way. Joined in the lead approaching the 400m mark before yielding significant ground in last section. Well beaten.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide early, pushed forward and took the lead after passing 800M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, commenced move after passing 400M, wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 600M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground to turn, angled out early in straight, produced some good late impression.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept on well until 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 wide in midfield, clipped heels and stumbled near 1000M, commenced move after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, inconvenienced near 1000M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made little progress in straight.

Jumped well from gate 11, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, ahead of midfield, sent forward after passing 1000M, but still 4 wide, 2 wide from 550M, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 650M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
In font of midfield, along the rail, battled on gamely, took led at 50M out, scored by a neck.
Sent forward, led on the rail, kept rolling but caught by winner about 50M out.
At rear, along the rail, saved ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Settled to race outside the lead, lost touch with leaders near 150M, emptied but hung on for 4th.
Began only fairly, then failed to muster, settled midfield 2 wide, continued one paced.
In midfield initially, slotted back to take cover by 600M turn, ran on fairly in the straight.
Prominent, wide and without cover however, showed no turn of foot.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
In front of midfield, wide but with cover, emptied passing 200M. (Bled)
Midfield, wide but with cover, lost ground in straight.
At rear, wide but with cover, not competitive.
Awkward start and failed to muster, prominent but wide by 600M turn, weakened soon after.
Jumped well from the 2 draw, held rails run inside of the leader most of the way until hitting the front about 450 metres out, hung on well under pressure.
Sluggish start, settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move on straightening and switched out for a run 200 metres out, ran on well to be nearest at finish.

Taken back from a wide gate, checked before settling towards the rear on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish despite briefly baulked 100 metres out.
Broke well settling just off the pace in 3rd, commenced move rounding home bend to reach backend of the leader turning in, unable to sustain effort.
Broke well, gradually settled just over 2L off the pace in 5th or 4th, gained slightly closer when 3rd turning in, kept on same pace but lost 3rd late.
Taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field to the 600 metres, saved ground on the inside turning for home, made modest progress without threatening.
Ridden along among the leaders early stages, drifted back to midfield on first turn, came under pressure over 400 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Settled well behind after beginning from the widest gate, trailed the field until running past well-beaten horses inside the final 150 metres.
Awkward start losing ground, quickly recovered to be just worse than midfield, came under pressure from approaching home bend, found nothing.
Prominent out wide early before shifting over 2L back in 5th, remained similar into straight but folded up quickly. (Reported tendon injury next day)
Jumped fairly from a wide gate settling wide without cover in midfield, remained similar through to home turn, soon weakened.
Ridden forward to gain slender advantage from outside the 2nd, unable to sustain effort when headed about 450 metres out, folded up quickly after straightening.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4-5Ls back, stayed on well final 300M, got up just in time to prevail in a blanket finish.
Taken back from draw 11, settled near last, took closer order passing 800M, 6th at 400M, kept finding in the straight, claimed 2nd in blanket finish.
Chased leaders, responded well on straightening, came close to win but had to settle for 3rd in a close finish.
Urged along after jump, tracked leader 2-wide, moved up to lead top of straight, kept on well, shifted in late stages causing jockey to stop riding, headed by first 3 near line.
Began only fairly, settled down behind midfield, moved away from fence 700M, swung wide into straight, ran on well to the line to finish a close 5th.
Held up behind mid-division, switched 3-wide 800M, moved up to be chasing leaders home turn, ran on well, outpaced by pursuing rivals late stages.
Set early pace, tracked leader from 1200M, stayed on moderately up the fence from 400M, had no clear run near 150M, checked and clipped heels near line losing momentum. Would have finished closer.
From draw 1 had a ground saving trip in mid-division, shuffled back to near last home turn, ran on mildly in straight but always behind leaders.
From draw 12 shifted across behind runners, in last spot until 500M, badly held up in straight and not able to obtain clear running until late stages. Not tested.
Guided to the fence soon after the start, help up near the rear, in last place from 600M, stayed on mildly to the line.
Positioned ahead of midfield, saved ground along the fence, not quickened in straight, never threatened.
Strolled forward, crossed to the lead passing 1200M, lost lead passing 400M, weakened passing 250M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.

Jumped well, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross after the first turn, sat a length behind the leader in the middle stages, 2w on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, bumped near 550M, moved closer on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, commenced move after passing 400M, made some progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, bumped near 550M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide and without cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped start, positioned outside to the leader, same position to turn, took the lead 300M, kept on well, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, angled out after passing 550M, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Slowly away, positioned on rail, slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, 3 to 4 wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.

Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 500M, not enough room early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 600M, wide into straight, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced at tail, 2 wide, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, found a 3 wide spot near 1000M, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, not enough room early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, peaked after turning in, headed near 300M, dropped away thereafter.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, hung out on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, drifted away 400M to score.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide behind midfield, dashed strongly 350M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Sat outside the leader, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide in front of midfield, held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, no turn of foot in straight.
Checked start, took rail at rear, lack room 5-3, dashed well when clear.
Eased back, took rail, little dash 200M.
Slow away, 2 wide, dashed only fairly in straight.
Eased back, checked early, never improved.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, dropped off rapidly 400M.
At back, eased out of race 200M.
Jumped sharply, took lead with nice early speed, travelled comfortably, worked home strongly to score.
Hard ridden to race in box seat, asked for effort passing 500M, fought nicely in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, responded well in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, placed pressure near 500M, made up some late ground.
Hard ridden but no early speed, raced midfield, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Jumped well, raced in front of midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Settled outside the lead with very nice early speed, placed pressure but gave ground passing 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on rail, finished one-paced.
Raced at back, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly and stumbled, raced at back, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, raced in one-back-one-off position, weakened passing 200M, mucus trachea.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, placed pressure but no response in the straight.

Showed early speed to assume the lead near the 1000m before crossing to rail shortly after. Raced three lengths clear in the lead entering the final section, before continuing on to score impressive big margin win. Easy.

Limited early speed & drifted back worse than midfield. Continued along rail, held up on straightening & again near 200m before finishing well in closing stages. Well behind dominant winner. (Tendon injury).

Couldn't go the early speed before being ridden forward to hold position 3rd last. Continued to be hard ridden in middle stages before cornering well off lead. Made steady headway late but like others was no match for winner.
Not as fast as others and raced just worse than midfield away from rail. Continued rearward, held up momentarily near the 300m before finishing off ok for 4th.
Had no early speed and raced at the rear shortly after the start. Moved four wide passing the 500m, straightened the widest before running home ok to finish not far behind second. Well behind winner.

Ridden forward to be prominent after start before racing on the leaders back from the 850m. Continued in second position but under heavy riding passing the 500m before peaking & being passed inside last 100m.
Began well before racing in midfield on rail. Was six lengths from lead entering the last section but could make no further impression and was well held.

No early speed & raced second from last on rail. Shuffled back to last passing half-way before cornering at the tail over 9L from lead. Moved the widest after straightening, passed a few tiring runners but was never a factor.
Shifted across after start to race in midfield, three wide with cover. Came under hard riding passing the 450m before weakening further in the straight to be beaten nearly 10 lengths.
Began well before being headed and racing in midfield between runners. Continued to be in midfield after straightening but weakened out badly in the final 150m. Beaten a big margin.
Improved after the start to stride to third, away from rail passing the 850m. Was hard ridden from passing the 550m before yielding significant ground in the final furlong. Beaten a big margin.

Hard ridden but failed to muster early, before improving mid-race to third position, three wide, passing the 750m. Came under hard riding & hung out passing the 500m before weakening out significantly in the straight. (Bled).
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the lead 600M, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide better than midfield, hard ridden from 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn but still 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 600M, a length behind the leader turning in, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, eased thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, just behind midfield, peaked on turn, one pace to the line.
Jumped well, positioned on rail, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, kept on one pace to 100M, eased thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Rolled forward into the box-seat, worked home nicely to score by a neck.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and hit the line strongly to take 2nd.
Asked early, settled to race outside the lead, stayed on in a tight battle to the line, took 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Urged to be prominent, wide however, stayed on till 100M out. (See Incident Report)
Awkward start, raced at the tail, wide but with cover, continued to make ground. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden to be prominent, sat outside lead by 700M, wide though, found no extra for final 100M.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, was one paced.
Awkward start and lost ground, at rear, wide but with cover, did not improve.
In front of midfield, wide but with cover, not competitive.
Bumped start, remained at rear 2 wide, showed nothing. (See Incident Report)
Rolled forward, took rail and led, emptied at 200M.
Ridden along in rear after a moderate start, improved steadily towards midfield before switching in off stands rails for a run 400 metres out, quickened well to take charge inside the 200 metres.
Always thereabouts, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure throughout final stages.
Settled in midfield, came to challenge under pressure from 400 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start losing ground, travelled in last few early stages, commenced move passing the 500 metres, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled keenly before settling just off the pace over half-way out, hit the front under pressure briefly about 200 metres out, soon weakened.
Broke well from the stands side draw, settled just off the pace on stands rail, hung in away from the rail on a few occasions, found no extra inside final 200 metres.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th about 2L off the pace, unable to quicken under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field early stages, made headway down the centre of the track to reach within 3L of leaders in 8th over 300 metres out, made no further impression.

Jumped fairly, awkwardly placed behind runners passing the 800 metres, remained in last few before closing off the race well inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for hands and heels riding closing stages)
Never better than midfield, inconvenienced over 400 metres out, ran home one-paced and forced to switch near the 250 metres, (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield, faded from inside final 300 metres.
Driven to lead from a low gate, obtained rails run on the stands side after the first 200 metres, came under pressure to hold place over 300 metres out, soon headed.
Jumped very awkwardly losing ground, always well behind, found nothing despite given reminders over 400 metres out.
Not far off early stages, yielded ground over half-way out.
Positioned ahead of midfield in a fast run race, led the chase on runaway leader passing 300M, got up near 50M.
Strode forward, crossed to lead before home turn, led at fast pace, 3-4Ls in front early straight, kept on until headed near 50M, weakened late but held on for 2nd. (Jockey dropped whip 100M.)
Failed to muster speed, settled down 3-wide towards the rear, 7Ls off runaway leader 400M, made good progress to the line, just missed 2nd.
Held up in midfield 3-wide, 5-6Ls off the quick pace, driven inside 400M, ran on well to go 3rd mid-straight, edged out to 4th near line.
Bumped by rival on jumping, dropped back to rear 8Ls off leader in a fast run race, swung widest 500M, ran on steadily to the line.
Towards the rear early and middle stages, moved closer 600M, ran on mildly final 300M, not reached leaders.
Began very awkwardly and crowded for room at start, settled in midfield 5-6Ls away from runaway leader, made limited progress on straightening, no threat.
Slow to begin, 8Ls off the pace in the rear, ran past beaten horses in straight, never near to challenge.
Never better than midfield, saved ground on the inside, crowded for room 500M and held up for some distance behind a weakening rival, didn't find much on straightening however.
4th on settling, moved up to 2nd 500M, run ended mid-straight, weakened rapidly.
Up with early pace, wide no cover from 700M chasing runaway leader, struggled to hold its spot from 450M, soon beaten turning in, dropped away quickly.
Strolled forward to be tracking leader, commenced to give ground 600M out, first to be beaten.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead near 150M, kept on well, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame. (Dead-heat for 4th.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, wide into straight, finished off strongly to make frame. (Dead-heat for 4th.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, wider from 600M, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, angled out after passing 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Jumped with them, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages but still the last, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked on run 200M, headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 100M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 800M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, travelled well to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from near 800M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take a place.

Jumped well from gate 10, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back in the middle stages, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from 900M, 8 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide turning, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, gradually moved forward to take the lead, 2 wide on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 3 wide at rear, carried wider near 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced very wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.

Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to score by a nose.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, commenced move from 550M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Crowded out start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, angled out from 450M, wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 750M, shared lead on turn, took brief lead near 200M, headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival turning in, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened from 150M.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 700M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Behind midfield, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Midfield, suited by the fast tempo, closed off well for 2nd.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Took rail easily and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Box seat, just held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, trapped wide, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Behind midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M, lack room 100M.
Midfield, held up badly in straight, not fully tested.
Eased back, favoured by the fast pace, made minor ground 300M.
At rear, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, weakened 350M.
Midfield, trapped wide, emptied 300M.
Raced in box seat, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 500M, responded solidly in the straight.
Began only fairly, from the 800M was left racing three wide and without cover, widest on straightening, made good late ground.
Improved to outside the lead passing 800M, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home well.
Raced behind midfield, passing 200M was directed out after being disappointed for run, finished well.
Broke well then taken back, placed pressure passing 400M, gained nice ground passing 100M.
Pushed along after start then taken back, placed pressure passing 500M, made ground passing 150M.
Raced in the lead with nice early speed, made the turn after 600M awkwardly, gave ground passing 100M.
Near 1050M hampered when crowded for room, settled midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Raced in handy position, inclined to lay out for the majority of race, gave ground near 50M.
Began very awkwardly, travelled keenly in the early stages, raced behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Raced at tail, reluctant to stretch out throughout the race despite being ridden along throughout, must trial.
Strode forward before getting nice run on leaders back. Assumed lead inside the 150m before dashing away to score impressively.

Not fast away but mustered quickly to improve to midfield on rail. Around 3 lengths from lead entering the final section before finishing off strongly in last 300m to snare second placing in final stride.
Improved after the start before getting good position behind leading pair away from the inside. Within two lengths of lead on cornering before maintaining similar margin in run to line.
Allowed to shift across behind runners to race worse than midfield away from rail. Made gradual headway in final 300m to be close behind second.

Showed customary early speed to be prominent & raced outside leader after 300m. Moved up to share lead at the 450m, before assuming lead at the 300m. Joined and headed at the 150m before yielding a length late.
Steadied after start & shifted across behind runners to race at the tail. Was a clear last on cornering, before finishing strongly in the straight to finish within a length of second.
Strode to midfield, wide on the track before drifting back, just worse than midfield. Hard ridden upon entering the final section before finishing off relatively well considering wide trip.
Strode to midfield but raced a little wide in middle stages. Hard ridden passing the 400m before finishing off only fairly to finish in midfield.
Shifted behind runners after the start and settled third from last away from rail. Continued third from last entering the straight & failed to make any impression in the run to the line.
Held the rail in midfield early before drifting back slightly after first 400m. Steadied and lost some momentum passing the 400m & never made any real headway thereafter.
Slow to begin and raced near the tail on the fence. Second from last on cornering & made no real impression after straightening & was well beaten.

Placing: PU
Comment: Strode to lead after 300m. Went amiss after straightening and failed to finish race.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, half length behind the leader, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight, just narrowly beaten.
Began smartly from the widest draw, showed good early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 100M, headed 50M, stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide without cover, 1-1/2L back, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 900M, weakened gradually in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, 4 wide with no cover after entering the back straight, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, worked home nicely to score by 3/4L.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to the line to take 2nd.
Settled in worse than midfield, along the rail, closed off nicely to the line. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward, settled outside lead, continued one paced to the line.
Taken back, at rear 2 wide, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, switched widest in straight and improved slightly.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground in straight.
In behind midfield but wide, improved and took lead outright at 600M, weakened and headed 100M out.
Settled to race in the box-seat, faded gradually from 200M out.
Rolled forward, took rail and led until 700M, weakened passing 150M.
Bumped start, settled in worse than midfield, wide mostly, lost ground in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start and lost ground, remained at rear, not a factor.
Settled well behind and waited with, commenced move entering home straight, quickened well to take charge close to home.
Jumped fairly but soon ridden up to first few, held slender lead most of the way before kicking over 1L clear after straightening only to be caught in the shadow of the post.

Badly hampered at the start but quickly recovered to 6th, gradually drifted back to midfield approaching back straight, saved ground on the inside turning for home, produced good late finish final stages.
Ridden forward to join the leader on the first bend, remained similar into home straight, kept on without quickening in the run to the line.
Broke well, with leaders early before shifting one-out-one-back in 4th, ran home one-paced from a similar position turning in.
Bumped and unbalanced at start settling towards the rear on the rail, remained similar to straight and saved ground turning in, made good headway down home straight but never threatening.
Settled just off the pace in 5th on the rail, gained slightly closer to 1L 3rd rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Hampered at start, travelled 3-wide in midfield, in similar position turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.

Began well from a wide gate, travelled 3-wide without cover before shifting backward to last few, made headway around home bend and a widest runner turning for home, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Hampered after a moderate beginning, midfield on the rail when travelling keenly around first bend and early in back straight and checked, inconvenienced again on home bend, folded up quickly.
Began well from a poor gate, travelled wide without cover in a prominent position most of the way to the 400 metres, folded up quickly. (Blood in trachea and restricted action next day)
Taken back from the widest gate, gave ground from approaching home bend and soon detached.
Began awkwardly, reserved behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, driven wide 400M, motored home final 200M to nail leader last stride.
Positively ridden from wide barrier, crossed to lead 1400M, led slowly before quickening up back-straight, kept on well opening up 3Ls lead 200M, caught by fast finishing winner late
Taken back to obtain cover, in last 9Ls back, pushed along 550M, came home widest, stayed on well to take 3rd without reaching top 2.
Chased leaders in 4th, kept on evenly on straightening, no impression on first 2.
Settled down midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, stayed on moderately final 300M, not reach leaders.
Positioned ahead of midfield, lacked a finishing kick passing 300M, kept on steadily, never threatened.
Held up along the fence in midfield, 7th on settling 5Ls off leader, ran home one paced.
Dropped back from wide draw, towards the rear always, ran on only fairly final 300M, never dangerous.
Held up towards the rear along inside, in 9th spot over 6Ls off the pace home turn, couldn't quicken in the straight.
Not hurried, settled down near last 8Ls behind leader, made limited progress early straight, raced in restricted room 250M, never in the picture.

Moved forward to track leader, driven out 400M, couldn't go on and weakened noticeably passing 200M. (Jockey: appeared to travel satisfactorily until middle stages at which time it didn't feel completely comfortable in its action.)
Chased leaders, came under serious pressure 500M, gave ground rapidly. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Began well from gate 10, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, moved closer after passing 600M, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 200M, kept on very strongly to the line.

Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, positioned on rail, just ahead of midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 700M, moved closer in the middle stages, made reasonable progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, carried wider near 600M, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 750M, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider after passing 400M, clipped heels and blundered turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, found cover near 600M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide from 650M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed no response in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Clean jump, positioned on rail, just ahead of midfield, angled out after passing 550M, showed good response after turning in, hit the front near 150M, kept on well to hold off the challengers, scored by narrow margin.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just denied.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider from 500M, took brief lead early in straight, headed 150M, stayed on well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, just missed frame.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider from 650M, made minor progress in straight.

Shifted in abruptly at start and made contact, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, ran on one pace.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 600M, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently. 2 wide, half length back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, no clear running early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Fast into stride, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out near 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by half length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Pushed to take rail and led at slow sectionals, made all.
Box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing effort 300M.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed well to the line.
Sat outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, trapped 4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Slow away, at back, not suited by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
At back, 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
Eased to rear, trapped 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide but favoured by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, weakened 350M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At rear, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Settled outside the leader, commenced to improve on straightening, responded solidly to score.
Slow out, travelled keenly near 1100M, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, quickened passing 200M.
Sent forward to take box seat, fought well in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home nicely.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort near 400M, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, widest on straightening, made up some late ground.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, wide on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, fought hard but only one-paced.
Raced in handy position, travelled keenly in the middle stages, finished one-paced.
Raced at rear, placed pressure passing 500M, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield, placed pressure and limited response in the straight.
Raced towards rear, niggled near 850M to maintain its position, no response in the straight.
Settled towards rear on rail, gave ground passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, crowded near 1000M, wide and without cover outside the lead, faded out passing 300M.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Travelled strongly, 2L from lead nearing the corner. Shifted in after straightening, sprinted quickly to assume lead at 250m before running away for very impressive victory.

Raced rearward before improving to midfield by half-way. Moved wider nearing bend before sprinting fast, within 1 length of lead at the 300m. Fought on strongly to snare second in closing stages but well behind easy winner.

Strode forward from widest gate, assuming lead & going fast early section. Continued over 1 length clear passing the 400m before being quickly passed at the 250m. Battled on well in closing stages but no match for winner.

Got back to rearward position early before being relegated to last passing the 1300m. Moved wider passing the 650m before commencing wide sustained run around the bend. Continued to make headway to finish just behind second.

Steadied & raced at tail shortly after start. Improved slightly, three wide with cover approaching the 600m before moving wider approaching corner. Passed a few in last 300m but was well behind dominant winner.
Raced worse than midfield away from rail, seven lengths from lead at half-way. Held up after straightening & again passing the 300m before getting clear & passing tiring opposition in closing stages.

Crossed to rail shortly after start before enjoying economical run in midfield. Moved away from rail approaching the 550m before cornering 4 lengths from lead. Maintained midfield position in last section.
Strode forward before getting nice trail on leaders back from the 1800m. Continued on leaders back but was being niggled along passing the 600m. Peaked on run at 350m & weakened out thereafter.

Crowded & lost ground at start before ridden forward to improve to midfield away from rail. Clipped heels & stumbled near the 600m losing momentum. Next to last on cornering & made little impression thereafter.

Not bustled at start & drifted back to rearward position. Continued near the tail passing the 800m before coming under heavy riding from the 600m. Stayed close to the inside but made no headway in straight & was well beaten.

Ridden forward at start before crossing to rail in midfield shortly after start. Had an economical passage throughout before cornering only 2.5 lengths form lead. Tired badly in last section & was well beaten.

Continued to improve after the start before racing in second away from the rail in middle stages. Came under heavy pressure passing the 600m mark & yielded significant ground in the straight. Well beaten.

Strode forward in early stages before getting trailing position behind leading trio. Two lengths form lead passing the 800m before moving 3 wide shortly after. Peaked on effort on cornering before weakening badly last 350m.
Strode across to midfield after start before being left wide without cover from the 1700m. Continued wide path throughout before weakening out from the 600m mark. Well beaten.
Began fairly, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off well to take 2nd on line.
Began smartly, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked near 100M, fought on, just headed close home, finished 3rd.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-1/2L back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 600M, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in one-off one-back position, showed good kick at 100M to peel away, scored by 1-1/4L.
Settled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, pressured all along to keep up, ran on gamely for 2nd.
Travelled towards the rear, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off well to take 3rd. (Blood in trachea)
Slotted in to race in midfield, 2 wide, continued on nicely to the finish.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, ran on fairly to the line.
Sent forward, shared lead one-off the rail, headed prior to 150M, emptied thereafter.
Eased back, raced at the tail along the rail, saved ground and continued on nicely.
Settled in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly until flattened late.
In behind midfield, 2 wide, continued on one paced.
Eased then raced at the tail, 2 wide, ran on but saved no ground.
Sent forward, shared lead on the rail, emptied passing 150M. (See Incident Report)
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, did not threaten.
In behind midfield, along the rail, showed nothing. (Blood in trachea)
Up on the pace early, wide until slotted back to take cover at 700M, gave ground in the straight and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Settled in 5th just over 2L off the pace, remained in similar position to straight, quickened well under pressure to hit the front over 100 metres out.

Began well from the widest gate, taken back to the rear after the first 400 metres, remained well behind into the straight, ran on well inside the final 300 metres but unable to peg back the winner close stages.
Tracked the leader, hit the front narrowly upon straightening only to be headed under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in rear of midfield in 6th just about 3L off the pace 3-wide with cover, remained similar into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Began awkwardly losing ground and raced keenly most of the way, mainly in 8th within 4L of pace before gaining closer approaching home turn, baulked early in straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back to last from a wide gate, trailed the field to the 200 metres, finished off the race well.
Settled mainly in rear of midfield in 7th on the rail, saved ground turning in, baulked for a run early in straight, produced good late finish inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, improved steadily on the rail to reach within 2L of pace mainly in 4th, in similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Soon took up running, led the field until joined into straight, soon headed and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well before taken back to 3rd while travelling wide without cover, came to join the leaders briefly entering straight, folded up quickly.
Chased leaders, driven out 400M, led mid-straight, fought off challenge from both sides and held on gamely at the finish.
Tracked leaders along the fence, awkwardly placed nearing 300M, switched lane, finished off well final 200M, just held.
Held up 5th of 8, switched out 500M to challenge, responded well to be vying for lead inside 200M, couldn't sustain run late, lost 2nd 50M out.
Towards the rear in the 6th spot, steadied 300M, stayed on well to the line but safely held by first 3.
Reserved near last 5Ls off the pace, ran on mildly over final 300M, not reached leaders.
Tracked leader on settling, had his chance in straight, out-finished final 200M.
Dropped back to last about 6Ls off the pace, took time to muster speed when put to pressure passing 400M, hampered 150M losing momentum, coasted home.
Disputed early lead, became sole leader 1400M, was challenged passing 400M, fought briefly before fading away mid-straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, made very good progress early in straight, led narrowly 200M, headed near 100M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked off heels near 700M, angled out early in straight, made good progress to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, hampered near 700M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, inconvenienced near 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 850M, led by half length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail better than the midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded start, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, shifted out away from heels near 700M,4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, checked off heels and travelled keenly near 750M, same margin turning in, showed limited response in straight, eased final 50M.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (Bled.)
Made contact at start, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly in the early stages, carried wider after passing 800M, half length back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly to turn, 2 wide from 800M, peaked after turning in, weakened final 300M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide at rear, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score by a head.

Made contact at start, raced 2 wide at rear early, bumped near 1100M, positioned on rail thereafter, moved closer on turn, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, finished off strongly final 200M, just narrowly beaten.

Taken back from gate 12, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, slightly improved in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, no clear running early in straight, angled out and made contact 200M, finished off very strongly to take a place.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front near 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the challengers late.

Shifted in abruptly at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, found cover 900M, travelled comfortably on turn, ridden after passing 300M, only showed limited response, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer on inner turning in, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.

Bumped start and unbalanced, taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, shifted in and bumped near 1100M, 2 wide thereafter, 5 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 900M, half length behind the leader turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 550M, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.

Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, not enough room 200M, ran on well until blocked near 50M, not ridden out late.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened steadily final 100M.
Moderately away, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, raced tight early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, soon weakened.

Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside early, allowed rival to cross near 600M, 1-1/2L back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 450M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 600M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on one pace to the line.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, a length or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, awkwardly placed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, bumped near 600M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, taken back to race at rear, made contact near 600M, 3 wide turning, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, slightly behind midfield, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, commenced move after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, inclined to lay out on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Hard ridden to hold the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well to score.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, mad steady ground for 2nd.
Bumped start, eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, overhauled 150M.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased at start, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
At back, took rail, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Slow away, at rear along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made good ground 200M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Had ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, dropped off rapidly 600M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take lead, asked effort on straightening, responded strongly, scored unchallenged.
Wide without cover then steadied to obtain cover passing 800M, settled in handy position, worked home solidly.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, gained ground near 100M.
Settled behind midfield, tried hard in the straight, finished nicely.
Crowded at start then steadied to obtain cover, raced midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 600M, worked home one-paced.
Taken back at start, checked near 1050M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, limited response in the straight.
Slow out, niggled to race in box seat, placed pressure prior to the Home Turn, gave ground passing 100M, must trial.
Raced towards rear on rail, placed pressure near 500M, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced outside the lead, weakened near 150M.
Raced at rear, made the turn after 600M awkwardly and lay out, gave ground passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, emptied passing 200M.

Ridden forward before getting good trailing position one pair from lead away from rail. Moved up to share the lead inside the last furlong before digging deep late to score narrowly. First two clear of third.

Strode forward before racing on leaders back from the 1300m. Travelled well on cornering, stayed close to inside, made headway to share the lead inside the last furlong before nosed out in closing stages. Clear of third.

Enjoyed economical run in midfield on rail in early & middle stages. Moved away from rail approaching 400m, made gradual headway until shifting to clear running near the 200m & finishing off well thereafter.

Crossed in the early stages before racing midfield away from rail. Stayed close to the rail when 4 lengths from lead entering last section before making up a few lengths in the last 300m. Not beaten far.
Strode forward before racing outside the leader in early & middle stages. Moved up to assume lead approaching the furlong marker before headed shortly after. Battled away late, not beaten too far.
Began well, assumed lead before crossing to rail near 1300m. Headed in the lead approaching the final furlong before weakening a few lengths thereafter.
Began only fairly & raced rearward throughout. Continued second last entering the last section when 6 lengths from lead before passing a few tiring runners late. Never a threat.
Shifted across behind runners after the start & raced just worse than midfield early. Moved three wide passing the 600m when improving. Cornered wide before maintaining margin in run to line.

Steadied from widest barrier before shifting across to last. Moved wider & commenced to improve passing the 700m. Cornered very wide, well off lead, made no further headway in straight & only held margin in last section.
Steadied & shifted behind runners to race third last in early stages. Shuffled back to last when racing wide passing the 400m & never really improved in last section. Well held.

Bumped at start before ridden to hold midfield position away from rail. Came under hard riding after moving three wide approaching the 400m mark before weakening out to second last in run to line. Well beaten.

Had limited early speed & settled worse than midfield on rail. Raced keenly & checked when pace slowed passing the 1300m. Five lengths off lead entering last section & weakened out to last in run to line.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, commenced move after passing 450M, wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still 8 lengths behind on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten, good debut.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first few late.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, awkwardly placed near 50M, one pace thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, not enough room after passing 100M, bumped close home.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight, bumped close home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Eased and in worse than midfield initially, moved after 900M, led by 2L at 400M, kept going to score by 1-1/4L.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, fought on gamely to narrow margin, finished 2nd and 1-1/4L behind.
Niggled out of the barriers, forward and settled in box-seat, slotted spot back at 700M, kept on going for 3rd.
Taken back, at rear initially, moved with the field at 700M, saved ground and ran on nicely.
Settled in about midfield, 3 wide and without cover at 600M turn, ran on to the line.
Taken back, at tail throughout, shifted out to 2 wide prior to 600M turn, improved slightly.
In behind midfield, 2 wide, was one paced in the straight.
Rolled forward, sat outside lead until 700M when others moved, found nothing.
Asked early to be prominent, led on rail until 700M when others improved, weakened at 100M.
Settled one-out one-back, raced keenly early, moved at 700M, no extra passing 200M.
In behind midfield, along the rail, emptied near 150M.
Jumped only fairly, at rear along the rail, never a factor.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield early stages, improved steadily in back straight to reach 2nd 800 metres out, sustained effort to hit the front turning for home, forged clear under pressure.

Settled just off the pace in 4th just over 2L off the pace, became 5th in similar position early in back straight, gained 3rd 3-wide rounding home bend, fought on under pressure but never threatening.
Settled behind midfield after beginning from a wide gate, commenced move under pressure rounding the home bend out wide, ran on in the centre of the straight.
Jumped well settling 2 back on the rail, became 6th in midfield 3L off the pace on the rail in back straight, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Taken back to rear from the widest gate, switched wide for a run entering home straight, ran on down the centre of the track.
In last few early, made steady headway to midfield early in back straight, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on same pace in the run to the line.
Slightly slow out, improved steadily to take up running on the rail 1200 metres out, led the field until headed on straightening, weakened.
Taken back from a poor gate, trailed the field to the 150 metres, ran on under pressure past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Broke well from a poor gate, wide approaching first bend before settling just off the pace in 2nd, lost postion over 700 metres out and came under pressure at the 600 metres, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, lost position rounding home bend, ran home one-paced. (Mucus)
Pressed forward early settling just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, became 4th in similar rails position passing the 900 metres, weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Began moderately, soon recovered to midfield on the rail, gradually drifted back to 10th over 4L back in back straight, saved ground on the inside turning in, folded up quickly after straightening.
Never far off from leaders, on straightening quickened up well under top weight to lead 150M, soon clear and won impressively.
Taken back to near the rear, 6Ls to make up top of straight, closed off best to take 2nd near line but no chance with easy winner.
Hampered at the start, shifted across behind runners, 9th at 400M, stayed on well for 3rd without troubling the runaway winner.
In touch behind leaders, produced with every chance in the straight, held ground final 150M.
Pressed forward and vied for lead on inside, led them from top of straight, headed 150M, weakened late and lost several places close home.
Driven forward and vied for lead on outside, fought on early straight but run ended 150M, faded towards the line.
Began awkwardly from draw 1, towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly in straight but no threat to leaders.

Settled behind midfield along the fence, found disappointingly little when asked passing 300M, never dangerous. (Jockey : travelled satisfactorily in middle stages but finished off the race only one-paced.)
Jumped on terms, held up midfield 3-4Ls back, kept on same pace final 300M, not reached leaders.
Positively ridden out the gate, tracked leaders on settling but wide no cover throughout, outpaced 300M, soon no threat.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover in midfield, wide into straight, didn't respond to riding, soon out of contention.
Checked on jumping, always in rear, 7-8Ls to make up 400M, made no progress.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight to score.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out after passing 400M, closed off well to take a place.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, useful debut.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, just behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 850M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, closer on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M.
