Began smartly, raced prominently near to the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, took the lead 200M, kept on well to the line, scored by a neck.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 700M, hard ridden 400M, headed 200M, kept battling to the line but always held.
Began fairly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader near to the stands rail, kept on well to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 14, raced prominently on the stands rail, hard ridden 350M, showed limited response, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, made some headway final 400M.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, slightly further back in the middle stages, kept on evenly final 400M. (Dropped whip near 50M.)
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 lengths or so back behind the leader, nearer to the middle of the track, showed limited response to riding after passing 400M, bumped near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 400M, showed limited response, bumped 250M, weakened thereafter.
Began very awkwardly, raced 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on the stand side, taken to the middle track after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the middle track, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Jumped well, raced behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, made no progress final 400M.
Taken back to race at rear in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 500M, showed no response, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Away well, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked 500M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, 2 away from the stands rail, showed no response to hard riding final 400M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M to score.
Settled in midfield, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, harmed by the fast sectionals, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
At rear, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
Pushed early, behind midfield on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, checked 300M, ran on ok.
Very slow away, suited by the fasts tempo, never improved.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, never a factor.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Urged to race outside the lead, gained ground passing 200M when asked for effort, worked home solidly.
Raced at back on rail, asked for effort near 400M, responded solidly in the straight.
Hard ridden to race in handy position, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, fought nicely in the straight.
Sent forward to take lead, placed pressure on straightening, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, finished one-paced.
Ridden along to race in box seat, fought hard in the straight but worked home one-paced.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, tried to improve near 500M, weakened near 100M.
Began awkwardly and then failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, raced towards rear, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, eased down over final 200M.
Raced midfield, niggled near 500M, faded out passing 300M.
Strode forward to lead. Continued to hold narrow lead entering the final section before breaking a length clear inside the last furlong & holding that margin to line.
Steadied & shifted across just worse than midfield on rail. Shifted into clear running on straightening before making up steady headway in last section to close to second in final few strides.

Touch slow to begin before improving to midfield away from rail. Moved three wide when improving nearing the 750m before moving 4 wide nearing the 600m. Moved up a length form the lead at the 400m & held that margin to line.
Obtained good position in midfield when shifting to the rail after 300m. Stayed close to the inside on straightening before holding margin in last section. Not beaten too far.
Mustered speed after start to race on leaders back. Moved away from rail nearing the corner before straightening only 1L from lead. Peaked in effort at the 250m & yielded a length or two late.

Steadied after start and raced third from last on rail shortly after start. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before being held up 350m until the final furlong before holding margin thereafter. Slightly unlucky.
Had no early speed & shifted across to last on rail. Continued rearward, cornering third from last. Shifted out at the 350m before passing a few in closing stages without being a genuine threat.
Raced just worse than midfield away from rail in early stages. Moved three wide passing the 700m before straightening 4 lengths from lead. Peaked inside the 300m & gave a few lengths late.
Pushed forward before racing outside leader. Continued in second, only a neck from lead entering final section before weakening out in last 300m to be well beaten.

Shifted across behind runners after start & settled 4th from last away from rail. Moved wider passing the 500m before cornering the widest, 5L from lead. Could offer no more inside the final 250m & was well held.

Had no early speed, shifted across worse than midfield on rail after start. Continued in the second half, straightening 5L from lead entering final section. All out passing the 300m & weakened further late. (Lame next day).

Steadied after start, shifted back to second last away from rail, before racing clear a last shortly after. Under heavy riding when cornering two lengths behind second last horse & never ran on in straight. Well beaten.

Hard ridden early before left three wide without cover, 1L from lead after first section. Continued to race wide throughout before coming under heavy pressure approaching bend. Yielded significant ground in last section.
Strode forward early before steadying to race 1,1 after first furlong. Came under heavy pressure passing the 600m & began yielding ground thereafter. Beaten a long way.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 850M, hard ridden turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, commenced move after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn but still the last, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.

Began well from gate 11, raced prominently but wide, took the lead near 1100M, found rail 900M, led by half length turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M, ran on evenly to the line.

Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out after passing 550M, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.

Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1000M, positioned 2 wide in 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail, better than midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, found rail 1000M, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 13, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Rolled into one-out one-back position, worked home nicely, held on to score by a neck.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sprinted home well to take 2nd.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, made nice ground and held on for 3rd.
Bumped start, raced in behind midfield along the rail, away from heels at 300M, closed off strongly.
Urged after start, badly hampered for some strides at 1400M, sat in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on.
Taken back, at rear along the rail, slightly awkward passing 400M, made ground and ran on fairly.
Settled to race in midfield, shifted to 3 wide at 700M, did not improve.
Hard ridden forward, shared lead on the rail, gave ground gradually from 300M out.
Taken back, remained at tail along the rail, did not threaten.
Rolled forward, sat 5th but trapped wide, gave ground in the straight.
Badly checked at 1300M, raced in midfield along the rail thereafter, 2 wide at turn, not competitive.
Ridden after the start, hampered at 1300M, settled in front of midfield on rail, showed nothing.
Eased and raced at the rear, 2 wide, never a factor.
Jumped fairly only, asked to sit outside the lead, weakened approaching 300M. (See Incident Report)
Settled wide in midfield after from a wide gate, gained closer to 4th on the outside rounding home bend, gained upper hand under pressure inside the 100 metres.
Settled in rear without cover from the widest gate, remained wide in similar position rounding home bend, responded well inside the final 300 metres but just failed to get up on line.
Driven to lead from a wide gate, obtained rails run coming out of back straight, led until headed under pressure about 100 metres out.
Quickly recovered from an awkward start to hold 2nd on the rail, drifted one back to 3rd coming onto home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening in straight.
Raced wide prominently from a wide gate, came to join the leader rounding home bend, faded under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Sluggish at start and given reminders, remained in last few into home straight, ran past well-beaten horses inside the final 250 metres.
Soon outpaced, trailed the field most of the way, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, gradually dropped towards the rear despite niggling along, well back into the straight, kept on.
Vied for lead early before settling just off the pace in 4th, drifted back to 3L 6th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, made no impression in home straight.
Jumped well, settling not far off the lead in 4th before hampered and lost position coming onto home bend, saved ground on the inside turning in, soon weakened after straightening.
Soon driven to rear of midfield after a moderate start, dropped towards the rear rounding home bend, made no impression thereafter.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 3/4L behind the leader turning in, hit the front early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 9, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made some headway in straight to take a place.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Out in line, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced prominently but wide in the early stages, took the lead near 1100M, found rail 700M, led by 3/4L turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly in the early stages, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and stumbled, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, wider from 600M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 8 lengths or so back, last turning in, taken very wide early in straight, passed a few tired runners.
Quickly into stride, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 to 7 back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back from 950M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 550M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Began smartly from gate 11, raced wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back no turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 900M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, showed very good response early after turning in, took the lead near 150M, kept on well to the line, scored by a length.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear final 150M to take a place.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, not enough room early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden from 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, a bit closer on turn, wider from 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped near 400M, finished off one pace.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear run from 400M until hampered over 200M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, closer on turn, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight. (Lame right front leg.) (Mucus in trachea.)

Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 500M, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front near 150M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 2 lengths.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight to take a place. (Sustained minor wounds to the left front fetlock and right front cannon.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, 3 to 4 wide turning in, peak and made contact early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began smartly from the widest draw, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, crowded early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, travelled keenly in the early stages, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield in the early stages, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, showed nothing in straight.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3w with no cover in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1300M, raced 2w in 2nd in the middle stages, 1/2L back, peaked turning in, emptied early in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 200M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, checked 600M, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
Checked start, at rear, 2-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 150M.
Pushed early to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M whilst hanging in.
Eased to sit in midfield, raced keenly along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed well.
At back, not suited by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Checked start, at rear, on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Raced outside the lead with nice early speed, asked for effort passing 500M, worked home strongly to score, trainer questioned improved performance.
Settled midfield, placed pressure passing 400M, wide on straightening, made some nice late ground.
Began only fairly and then was crowded, raced midfield on rail, asked for effort near 400M, responded solidly in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, passing 1000M proved difficult to settle and was checked, gained some ground in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Raced midfield, widest on straightening, worked home one-paced.
Settled in box seat, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground near 50M.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, one-paced when placed pressure in the straight.
Slow out then was crowded and lost ground, settled at rear, crowded and lost ground when checked passing 150M.
Began awkwardly, settled in one-back-one-off position, gave ground near 200M.
Took lead with nice early speed, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, faded out near 200M.
Crowded at start, raced at tail, came under pressure near 700M, finished tailed out.

Pushed after the start before being steady after first bend to race worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Cornered the second widest before making gradual ground to strike lead inside final 100m, strong late.

Bumped at start, shifted behind runners to race third last, three wide with cover. Moved very wide approaching the 400m, cornered the widest before sprinting sharply to share lead at the 100m. Headed & passed in final 100m.

Began well before racing in midfield away from rail, only 2L from lead at the 800m. Improved three wide passing the 600m, sprinted up on straightening to share lead passing the 250m before sticking on gamely late.

Hard ridden to race prominent, three wide outside early leaders before racing outside leader, 2 wide by the 650m. Assumed lead shortly after straightening, joined at the 250m before battling on gamely to finish just behind.
Steadied at start & raced at tail of field on the rail. Continued last on cornering before making strong late headway in closing stages to be close behind. Finished quickly.
Nice run behind leading trio before shifting to 1,1 position approaching half-way. Steadied & shifted outward inside the last 100m before finishing off well in closing stages.
Crowded on jumping before settling worse than midfield between runners. Travelled strongly passing the 400m before closing off well in final furlong under little riding. Close behind.

Strode forward, improved after first bend, challenged for lead when racing keenly before crossing to rail when leading by the 650m. Peaked on effort & headed shortly after straightening before yielding a few lengths late.
Not bustled & raced just worse than midfield on rail. Shuffled back to third last on cornering before shifting out at the 250m & finishing off ok in last furlong. Not beaten far.
Had no early speed & shifted across to second last between runners. Hard ridden approaching the 400m before finishing off evenly without threatening.

Began well before steadying across to midfield on the rail after 350m. Held up on turn before shifting out & again being held up inside the last furlong. Never really got a chance to challenge in straight.
Began fast, assumed early lead before being joined, headed & crossed mid-race. Peaked on cornering & weakened out badly in straight. Well beaten.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide, no cover throughout, 2 wide from 550M, 3/4L back turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them and made contact, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, commenced move after passing 450M, raced tight early in straight, finished off well to take a place.
Began awkwardly, bumped early, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, angled out 450M, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, only showed limited response in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide from 650M, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made little progress. (Bled.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, improved from 400M, raced tight early in straight, not enough room near 250M, eased thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled to race in box-seat, sprinted away from 100M and scored with something in hand.
Eased back, at rear 2 wide, closed off strongly from 200M onwards. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward, took rail and led, headed at 100M and missed out on 2nd prior going to the line.
In midfield after jumping awkwardly, 2 wide, closed off fairly.
Travelled in midfield, wide and without cover, ran on one paced to the line.
Taken back, then shifted to the rail, saved ground and showed good dash at 150M.
Bumped start, in midfield wide but with cover, pretty much one paced.
Sent forward, settled outside the lead, stayed on till 150M only.
Prominent, wide and without cover however, gradually gave ground in the straight.
In one-out one-back position, lost ground from approaching 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, in midfield along the rail, weakened passing 200M.
Lost ground at start, remained at tail, never a factor.
Virtually made all, briefly joined rounding home bend, drew clear after straightening.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled just off the pace in 2nd, improved to dispute the lead briefly on home bend, unable to match speed of winner closing stages.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, similar entering straight, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear, commenced move when wide rounding home bend, ran on well down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled mainly in midfield, stayed near the rail for a run upon straightening, fought on steadily.

Settled mainly in 4th just over 3L off the pace on the rail, became closer when pace slackened around home bend, saved ground on the inside to reach 1L 3rd entering straight, found on extra after straightening.
Pressed forward for a prominent 3-wide position without cover, mainly in 3rd some 3L back travelling down back straight, came under pressure around home bend, one-paced in the run to the line.
Very slowly away, soon recovered to midfield on the rail, kept on same pace without quickening in home straight.
Wide in midfield early stages, drifted towards the rear in back straight, made short-lived effort circling the field on home bend, found no extra after straightening.
Broke well settling in forward of midfield in 5th, commenced move 500 metres out and swung wide into straight, ran home one-paced and crowded late.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled well behind, made swift progress from the 750 metres to reach 3rd 3-wide coming onto home bend, crowded 150 metres out and weakened.
Quickly into stride on jumping from draw 1, led uncontested, travelled well into straight, drew clear passing 300M for an effortless wide margin victory.
Settled down in 4th, 3Ls behind leader /eventual winner home turn, kept on steadily to go 2nd near 100M, no chance with runaway winner.
In mid-division 5Ls off the pace, 6th on settling, ran on moderately final 300M, went 3rd near line but well behind winner.
Chased leader, outpaced by winner on straightening, lost 2nd 100M, edged out to 4th just before line.
Settled down behind midfield 6Ls behind leader, stayed on without threat final 300M, held ground late stages.
Held up in 5th about 4Ls off the pace, kept on one pace from 300M, no threat to leaders.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, held up towards the rear, driven nearing 400M, responded only fairly never dangerous.
Slowly away, ended up racing in the rear and much further back than had been intended, failed to make ground final 300M.
Began only fairly, recovered to track leaders in 3rd, battled on same pace early straight, no extra and faded.
Dropped back to race near the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M but failed to make ground on straightening.
Taken back on jumping, settled at the rear, swung widest home, didn't run on.
Out in line, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, commenced move after passing 500M, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 5 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, headed 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, travelled keenly in the middle stages, moved closer after passing 800M, 3 wide turning, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, ran on one pace.

Average to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly early, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, inconvenienced near 200M, one pace thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider on turn, made no progress in straight.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 850M, allowed rival to cross 750M, sat right behind the leader on turn, commenced move 400M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight.

Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to hold off the challengers, won by 3/4L.
Moderately away, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide at rear, checked off heels near 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to near 650M, 4 wide turning in, made some progress in straight to take 3rd.

Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, commenced move after passing 500M, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost left front plate near 1400M.)
Taken back from gate 7, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, got cover from 850M, a length behind the leader no turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 850M, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide into straight, emptied early in straight.

Away with them, unable to slot in, raced 3w better than midfield early, found a 2w spot in midfield after passing 1100M, peaked on turn, weakened from 500M, eased early in straight. (Sustained a cut above the right hind fetlock.)
Settled in front, trapped 3 wide, drifted away 250M to score with ease.
In front of midfield, lack room 400M, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, trapped 3-4 wide at rear, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, trapped 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 350M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, shared the lead at slow tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, took rail, blocked most straight, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 2 wide, checked 900M, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased at start, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly when clear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied 300M.
Slow away, pushed early, at back on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Pushed to share the lead at slow sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Settled towards rear, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Raced behind midfield, improved passing 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Jumped sharply, sent forward, raced in handy position, stayed on to the line.
Settled behind midfield, wide with cover rounding the Home Turn, gained ground passing 100M.
Niggled along to race midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 550M, responded well in the straight.
Settled midfield, fought hard and made some ground in the straight.
Ridden along then settled behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, travelled with and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled comfortably, came under pressure in the early part of straight, weakened passing 150M.
Travelled wide and without cover in handy position, gave ground passing 200M.
Urged along to obtain forward position, raced behind the lead on rail, gave ground passing 300M.
Taken back at start, tried to improve but no response in the straight.
Raced towards rear on rail, faded out in the straight.
Raced in midfield, away from rail throughout. Moved three wide passing the 650m, travelled strongly approaching the corner. Sprinted up to assume lead at 125m & continued strongly to line.

Began awkwardly, bumped & lost ground before racing in midfield, 6L from lead approaching the 800m. Moved wider nearing bend, straightened widest runner, closed off strongly in last 300m to be narrowly beaten.

Obtained good position away from rail behind leaders. Moved three wide when improving approaching the 650m. Moved up to share lead at the 400m, headed & passed at the 125m before battling on gamely in closing stages.

Ridden forward after start, continued to improve, racing to second, 1L from lead by the 1000m. Moved up to share lead at the 400m, continued close before peaking at 300m. Battled hard in closing stages to be close behind.

Shifted & bumped heavily before clipping heels & losing ground at start. Race at the rear, over 10L from lead at the 800m. Continued a clear last on cornering before closing off strongly in last section from poor position.

Ridden hard before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 1100m. Shifted wider on straightening before entering final section only 1.5L from lead. Could make no further headway & yielded a length in closing stages.

Began well before racing two pairs behind lead on rail. Moved away from the rail passing the 650m before straightening 3L from the lead. Shifted out further after the 400m before finishing off evenly in the last furlong.

Steadied after the start & shifted across to race near the rear away from the rail. Raced very wide approaching the corner before making up a length in the final section from a rearward position. Was never a genuine threat.
Showed speed after start, assumed early lead, continued on to cross to rail in lead passing the 1100m. Headed in the lead passing the 400m & weakening out in final 250m.

Not the fastest to begin, raced in midfield on rail 6 lengths from lead approaching the 800m. Stayed close to the inside, 4L from lead entering the final section before yielding a further length in closing stages. No threat.

Steadied at start & shifted behind runners, racing second from last throughout early & middle stages. Continued rearward on straightening, over 4L form lead entering final section. Made no further headway thereafter.

Steadied after start & shifted behind runners, sharing second last position, 6L from lead. Moved wider on straightening, moved closer entering last section before peaking at the 250m & offering no more thereafter.

Shifted across from outside gate, improved to midfield after 300m. Continued to improve closer to lead while racing wide without cover throughout. Peaked on cornering & weakened out in final 350m. Well beaten last.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 200M, finished off very strongly to score by a head, impressive debut.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, hard ridden from 350M, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced 3 to 4 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Out in line, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 6 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, showed limited response early in straight, bumped near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, bumped 250M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Took keen hold, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never competitive. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Eased and slotted in behind midfield, wide but with cover, closed off strongly, scored by a short-head.
In midfield, 2 wide, continued to close off nicely, missed by a short-head in a tight battle to the line. (Whip dropped at 300M)
Rolled forward, took rail and led, sprinted home but caught prior going to the line.
Began only fairly, in midfield along the rail, ran on fairly inside final 200M once cleared.
Eased to find cover, settled one-out one-back, ran on till about 100M out. (Mildly lame right front)
Niggled along, settled outside the lead, stayed on till passing 150M, out of steam thereafter.
Awkward start, settled in front of midfield, wide and without cover, pretty one paced.
Raced in the box-seat, showed no kick to keep up in the straight.
Eased then shifted to rail, at tail throughout, made slight ground.
Travelled in about midfield, wide but with cover, did not run on. (See Incident Report)
Crowded after start, settled in behind midfield 2 wide, did not challenge. (See Incident Report)
Checked after start, recovered in behind midfield along the rail, wasn't in it.
Taken back, at rear, wide but with cover, didn't improve.
Bumped start, at rear 2 wide, never a factor.

Began well, amongst the leaders before settling one back 2-wide approaching home bend, came to challenge entering home straight drawing level inside the final 200 metres, prevailed in the bobbing of heads.
Ridden along from a wide gate, with leaders 3-wide before taking over coming onto home bend, came under pressure to hold narrow advantage early in straight only to be pipped at post.
Began well amongst the leaders early, shifted just over 2L back in 5th coming onto home bend, became 3rd after straightening, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, ran on under pressure inside the final 250 metres but without threatening.
Settled in rear from a wide gate and waited with, switched out and obtained a clear run over 200 metres out, finished off the race well.
Jumped fairly settling better than midfield in 6th, fought on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start, settled 3-wide behind midfield, remained in similar position but wider rounding home bend, produced some late impression inside the final 300 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, quickly recovered to rear of midfield in 9th on the rail, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Jumped well from the one draw, ceded front-runner position on the rail coming onto home bend, weakened under pressure after straightening.
Began fairly, drifted backward steadily and in last few rounding home bend, made some late impression close to home.
Settled in last few from the widest gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran on past well-beaten runners near the centre of the straight.
Travelled mainly 3-wide in midfield, gained closer when wider rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening and ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to the tail-end, made no impression in home straight.
Pressed forward from a wide gate reaching over 2L back in 4th 3-wide around the first bend, unable to sustain effort and faded gradually after straightening.
Held up in midfield, driven out 400M, good headway to lead near 100M, firmly in control final stages.
Reserved behind mid-division, driven along 400M, took a while to muster, did best work final 200M to take 2nd last stride, not reached winner.
Vied for lead in a fast run race, took narrow lead passing 300M, not pace of winner final 150M, lost 2nd just before line.
Ahead of midfield never far off the pace, closed off steadily over final 300M but always held.

Crossed to lead along the stands' rail, soon joined by rivals, waited with until 250M, kept battling until 150M, one paced late stages. (Jockey : pressed by rivals early stages, didn't close off as strongly as expected.)
Positively ridden from draw 1, tracked leading trio in fast run race, driven out 350M but not pace to challenge leaders, faded final stages.
In mid-division about 3Ls behind leaders, stayed on moderately when asked, never threatened.
Sat midfield racing along the stand's rail, one paced final 400M, no impression on leaders.

Raced keenly, moved up to join leaders in a race run at fast tempo, remained in contention until weakened passing 200M. (Jockey : travelled too keenly in early stages and inclined to lay in under pressure.)
Towards the rear, gave limited response over final 300M, not reached contention.
Lacked early pace, settled near last, not quickened when driven along 400M, never in the picture.
Settled in midfield on the outside of group, couldn't keep up passing halfway, soon beaten.
Began awkwardly, outpaced in last, didn't finish off.
In midfield, struggled from halfway, dropped out rapidly passing 300M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter, scored by 1/2L.

Away with them, raced 2 wide, just behind midfield, there to turn, commenced move after passing 550M, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner 75M, finished 2nd.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 550M, raced tight early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take a place, no threat to the first two.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, moved closer after passing 600M, very wide into straight, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Stumbled at start, raced 3 wide at rear, 10 lengths back, 2 wide from 1100M, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back to race 8 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail, just behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 550M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, one paced thereafter.
Out in line, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, peaked and made contact early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 1300M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.

Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross after entering the back straight, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Made contact at start, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back to race 5 lengths behind the leader, 2 wide, a bit closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail, just behind midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away well, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, 2 wide from 500M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away well from gate 10, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, carried wider from 500M, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.

Jumped with them, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 6Ls back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 350M, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 150M, made good progress to make frame.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 700M, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, commenced move after passing 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages but still the last, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, crowded near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, carried wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 450M, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Trapped 3-4 wide throughout in midfield, made early move 600M, led 300M, overhauled 50M, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to rear, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily around the field 350M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
At back, on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened quickly 300M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, dropped off quickly 300M.
Settled in box seat, made the turn 600M awkwardly and lost ground, responded strongly in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 550M, wide on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, gained nice ground in the straight, worked home solidly.
Settled in handy position, placed pressure near 500M, fought well in the straight.
Sent forward to race outside the lead, placed pressure near 600M, finished nicely.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 700M, worked home well.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield, improved to lead near 600M, lay in leaving 500M, finished one-paced.
Settled midfield, at 1100M was hampered for some distance and checked at 850M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, asked for effort near 500M, limited response.
Taken back at start, raced at tail on rail, placed pressure passing 500M, no response in the straight.
Ridden forward to take lead, weakened passing 200M.
Settled towards rear, placed pressure but no response, failed to run on.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside early, sent forward after entering the back straight, a length or so back on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to hold off the challenger.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 700M, 3 wide turning, finished off well to take 2nd.
Out in line, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, found a 2 wide spot after entering the back straight, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider from 800M, hard ridden from 550M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, carried wider from 500M, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, still 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1100M, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.

Began only fairly, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, difficult to settle for some distance until entering the back straight, peaked 500M, weakened thereafter, eased early in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, carried wider from 500M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, found rail 400M, kept to inside after turning in, finished off very well to take 2nd.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Away with them, positioned 2 to 3 wide, 2 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, made no progress in straight.
Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, peaked on turn, ran on one pace.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Rolled forward, sat in box-seat, sprinted home gamely to score by 3/4L.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, swung wide on straightening, continued on strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in advance of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
Settled to race in midfield, 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily to the line.
Prominent, however trapped wide and without cover, stayed on until emptied passing 100M.
Slotted in behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, improved steadily.
Sent forward, took rail and led, weakened and headed approaching 100M.
At rear, 2 wide, improved in straight and ran on fairly
In behind midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Taken back, at rear 3 wide but with cover, saved ground.
At rear throughout, saved ground and closed off to the line. (See Incident Report)
Settled outside lead, hampered at 250M, eased down afterwards. (See Incident Report)
Pressed forward from a wide gate before settling in 3rd 2-wide, gained 2nd outside the leader down back straight and hit the front turning in, soon ridden clear.
Moderate start, settled worse than midfield on the rail, carried backward to last few in back straight, saved ground on inside turning for home, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled at the back from a wide gate, remained in last few into home straight, quickened well after straightening, did best work late.
Settled mainly 2L off the pace in 4th or 5th, commenced move rounding home bend, gained joint 3rd some 1L back entering home straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.

Taken back from the widest gate but unable to obtain cover and remained 3-wide in midfield, raced keenly round first bend before allowed to improve down back straight, joined the leaders going up the Rock but ran home one-paced.

Broke well, shifted one back to 3rd on the rail coming onto first bend, similar when 4th in back straight, remained one back turning for home, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.

Began well from the one draw, settled in rear of midfield in 7th, drifted slightly backward to 8th in midway down back straight, renewed effort rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in forward of midfield on the rail, mainly within 3L of pace in 6th throughout back straight, briefly baulked over 250 metres out, never threatening.
Settled well back, travelled wide in last few in back straight, came under pressure rounding home bend and widest turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Always in last few, wide into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, improved steadily to take up running for rails run passing the 1200 metres, came under pressure to hold position rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled wide without cover in midfield, went wider into home straight, found nothing under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped on terms from draw 1, never far off from leaders, travelled well into straight, quickened up smartly to lead inside 200M, kept on well to score debut win under mainly hands and heels riding.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners soon after the jump, settled down behind midfield, moved up to challenge passing 300M, chased winner hard final stages but always held.
Close up to early leaders before taking up a midfield position, ran on moderately on straightening, got up 3rd close home.
Caught wide no cover entering first bend, moved up to join leader, fought on early straight, not finishing pace of eventual winner inside 250M, dropped to 4th close home.
Not hurried early stages, races towards the rear in 10th spot, niggled along 500M, gave limited response in straight, not reached leaders.
Dropped back to last 6Ls off the pace, switched wide 400M to challenge, ran on only fairly, never able to challenge leaders.
From wide draw settled down 3-wide towards the rear, 4-5Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, widest into straight, stayed on without threat.
Jumped well, restrained to race near last 5-6Ls back, failed to quicken passing 400M, never dangerous.
Tracked leaders, found disappointingly little turning home, dropped away passing 200M. (Trainer reported hearing harsh breathing noise upon returning to the scale.)
Soon led, pressed by rival from 1000M, lacked extra turning home, weakened out of contention 250M.
Settled down in mid-division 3-wide, couldn't go on turning for home, soon behind. (Lame next day.)
In midfield early stages, caught wide no cover from 1200M, strode closer to pace but remained wide to straight, soon beaten on straightening.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the uncontested lead throughout, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well in straight to score.
Out in line, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Made contact on jumping, raced behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Away with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 8 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made some headway thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight, eased final 50M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, bumped 450M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off one pace.
Made contact at start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Began well, raced 3w with no cover, just ahead of midfield, found cover 900M, 1 out 1 back on turn, made contact early in straight, hard ridden 300M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to score.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length behind the leader, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked on run 200M, headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, travelled keenly near 950M, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 150M, kept on well to take a place. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, kept on well until 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, travelled keenly near 1000M, saved ground on turn, made contact and blocked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 1100M, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Stumbled at start, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 150M.
Eased at start, took rail at back, pace good, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, made ground around the field in 4-5 wide, dashed well 300M.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, made steady ground around the field in 4-5 wide, dashed well 300M.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 450M, run ended 150M.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, just held ground.
Hard ridden early, trapped 4-5 wide in midfield, ran on ok.
Shared the lead at good pace, out of fuel 300M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 500M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, emptied 350M.
Never muster speed, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 400M.
Trapped 4 wide throughout, faded 400M.
Settled midfield, near 350M shifted out abruptly away from heels, continued to make ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Crowded on jumping, raced in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, finished solidly, missed by 1/2L.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground, finished nicely.
Raced behind the lead, fought hard in the straight, finished well.
Taken back at start, raced greenly, wide on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Raced wide in midfield position, asked for effort on straightening, battled well in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, widest on straightening, gained some late ground.
Raced at back, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Jumped well, took box seat with nice early speed, placed pressure in the straight, gave ground near 100M.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 500M, weakened passing 150M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on rail, difficult to ride when placed pressure, limited response.
Began only fairly then ridden along to take forward position, took lead near 800M, gave ground near 300M.
Settled behind midfield, faded out passing 300M.

Prominent early, good position 3 wide with cover in midfield. Moved wider when travelling strongly nearing corner, sprinted fast to assume lead at 350m before dashing clear. Had enough in hand to hold fast finishing second.

Crowded on jumping, consequently raced worse than midfield. Moved wider & improved approaching corner. Checked & lost ground on straightening, shifted out, finished very strongly in closing stages to just miss. Unlucky.

Began awkwardly, shifted back to last. Continued a clear last entering final section when 8 lengths form lead. Made up substantial late ground in last 400m, running into third position in closing stages. Not beaten far.
Raced in midfield, away from rail, just over 4L from lead approaching half-way. Shifted out on straightening when 3 lengths from lead. Made up a length in last section but was not a winning threat.
Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Continued between runners, 4L from lead at half-way. Moved wide on cornering when improving before finishing off moderately in last 300m.
Ridden forward after start, improved to race 3 wide without cover in third position by the 1000m mark. Continued wide on cornering, peaked shortly after straightening & weakened over final 300m.

Not fast to begin & consequently shifted back to second last away from rail. Continued rearward, 6 lengths from lead entering final section. Passed a few in the late stages but was still beaten a substantial margin.

Ridden forward after start, crossing to rail when leading passing the 1300m. Maintained 1.8L margin entering final section before peaking on effort, headed at the 350m before weakening significantly thereafter.
Had no early speed, ridden up to maintain position throughout. Stayed close to the inside rail on cornering when only 4L from the lead before weakening out to be beaten over 10L.

Steadied after start, shifted across behind runners, racing with only one pair behind in early & middle stages. Was second from last on cornering and made no headway in last section & was beaten a substantial margin.
Ridden forward, very wide at first bend before being left 4 wide without cover throughout. Cover additional ground, very wide on nearing corner, began yielding ground before straightening.

Began fast & strode to forward position, settled outside leader by the 1300m. Came under hard riding passing the 650m before yielding significant ground in the last section. Beaten a long way. (Blood in trachea-post race).
Began well, crossed & raced on leaders back from 1300m. Hard ridden passing the 550m mark before yielding significant ground in the final section. Beaten a big margin.
Obtained good position, one out one back, 2L from lead by the 1200m. Hard ridden approaching the 600m before beginning to yield ground shortly after. Tailed out a long last.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide from 900M, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths, easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M, finished 2nd.
Commenced well, raced in 3rd, 3 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, checked near 950M, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, made some progress in straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Away well, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 850M, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Asked and settled to race outside the lead, worked home gamely, held on to score by a short-head.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, closed off gamely, only to miss by a short-head.
Sent forward to take rail and led, stayed on but headed by first two inside final 50M.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, continued on well to the line.
Awkward start, settled in front of midfield on rail, raced greenly early in the straight, ran on okay.
Eased and raced at the rear, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly. (See Incident Report)
In behind midfield, along the rail, ran on one paced.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Inconvenienced at start, settled at rear, wide but with cover, did not close off. (See Incident Report)
In worse than midfield, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced in box-seat, stayed on until faded gradually from 200M out.
In one-out one-back position, did not run on.
Taken back, at tail throughout, never a factor.
Prominent, wide throughout however, run ended at 300M.
Tracked the leaders near stands rails, commenced move inside the 300 metres and took charge 150 metres out, won convincingly.
Disputed lead, hit the front under pressure 400 metres out, found winner too strong when swamped 150 metres out.
Niggled at most of the way, not far off the pace in 3rd or 4th, came to challenge inside the final 300 metres while handing in under pressure.
Settled in rear of the small field, commenced move inside the 400 metres, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Held slender lead to the 400 metres, gradually weakened after coming onto course proper.
Settled mainly in 6th without cover within 3L of pace near the centre of the track, yielded ground over 200 metres out. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in rear of the small field near the centre of track and without cover, yielded ground from over 300 metres out.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, quickened to the fore 350M, opened up 2Ls lead mid-straight, began to weaken late, held on just.
Jumped well, reigned back to race in midfield 3-wide, no cover from 900M, moved closer to pace nearing top of straight, battled hard to close the gap on winner final 200M, just held.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, chased hard on leaders passing 400M, nearest finish.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover early stages, held up towards the rear 8Ls back, driven out 400M, ran on steadily down outside, safely held by first 3.
Began awkwardly, settled towards rear of midfield 6Ls off leader, stayed on moderately over final 400M, no threat to leaders.
Drawn 1, held up in midfield along the fence, hard pressed from 500M, responded well early straight but couldn't sustain run final 150M.
Dropped back to race in rear pair on jumping from wide draw, 10Ls off the pace in middle stages, ran on steadily final 400M, not reach leaders.
Began only fairly and crowded for room at start, ended up racing in rear pair, 6Ls behind at 400M, made limited progress, lay in under pressure and proved difficult to ride.
Bustled along to go forward, tracked leader going into the turn, outpaced from 300M, weakened towards the finish.
Close up to leaders early stages before settling down ahead of midfield, briefly went 3rd in the straight, run ended 150M from home.
Settled behind midfield 2-wide, driven along 450M, couldn't go on in the straight, never dangerous.

Up with early pace, tracked leaders on settling, under pressure passing 500M, unable to finish off in the straight. (Jockey : travelled satisfactorily until 500M when off the bridle and commenced to give ground.)
Pressed forward, led from 900M, lacked further response passing 400M, soon headed and weakened away.
Restrained to race near the rear, couldn't go on in the straight, soon left behind.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 900M, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.

Clean jump, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield in the early stages, moved closer after entering the back straight, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.

Began smartly from gate 10, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 950M, travelled comfortably on turn, retook the lead 400M, showed limited response early in straight, headed near 250M, kept on evenly to take a place.

Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly near 1050M, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 4 wide at rear, a bit closer in the middle stages, carried wider on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, took the lead 600M, peaked and headed 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 900M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Fractious in gate and missed the start, recovered, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, no early speed, raced at rear throughout, never competitive. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead 950M, headed 600M, weakened turning in, finished tailed out.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, just ahead of midfield, wider on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out 550M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Began well, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, wider on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened from 500M, finished last.
